3.1.127|3.1.127 aanaayyo.anitye|aanaayyo.anitye|aanaayyo.anitye 3.1.127|आनाय्योऽनित्ये|आनाय्योऽनित्ये ३.१.१२७|३.१.१२७|३.१.१२७ आनाय्योऽनित्ये
The word आनाय्यः is irregularly formed when meaning 'impermanent'.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

