The word प्रणाय्य is irregularly formed when meaning 'disapproved'.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

3.1.129|3.1.129 paayyasaannaayyanikaayyadhaayyaa maanahavirnivaasasaamidheniiShu|paayyasaannaayyanikaayyadhaayyaa maanahavirnivaasasaamidheniiShu|paayyasaannaayyanikaayyadhaayyaa maanahavirnivaasasaamidheniiShu 3.1.129|पाय्यसान्नाय्यनिकाय्यधाय्या मानहविर्निवाससामिधेनीषु|पाय्यसान्नाय्यनिकाय्यधाय्या मानहविर्निवाससामिधेनीषु ३.१.१२९|३.१.१२९|३.१.१२९ पाय्यसान्नाय्यनिकाय्यधाय्या मानहविर्निवाससामिधेनीषु
The words पाय्य , सान्नाय्य , निकाय्य and धाय्या are irregularly formed meaning 'a measure', 'an oblation to fire', 'a dwelling' and 'a sacrificial prayer', respectively.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

3.1.130|3.1.130 kratau kuNDapaayyasaMchaayyau|kratau kuNDapaayyasaMchaayyau|kratau kuNDapaayyasaMchaayyau 3.1.130|क्रतौ कुण्डपाय्यसंचाय्यौ|क्रतौ कुण्डपाय्यसंचाय्यौ ३.१.१३०|३.१.१३०|३.१.१३० क्रतौ कुण्डपाय्यसंचाय्यौ
The words कुण्डपाय्यः and संचाय्यः are irregularly formed meaning 'a sacrifice'.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

3.1.131|3.1.131 agnau parichaayyopachaayyasamuuhyaaH|agnau parichaayyopachaayyasamuuhyaaH|agnau parichaayyopachaayyasamuuhyaaH 3.1.131|अग्नौ परिचाय्योपचाय्यसमूह्याः|अग्नौ परिचाय्योपचाय्यसमूह्याः ३.१.१३१|३.१.१३१|३.१.१३१ अग्नौ परिचाय्योपचाय्यसमूह्याः
