3.1.132|3.1.132 chityaagnichitye cha|chityaagnichitye cha|chityaagnichitye cha 3.1.132|चित्याग्निचित्ये च|चित्याग्निचित्ये च ३.१.१३२|३.१.१३२|३.१.१३२ चित्याग्निचित्ये च
The words चित्य and ग्निचित्य are also irregularly formed.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

3.1.133|3.1.133 NvultRchau|NvultRchau|NvultRchau 3.1.133|ण्वुल्तृचौ|ण्वुल्तृचौ ३.१.१३३|३.१.१३३|३.१.१३३ ण्वुल्तृचौ
The affixes ण्वुल् (अक्) and तृच् (तृ) are placed after all verbal roots, expressing the agent.<br><br>Terms: ण्वुल् and तृच्

3.1.134|3.1.134 nandigrahipachaadibhyo lyuNinyachaH|nandigrahipachaadibhyo lyuNinyachaH|nandigrahipachaadibhyo lyuNinyachaH 3.1.134|नन्दिग्रहिपचादिभ्यो ल्युणिन्यचः|नन्दिग्रहिपचादिभ्यो ल्युणिन्यचः ३.१.१३४|३.१.१३४|३.१.१३४ नन्दिग्रहिपचादिभ्यो ल्युणिन्यचः
After the verbs classed as नन्द 'to be happy', ग्रह 'to take' and पच् 'to cook' there are the affixes ल्यु (अन), णिनि (इन्) and अच (अ) respectively.<br><br>Terms: ल्यु , णिनि and अच

3.1.135|3.1.135 igupadhaJNaapriikiraH kaH|igupadhaJNaapriikiraH kaH|igupadhaJNaapriikiraH kaH 3.1.135|इगुपधज्ञाप्रीकिरः कः|इगुपधज्ञाप्रीकिरः कः ३.१.१३५|३.१.१३५|३.१.१३५ इगुपधज्ञाप्रीकिरः कः
After a vern ending in a consonant but preceded by इ , उ or ऋ -long or short, and after the verbs ज्ञा 'to know', श्री 'to please' and कॄ 'to scatter', comes the affix क (अ)।<br><br>Terms: क

3.1.136|3.1.136 aatashchopasarge|aatashchopasarge|aatashchopasarge 3.1.136|आतश्चोपसर्गे|आतश्चोपसर्गे ३.१.१३६|३.१.१३६|३.१.१३६ आतश्चोपसर्गे
Also after a verb ening in long आ when there is a preposition along with it, the affix क is placed.<br><br>Terms: क

3.1.137|3.1.137 paaghraadhmaadheTdRshaH shaH|paaghraadhmaadheTdRshaH shaH|paaghraadhmaadheTdRshaH shaH 3.1.137|पाघ्राध्माधेट्दृशः शः|पाघ्राध्माधेट्दृशः शः ३.१.१३७|३.१.१३७|३.१.१३७ पाघ्राध्माधेट्दृशः शः
The affix श (अ) is used after the roots पा 'to drink', घ्रा 'to smell', ध्मा 'to blow' and धेट् 'to suck' and दृश् 'to see' when there is a preposition along with these roots.<br><br>Terms: श

3.1.138|3.1.138 anupasargaallimpavindadhaaripaarivedyudejichetisaatisaahibhyashcha|anupasargaallimpavindadhaaripaarivedyudejichetisaatisaahibhyashcha|anupasargaallimpavindadhaaripaarivedyudejichetisaatisaahibhyashcha 3.1.138|अनुपसर्गाल्लिम्पविन्दधारिपारिवेद्युदेजिचेतिसातिसाहिभ्यश्च|अनुपसर्गाल्लिम्पविन्दधारिपारिवेद्युदेजिचेतिसातिसाहिभ्यश्च ३.१.१३८|३.१.१३८|३.१.१३८ अनुपसर्गाल्लिम्पविन्दधारिपारिवेद्युदेजिचेतिसातिसाहिभ्यश्च
The affix श is used after the verbs - धारि , पारि , वेदि , उदेजि , चेति , साति and साहि , when used without a preposition.<br><br>Terms: श

3.1.139|3.1.139 dadaatidadhaatyorvibhaaShaa|dadaatidadhaatyorvibhaaShaa|dadaatidadhaatyorvibhaaShaa 3.1.139|ददातिदधात्योर्विभाषा|ददातिदधात्योर्विभाषा ३.१.१३९|३.१.१३९|३.१.१३९ ददातिदधात्योर्विभाषा
The affix श is optionally used after the root दा 'to give' and धा 'to hold', when used without a preposition.<br><br>Terms: श

3.1.140|3.1.140 jvalitikasantebhyo NaH|jvalitikasantebhyo NaH|jvalitikasantebhyo NaH 3.1.140|ज्वलितिकसन्तेभ्यो णः|ज्वलितिकसन्तेभ्यो णः ३.१.१४०|३.१.१४०|३.१.१४० ज्वलितिकसन्तेभ्यो णः
After the verbs beginning with ज्वल 'to shine' and ending with कस 'to go', when used without apreposition, the affix ण is optionally used.<br><br>Terms: ण

3.1.141|3.1.141 shyaa.a.advyadhaasrusaMsrvatiiNavasaa.avahRlihashliShashvasashcha|shyaa.a.advyadhaasrusaMsrvatiiNavasaa.avahRlihashliShashvasashcha|shyaa.a.advyadhaasrusaMsrvatiiNavasaa.avahRlihashliShashvasashcha 3.1.141|श्याऽऽद्व्यधास्रुसंस्र्वतीणवसाऽवहृलिहश्लिषश्वसश्च|श्याऽऽद्व्यधास्रुसंस्र्वतीणवसाऽवहृलिहश्लिषश्वसश्च ३.१.१४१|३.१.१४१|३.१.१४१ श्याऽऽद्व्यधास्रुसंस्र्वतीणवसाऽवहृलिहश्लिषश्वसश्च
The affix ण is also used after the verbs - श्यै 'to go', verbs ending in a long भा , व्यद् 'to pierce', आस्रु 'to pain', संत्रु 'to flow', अतीण् 'to pass on', अवसा 'to complete', अवह 'to take away', लिह 'to lick', श्लिष 'to embrace' and श्वस 'to breathe'.<br><br>Terms: ण

3.1.142|3.1.142 dunyoranupasarge|dunyoranupasarge|dunyoranupasarge 3.1.142|दुन्योरनुपसर्गे|दुन्योरनुपसर्गे ३.१.१४२|३.१.१४२|३.१.१४२ दुन्योरनुपसर्गे
The affix ण is used after the verbs दु 'to burn' and नी 'to lead', when used without a preposition.<br><br>Terms: ण

3.1.143|3.1.143 vibhaaShaa graheH|vibhaaShaa graheH|vibhaaShaa graheH 3.1.143|विभाषा ग्रहेः|विभाषा ग्रहेः ३.१.१४३|३.१.१४३|३.१.१४३ विभाषा ग्रहेः
