3.1.147|3.1.147 NyuT cha|NyuT cha|NyuT cha 3.1.147|ण्युट् च|ण्युट् च ३.१.१४७|३.१.१४७|३.१.१४७ ण्युट् च
The affix ण्युट् is also used after the verb गै 'to sing' when the agent so expressed denotes an artist.<br><br>Terms: ण्युट्

3.1.148|3.1.148 hashcha vriihikaalayoH|hashcha vriihikaalayoH|hashcha vriihikaalayoH 3.1.148|हश्च व्रीहिकालयोः|हश्च व्रीहिकालयोः ३.१.१४८|३.१.१४८|३.१.१४८ हश्च व्रीहिकालयोः
After the verb हा , also the affix ण्युट् is used when the agent so expressed denotes 'rice' and 'time'.<br><br>Terms: हा

3.1.149|3.1.149 prusRlvaH samabhihaare vun|prusRlvaH samabhihaare vun|prusRlvaH samabhihaare vun 3.1.149|प्रुसृल्वः समभिहारे वुन्|प्रुसृल्वः समभिहारे वुन् ३.१.१४९|३.१.१४९|३.१.१४९ प्रुसृल्वः समभिहारे वुन्
After the verbs प्रु 'to go', सृ 'to move', स्रु 'to flow' and लू 'to cut', the affix वुन् is used, when repitition is meant.<br><br>Terms: वुन्

3.1.150|3.1.150 aashiShi cha|aashiShi cha|aashiShi cha 3.1.150|आशिषि च|आशिषि च ३.१.१५०|३.१.१५०|३.१.१५० आशिषि च
The affix वुन् is applied after all verbs when Benediction is intended.<br><br>Terms: वुन्

3.2.1|3.2.1 karmaNyaN|karmaNyaN|karmaNyaN 3.2.1|कर्मण्यण्|कर्मण्यण् ३.२.१|३.२.१|३.२.१ कर्मण्यण्
The affix अण् comes after a verbal root when the object (or whatever sort it may be), is in composition with it (an an उपपद).<br><br>Terms: अण्

3.2.2|3.2.2 hvaavaamashcha|hvaavaamashcha|hvaavaamashcha 3.2.2|ह्वावामश्च|ह्वावामश्च ३.२.२|३.२.२|३.२.२ ह्वावामश्च
The affix अण् comes after a root हूञ् 'to call' वेञ् 'to weave', माङ् 'to measure', when the object is in composition with it.<br><br>Terms: अण्

3.2.3|3.2.3 aato.anupasarge kaH|aato.anupasarge kaH|aato.anupasarge kaH 3.2.3|आतोऽनुपसर्गे कः|आतोऽनुपसर्गे कः ३.२.३|३.२.३|३.२.३ आतोऽनुपसर्गे कः
The affix क comes after a verbal root that ends in long आ when there is no उपसर्ग preceding it and when the object is in composition with it.<br><br>Terms: अण्

3.2.4|3.2.4 supi sthaH|supi sthaH|supi sthaH 3.2.4|सुपि स्थः|सुपि स्थः ३.२.४|३.२.४|३.२.४ सुपि स्थः
The affix क comes after the root स्था when in composition with a word ending in a case-affix, as an उपपद ।<br><br>Terms: क

3.2.5|3.2.5 tundashokayoH parimRjaapanudoH|tundashokayoH parimRjaapanudoH|tundashokayoH parimRjaapanudoH 3.2.5|तुन्दशोकयोः परिमृजापनुदोः|तुन्दशोकयोः परिमृजापनुदोः ३.२.५|३.२.५|३.२.५ तुन्दशोकयोः परिमृजापनुदोः
The affix क comes after the verbs परिमृज् 'to wash out' and अपनुद् 'to drive away' when in composition with the words तुन्द 'navel' and शोक 'grief', as objects respectively.<br><br>Terms: क

3.2.6|3.2.6 pre daaJNaH|pre daaJNaH|pre daaJNaH 3.2.6|प्रे दाज्ञः|प्रे दाज्ञः ३.२.६|३.२.६|३.२.६ प्रे दाज्ञः
The affix क comes after the root दा 'to give' and ज्ञ 'to know', when taking the preposition प्र in composition with a word in the Accusative -2nd case.<br><br>Terms: क

3.2.7|3.2.7 sami khyaH|sami khyaH|sami khyaH 3.2.7|समि ख्यः|समि ख्यः ३.२.७|३.२.७|३.२.७ समि ख्यः
The affix क comes after root ख्या 'to tell', when preceded by the preposition सम् and when the object is in compsition with it.<br><br>Terms: क

3.2.8|3.2.8 gaapoShTak|gaapoShTak|gaapoShTak 3.2.8|गापोष्टक्|गापोष्टक् ३.२.८|३.२.८|३.२.८ गापोष्टक्
The affix टक comes after the verbs गै 'to sing' and पा 'to drink' when used without a preposition and when the object is in composition with it.<br><br>Terms: क

3.2.9|3.2.9 harateranudyamane.ach|harateranudyamane.ach|harateranudyamane.ach 3.2.9|हरतेरनुद्यमनेऽच्|हरतेरनुद्यमनेऽच् ३.२.९|३.२.९|३.२.९ हरतेरनुद्यमनेऽच्
The affix अच् comes after the verb हृञ् when it does not mean 'to raise up', when the object is in composition with it.<br><br>Terms: अच्

3.2.10|3.2.10 vayasi cha|vayasi cha|vayasi cha 3.2.10|वयसि च|वयसि च ३.२.१०|३.२.१०|३.२.१० वयसि च
The affix अच् comes after the verb हृञ् when the object is in composition with it and when the meaning of the word to be formed is descriptive of age.<br><br>Terms: अच्

3.2.11|3.2.11 aaNGi taachChiilye|aaNGi taachChiilye|aaNGi taachChiilye 3.2.11|आङि ताच्छील्ये|आङि ताच्छील्ये ३.२.११|३.२.११|३.२.११ आङि ताच्छील्ये
The affix अच् comes after the verb हृञ् (when the object is in composition with it) the root taking the preposition आञ् and the sense of the word to be formed in inclination or accustomed occupation.<br><br>Terms: अच्

