3.2.30|3.2.30 naaDiimuShTyoshcha|naaDiimuShTyoshcha|naaDiimuShTyoshcha 3.2.30|नाडीमुष्ट्योश्च|नाडीमुष्ट्योश्च ३.२.३०|३.२.३०|३.२.३० नाडीमुष्ट्योश्च
And when the words नाडी 'a tube' and मुष्टि 'a fist' are objects in composition with the verbs ध्मा 'to blow' and धे 'to suck', ghe affix खश् is used.<br><br>Terms: खश्

