The affix खश् comes after the verb पच् 'to cook' when the object in composition with it denotes a measure.<br><br>Terms: खश्

3.2.34|3.2.34 mitanakhe cha|mitanakhe cha|mitanakhe cha 3.2.34|मितनखे च|मितनखे च ३.२.३४|३.२.३४|३.२.३४ मितनखे च
The affix खश् is used after the verb पच् 'to cook' when मित 'a measured partition' or नख 'a nail' is the word in composition with it as an object.<br><br>Terms: खश्

3.2.35|3.2.35 vidhvaruShoH tudaH|vidhvaruShoH tudaH|vidhvaruShoH tudaH 3.2.35|विध्वरुषोः तुदः|विध्वरुषोः तुदः ३.२.३५|३.२.३५|३.२.३५ विध्वरुषोः तुदः
The affix खश् comes after the verb तुद् 'to strike' when विधु 'the moon' or अरुस् 'a wound' is the word in composition with it as object.<br><br>Terms: खश्

3.2.36|3.2.36 asuuryalalaaTayordRshitapoH|asuuryalalaaTayordRshitapoH|asuuryalalaaTayordRshitapoH 3.2.36|असूर्यललाटयोर्दृशितपोः|असूर्यललाटयोर्दृशितपोः ३.२.३६|३.२.३६|३.२.३६ असूर्यललाटयोर्दृशितपोः
The affix खश् comes after the verb दृश् 'to see' and तप् 'to heat' when असूर्य and ललाट are the words in composition with it as object.<br><br>Terms: खश्

