The words उग्रम्पश्य , इरम्मद , पाणिन्धम are irregularly formed.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

3.2.38|3.2.38 priyavashe vadaH khach|priyavashe vadaH khach|priyavashe vadaH khach 3.2.38|प्रियवशे वदः खच्|प्रियवशे वदः खच् ३.२.३८|३.२.३८|३.२.३८ प्रियवशे वदः खच्
The affix खच् comes after the verb वद् 'to speak' when प्रिय or वश is the word in composition with it as an object.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.39|3.2.39 dviShatparayostaapeH|dviShatparayostaapeH|dviShatparayostaapeH 3.2.39|द्विषत्परयोस्तापेः|द्विषत्परयोस्तापेः ३.२.३९|३.२.३९|३.२.३९ द्विषत्परयोस्तापेः
The affix खच् comes after the verb ताप् 'to heat' when द्विषत् or पर is the word in composition with it as an object.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.40|3.2.40 vaachi yamo vrate|vaachi yamo vrate|vaachi yamo vrate 3.2.40|वाचि यमो व्रते|वाचि यमो व्रते ३.२.४०|३.२.४०|३.२.४० वाचि यमो व्रते
The affix खच् comes after the verb यस् 'to curb'when the word वाक् 'speech' is in composition with it as an object and the sense indicated is that of a vow.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.41|3.2.41 puuHsarvayordaarisahoH|puuHsarvayordaarisahoH|puuHsarvayordaarisahoH 3.2.41|पूःसर्वयोर्दारिसहोः|पूःसर्वयोर्दारिसहोः ३.२.४१|३.२.४१|३.२.४१ पूःसर्वयोर्दारिसहोः
The affix खच् comes after the verb दारि 'to split' and सह् 'to bear' when respectively in composition with the words पुर् 'a city' and सर्व 'all', as objects.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.42|3.2.42 sarvakuulaabhrakariiSheShu kaShaH|sarvakuulaabhrakariiSheShu kaShaH|sarvakuulaabhrakariiSheShu kaShaH 3.2.42|सर्वकूलाभ्रकरीषेषु कषः|सर्वकूलाभ्रकरीषेषु कषः ३.२.४२|३.२.४२|३.२.४२ सर्वकूलाभ्रकरीषेषु कषः
The affix खच् comes after the verb कष् 'to rub' when the words सर्व 'all', कूल 'bank', अभ्र 'cloud' and करीष 'a dry cow-dung' are in composition with it as objects.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.43|3.2.43 meghartibhayeShu kRNJaH|meghartibhayeShu kRNJaH|meghartibhayeShu kRNJaH 3.2.43|मेघर्तिभयेषु कृञः|मेघर्तिभयेषु कृञः ३.२.४३|३.२.४३|३.२.४३ मेघर्तिभयेषु कृञः
The affix खच् comes after the verb कृ 'to make' when the words मेघ 'cloud' अर्ति 'misfortune' and भय 'fear' are in composition as objects.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.44|3.2.44 xemapriyamadre.aN cha|xemapriyamadre.aN cha|xemapriyamadre.aN cha 3.2.44|क्षेमप्रियमद्रेऽण् च|क्षेमप्रियमद्रेऽण् च ३.२.४४|३.२.४४|३.२.४४ क्षेमप्रियमद्रेऽण् च
And the affix अण् as well as खच् come after the verb कृ 'to make' when the words क्षेम 'happiness', प्रिय 'pleasant' and भद्र 'joy' are in composition as objects.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.45|3.2.45 aashite bhuvaH karaNabhaavayoH|aashite bhuvaH karaNabhaavayoH|aashite bhuvaH karaNabhaavayoH 3.2.45|आशिते भुवः करणभावयोः|आशिते भुवः करणभावयोः ३.२.४५|३.२.४५|३.२.४५ आशिते भुवः करणभावयोः
The affix खच् comes after the verb भू 'to be' when in composition with the case-inflected word आशित 'satisfied by eating' and the sense is that of instrument or condition.<br><br>Terms: खच्

3.2.46|3.2.46 saMJNaayaaM bhRtRRvRjidhaarisahitapidamaH|saMJNaayaaM bhRtRRvRjidhaarisahitapidamaH|saMJNaayaaM bhRtRRvRjidhaarisahitapidamaH 3.2.46|संज्ञायां भृतॄवृजिधारिसहितपिदमः|संज्ञायां भृतॄवृजिधारिसहितपिदमः ३.२.४६|३.२.४६|३.२.४६ संज्ञायां भृतॄवृजिधारिसहितपिदमः
The affix खच् comes after the verbs - 1. भृ 'to bear' 2. तॄ 'to cross over' 3. वृ 'to choose' 4. जि 'to conquer' 5. धारि 'to hold' 6. सहि 'to bear' 7. तपि 'to heat' 8. दम 'to subdue'<br><br>Terms: खच्

