The feminine affix ङीष् comes after a प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) ending with the word वाह्।<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-ङीष्

4.1.62|4.1.62 sakhyashishviiti bhaaShaayaam|sakhyashishviiti bhaaShaayaam|sakhyashishviiti bhaaShaayaam 4.1.62|सख्यशिश्वीति भाषायाम्|सख्यशिश्वीति भाषायाम् ४.१.६२|४.१.६२|४.१.६२ सख्यशिश्वीति भाषायाम्
The forms सखी and अशिश्वी are irregular forms ending in ङीष् found in secular (or vernacular as opposed to Vedic) Sanskrit.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

4.1.63|4.1.63 jaaterastriiviShayaadayopadhaat‌|jaaterastriiviShayaadayopadhaat‌|jaaterastriiviShayaadayopadhaat‌ 4.1.63|जातेरस्त्रीविषयादयोपधात्‌|जातेरस्त्रीविषयादयोपधात्‌ ४.१.६३|४.१.६३|४.१.६३ जातेरस्त्रीविषयादयोपधात्‌
The feminine affix ङीष् comes after a word denoting a जाति or species when it does not express in its original meaning a feminine and which moreovere has not the letter य् for its penultimate.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-ङीष्

4.1.64|4.1.64 paakakarNaparNapuShpaphalamuulabaalottarapadaachcha|paakakarNaparNapuShpaphalamuulabaalottarapadaachcha|paakakarNaparNapuShpaphalamuulabaalottarapadaachcha 4.1.64|पाककर्णपर्णपुष्पफलमूलबालोत्तरपदाच्च|पाककर्णपर्णपुष्पफलमूलबालोत्तरपदाच्च ४.१.६४|४.१.६४|४.१.६४ पाककर्णपर्णपुष्पफलमूलबालोत्तरपदाच्च
And the feminine affix ङीष् comes after the प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) expressive of जाति , followed by the following 1. पाक 'cooked' 2. कर्ण 'ear' 3. पुष्प 'flower' 4. फल 'fruit' 5. मूल 'root' 6. बाल 'youth'<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-ङीष्

4.1.65|4.1.65 ito manuShyajaateH|ito manuShyajaateH|ito manuShyajaateH 4.1.65|इतो मनुष्यजातेः|इतो मनुष्यजातेः ४.१.६५|४.१.६५|४.१.६५ इतो मनुष्यजातेः
The feminine affix ङीष् comes after a प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) ending in short इ denoting classes or races of men.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-ङीष्

4.1.66|4.1.66 UNGutaH|UNGutaH|UNGutaH 4.1.66|ऊङुतः|ऊङुतः ४.१.६६|४.१.६६|४.१.६६ ऊङुतः
After a प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) ending in short उ , not having the letter य् as its penultimate letter and being expressive of races of men, the affix in the feminine is ऊङ्।<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-ऊङ्

4.1.67|4.1.67 baahvantaat‌ saMJNaayaam|baahvantaat‌ saMJNaayaam|baahvantaat‌ saMJNaayaam 4.1.67|बाह्वन्तात्‌ संज्ञायाम्|बाह्वन्तात्‌ संज्ञायाम् ४.१.६७|४.१.६७|४.१.६७ बाह्वन्तात्‌ संज्ञायाम्
