4.2.21|4.2.21 saa.asmin paurNamaasiiti (saMJNaayaam)|saa.asmin paurNamaasiiti (saMJNaayaam)|saa.asmin paurNamaasiiti (saMJNaayaam) 4.2.21|साऽस्मिन् पौर्णमासीति (संज्ञायाम्)|साऽस्मिन् पौर्णमासीति (संज्ञायाम्) ४.२.२१|४.२.२१|४.२.२१ साऽस्मिन् पौर्णमासीति (संज्ञायाम्)
The affix अण् comes after the name of a full-moon-night to denote the division of time in which the night falls.<br><br>Terms: अण्

4.2.22|4.2.22 aagrahaayaNyashvatthaaTThak|aagrahaayaNyashvatthaaTThak|aagrahaayaNyashvatthaaTThak 4.2.22|आग्रहायण्यश्वत्थाट्ठक्|आग्रहायण्यश्वत्थाट्ठक् ४.२.२२|४.२.२२|४.२.२२ आग्रहायण्यश्वत्थाट्ठक्
The affix ठक् comes in the sense of Locative -7th case after the words आग्रहायणी and अश्वत्थ ending in the 1st - Nominative Case-affix in construction and being the name of a full-moon night.<br><br>Terms: ठक्

4.2.23|4.2.23 vibhaaShaa phaalguniishravaNaakaarttikiichaitriibhyaH|vibhaaShaa phaalguniishravaNaakaarttikiichaitriibhyaH|vibhaaShaa phaalguniishravaNaakaarttikiichaitriibhyaH 4.2.23|विभाषा फाल्गुनीश्रवणाकार्त्तिकीचैत्रीभ्यः|विभाषा फाल्गुनीश्रवणाकार्त्तिकीचैत्रीभ्यः ४.२.२३|४.२.२३|४.२.२३ विभाषा फाल्गुनीश्रवणाकार्त्तिकीचैत्रीभ्यः
The affix ढक् optionally comes after the words 1. फाल्गुनी 2. कार्त्तिकी and 3. चैत्री being the names of full-moon nights, the whole word so formed being a Name denoting a division of time (a month, a fortnight or a year) in which the moon is full.<br><br>Terms: ढक्

