4.4.26|4.4.26 vyanjanairupasikte|vyanjanairupasikte|vyanjanairupasikte 4.4.26|व्यञ्जनैरुपसिक्ते|व्यञ्जनैरुपसिक्ते ४.४.२६|४.४.२६|४.४.२६ व्यञ्जनैरुपसिक्ते
The affix ठक् comes after a word denoting a condiment, being in the Instrumental -3rd case in construction when the sense is 'sprinkled therewith'.<br><br>Terms: ठक्

4.4.27|4.4.27 ojassaho.ambhasaa vartate|ojassaho.ambhasaa vartate|ojassaho.ambhasaa vartate 4.4.27|ओजस्सहोऽम्भसा वर्तते|ओजस्सहोऽम्भसा वर्तते ४.४.२७|४.४.२७|४.४.२७ ओजस्सहोऽम्भसा वर्तते
The affix ठक् comes in the sense of 'it exists' after the words 1. ओजस् 2. सहस् and 3. अभस् being in the Instrumental -3rd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: ठक्

4.4.28|4.4.28 tat pratyanupuurvamiipalomakuulam|tat pratyanupuurvamiipalomakuulam|tat pratyanupuurvamiipalomakuulam 4.4.28|तत् प्रत्यनुपूर्वमीपलोमकूलम्|तत् प्रत्यनुपूर्वमीपलोमकूलम् ४.४.२८|४.४.२८|४.४.२८ तत् प्रत्यनुपूर्वमीपलोमकूलम्
The affix ठक् comes in the sense of 'it exists' after 1. ईप 2. लोम and 3. कूल preceded by अनु and प्रति ; the word being in the Accusative -2nd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: ठक्

4.4.29|4.4.29 parimukhaM cha|parimukhaM cha|parimukhaM cha 4.4.29|परिमुखं च|परिमुखं च ४.४.२९|४.४.२९|४.४.२९ परिमुखं च
The affix ठक् comes in the sense of 'it exists' after the word परिमुख being it the Accusative -2nd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: ठक्

4.4.30|4.4.30 prayachChati garhyam|prayachChati garhyam|prayachChati garhyam 4.4.30|प्रयच्छति गर्ह्यम्|प्रयच्छति गर्ह्यम् ४.४.३०|४.४.३०|४.४.३० प्रयच्छति गर्ह्यम्
The affix ठक् comes after a word in the Accusative -2nd case in construction when the sense is 'he gives', the motive being mean.<br><br>Terms: ठक्

4.4.31|4.4.31 kusiidadashaikaadashaat‌ ShThanShThachau|kusiidadashaikaadashaat‌ ShThanShThachau|kusiidadashaikaadashaat‌ ShThanShThachau 4.4.31|कुसीददशैकादशात्‌ ष्ठन्ष्ठचौ|कुसीददशैकादशात्‌ ष्ठन्ष्ठचौ ४.४.३१|४.४.३१|४.४.३१ कुसीददशैकादशात्‌ ष्ठन्ष्ठचौ
The affixes ष्ठन् and ष्ठच् come respectively after the words कुसीद and दशैकादश when the sense is 'he gives for a mean motive'.<br><br>Terms: ष्ठन् and ष्ठच्

4.4.32|4.4.32 unChati|unChati|unChati 4.4.32|उञ्छति|उञ्छति ४.४.३२|४.४.३२|४.४.३२ उञ्छति
