5.1.7|5.1.7 khalayavamaaShatilavRShabrahmaNashcha|khalayavamaaShatilavRShabrahmaNashcha|khalayavamaaShatilavRShabrahmaNashcha 5.1.7|खलयवमाषतिलवृषब्रह्मणश्च|खलयवमाषतिलवृषब्रह्मणश्च ५.१.७|५.१.७|५.१.७ खलयवमाषतिलवृषब्रह्मणश्च
The affix यत् comes in the sense of 'good for that' after the word खल, यव, माष, तिल, वृष and ब्रह्मण।<br><br>Terms: 

5.1.8|5.1.8 ajaavibhyaaM thyan|ajaavibhyaaM thyan|ajaavibhyaaM thyan 5.1.8|अजाविभ्यां थ्यन्|अजाविभ्यां थ्यन् ५.१.८|५.१.८|५.१.८ अजाविभ्यां थ्यन्
The affix थ्यन् comes in the sense of 'good for that' after the words अज and अवि।<br><br>Terms: 

5.1.9|5.1.9 aatmanvishvajanabhogottarapadaat‌ khaH|aatmanvishvajanabhogottarapadaat‌ khaH|aatmanvishvajanabhogottarapadaat‌ khaH 5.1.9|आत्मन्विश्वजनभोगोत्तरपदात्‌ खः|आत्मन्विश्वजनभोगोत्तरपदात्‌ खः ५.१.९|५.१.९|५.१.९ आत्मन्विश्वजनभोगोत्तरपदात्‌ खः
