5.1.10|5.1.10 sarvapuruShaabhyaaM NaDhaNJau|sarvapuruShaabhyaaM NaDhaNJau|sarvapuruShaabhyaaM NaDhaNJau 5.1.10|सर्वपुरुषाभ्यां णढञौ|सर्वपुरुषाभ्यां णढञौ ५.१.१०|५.१.१०|५.१.१० सर्वपुरुषाभ्यां णढञौ
The affixes ण and ढञ् come in the sense of 'good for that' after the words सर्व and पुरुष।<br><br>Terms: 

5.1.11|5.1.11 maaNavacharakaabhyaaM khaNJ|maaNavacharakaabhyaaM khaNJ|maaNavacharakaabhyaaM khaNJ 5.1.11|माणवचरकाभ्यां खञ्|माणवचरकाभ्यां खञ् ५.१.११|५.१.११|५.१.११ माणवचरकाभ्यां खञ्
