5.1.66|5.1.66 daNDaadibhyaH|daNDaadibhyaH|daNDaadibhyaH 5.1.66|दण्डादिभ्यः|दण्डादिभ्यः ५.१.६६|५.१.६६|५.१.६६ दण्डादिभ्यः
After the words दण्ड etc. in the Accusative -2nd case the affix य comes in the sense of 'who deserves that'.<br><br>Terms: य

5.1.67|5.1.67 Chandasi cha|Chandasi cha|Chandasi cha 5.1.67|छन्दसि च|छन्दसि च ५.१.६७|५.१.६७|५.१.६७ छन्दसि च
