5.1.71|5.1.71 yaJNartvigbhyaaM ghakhaNJau|yaJNartvigbhyaaM ghakhaNJau|yaJNartvigbhyaaM ghakhaNJau 5.1.71|यज्ञर्त्विग्भ्यां घखञौ|यज्ञर्त्विग्भ्यां घखञौ ५.१.७१|५.१.७१|५.१.७१ यज्ञर्त्विग्भ्यां घखञौ
The affixes घ (इ य) and खञ् (+/- --ईन) come respectively after the words 1. यज्ञ and 2. ऋत्विज in the sense of 'deserving that'<br><br>Terms: घ and खञ्

5.1.72|5.1.72 paaraayaNaturaayaNachaandraayaNaM vartayati|paaraayaNaturaayaNachaandraayaNaM vartayati|paaraayaNaturaayaNachaandraayaNaM vartayati 5.1.72|पारायणतुरायणचान्द्रायणं वर्तयति|पारायणतुरायणचान्द्रायणं वर्तयति ५.१.७२|५.१.७२|५.१.७२ पारायणतुरायणचान्द्रायणं वर्तयति
The affix ठञ् (+/- -- इक , प्राग्वतेष्ठञ् ५.१.१८) comes in the sense of 'who performs this' after the words 1. पारायण 2. तुरायण and 3. चान्द्रायण being in the Accusative -2nd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: ठञ्

5.1.73|5.1.73 saMshayamaapannaH|saMshayamaapannaH|saMshayamaapannaH 5.1.73|संशयमापन्नः|संशयमापन्नः ५.१.७३|५.१.७३|५.१.७३ संशयमापन्नः
The affix ठञ् (+/- -- इक) comes in the sense of 'being fallen into this or thrown into it' after the word संशय in the Accusative -2nd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: ठञ्

5.1.74|5.1.74 yojanaM gachChati|yojanaM gachChati|yojanaM gachChati 5.1.74|योजनं गच्छति|योजनं गच्छति ५.१.७४|५.१.७४|५.१.७४ योजनं गच्छति
