5.1.100|5.1.100 karmaveShaadyat|karmaveShaadyat|karmaveShaadyat 5.1.100|कर्मवेषाद्यत्|कर्मवेषाद्यत् ५.१.१००|५.१.१००|५.१.१०० कर्मवेषाद्यत्
The affix यत् (यं) comes in the sense of 'being fitted with that', after the words 1. कर्म and 2. वेष being in the Instrumental -3rd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: यत् (यं)

5.1.101|5.1.101 tasmai prabhavati saMtaapaadibhyaH|tasmai prabhavati saMtaapaadibhyaH|tasmai prabhavati saMtaapaadibhyaH 5.1.101|तस्मै प्रभवति संतापादिभ्यः|तस्मै प्रभवति संतापादिभ्यः ५.१.१०१|५.१.१०१|५.१.१०१ तस्मै प्रभवति संतापादिभ्यः
