5.1.105|5.1.105 RtoraN|RtoraN|RtoraN 5.1.105|ऋतोरण्|ऋतोरण् ५.१.१०५|५.१.१०५|५.१.१०५ ऋतोरण्
The affix अण् comes in the sense of 'that has come for it' after the word ऋतु।<br><br>Terms: अण्

5.1.106|5.1.106 Chandasi ghas|Chandasi ghas|Chandasi ghas 5.1.106|छन्दसि घस्|छन्दसि घस् ५.१.१०६|५.१.१०६|५.१.१०६ छन्दसि घस्
