5.2.21|5.2.21 vraatena jiivati|vraatena jiivati|vraatena jiivati 5.2.21|व्रातेन जीवति|व्रातेन जीवति ५.२.२१|५.२.२१|५.२.२१ व्रातेन जीवति
The affix खञ् comes in the sense of 'who leads this life' or 'who lives by this' after the word व्रात being in the Instrumental -3rd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: खञ्

5.2.22|5.2.22 saaptapadiinaM sakhyam|saaptapadiinaM sakhyam|saaptapadiinaM sakhyam 5.2.22|साप्तपदीनं सख्यम्|साप्तपदीनं सख्यम् ५.२.२२|५.२.२२|५.२.२२ साप्तपदीनं सख्यम्
