5.2.24|5.2.24 tasya paakamuule piilvadikarNaadibhyaH kuNabjaahachau|tasya paakamuule piilvadikarNaadibhyaH kuNabjaahachau|tasya paakamuule piilvadikarNaadibhyaH kuNabjaahachau 5.2.24|तस्य पाकमूले पील्वदिकर्णादिभ्यः कुणब्जाहचौ|तस्य पाकमूले पील्वदिकर्णादिभ्यः कुणब्जाहचौ ५.२.२४|५.२.२४|५.२.२४ तस्य पाकमूले पील्वदिकर्णादिभ्यः कुणब्जाहचौ
The affixes कुणप् (कुण) and जाहच् (जाह) come in the senses of 'the fruiting-season of this' and 'the root of this'.<br><br>Terms: कुणप् (कुण) and जाहच् (जाह)

5.2.25|5.2.25 paxaattiH|paxaattiH|paxaattiH 5.2.25|पक्षात्तिः|पक्षात्तिः ५.२.२५|५.२.२५|५.२.२५ पक्षात्तिः
The affix ति comes in the sense of 'the root of it' after the word पक्ष in the Genitive 6th-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: ति

5.2.26|5.2.26 tena vittashchuncupchaNapau|tena vittashchuncupchaNapau|tena vittashchuncupchaNapau 5.2.26|तेन वित्तश्चुञ्चुप्चणपौ|तेन वित्तश्चुञ्चुप्चणपौ ५.२.२६|५.२.२६|५.२.२६ तेन वित्तश्चुञ्चुप्चणपौ
The affixes चुञ्चुप् (चुञ्चु) and चणप् (चण) come in the sense of 'celebrated through this' after a word in the Instrumental -3rd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: चुञ्चुप् (चुञ्चु) and चणप् (चण)

5.2.27|5.2.27 vinaNJbhyaaM naanaaNJau nasaha|vinaNJbhyaaM naanaaNJau nasaha|vinaNJbhyaaM naanaaNJau nasaha 5.2.27|विनञ्भ्यां नानाञौ नसह|विनञ्भ्यां नानाञौ नसह ५.२.२७|५.२.२७|५.२.२७ विनञ्भ्यां नानाञौ नसह
The affixes ना and नाञ् comes in the sense of 'not being together' after the words 1. वि and 2. नञ् respectively.<br><br>Terms: ना and नाञ्

5.2.28|5.2.28 veH shaalachChankaTachau|veH shaalachChankaTachau|veH shaalachChankaTachau 5.2.28|वेः शालच्छङ्कटचौ|वेः शालच्छङ्कटचौ ५.२.२८|५.२.२८|५.२.२८ वेः शालच्छङ्कटचौ
The affixes शालच् (शाल) and शङ्कटच् (शङ्कट) come after the preposition वि without changing the sense.<br><br>Terms: शालच् (शाल) and शङ्कटच् (शङ्कट)

5.2.29|5.2.29 samprodashcha kaTach|samprodashcha kaTach|samprodashcha kaTach 5.2.29|सम्प्रोदश्च कटच्|सम्प्रोदश्च कटच् ५.२.२९|५.२.२९|५.२.२९ सम्प्रोदश्च कटच्
The affix कटच् (कट) comes after the words 1. सम् 2. प्रद् 3. उद् and 4. वि।<br><br>Terms: कटच् (कट)

5.2.30|5.2.30 avaat‌ kuTaarachcha|avaat‌ kuTaarachcha|avaat‌ kuTaarachcha 5.2.30|अवात्‌ कुटारच्च|अवात्‌ कुटारच्च ५.२.३०|५.२.३०|५.२.३० अवात्‌ कुटारच्च
The affixes कुटारच् and कटच् come after the word अव।<br><br>Terms: कुटारच् and कटच्

5.2.31|5.2.31 nate naasikaayaaH saMJNaayaaM TiiTaNJnaaTajbhraaTachaH|nate naasikaayaaH saMJNaayaaM TiiTaNJnaaTajbhraaTachaH|nate naasikaayaaH saMJNaayaaM TiiTaNJnaaTajbhraaTachaH 5.2.31|नते नासिकायाः संज्ञायां टीटञ्नाटज्भ्राटचः|नते नासिकायाः संज्ञायां टीटञ्नाटज्भ्राटचः ५.२.३१|५.२.३१|५.२.३१ नते नासिकायाः संज्ञायां टीटञ्नाटज्भ्राटचः
The affixes टीटच् , नाटच् and भ्रटच् come in the sense of 'a hooked nose' after the word अव when the word so formed is a Name.<br><br>Terms: टीटच् , नाटच् and भ्रटच्

5.2.32|5.2.32 nerbiDajbiriisachau|nerbiDajbiriisachau|nerbiDajbiriisachau 5.2.32|नेर्बिडज्बिरीसचौ|नेर्बिडज्बिरीसचौ ५.२.३२|५.२.३२|५.२.३२ नेर्बिडज्बिरीसचौ
The affixes बिडच् and बिरीसच् come in the sense of 'a hooked nose' after the word नि when the word so formed is a Name.<br><br>Terms: बिडच् and बिरीसच्

5.2.33|5.2.33 inachpiTachchikachi cha|inachpiTachchikachi cha|inachpiTachchikachi cha 5.2.33|इनच्पिटच्चिकचि च|इनच्पिटच्चिकचि च ५.२.३३|५.२.३३|५.२.३३ इनच्पिटच्चिकचि च
The affixes इनच् and पिटच् come in the sense of 'a hooked nose' after the word नि ; and चिक् and चि are the substitutes of नि before those affixes respectively.<br><br>Terms: इनच् and पिटच्

5.2.34|5.2.34 upaadhibhyaaM tyakannaasannaaruuDhayoH|upaadhibhyaaM tyakannaasannaaruuDhayoH|upaadhibhyaaM tyakannaasannaaruuDhayoH 5.2.34|उपाधिभ्यां त्यकन्नासन्नारूढयोः|उपाधिभ्यां त्यकन्नासन्नारूढयोः ५.२.३४|५.२.३४|५.२.३४ उपाधिभ्यां त्यकन्नासन्नारूढयोः
The affix त्यकन् comes in the sense of 'nearness' and after the words 1. उप and 2. अधि , respectively, the words so formed being Names.<br><br>Terms: त्यकन्

5.2.35|5.2.35 karmaNi ghaTo.aThach|karmaNi ghaTo.aThach|karmaNi ghaTo.aThach 5.2.35|कर्मणि घटोऽठच्|कर्मणि घटोऽठच् ५.२.३५|५.२.३५|५.२.३५ कर्मणि घटोऽठच्
The affix अठच् comes in the sense of 'employing oneself zealously in it' after the word कर्म in the Locative -7th case in construction.<br><br>Terms: अठच्

5.2.36|5.2.36 tadasya saMjaataM taarakaa.a.adibhya itach|tadasya saMjaataM taarakaa.a.adibhya itach|tadasya saMjaataM taarakaa.a.adibhya itach 5.2.36|तदस्य संजातं तारकाऽऽदिभ्य इतच्|तदस्य संजातं तारकाऽऽदिभ्य इतच् ५.२.३६|५.२.३६|५.२.३६ तदस्य संजातं तारकाऽऽदिभ्य इतच्
The affix इतच् comes in the sense of 'that whereof this is observed' after the words तारका etc. in the Nominative 1st-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: इतच्

5.2.37|5.2.37 pramaaNe dvayasajdaghnaNJmaatrachaH|pramaaNe dvayasajdaghnaNJmaatrachaH|pramaaNe dvayasajdaghnaNJmaatrachaH 5.2.37|प्रमाणे द्वयसज्दघ्नञ्मात्रचः|प्रमाणे द्वयसज्दघ्नञ्मात्रचः ५.२.३७|५.२.३७|५.२.३७ प्रमाणे द्वयसज्दघ्नञ्मात्रचः
The affixes द्वयसच् , दघ्नश्च and मात्रच् come in the sense of 'that whereof this is the lineal measure' after a word in Nominative 1st-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: द्वयसच् , दघ्नश्च and मात्रच्

5.2.38|5.2.38 puruShahastibhyaamaN cha|puruShahastibhyaamaN cha|puruShahastibhyaamaN cha 5.2.38|पुरुषहस्तिभ्यामण् च|पुरुषहस्तिभ्यामण् च ५.२.३८|५.२.३८|५.२.३८ पुरुषहस्तिभ्यामण् च
The affix अण् , द्वयसच् , दघ्नश्च and मात्रच् come in the sense of 'that whereof this is the lineal measure' after the words 1. पुरुष and 2. हस्ति in the Nominative 1st-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: अण् , द्वयसच् , दघ्नश्च and मात्रच्

5.2.39|5.2.39 yadtadetebhyaH parimaaNe vatup‌|yadtadetebhyaH parimaaNe vatup‌|yadtadetebhyaH parimaaNe vatup‌ 5.2.39|यद्तदेतेभ्यः परिमाणे वतुप्‌|यद्तदेतेभ्यः परिमाणे वतुप्‌ ५.२.३९|५.२.३९|५.२.३९ यद्तदेतेभ्यः परिमाणे वतुप्‌
The affix वतुप्‌ comes in the sense of 'that where of this is the measure of volume' after the words 1.यद् 2. तद् and 3. एतद् being in the Nominative 1st-Case of construction.<br><br>Terms: वतुप्‌

5.2.40|5.2.40 kimidaMbhyaaM vo ghaH|kimidaMbhyaaM vo ghaH|kimidaMbhyaaM vo ghaH 5.2.40|किमिदंभ्यां वो घः|किमिदंभ्यां वो घः ५.२.४०|५.२.४०|५.२.४० किमिदंभ्यां वो घः
After the words किम् and इदम् , घ (इय्) is substituted for the व् of वतुप्‌।<br><br>Terms: किम् and इदम्

5.2.41|5.2.41 kimaH saMkhyaaparimaaNe Dati cha|kimaH saMkhyaaparimaaNe Dati cha|kimaH saMkhyaaparimaaNe Dati cha 5.2.41|किमः संख्यापरिमाणे डति च|किमः संख्यापरिमाणे डति च ५.२.४१|५.२.४१|५.२.४१ किमः संख्यापरिमाणे डति च
The affixes डति (अति with the elision of इम्) and वतुप्‌ come in the sense of 'numerical quantity' after the word किम् in the Nominative 1st-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: डति and वतुप्‌

5.2.42|5.2.42 saMkhyaayaa avayave tayap‌|saMkhyaayaa avayave tayap‌|saMkhyaayaa avayave tayap‌ 5.2.42|संख्याया अवयवे तयप्‌|संख्याया अवयवे तयप्‌ ५.२.४२|५.२.४२|५.२.४२ संख्याया अवयवे तयप्‌
The affix तयप्‌ comes in the sense of 'that whereof the parts are so many' after a numeral.<br><br>Terms: तयप्‌

5.2.43|5.2.43 dvitribhyaaM tayasyaayajvaa|dvitribhyaaM tayasyaayajvaa|dvitribhyaaM tayasyaayajvaa 5.2.43|द्वित्रिभ्यां तयस्यायज्वा|द्वित्रिभ्यां तयस्यायज्वा ५.२.४३|५.२.४३|५.२.४३ द्वित्रिभ्यां तयस्यायज्वा
The affix अयच् is optionally the substitute of तयप्‌ after the words 1. द्वि and 2. त्रि।<br><br>Terms: अयच्

5.2.44|5.2.44 ubhaadudaatto nityam|ubhaadudaatto nityam|ubhaadudaatto nityam 5.2.44|उभादुदात्तो नित्यम्|उभादुदात्तो नित्यम् ५.२.४४|५.२.४४|५.२.४४ उभादुदात्तो नित्यम्
After the word उभ , अयच् is always the substitute for तयप्‌ , having the उदात्त (acute accent) on its first syllable.<br><br>Terms: उभ

5.2.45|5.2.45 tadasminnadhikamiti dashaantaaDDaH|tadasminnadhikamiti dashaantaaDDaH|tadasminnadhikamiti dashaantaaDDaH 5.2.45|तदस्मिन्नधिकमिति दशान्ताड्डः|तदस्मिन्नधिकमिति दशान्ताड्डः ५.२.४५|५.२.४५|५.२.४५ तदस्मिन्नधिकमिति दशान्ताड्डः
The affix ड (अ with the elision of अन् of the base) comes in the sense of 'this is surplus in it' after a Numeral ending in दशन् being in the Nominative 1st-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: ड

5.2.46|5.2.46 shadantaviMshateshcha|shadantaviMshateshcha|shadantaviMshateshcha 5.2.46|शदन्तविंशतेश्च|शदन्तविंशतेश्च ५.२.४६|५.२.४६|५.२.४६ शदन्तविंशतेश्च
The affix ड comes in the sense of 'this is surplus in it' after a Numeral ending in शत् and after विंशति with the elision of अत् and अति।<br><br>Terms: ड

5.2.47|5.2.47 saMkhyaayaa guNasya nimaane mayaT|saMkhyaayaa guNasya nimaane mayaT|saMkhyaayaa guNasya nimaane mayaT 5.2.47|संख्याया गुणस्य निमाने मयट्|संख्याया गुणस्य निमाने मयट् ५.२.४७|५.२.४७|५.२.४७ संख्याया गुणस्य निमाने मयट्
The affix मयट् (मथ with feminine in ङीप्) comes when denoting a thing given in exchange in the sense of 'containing so many times more of something' or 'the price of a portion of this is so many equal portion of the other' after a Numeral.<br><br>Terms: मयट्

5.2.48|5.2.48 tasya puuraNe DaT|tasya puuraNe DaT|tasya puuraNe DaT 5.2.48|तस्य पूरणे डट्|तस्य पूरणे डट् ५.२.४८|५.२.४८|५.२.४८ तस्य पूरणे डट्
The affix डट् (अ causing the elision of the last vowel with the consonant following it) comes in the sense of 'making full this number' after a Numeral being the Genitive 6th-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: डट्

5.2.49|5.2.49 naantaadasaMkhyaa.a.adermaT|naantaadasaMkhyaa.a.adermaT|naantaadasaMkhyaa.a.adermaT 5.2.49|नान्तादसंख्याऽऽदेर्मट्|नान्तादसंख्याऽऽदेर्मट् ५.२.४९|५.२.४९|५.२.४९ नान्तादसंख्याऽऽदेर्मट्
The augment मट् comes before डट् in the sense of 'making full this number' after a Numeral which ends in न् when no other Numeral precedes it.<br><br>Terms: डट् and (मट्)

5.2.50|5.2.50 thaT cha chChandasi|thaT cha chChandasi|thaT cha chChandasi 5.2.50|थट् च च्छन्दसि|थट् च च्छन्दसि ५.२.५०|५.२.५०|५.२.५० थट् च च्छन्दसि
The थट् is the augment of डट् in the छन्दस् (Vedas) after a Numeral ending in न् and not preceded by another Numeral as well as the augment मट्।<br><br>Terms: डट् and (थट्)

5.2.51|5.2.51 ShaTkatikatipayachaturaaM thuk|ShaTkatikatipayachaturaaM thuk|ShaTkatikatipayachaturaaM thuk 5.2.51|षट्कतिकतिपयचतुरां थुक्|षट्कतिकतिपयचतुरां थुक् ५.२.५१|५.२.५१|५.२.५१ षट्कतिकतिपयचतुरां थुक्
When डट् follows, थुक् is the augment of the words 1. षट् 2. कति 3. कतिपय and 4. चतुर्।<br><br>Terms: डट् and (थुक्)

5.2.52|5.2.52 bahupuugagaNasaMghasya tithuk|bahupuugagaNasaMghasya tithuk|bahupuugagaNasaMghasya tithuk 5.2.52|बहुपूगगणसंघस्य तिथुक्|बहुपूगगणसंघस्य तिथुक् ५.२.५२|५.२.५२|५.२.५२ बहुपूगगणसंघस्य तिथुक्
When डट् follows, तिथुक् is the augment of the words 1. बहु 2. पूग 3. गण and 4. सङ्गघ।<br><br>Terms: डट् and (तिथुक्)

5.2.53|5.2.53 vatorithuk|vatorithuk|vatorithuk 5.2.53|वतोरिथुक्|वतोरिथुक् ५.२.५३|५.२.५३|५.२.५३ वतोरिथुक्
When follows is the augment of a stem ending in वतु।<br><br>Terms: डट् and (इथुक्)

5.2.54|5.2.54 dvestiiyaH|dvestiiyaH|dvestiiyaH 5.2.54|द्वेस्तीयः|द्वेस्तीयः ५.२.५४|५.२.५४|५.२.५४ द्वेस्तीयः
The affix तीय comes in the sense of 'completer thereof' after the word द्वि।<br><br>Terms: तीय

5.2.55|5.2.55 treH samprasaaraNam cha|treH samprasaaraNam cha|treH samprasaaraNam cha 5.2.55|त्रेः सम्प्रसारणम् च|त्रेः सम्प्रसारणम् च ५.२.५५|५.२.५५|५.२.५५ त्रेः सम्प्रसारणम् च
The affix तीय comes in the sense of 'completer thereof' after the word त्रि and there is सम्प्रसारण (Vocalisation) of the stem.<br><br>Terms: तीय

5.2.56|5.2.56 viMshatyaadibhyastamaDanyatarasyaam|viMshatyaadibhyastamaDanyatarasyaam|viMshatyaadibhyastamaDanyatarasyaam 5.2.56|विंशत्यादिभ्यस्तमडन्यतरस्याम्|विंशत्यादिभ्यस्तमडन्यतरस्याम् ५.२.५६|५.२.५६|५.२.५६ विंशत्यादिभ्यस्तमडन्यतरस्याम्
After the words विंशति etc. तमट् (तम feminine in ङीप्) is optionally the augment of डट्।<br><br>Terms: डट् and (तमट्)

5.2.57|5.2.57 nityaM shataadimaasaardhamaasasaMvatsaraachcha|nityaM shataadimaasaardhamaasasaMvatsaraachcha|nityaM shataadimaasaardhamaasasaMvatsaraachcha 5.2.57|नित्यं शतादिमासार्धमाससंवत्सराच्च|नित्यं शतादिमासार्धमाससंवत्सराच्च ५.२.५७|५.२.५७|५.२.५७ नित्यं शतादिमासार्धमाससंवत्सराच्च
After the words शत etc. and after 1. मास 2. अर्धमास and 3. संवत्सर तमट् (तम feminine in ङीप्) is always the augment of डट्।<br><br>Terms: डट् and (तमट्)

5.2.58|5.2.58 ShaShTyaadeshchaasaMkhyaa.a.adeH|ShaShTyaadeshchaasaMkhyaa.a.adeH|ShaShTyaadeshchaasaMkhyaa.a.adeH 5.2.58|षष्ट्यादेश्चासंख्याऽऽदेः|षष्ट्यादेश्चासंख्याऽऽदेः ५.२.५८|५.२.५८|५.२.५८ षष्ट्यादेश्चासंख्याऽऽदेः
After the words षष्ठी etc. when no other Numeral precedes them; तमट् is always the augment of डट्।<br><br>Terms: डट् and (तमट्)

5.2.59|5.2.59 matau chChaH suuktasaamnoH|matau chChaH suuktasaamnoH|matau chChaH suuktasaamnoH 5.2.59|मतौ च्छः सूक्तसाम्नोः|मतौ च्छः सूक्तसाम्नोः ५.२.५९|५.२.५९|५.२.५९ मतौ च्छः सूक्तसाम्नोः
When a सूक्त or साम्न् is to be expressed, the affix छ (ईय) comes after a प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) in the sense of the affix मतुप् -- तदस्यास्त्यस्मिन्निति मतुप्‌ ५.२.९४.<br><br>Terms: छ (ईय)

5.2.60|5.2.60 adhyaayaanuvaakayorluk|adhyaayaanuvaakayorluk|adhyaayaanuvaakayorluk 5.2.60|अध्यायानुवाकयोर्लुक्|अध्यायानुवाकयोर्लुक् ५.२.६०|५.२.६०|५.२.६० अध्यायानुवाकयोर्लुक्
When an अध्याय or अनुवाक is to be expressed there is लुक् elision of the affix छ (ईय) having the sense of मतुप् -- तदस्यास्त्यस्मिन्निति मतुप्‌ ५.२.९४.<br><br>Terms: छ (ईय)

5.2.61|5.2.61 vimuktaadibhyo.aN|vimuktaadibhyo.aN|vimuktaadibhyo.aN 5.2.61|विमुक्तादिभ्योऽण्|विमुक्तादिभ्योऽण् ५.२.६१|५.२.६१|५.२.६१ विमुक्तादिभ्योऽण्
The affix अण् comes in the sense of मतुप् when an अध्याय or अनुवाक is to be expressed, after the words विमुक्त etc.<br><br>Terms: अण्

5.2.62|5.2.62 goShadaadibhyo vun|goShadaadibhyo vun|goShadaadibhyo vun 5.2.62|गोषदादिभ्यो वुन्|गोषदादिभ्यो वुन् ५.२.६२|५.२.६२|५.२.६२ गोषदादिभ्यो वुन्
The affix वुन् comes in the sense of मतुप् when an अध्याय or अनुवाक is to be expressed<br><br>Terms: वुन्

5.2.63|5.2.63 tatra kushalaH pathaH|tatra kushalaH pathaH|tatra kushalaH pathaH 5.2.63|तत्र कुशलः पथः|तत्र कुशलः पथः ५.२.६३|५.२.६३|५.२.६३ तत्र कुशलः पथः
The affix वुन् comes in the sense of 'versed therein or skilled therein' after the word पथिन् being in the Locative -7th case in construction.<br><br>Terms: वुन्

5.2.64|5.2.64 aakarShaadibhyaH kan|aakarShaadibhyaH kan|aakarShaadibhyaH kan 5.2.64|आकर्षादिभ्यः कन्|आकर्षादिभ्यः कन् ५.२.६४|५.२.६४|५.२.६४ आकर्षादिभ्यः कन्
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'versed therein or skilled therein' after the प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) आकर्ष etc. being in the Locative -7th case in construction.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.65|5.2.65 dhanahiraNyaat‌ kaame|dhanahiraNyaat‌ kaame|dhanahiraNyaat‌ kaame 5.2.65|धनहिरण्यात्‌ कामे|धनहिरण्यात्‌ कामे ५.२.६५|५.२.६५|५.२.६५ धनहिरण्यात्‌ कामे
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'a desire thereafter' after the words 1. धन and 2. हिरण्य being in the Locative -7th case in construction.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.66|5.2.66 svaangebhyaH prasite|svaangebhyaH prasite|svaangebhyaH prasite 5.2.66|स्वाङ्गेभ्यः प्रसिते|स्वाङ्गेभ्यः प्रसिते ५.२.६६|५.२.६६|५.२.६६ स्वाङ्गेभ्यः प्रसिते
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'who takes care of it, who bestows care upon' after a word denoting a part of one's body.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.67|5.2.67 udaraaTThagaadyuune|udaraaTThagaadyuune|udaraaTThagaadyuune 5.2.67|उदराट्ठगाद्यूने|उदराट्ठगाद्यूने ५.२.६७|५.२.६७|५.२.६७ उदराट्ठगाद्यूने
The affix ठक् comes in the sense of 'voracious' after the word उदर।<br><br>Terms: ठक्

5.2.68|5.2.68 sasyena parijaataH|sasyena parijaataH|sasyena parijaataH 5.2.68|सस्येन परिजातः|सस्येन परिजातः ५.२.६८|५.२.६८|५.२.६८ सस्येन परिजातः
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'to supply richly with it' after the word सस्य being in the Instrumental -3rd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.69|5.2.69 aMshaM haarii|aMshaM haarii|aMshaM haarii 5.2.69|अंशं हारी|अंशं हारी ५.२.६९|५.२.६९|५.२.६९ अंशं हारी
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'who must take that' after the word अंश 'a share' being in the Accusative -2nd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.70|5.2.70 tantraadachiraapahRte|tantraadachiraapahRte|tantraadachiraapahRte 5.2.70|तन्त्रादचिरापहृते|तन्त्रादचिरापहृते ५.२.७०|५.२.७०|५.२.७० तन्त्रादचिरापहृते
The affix कन् comes in the sense of taken off there from not long ago or shortly before' after the word तन्त्र 'a loom'.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.71|5.2.71 braahmaNakoShNike saMJNaayaam|braahmaNakoShNike saMJNaayaam|braahmaNakoShNike saMJNaayaam 5.2.71|ब्राह्मणकोष्णिके संज्ञायाम्|ब्राह्मणकोष्णिके संज्ञायाम् ५.२.७१|५.२.७१|५.२.७१ ब्राह्मणकोष्णिके संज्ञायाम्
The words ब्राह्मण and उष्णिक are anomalous when they are a Name.<br><br>Terms: Anomalous

5.2.72|5.2.72 shiitoShNaabhyaaM kaariNi|shiitoShNaabhyaaM kaariNi|shiitoShNaabhyaaM kaariNi 5.2.72|शीतोष्णाभ्यां कारिणि|शीतोष्णाभ्यां कारिणि ५.२.७२|५.२.७२|५.२.७२ शीतोष्णाभ्यां कारिणि
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'who goes to work thus' after the words शीत and उष्ण।<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.73|5.2.73 adhikam|adhikam|adhikam 5.2.73|अधिकम्|अधिकम् ५.२.७३|५.२.७३|५.२.७३ अधिकम्
The word अधिक is anomalous.<br><br>Terms: Anomalous

5.2.74|5.2.74 anukaabhikaabhiikaH kamitaa|anukaabhikaabhiikaH kamitaa|anukaabhikaabhiikaH kamitaa 5.2.74|अनुकाभिकाभीकः कमिता|अनुकाभिकाभीकः कमिता ५.२.७४|५.२.७४|५.२.७४ अनुकाभिकाभीकः कमिता
The words 1. अनुक 2. अभिक and 3. अभीक are anomalous meaning 'being at liberty to do or being fond of'.<br><br>Terms: Anomalous

5.2.75|5.2.75 paarshvenaanvichChati|paarshvenaanvichChati|paarshvenaanvichChati 5.2.75|पार्श्वेनान्विच्छति|पार्श्वेनान्विच्छति ५.२.७५|५.२.७५|५.२.७५ पार्श्वेनान्विच्छति
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'who strives to gain something by that' after the word पार्श्व in the Instrumental -3rd case in construction.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.76|5.2.76 ayaHshuuladaNDaajinaabhyaaM ThakThaNJau|ayaHshuuladaNDaajinaabhyaaM ThakThaNJau|ayaHshuuladaNDaajinaabhyaaM ThakThaNJau 5.2.76|अयःशूलदण्डाजिनाभ्यां ठक्ठञौ|अयःशूलदण्डाजिनाभ्यां ठक्ठञौ ५.२.७६|५.२.७६|५.२.७६ अयःशूलदण्डाजिनाभ्यां ठक्ठञौ
The affixes ठक् and ठञ् come in the sense of 'who strives to gain something by that 'after the words 1. अयःशूल and 2. दण्डाजिन , respectively<br><br>Terms: ठक् and ठञ्

5.2.77|5.2.77 taavatithaM grahaNamiti lugvaa|taavatithaM grahaNamiti lugvaa|taavatithaM grahaNamiti lugvaa 5.2.77|तावतिथं ग्रहणमिति लुग्वा|तावतिथं ग्रहणमिति लुग्वा ५.२.७७|५.२.७७|५.२.७७ तावतिथं ग्रहणमिति लुग्वा
The affix कन् is added to an ordinal number in the sense of 'acquiring a subject after so many attempts' and there is optionally the elision of the affix denoting the ordinal number.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.78|5.2.78 sa eShaaM graamaNiiH|sa eShaaM graamaNiiH|sa eShaaM graamaNiiH 5.2.78|स एषां ग्रामणीः|स एषां ग्रामणीः ५.२.७८|५.२.७८|५.२.७८ स एषां ग्रामणीः
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'he is their leader' after a word in the Nominative 1st-Case with the force of Genitive 6th-Case.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.79|5.2.79 shRNGkhalamasya bandhanaM karabhe|shRNGkhalamasya bandhanaM karabhe|shRNGkhalamasya bandhanaM karabhe 5.2.79|शृङ्खलमस्य बन्धनं करभे|शृङ्खलमस्य बन्धनं करभे ५.२.७९|५.२.७९|५.२.७९ शृङ्खलमस्य बन्धनं करभे
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'clog is its fetter' after the word शृङ्खल 'a clog' when the whole word means 'a young camel'.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.80|5.2.80 utka unmanaaH|utka unmanaaH|utka unmanaaH 5.2.80|उत्क उन्मनाः|उत्क उन्मनाः ५.२.८०|५.२.८०|५.२.८० उत्क उन्मनाः
The word उत्क is anomalous meaning 'longing after, yearning'.<br><br>Terms: Anomalous

5.2.81|5.2.81 kaalaprayojanaadroge|kaalaprayojanaadroge|kaalaprayojanaadroge 5.2.81|कालप्रयोजनाद्रोगे|कालप्रयोजनाद्रोगे ५.२.८१|५.२.८१|५.२.८१ कालप्रयोजनाद्रोगे
The affix कन् comes after a word expressing a time or a cause or effect (of the disease) when an illness is denoted.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.82|5.2.82 tadasminnannaM praaye saMJNaayaam‌|tadasminnannaM praaye saMJNaayaam‌|tadasminnannaM praaye saMJNaayaam‌ 5.2.82|तदस्मिन्नन्नं प्राये संज्ञायाम्‌|तदस्मिन्नन्नं प्राये संज्ञायाम्‌ ५.२.८२|५.२.८२|५.२.८२ तदस्मिन्नन्नं प्राये संज्ञायाम्‌
The affix कन् comes in the sense of 'this is the principal food of this particular occasion' after a word denoting food in the Nominative 1st-Case in construction, when the whole word so formed is a Name.<br><br>Terms: कन्

5.2.83|5.2.83 kulmaaShaadaNJ|kulmaaShaadaNJ|kulmaaShaadaNJ 5.2.83|कुल्माषादञ्|कुल्माषादञ् ५.२.८३|५.२.८३|५.२.८३ कुल्माषादञ्
The affix अण् comes in the sense of 'this is the principal food on this particular occasion' after the word कुल्माष when the whole word is a Name.<br><br>Terms: अण्

5.2.84|5.2.84 shrotriyaMshChando.adhiite|shrotriyaMshChando.adhiite|shrotriyaMshChando.adhiite 5.2.84|श्रोत्रियंश्छन्दोऽधीते|श्रोत्रियंश्छन्दोऽधीते ५.२.८४|५.२.८४|५.२.८४ श्रोत्रियंश्छन्दोऽधीते
The word श्रोत्रिन् is irregularly formed meaning 'who has studied the छन्दस् (Vedas)'.<br><br>Terms: Irregularly

5.2.85|5.2.85 shraaddhamanena bhuktaminiThanau|shraaddhamanena bhuktaminiThanau|shraaddhamanena bhuktaminiThanau 5.2.85|श्राद्धमनेन भुक्तमिनिठनौ|श्राद्धमनेन भुक्तमिनिठनौ ५.२.८५|५.२.८५|५.२.८५ श्राद्धमनेन भुक्तमिनिठनौ
The affixes इनि (इन्) and ठन् come in the sense of 'this is eaten by him' after the word ।<br><br>Terms: इनि and ठन्

5.2.86|5.2.86 puurvaadiniH|puurvaadiniH|puurvaadiniH 5.2.86|पूर्वादिनिः|पूर्वादिनिः ५.२.८६|५.२.८६|५.२.८६ पूर्वादिनिः
The affix इनि (इन्) comes in the sense of 'by whom something was done formerly' after the word पूर्व।<br><br>Terms: इनि (इन्)

5.2.87|5.2.87 sapuurvaachcha|sapuurvaachcha|sapuurvaachcha 5.2.87|सपूर्वाच्च|सपूर्वाच्च ५.२.८७|५.२.८७|५.२.८७ सपूर्वाच्च
The affix इनि (इन्) comes in the sense of 'by whom something is done' after the word पूर्व, also when another word precedes it.<br><br>Terms: इनि (इन्)

5.2.88|5.2.88 iShTaadibhyashcha|iShTaadibhyashcha|iShTaadibhyashcha 5.2.88|इष्टादिभ्यश्च|इष्टादिभ्यश्च ५.२.८८|५.२.८८|५.२.८८ इष्टादिभ्यश्च
The affix इनि (इन्) comes in the sense of 'by him' after इष्ट etc.<br><br>Terms: इनि (इन्)

5.2.89|5.2.89 Chandasi paripanthiparipariNau paryavasthaatari|Chandasi paripanthiparipariNau paryavasthaatari|Chandasi paripanthiparipariNau paryavasthaatari 5.2.89|छन्दसि परिपन्थिपरिपरिणौ पर्यवस्थातरि|छन्दसि परिपन्थिपरिपरिणौ पर्यवस्थातरि ५.२.८९|५.२.८९|५.२.८९ छन्दसि परिपन्थिपरिपरिणौ पर्यवस्थातरि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the words 1. परिपन्थिन् and 2. परिपरिण् are anomalously formed by this affix and have the sense of 'an antagonist'.<br><br>Terms: छन्दस्

5.2.90|5.2.90 anupadyanveShTaa|anupadyanveShTaa|anupadyanveShTaa 5.2.90|अनुपद्यन्वेष्टा|अनुपद्यन्वेष्टा ५.२.९०|५.२.९०|५.२.९० अनुपद्यन्वेष्टा
The word अनुपदिन् formed anomalously by इनि denotes 'who goes after, who searches'.<br><br>Terms: Anomalous

5.2.91|5.2.91 saaxaaddraShTari saMJNaayaam|saaxaaddraShTari saMJNaayaam|saaxaaddraShTari saMJNaayaam 5.2.91|साक्षाद्द्रष्टरि संज्ञायाम्|साक्षाद्द्रष्टरि संज्ञायाम् ५.२.९१|५.२.९१|५.२.९१ साक्षाद्द्रष्टरि संज्ञायाम्
The affix इनि comes in the sense of 'a spectator, looker on' after the word साक्षात् when the word so formed is a Name.<br><br>Terms: इनि

5.2.92|5.2.92 xetriyach paraxetre chikitsyaH|xetriyach paraxetre chikitsyaH|xetriyach paraxetre chikitsyaH 5.2.92|क्षेत्रियच् परक्षेत्रे चिकित्स्यः|क्षेत्रियच् परक्षेत्रे चिकित्स्यः ५.२.९२|५.२.९२|५.२.९२ क्षेत्रियच् परक्षेत्रे चिकित्स्यः
The word क्षेत्रियच् (क्षेत्रिय) is anomalous meaning 'curable in another body' i.e. 'not curable in this life'.<br><br>Terms: Anomalous

5.2.93|5.2.93 indriyamindraliMgamindradRShTamindrasRShTamindrajuShTamindradattamiti vaa|indriyamindraliMgamindradRShTamindrasRShTamindrajuShTamindradattamiti vaa|indriyamindraliMgamindradRShTamindrasRShTamindrajuShTamindradattamiti vaa 5.2.93|इन्द्रियमिन्द्रलिंगमिन्द्रदृष्टमिन्द्रसृष्टमिन्द्रजुष्टम्इन्द्रदत्तमिति वा|इन्द्रियमिन्द्रलिंगमिन्द्रदृष्टमिन्द्रसृष्टमिन्द्रजुष्टम्इन्द्रदत्तमिति वा ५.२.९३|५.२.९३|५.२.९३ इन्द्रियमिन्द्रलिंगमिन्द्रदृष्टमिन्द्रसृष्टमिन्द्रजुष्टम्इन्द्रदत्तमिति वा
The word इन्द्रियम् (having उदात्त (acute accent) on the last) is anomalous meaning 'an organ of sense' and so called either because it is 'the characteristic from which the existence of इन्द्र is inferred' or 'it is seen by इन्द्र ' or 'it is created by इन्द्र ' or it is wished by इन्द्र ' or 'it is given by इन्द्र '.<br><br>Terms: 

5.2.94|5.2.94 tadasyaastyasminniti matup‌|tadasyaastyasminniti matup‌|tadasyaastyasminniti matup‌ 5.2.94|तदस्यास्त्यस्मिन्निति मतुप्‌|तदस्यास्त्यस्मिन्निति मतुप्‌ ५.२.९४|५.२.९४|५.२.९४ तदस्यास्त्यस्मिन्निति मतुप्‌
The affix मतुप् comes in the sense of 'whose it is' or 'in whom it is' after a word in the Nominative 1st-Case in construction.<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

5.2.95|5.2.95 rasaadibhyashcha|rasaadibhyashcha|rasaadibhyashcha 5.2.95|रसादिभ्यश्च|रसादिभ्यश्च ५.२.९५|५.२.९५|५.२.९५ रसादिभ्यश्च
The affix मतुप् comes in the sense of 'whose it is' or 'in whom it is' after the प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) रस etc.<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

5.2.96|5.2.96 praaNisthaadaato lajanyatarasyaam|praaNisthaadaato lajanyatarasyaam|praaNisthaadaato lajanyatarasyaam 5.2.96|प्राणिस्थादातो लजन्यतरस्याम्|प्राणिस्थादातो लजन्यतरस्याम् ५.२.९६|५.२.९६|५.२.९६ प्राणिस्थादातो लजन्यतरस्याम्
The affix लच् comes optionally in the sense of मतुप् after a stem ending in long आ the word expressing something which is found only in a living being.<br><br>Terms: लच्

5.2.97|5.2.97 sidhmaadibhyashcha|sidhmaadibhyashcha|sidhmaadibhyashcha 5.2.97|सिध्मादिभ्यश्च|सिध्मादिभ्यश्च ५.२.९७|५.२.९७|५.२.९७ सिध्मादिभ्यश्च
The affix लच् comes in the sense of मतुप् after the words सिध्म etc. and optionally after मतुप् also.<br><br>Terms: लच् and मतुप्

5.2.98|5.2.98 vatsaaMsaabhyaaM kaamabale|vatsaaMsaabhyaaM kaamabale|vatsaaMsaabhyaaM kaamabale 5.2.98|वत्सांसाभ्यां कामबले|वत्सांसाभ्यां कामबले ५.२.९८|५.२.९८|५.२.९८ वत्सांसाभ्यां कामबले
The affix लच् comes in the senses of 'love' and 'strength' respectively after the words वत्स and अंस।<br><br>Terms: लच्

5.2.99|5.2.99 phenaadilach cha|phenaadilach cha|phenaadilach cha 5.2.99|फेनादिलच् च|फेनादिलच् च ५.२.९९|५.२.९९|५.२.९९ फेनादिलच् च
The affixes इलच् and लच् come in the sense of मतुप् after the word फेन and optionally after the affix मतुप् also.<br><br>Terms: इलच् and लच्

5.2.100|5.2.100 lomaadipaamaadipichChaadibhyaH shanelachaH|lomaadipaamaadipichChaadibhyaH shanelachaH|lomaadipaamaadipichChaadibhyaH shanelachaH 5.2.100|लोमादिपामादिपिच्छादिभ्यः शनेलचः|लोमादिपामादिपिच्छादिभ्यः शनेलचः ५.२.१००|५.२.१००|५.२.१०० लोमादिपामादिपिच्छादिभ्यः शनेलचः
The three affixes श , न and इलच् come in the sense of मतुप् respectively after the words of the three classes i.e. 1. लोमदि 2. पामादि and 3. पिच्छादि and the affix मतुप् also comes in the alternative.<br><br>Terms: मतुप् , श , न and इलच्

5.2.101|5.2.101 praJNaashraddhaa.archaavRttibhyo NaH|praJNaashraddhaa.archaavRttibhyo NaH|praJNaashraddhaa.archaavRttibhyo NaH 5.2.101|प्रज्ञाश्रद्धाऽर्चावृत्तिभ्यो णः|प्रज्ञाश्रद्धाऽर्चावृत्तिभ्यो णः ५.२.१०१|५.२.१०१|५.२.१०१ प्रज्ञाश्रद्धाऽर्चावृत्तिभ्यो णः
The affix ण् comes in the sense of मतुप् after the words 1. प्रज्ञा 2. श्रद्धा and 3. अर्चा as well as the affix मतुप् ।<br><br>Terms: ण्

5.2.102|5.2.102 tapaHsahasraabhyaaM viniinii|tapaHsahasraabhyaaM viniinii|tapaHsahasraabhyaaM viniinii 5.2.102|तपःसहस्राभ्यां विनीनी|तपःसहस्राभ्यां विनीनी ५.२.१०२|५.२.१०२|५.२.१०२ तपःसहस्राभ्यां विनीनी
The affixes विनि and इनि come with the force of मतुप् after the words तपस् and सहर respectively.<br><br>Terms: विनि and इनि

5.2.103|5.2.103 aN cha|aN cha|aN cha 5.2.103|अण् च|अण् च ५.२.१०३|५.२.१०३|५.२.१०३ अण् च
And also अण् comes after तपस् and सहर।<br><br>Terms: अण्

5.2.104|5.2.104 sikataasharkaraabhyaaM cha|sikataasharkaraabhyaaM cha|sikataasharkaraabhyaaM cha 5.2.104|सिकताशर्कराभ्यां च|सिकताशर्कराभ्यां च ५.२.१०४|५.२.१०४|५.२.१०४ सिकताशर्कराभ्यां च
