5.2.105|5.2.105 deshe lubilachau cha|deshe lubilachau cha|deshe lubilachau cha 5.2.105|देशे लुबिलचौ च|देशे लुबिलचौ च ५.२.१०५|५.२.१०५|५.२.१०५ देशे लुबिलचौ च
When the sense if of 'locality' there may take place लुप् elision of the affixes denoting मतुप् (with the preservation of the gender and number of the word) or there may be the affixes इलच् , अण् and मतुप् after the words सिकता and शर्करा।<br><br>Terms: इलच् , अण् and मतुप् 

5.2.106|5.2.106 danta unnata urach|danta unnata urach|danta unnata urach 5.2.106|दन्त उन्नत उरच्|दन्त उन्नत उरच् ५.२.१०६|५.२.१०६|५.२.१०६ दन्त उन्नत उरच्
The affix उरच् comes in the sense of 'having projecting teeth' after the word दन्त।<br><br>Terms: उरच्

