is not elided after a word denoting a part of the body (with the exception of मूर्धन् and मस्तक) before every word other than काम।<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.13|6.3.13 bandhe cha vibhaaShaa|bandhe cha vibhaaShaa|bandhe cha vibhaaShaa 6.3.13|बन्धे च विभाषा|बन्धे च विभाषा ६.३.१३|६.३.१३|६.३.१३ बन्धे च विभाषा
