6.3.24|6.3.24 vibhaaShaa svasRpatyoH|vibhaaShaa svasRpatyoH|vibhaaShaa svasRpatyoH 6.3.24|विभाषा स्वसृपत्योः|विभाषा स्वसृपत्योः ६.३.२४|६.३.२४|६.३.२४ विभाषा स्वसृपत्योः
The Genitive 6th-Case-affix is optionally elided after a stem ending in ऋ when 1. स्वसृ and 2. पितृ follow.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.25|6.3.25 aanaNG Rto dvaMdve|aanaNG Rto dvaMdve|aanaNG Rto dvaMdve 6.3.25|आनङ् ऋतो द्वंद्वे|आनङ् ऋतो द्वंद्वे ६.३.२५|६.३.२५|६.३.२५ आनङ् ऋतो द्वंद्वे
In a द्वन्द समास of words ending in the short ऋ and expressing relationship through study or blood, the आनङ् is the substitute of ऋ of the first member.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.26|6.3.26 devataadvaMdve cha|devataadvaMdve cha|devataadvaMdve cha 6.3.26|देवताद्वंद्वे च|देवताद्वंद्वे च ६.३.२६|६.३.२६|६.३.२६ देवताद्वंद्वे च
The आनङ् is the substitute for the final of the first member in a द्वन्द समास of the names of the देवता-s.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.27|6.3.27 iidagneH somavaruNayoH|iidagneH somavaruNayoH|iidagneH somavaruNayoH 6.3.27|ईदग्नेः सोमवरुणयोः|ईदग्नेः सोमवरुणयोः ६.३.२७|६.३.२७|६.३.२७ ईदग्नेः सोमवरुणयोः
For the final of अग्नि is substituted the long ई when 1. सोम or 2. वरुण follow.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.28|6.3.28 idvRddhau|idvRddhau|idvRddhau 6.3.28|इद्वृद्धौ|इद्वृद्धौ ६.३.२८|६.३.२८|६.३.२८ इद्वृद्धौ
The short इ is the substitute of the final of the अग्नि in such a द्वन्द समास in which both the members take the वृद्धि।<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.29|6.3.29 divo dyaavaa|divo dyaavaa|divo dyaavaa 6.3.29|दिवो द्यावा|दिवो द्यावा ६.३.२९|६.३.२९|६.३.२९ दिवो द्यावा
For दिव् is substituted द्यावा in a द्वन्द समास of names of देवता-s.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.30|6.3.30 divasashcha pRthivyaam|divasashcha pRthivyaam|divasashcha pRthivyaam 6.3.30|दिवसश्च पृथिव्याम्|दिवसश्च पृथिव्याम् ६.३.३०|६.३.३०|६.३.३० दिवसश्च पृथिव्याम्
For दिव् is also substituted दिवस् (as well as a द्यावा) when पृथिवी follows in a द्वन्द समास of names of देवता-s.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.31|6.3.31 uShaasoShasaH|uShaasoShasaH|uShaasoShasaH 6.3.31|उषासोषसः|उषासोषसः ६.३.३१|६.३.३१|६.३.३१ उषासोषसः
For उषस् is substituted उषासा in a देवता - द्वन्द समास।<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.32|6.3.32 maatarapitaraavudiichaam|maatarapitaraavudiichaam|maatarapitaraavudiichaam 6.3.32|मातरपितरावुदीचाम्|मातरपितरावुदीचाम् ६.३.३२|६.३.३२|६.३.३२ मातरपितरावुदीचाम्
According to Northern Grammarians मातरपितरौ is a valid form.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.33|6.3.33 pitaraamaataraa cha chChandasi|pitaraamaataraa cha chChandasi|pitaraamaataraa cha chChandasi 6.3.33|पितरामातरा च च्छन्दसि|पितरामातरा च च्छन्दसि ६.३.३३|६.३.३३|६.३.३३ पितरामातरा च च्छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the form पितरामातरा is a valid form.<br><br>Terms: विभक्ति-Non-elision

6.3.34|6.3.34 striyaaH puMvadbhaaShitapuMskaadanuuNG samaanaadhikaraNe striyaamapuuraNiipriyaa.a.adiShu|striyaaH puMvadbhaaShitapuMskaadanuuNG samaanaadhikaraNe striyaamapuuraNiipriyaa.a.adiShu|striyaaH puMvadbhaaShitapuMskaadanuuNG samaanaadhikaraNe striyaamapuuraNiipriyaa.a.adiShu 6.3.34|स्त्रियाः पुंवद्भाषितपुंस्कादनूङ् समानाधिकरणे स्त्रियामपूरणीप्रियाऽऽदिषु|स्त्रियाः पुंवद्भाषितपुंस्कादनूङ् समानाधिकरणे स्त्रियामपूरणीप्रियाऽऽदिषु ६.३.३४|६.३.३४|६.३.३४ स्त्रियाः पुंवद्भाषितपुंस्कादनूङ् समानाधिकरणे स्त्रियामपूरणीप्रियाऽऽदिषु
In the room of a feminine word there is substituted an equivalent and uniform masculine form when it is a word which has an actual corresponding masculine and does not end in the feminine affix ऊङ् and is followed by another feminine word in the relation of apposition with it, but not when such subsequent word is an ordinal numeral, nor प्रिय etc.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.35|6.3.35 tasilaadiShu aakRtvasuchaH|tasilaadiShu aakRtvasuchaH|tasilaadiShu aakRtvasuchaH 6.3.35|तसिलादिषु आकृत्वसुचः|तसिलादिषु आकृत्वसुचः ६.३.३५|६.३.३५|६.३.३५ तसिलादिषु आकृत्वसुचः
A feminine word not ending in the affix ऊङ् and having an equivalent and uniform masculine is changed into such masculine form, before the affixes beginning with तसिल् etc. -- पञ्चम्यास्तसिल् ५.३.७, and ending with कृत्वसुच् -- संख्यायाः क्रियाऽभ्यावृत्तिगणने कृत्वसुच् ५.४.१७.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.36|6.3.36 kyaNGmaaninoshcha|kyaNGmaaninoshcha|kyaNGmaaninoshcha 6.3.36|क्यङ्मानिनोश्च|क्यङ्मानिनोश्च ६.३.३६|६.३.३६|६.३.३६ क्यङ्मानिनोश्च
A feminine word not ending in ऊङ् and having an equivalent and uniform masculine is changed into masculine before the Denominative कयङ् and the affix मानिन्।<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.37|6.3.37 na kopadhaayaaH|na kopadhaayaaH|na kopadhaayaaH 6.3.37|न कोपधायाः|न कोपधायाः ६.३.३७|६.३.३७|६.३.३७ न कोपधायाः
A feminine word having a penultimate क् does not assume the masculine form.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.38|6.3.38 saMJNaapuuraNyoshcha|saMJNaapuuraNyoshcha|saMJNaapuuraNyoshcha 6.3.38|संज्ञापूरण्योश्च|संज्ञापूरण्योश्च ६.३.३८|६.३.३८|६.३.३८ संज्ञापूरण्योश्च
The feminine is not changed to masculine when it is a Name or an Ordinal Numeral.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.39|6.3.39 vRddhinimittasya cha taddhitasyaaraktavikaare|vRddhinimittasya cha taddhitasyaaraktavikaare|vRddhinimittasya cha taddhitasyaaraktavikaare 6.3.39|वृद्धिनिमित्तस्य च तद्धितस्यारक्तविकारे|वृद्धिनिमित्तस्य च तद्धितस्यारक्तविकारे ६.३.३९|६.३.३९|६.३.३९ वृद्धिनिमित्तस्य च तद्धितस्यारक्तविकारे
The feminine is not changed into masculine when it is formed by such a तद्धित affix which causes the वृद्धि of the first syllable with exception however of तद्धित-substitute meaning 'coloured therewith' and 'made thereof'.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.40|6.3.40 svaangaachcheto.amaanini|svaangaachcheto.amaanini|svaangaachcheto.amaanini 6.3.40|स्वाङ्गाच्चेतोऽमानिनि|स्वाङ्गाच्चेतोऽमानिनि ६.३.४०|६.३.४०|६.३.४० स्वाङ्गाच्चेतोऽमानिनि
A feminine in ई ending in the name of a part of body does not become masculine except the word मानिन् follows.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.41|6.3.41 jaateshcha|jaateshcha|jaateshcha 6.3.41|जातेश्च|जातेश्च ६.३.४१|६.३.४१|६.३.४१ जातेश्च
A feminine noun expressing a class of kind does not become masculine.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.42|6.3.42 puMvat‌ karmadhaarayajaatiiyadeshiiyeShu|puMvat‌ karmadhaarayajaatiiyadeshiiyeShu|puMvat‌ karmadhaarayajaatiiyadeshiiyeShu 6.3.42|पुंवत्‌ कर्मधारयजातीयदेशीयेषु|पुंवत्‌ कर्मधारयजातीयदेशीयेषु ६.३.४२|६.३.४२|६.३.४२ पुंवत्‌ कर्मधारयजातीयदेशीयेषु
The feminine (unless it ends in ऊ) having an equivalent and uniform masculine becomes masculine in a कर्मधारय समास and before 1. जातीय and 2. देशीय।<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.43|6.3.43 gharuupakalpachelaDbruvagotramatahateShu NGyo.anekaacho hrasvaH|gharuupakalpachelaDbruvagotramatahateShu NGyo.anekaacho hrasvaH|gharuupakalpachelaDbruvagotramatahateShu NGyo.anekaacho hrasvaH 6.3.43|घरूपकल्पचेलड्ब्रुवगोत्रमतहतेषु ङ्योऽनेकाचो ह्रस्वः|घरूपकल्पचेलड्ब्रुवगोत्रमतहतेषु ङ्योऽनेकाचो ह्रस्वः ६.३.४३|६.३.४३|६.३.४३ घरूपकल्पचेलड्ब्रुवगोत्रमतहतेषु ङ्योऽनेकाचो ह्रस्वः
Before the affixes 1. तर 2. तम 3. रूप 4. कल्प 5. चेल (with the feminine affix ई) 6. ब्रुव 7. गोत्र 8 मत and 9. हत a word ending in the feminine affix ङी becomes short when the feminine consists of two or more syllables and has an equivalent and uniform masculine.<br><br>Terms: Masculisation

6.3.44|6.3.44 nadyaaH sheShasyaanyatarasyaam|nadyaaH sheShasyaanyatarasyaam|nadyaaH sheShasyaanyatarasyaam 6.3.44|नद्याः शेषस्यान्यतरस्याम्|नद्याः शेषस्यान्यतरस्याम् ६.३.४४|६.३.४४|६.३.४४ नद्याः शेषस्यान्यतरस्याम्
In all the remaining feminine words called नदी -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३ and नेयङुवङ्स्थानावस्त्री १.४.४, the substitution of short vowel under the preceding circumstances is optional.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.45|6.3.45 ugitashcha|ugitashcha|ugitashcha 6.3.45|उगितश्च|उगितश्च ६.३.४५|६.३.४५|६.३.४५ उगितश्च
The feminine ङी (ई) added to a word formed by a तद्धित affix having an indicatory उ or ऋ is optionally shortened before the घ etc. -- घरूपकल्पचेलड्ब्रुवगोत्रमतहतेषु ङ्योऽनेकाचो ह्रस्वः ६.३.४३.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.46|6.3.46 aanmahataH samaanaadhikaraNajaatiiyayoH|aanmahataH samaanaadhikaraNajaatiiyayoH|aanmahataH samaanaadhikaraNajaatiiyayoH 6.3.46|आन्महतः समानाधिकरणजातीययोः|आन्महतः समानाधिकरणजातीययोः ६.३.४६|६.३.४६|६.३.४६ आन्महतः समानाधिकरणजातीययोः
For the final महत् of is substituted आत् (आ) before a word which is in apposition with it and before जातीय।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.47|6.3.47 dvyaShTanaH saMkhyaayaamabahuvriihyashiityoH|dvyaShTanaH saMkhyaayaamabahuvriihyashiityoH|dvyaShTanaH saMkhyaayaamabahuvriihyashiityoH 6.3.47|द्व्यष्टनः संख्यायामबहुव्रीह्यशीत्योः|द्व्यष्टनः संख्यायामबहुव्रीह्यशीत्योः ६.३.४७|६.३.४७|६.३.४७ द्व्यष्टनः संख्यायामबहुव्रीह्यशीत्योः
आत् (आ) is substituted for the final of द्वि and अष्टन् when another numeral follows but not in a बहुव्रीहि समास or before आशीतिः।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.48|6.3.48 trestrayaH|trestrayaH|trestrayaH 6.3.48|त्रेस्त्रयः|त्रेस्त्रयः ६.३.४८|६.३.४८|६.३.४८ त्रेस्त्रयः
For त्रि is substituted त्रयस् when another numeral follows but not in a बहुव्रीहि समास or before आशीतिः।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.49|6.3.49 vibhaaShaa chatvaariMshatprabhRtau sarveShaam|vibhaaShaa chatvaariMshatprabhRtau sarveShaam|vibhaaShaa chatvaariMshatprabhRtau sarveShaam 6.3.49|विभाषा चत्वारिंशत्प्रभृतौ सर्वेषाम्|विभाषा चत्वारिंशत्प्रभृतौ सर्वेषाम् ६.३.४९|६.३.४९|६.३.४९ विभाषा चत्वारिंशत्प्रभृतौ सर्वेषाम्
The above substitution is the case of all (द्वि , त्रि and अष्टन्) is optional when the word चत्वारिंशत् and the numerals which follow it are the second member.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.50|6.3.50 hRdayasya hRllekhayadaNlaaseShu|hRdayasya hRllekhayadaNlaaseShu|hRdayasya hRllekhayadaNlaaseShu 6.3.50|हृदयस्य हृल्लेखयदण्लासेषु|हृदयस्य हृल्लेखयदण्लासेषु ६.३.५०|६.३.५०|६.३.५० हृदयस्य हृल्लेखयदण्लासेषु
हृद् is substituted for हृदय before लेख and the affixes यत् and अण् and before लास।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.51|6.3.51 vaa shokaShyaNJrogeShu|vaa shokaShyaNJrogeShu|vaa shokaShyaNJrogeShu 6.3.51|वा शोकष्यञ्रोगेषु|वा शोकष्यञ्रोगेषु ६.३.५१|६.३.५१|६.३.५१ वा शोकष्यञ्रोगेषु
हृद् is optionally substituted for हृदय before the words शोक and रोग or the affix ष्यङ् follow.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.52|6.3.52 paadasya padaajyaatigopahateShu|paadasya padaajyaatigopahateShu|paadasya padaajyaatigopahateShu 6.3.52|पादस्य पदाज्यातिगोपहतेषु|पादस्य पदाज्यातिगोपहतेषु ६.३.५२|६.३.५२|६.३.५२ पादस्य पदाज्यातिगोपहतेषु
पद् is substituted for पाद before 1. आजि 2. आति 3. ग and 4. उपहत।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.53|6.3.53 pad yatyatadarthe|pad yatyatadarthe|pad yatyatadarthe 6.3.53|पद् यत्यतदर्थे|पद् यत्यतदर्थे ६.३.५३|६.३.५३|६.३.५३ पद् यत्यतदर्थे
पद् is substituted for पाद before the affix यत् used in any sense other than that of 'suited there to'.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.54|6.3.54 himakaaShihatiShu cha|himakaaShihatiShu cha|himakaaShihatiShu cha 6.3.54|हिमकाषिहतिषु च|हिमकाषिहतिषु च ६.३.५४|६.३.५४|६.३.५४ हिमकाषिहतिषु च
पद् is substituted for पाद before 1. हिम 2. काषिन् and 3. हति।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.55|6.3.55 RchaH she|RchaH she|RchaH she 6.3.55|ऋचः शे|ऋचः शे ६.३.५५|६.३.५५|६.३.५५ ऋचः शे
पद् is substituted for पाद before the affix शस् when the meaning is that of a ऋक् (Hymn).<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.56|6.3.56 vaa ghoShamishrashabdeShu|vaa ghoShamishrashabdeShu|vaa ghoShamishrashabdeShu 6.3.56|वा घोषमिश्रशब्देषु|वा घोषमिश्रशब्देषु ६.३.५६|६.३.५६|६.३.५६ वा घोषमिश्रशब्देषु
पद् is optionally substituted for पाद before 1. घोष 2. मिश्र and 3. शब्द।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.57|6.3.57 udakasyodaH saMJNaayaam|udakasyodaH saMJNaayaam|udakasyodaH saMJNaayaam 6.3.57|उदकस्योदः संज्ञायाम्|उदकस्योदः संज्ञायाम् ६.३.५७|६.३.५७|६.३.५७ उदकस्योदः संज्ञायाम्
उद is substituted for उदक when the compound is a Name.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.58|6.3.58 peShaMvaasavaahanadhiShu cha|peShaMvaasavaahanadhiShu cha|peShaMvaasavaahanadhiShu cha 6.3.58|पेषंवासवाहनधिषु च|पेषंवासवाहनधिषु च ६.३.५८|६.३.५८|६.३.५८ पेषंवासवाहनधिषु च
उद is substituted for उदक before 1. पेषं 2. वास 3. वाह and 4. धि।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.59|6.3.59 ekahalaadau puurayitavye.anyatarasyaam|ekahalaadau puurayitavye.anyatarasyaam|ekahalaadau puurayitavye.anyatarasyaam 6.3.59|एकहलादौ पूरयितव्येऽन्यतरस्याम्|एकहलादौ पूरयितव्येऽन्यतरस्याम् ६.३.५९|६.३.५९|६.३.५९ एकहलादौ पूरयितव्येऽन्यतरस्याम्
उद is optionally substituted for उदक before a word beginning with a single consonant and which expresses that which is filled with water.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.60|6.3.60 manthaudanasaktubinduvajrabhaarahaaraviivadhagaaheShu cha|manthaudanasaktubinduvajrabhaarahaaraviivadhagaaheShu cha|manthaudanasaktubinduvajrabhaarahaaraviivadhagaaheShu cha 6.3.60|मन्थौदनसक्तुबिन्दुवज्रभारहारवीवधगाहेषु च|मन्थौदनसक्तुबिन्दुवज्रभारहारवीवधगाहेषु च ६.३.६०|६.३.६०|६.३.६० मन्थौदनसक्तुबिन्दुवज्रभारहारवीवधगाहेषु च
उद is optionally substituted for उदक before 1. मन्थ 2. ओदन 3. सक्तु 4. बिन्दु 5. वज्र 5. भार 6. हार 7. वीवध and 8. गाह।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.61|6.3.61 iko hrasvo.aNGyo gaalavasya|iko hrasvo.aNGyo gaalavasya|iko hrasvo.aNGyo gaalavasya 6.3.61|इको ह्रस्वोऽङ्यो गालवस्य|इको ह्रस्वोऽङ्यो गालवस्य ६.३.६१|६.३.६१|६.३.६१ इको ह्रस्वोऽङ्यो गालवस्य
According to the opinion of गालव a short vowel is substituted in a compound before the second member for the long इक् vowels (ई , ऊ , ॠ) unless it is the long vowel of the feminine affix ई (ङी).<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.62|6.3.62 eka taddhite cha|eka taddhite cha|eka taddhite cha 6.3.62|एक तद्धिते च|एक तद्धिते च ६.३.६२|६.३.६२|६.३.६२ एक तद्धिते च
The short is substituted for the long एका before a तद्धित affix and when a second member follows.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.63|6.3.63 NGyaapoH saMJNaaChandasorbahulam|NGyaapoH saMJNaaChandasorbahulam|NGyaapoH saMJNaaChandasorbahulam 6.3.63|ङ्यापोः संज्ञाछन्दसोर्बहुलम्|ङ्यापोः संज्ञाछन्दसोर्बहुलम् ६.३.६३|६.३.६३|६.३.६३ ङ्यापोः संज्ञाछन्दसोर्बहुलम्
The short is diversely substituted for the feminine affixes ई and आ (ङी and आप्) in a Name and in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: Shortening

6.3.64|6.3.64 tve cha|tve cha|tve cha 6.3.64|त्वे च|त्वे च ६.३.६४|६.३.६४|६.३.६४ त्वे च
The feminine affixes ई and आ (ङी and आप्) diversely become short before the affix त्व।<br><br>Terms: Shortening

6.3.65|6.3.65 iShTakeShiikaamaalaanaaM chitatuulabhaariShu|iShTakeShiikaamaalaanaaM chitatuulabhaariShu|iShTakeShiikaamaalaanaaM chitatuulabhaariShu 6.3.65|इष्टकेषीकामालानां चिततूलभारिषु|इष्टकेषीकामालानां चिततूलभारिषु ६.३.६५|६.३.६५|६.३.६५ इष्टकेषीकामालानां चिततूलभारिषु
For the long vowel a short is substituted in इष्टका before चित in इषीका before तूल and in माला before भारिन्।<br><br>Terms: Shortening

6.3.66|6.3.66 khityanavyayasya|khityanavyayasya|khityanavyayasya 6.3.66|खित्यनव्ययस्य|खित्यनव्ययस्य ६.३.६६|६.३.६६|६.३.६६ खित्यनव्ययस्य
A short is always substituted for the final of the first member when the second member is a word formed by an affix having an indicatory ख but not when the first member is an indeclinable.<br><br>Terms: Shortening

6.3.67|6.3.67 arurdviShadajantasya mum|arurdviShadajantasya mum|arurdviShadajantasya mum 6.3.67|अरुर्द्विषदजन्तस्य मुम्|अरुर्द्विषदजन्तस्य मुम् ६.३.६७|६.३.६७|६.३.६७ अरुर्द्विषदजन्तस्य मुम्
मुम् is the augment added immediately after the final vowel of अरुस , द्विषत् and of a stem ending in a vowel unless it is an indeclinable, when the word formed by a खित् affix follows.<br><br>Terms: मुम् Augment

6.3.68|6.3.68 icha ekaacho.ampratyayavachcha|icha ekaacho.ampratyayavachcha|icha ekaacho.ampratyayavachcha 6.3.68|इच एकाचोऽम्प्रत्ययवच्च|इच एकाचोऽम्प्रत्ययवच्च ६.३.६८|६.३.६८|६.३.६८ इच एकाचोऽम्प्रत्ययवच्च
A monosyllabic word ending in any vowel other than अ when followed by a word formed by a खित् affix receives the augment अम् which is added in the same way as the affix अम् of the Accusative -2nd case singular.<br><br>Terms: अम् Augment

6.3.69|6.3.69 vaachaMyamapuraMdarau cha|vaachaMyamapuraMdarau cha|vaachaMyamapuraMdarau cha 6.3.69|वाचंयमपुरंदरौ च|वाचंयमपुरंदरौ च ६.३.६९|६.३.६९|६.३.६९ वाचंयमपुरंदरौ च
वाचंयम and पुरंदर are irregularly formed.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

6.3.70|6.3.70 kaare satyaagadasya|kaare satyaagadasya|kaare satyaagadasya 6.3.70|कारे सत्यागदस्य|कारे सत्यागदस्य ६.३.७०|६.३.७०|६.३.७० कारे सत्यागदस्य
मुम् is the augment of सत्य and अगद when the word कार follows.<br><br>Terms: मुम् Augment

6.3.71|6.3.71 shyenatilasya paate NJe|shyenatilasya paate NJe|shyenatilasya paate NJe 6.3.71|श्येनतिलस्य पाते ञे|श्येनतिलस्य पाते ञे ६.३.७१|६.३.७१|६.३.७१ श्येनतिलस्य पाते ञे
मुम् is the augment of the words श्येन and तिल before पात when the affix ञ् follows.<br><br>Terms: मुम् Augment

6.3.72|6.3.72 raatreH kRti vibhaaShaa|raatreH kRti vibhaaShaa|raatreH kRti vibhaaShaa 6.3.72|रात्रेः कृति विभाषा|रात्रेः कृति विभाषा ६.३.७२|६.३.७२|६.३.७२ रात्रेः कृति विभाषा
The word रात्रि optionally takes मुम् augment before a word formed by कृत् affix.<br><br>Terms: मुम् Augment

6.3.73|6.3.73 nalopo naNJaH|nalopo naNJaH|nalopo naNJaH 6.3.73|नलोपो नञः|नलोपो नञः ६.३.७३|६.३.७३|६.३.७३ नलोपो नञः
The न of the Negative Particle नञ् is elided when it is the first member of a compound.<br><br>Terms: नुट् Augment

6.3.74|6.3.74 tasmaannuDachi|tasmaannuDachi|tasmaannuDachi 6.3.74|तस्मान्नुडचि|तस्मान्नुडचि ६.३.७४|६.३.७४|६.३.७४ तस्मान्नुडचि
After the above न-elided of the Negative Particle नञ् (i.e. after अ) is added the augment नुट् to a word beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: नुट् Augment

6.3.75|6.3.75 nabhraaNnapaannavedaanaasatyaanamuchinakulanakhanapuMsakanaxatranakranaakeShu prakRtyaa|nabhraaNnapaannavedaanaasatyaanamuchinakulanakhanapuMsakanaxatranakranaakeShu prakRtyaa|nabhraaNnapaannavedaanaasatyaanamuchinakulanakhanapuMsakanaxatranakranaakeShu prakRtyaa 6.3.75|नभ्राण्नपान्नवेदानासत्यानमुचिनकुलनखनपुंसकनक्षत्रनक्रनाकेषु प्रकृत्या|नभ्राण्नपान्नवेदानासत्यानमुचिनकुलनखनपुंसकनक्षत्रनक्रनाकेषु प्रकृत्या ६.३.७५|६.३.७५|६.३.७५ नभ्राण्नपान्नवेदानासत्यानमुचिनकुलनखनपुंसकनक्षत्रनक्रनाकेषु प्रकृत्या
The Negative Particle remains unchanged in - 1. नभ्राज् 2. नपात् 3. नवेदस् 4. नासत्या (dual) 5. नमुचि 6. नकुल 7. नख 8. नपुंसक 9. नक्षत्र 10. नक्र and 11. नाक।<br><br>Terms: नुट् Augment

6.3.76|6.3.76 ekaadishchaikasya chaaduk|ekaadishchaikasya chaaduk|ekaadishchaikasya chaaduk 6.3.76|एकादिश्चैकस्य चादुक्|एकादिश्चैकस्य चादुक् ६.३.७६|६.३.७६|६.३.७६ एकादिश्चैकस्य चादुक्
The Negative Particle remains unchanged in a word which begins with एक and of this एक there is the augment अदुक् (अद्)।<br><br>Terms: नुट् Augment

6.3.77|6.3.77 nago.apraaNiShvanyatarasyaam|nago.apraaNiShvanyatarasyaam|nago.apraaNiShvanyatarasyaam 6.3.77|नगोऽप्राणिष्वन्यतरस्याम्|नगोऽप्राणिष्वन्यतरस्याम् ६.३.७७|६.३.७७|६.३.७७ नगोऽप्राणिष्वन्यतरस्याम्
The Negative Particle is optionally retained unchanged in नगो when it does not mean a living animate being.<br><br>Terms: नुट् Augment

6.3.78|6.3.78 sahasya saH saMJNaayaam|sahasya saH saMJNaayaam|sahasya saH saMJNaayaam 6.3.78|सहस्य सः संज्ञायाम्|सहस्य सः संज्ञायाम् ६.३.७८|६.३.७८|६.३.७८ सहस्य सः संज्ञायाम्
स is substituted for सह , in a Name.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.79|6.3.79 granthaantaadhike cha|granthaantaadhike cha|granthaantaadhike cha 6.3.79|ग्रन्थान्ताधिके च|ग्रन्थान्ताधिके च ६.३.७९|६.३.७९|६.३.७९ ग्रन्थान्ताधिके च
स is substituted for सह when it has the sense of 'up to the end'.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.80|6.3.80 dvitiiye chaanupaakhye|dvitiiye chaanupaakhye|dvitiiye chaanupaakhye 6.3.80|द्वितीये चानुपाख्ये|द्वितीये चानुपाख्ये ६.३.८०|६.३.८०|६.३.८० द्वितीये चानुपाख्ये
स is substituted for सह when it is in connection with a word which refers to a second object which latter however is not directly perceived.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.81|6.3.81 avyayiibhaave chaakaale|avyayiibhaave chaakaale|avyayiibhaave chaakaale 6.3.81|अव्ययीभावे चाकाले|अव्ययीभावे चाकाले ६.३.८१|६.३.८१|६.३.८१ अव्ययीभावे चाकाले
स is substituted for सह in an अव्ययीभाव समास when the second member is not a word denoting time.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.82|6.3.82 vopasarjanasya|vopasarjanasya|vopasarjanasya 6.3.82|वोपसर्जनस्य|वोपसर्जनस्य ६.३.८२|६.३.८२|६.३.८२ वोपसर्जनस्य
स is optionally substituted for सह when the compound is a बहुव्रीहि समास।<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.83|6.3.83 prakRtyaa.a.ashiShyagovatsahaleShu|prakRtyaa.a.ashiShyagovatsahaleShu|prakRtyaa.a.ashiShyagovatsahaleShu 6.3.83|प्रकृत्याऽऽशिष्यगोवत्सहलेषु|प्रकृत्याऽऽशिष्यगोवत्सहलेषु ६.३.८३|६.३.८३|६.३.८३ प्रकृत्याऽऽशिष्यगोवत्सहलेषु
The word सह retains its original form when the sentence denotes benediction, except when it is गो , वत्स or हल।<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.84|6.3.84 samaanasya ChandasyamuurdhaprabhRtyudarkeShu|samaanasya ChandasyamuurdhaprabhRtyudarkeShu|samaanasya ChandasyamuurdhaprabhRtyudarkeShu 6.3.84|समानस्य छन्दस्यमूर्धप्रभृत्युदर्केषु|समानस्य छन्दस्यमूर्धप्रभृत्युदर्केषु ६.३.८४|६.३.८४|६.३.८४ समानस्य छन्दस्यमूर्धप्रभृत्युदर्केषु
स is substituted for समान् in the छन्दस् (Vedas), but not before 1. मूर्धन् 2. प्रभृति and 3. उदर्क।<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.85|6.3.85 jyotirjanapadaraatrinaabhinaamagotraruupasthaanavarNavayovachanabandhuShu|jyotirjanapadaraatrinaabhinaamagotraruupasthaanavarNavayovachanabandhuShu|jyotirjanapadaraatrinaabhinaamagotraruupasthaanavarNavayovachanabandhuShu 6.3.85|ज्योतिर्जनपदरात्रिनाभिनामगोत्ररूपस्थानवर्णवयोवचनबन्धुषु|ज्योतिर्जनपदरात्रिनाभिनामगोत्ररूपस्थानवर्णवयोवचनबन्धुषु ६.३.८५|६.३.८५|६.३.८५ ज्योतिर्जनपदरात्रिनाभिनामगोत्ररूपस्थानवर्णवयोवचनबन्धुषु
This substitution of स for समान् takes place before 1. ज्योतिस् 2. जनपद 3. रात्रि 4. गोत्र 5. रूप 6. स्थान 7. वर्ण 8. वयस् 9. वचन and 10. बन्धु in the common language also.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.86|6.3.86 charaNe brahmachaariNi|charaNe brahmachaariNi|charaNe brahmachaariNi 6.3.86|चरणे ब्रह्मचारिणि|चरणे ब्रह्मचारिणि ६.३.८६|६.३.८६|६.३.८६ चरणे ब्रह्मचारिणि
स is substituted for समान् before ब्रह्मचारिन् when it denotes persons engaged in fulfilling a common vow of studying the Vedas.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.87|6.3.87 tiirthe ye|tiirthe ye|tiirthe ye 6.3.87|तीर्थे ये|तीर्थे ये ६.३.८७|६.३.८७|६.३.८७ तीर्थे ये
स is substituted for समान् before तीर्थ when the affix यत् is added to it.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.88|6.3.88 vibhaaShodare|vibhaaShodare|vibhaaShodare 6.3.88|विभाषोदरे|विभाषोदरे ६.३.८८|६.३.८८|६.३.८८ विभाषोदरे
स is optionally substituted for समान् before उदर when the affix यत् is added to it.<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.89|6.3.89 dRgdRshavatuShu|dRgdRshavatuShu|dRgdRshavatuShu 6.3.89|दृग्दृशवतुषु|दृग्दृशवतुषु ६.३.८९|६.३.८९|६.३.८९ दृग्दृशवतुषु
स is substituted for समान् before 1. दृग् 2. दृश and the affix वत्।<br><br>Terms: स Substitute

6.3.90|6.3.90 idankimoriishkii|idankimoriishkii|idankimoriishkii 6.3.90|इदङ्किमोरीश्की|इदङ्किमोरीश्की ६.३.९०|६.३.९०|६.३.९० इदङ्किमोरीश्की
ई is substituted for इदम् and की for किम् before the words 1. दृग् 2. दृश and the affix वत्।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.91|6.3.91 aa sarvanaamnaH|aa sarvanaamnaH|aa sarvanaamnaH 6.3.91|आ सर्वनाम्नः|आ सर्वनाम्नः ६.३.९१|६.३.९१|६.३.९१ आ सर्वनाम्नः
आ is substituted for the final of the pronouns - सर्वादीनि सर्वनामानि १.१.२७, before the words 1. दृग् 2. दृश and the affix वत्।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.92|6.3.92 viShvagdevayoshcha Teradryancatau vapratyaye|viShvagdevayoshcha Teradryancatau vapratyaye|viShvagdevayoshcha Teradryancatau vapratyaye 6.3.92|विष्वग्देवयोश्च टेरद्र्यञ्चतौ वप्रत्यये|विष्वग्देवयोश्च टेरद्र्यञ्चतौ वप्रत्यये ६.३.९२|६.३.९२|६.३.९२ विष्वग्देवयोश्च टेरद्र्यञ्चतौ वप्रत्यये
In the room of the last consonant that follows it, of a pronoun and of the words विषवक् and देव is substituted अद्रि when अञ्च् with the affix व follows.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.93|6.3.93 samaH sami|samaH sami|samaH sami 6.3.93|समः समि|समः समि ६.३.९३|६.३.९३|६.३.९३ समः समि
समि is substituted for सम् before this अञ्च् when no affix (or व affix) follows.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.94|6.3.94 tirasastiryalope|tirasastiryalope|tirasastiryalope 6.3.94|तिरसस्तिर्यलोपे|तिरसस्तिर्यलोपे ६.३.९४|६.३.९४|६.३.९४ तिरसस्तिर्यलोपे
तिरि is substituted for तिरस् before this अञ्च् when no affix (or व affix) follows, provided that the अ of अञ्च् is not elided.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.95|6.3.95 sahasya sadhriH|sahasya sadhriH|sahasya sadhriH 6.3.95|सहस्य सध्रिः|सहस्य सध्रिः ६.३.९५|६.३.९५|६.३.९५ सहस्य सध्रिः
सघ्रि is the substitute of सह before अञ्च् when no affix (or व affix) follows.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.96|6.3.96 sadha maadasthayoshChandasi|sadha maadasthayoshChandasi|sadha maadasthayoshChandasi 6.3.96|सध मादस्थयोश्छन्दसि|सध मादस्थयोश्छन्दसि ६.३.९६|६.३.९६|६.३.९६ सध मादस्थयोश्छन्दसि
सध is substituted for सह in the छन्दस् (Vedas) when माद and स्थ follow.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.97|6.3.97 dvyantarupasargebhyo.apa iit‌|dvyantarupasargebhyo.apa iit‌|dvyantarupasargebhyo.apa iit‌ 6.3.97|द्व्यन्तरुपसर्गेभ्योऽप ईत्‌|द्व्यन्तरुपसर्गेभ्योऽप ईत्‌ ६.३.९७|६.३.९७|६.३.९७ द्व्यन्तरुपसर्गेभ्योऽप ईत्‌
After 1. द्वि 2. अन्तर and prepositions, long ई is the substitute of अप्।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.98|6.3.98 Udanordeshe|Udanordeshe|Udanordeshe 6.3.98|ऊदनोर्देशे|ऊदनोर्देशे ६.३.९८|६.३.९८|६.३.९८ ऊदनोर्देशे
After अनु , ऊ is substituted for (the अ of) अप् when the sense is that of a locality.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.99|6.3.99 aShaShThyatRtiiyaasthasyaanyasya dugaashiraashaa.a.asthaa.a.asthitotsukotikaarakaraagachCheShu|aShaShThyatRtiiyaasthasyaanyasya dugaashiraashaa.a.asthaa.a.asthitotsukotikaarakaraagachCheShu|aShaShThyatRtiiyaasthasyaanyasya dugaashiraashaa.a.asthaa.a.asthitotsukotikaarakaraagachCheShu 6.3.99|अषष्ठ्यतृतीयास्थस्यान्यस्य दुगाशिराशाऽऽस्थाऽऽस्थितोत्सुकोतिकारकरागच्छेषु|अषष्ठ्यतृतीयास्थस्यान्यस्य दुगाशिराशाऽऽस्थाऽऽस्थितोत्सुकोतिकारकरागच्छेषु ६.३.९९|६.३.९९|६.३.९९ अषष्ठ्यतृतीयास्थस्यान्यस्य दुगाशिराशाऽऽस्थाऽऽस्थितोत्सुकोतिकारकरागच्छेषु
अन्य when not used in the Genitive 6th-Case or the Instrumental -3rd case gets the augment दुक् (द्) before 1. आशिस् 2. आशा 3. आस्था 4. उत्सुक 5. कारक and 6. राग as well as before the affix छ (ईय).<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.100|6.3.100 arthe vibhaaShaa|arthe vibhaaShaa|arthe vibhaaShaa 6.3.100|अर्थे विभाषा|अर्थे विभाषा ६.३.१००|६.३.१००|६.३.१०० अर्थे विभाषा
दुक् (द्) is optionally the augment of अन्य when अर्थ follows.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.101|6.3.101 koH kat‌ tatpuruShe.achi|koH kat‌ tatpuruShe.achi|koH kat‌ tatpuruShe.achi 6.3.101|कोः कत्‌ तत्पुरुषेऽचि|कोः कत्‌ तत्पुरुषेऽचि ६.३.१०१|६.३.१०१|६.३.१०१ कोः कत्‌ तत्पुरुषेऽचि
कत्‌ is substituted for कु in a तत्-पुरुष समास when a word beginning with a vowel follows as the second member.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.102|6.3.102 rathavadayoshcha|rathavadayoshcha|rathavadayoshcha 6.3.102|रथवदयोश्च|रथवदयोश्च ६.३.१०२|६.३.१०२|६.३.१०२ रथवदयोश्च
कत्‌ is substituted for कु before रथ and वद।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.103|6.3.103 tRNe cha jaatau|tRNe cha jaatau|tRNe cha jaatau 6.3.103|तृणे च जातौ|तृणे च जातौ ६.३.१०३|६.३.१०३|६.३.१०३ तृणे च जातौ
कत्‌ is substituted for कु when तृण follows denoting a species.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.104|6.3.104 kaa pathyaxayoH|kaa pathyaxayoH|kaa pathyaxayoH 6.3.104|का पथ्यक्षयोः|का पथ्यक्षयोः ६.३.१०४|६.३.१०४|६.३.१०४ का पथ्यक्षयोः
का is the substitute of कु before पथिन् and अक्ष।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.105|6.3.105 iiShadarthe|iiShadarthe|iiShadarthe 6.3.105|ईषदर्थे|ईषदर्थे ६.३.१०५|६.३.१०५|६.३.१०५ ईषदर्थे
का is the substitute of कु when the meaning is 'a small'.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.106|6.3.106 vibhaaShaa puruShe|vibhaaShaa puruShe|vibhaaShaa puruShe 6.3.106|विभाषा पुरुषे|विभाषा पुरुषे ६.३.१०६|६.३.१०६|६.३.१०६ विभाषा पुरुषे
का is optionally the substitute of कु when the word पुरुष follows.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.107|6.3.107 kavaM choShNe|kavaM choShNe|kavaM choShNe 6.3.107|कवं चोष्णे|कवं चोष्णे ६.३.१०७|६.३.१०७|६.३.१०७ कवं चोष्णे
का and कवङ् are optionally the substitutes of कु when उष्ण follows.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.108|6.3.108 pathi cha chChandasi|pathi cha chChandasi|pathi cha chChandasi 6.3.108|पथि च च्छन्दसि|पथि च च्छन्दसि ६.३.१०८|६.३.१०८|६.३.१०८ पथि च च्छन्दसि
This substitution of का and कव for कु takes place in the छन्दस् (Vedas) before पथ।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.109|6.3.109 pRShodaraadiini yathopadiShTam|pRShodaraadiini yathopadiShTam|pRShodaraadiini yathopadiShTam 6.3.109|पृषोदरादीनि यथोपदिष्टम्|पृषोदरादीनि यथोपदिष्टम् ६.३.१०९|६.३.१०९|६.३.१०९ पृषोदरादीनि यथोपदिष्टम्
The elision, augment and mutation of letters to be seen in पृषोदर etc. though not found taught in the treatises of Grammar, are valid to that extent and in the mode, as taught by the usage of the sages.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.110|6.3.110 saMkhyaavisaayapuurvasyaahnasyaahannanyatarasyaaM NGau|saMkhyaavisaayapuurvasyaahnasyaahannanyatarasyaaM NGau|saMkhyaavisaayapuurvasyaahnasyaahannanyatarasyaaM NGau 6.3.110|संख्याविसायपूर्वस्याह्नस्याहन्नन्यतरस्यां ङौ|संख्याविसायपूर्वस्याह्नस्याहन्नन्यतरस्यां ङौ ६.३.११०|६.३.११०|६.३.११० संख्याविसायपूर्वस्याह्नस्याहन्नन्यतरस्यां ङौ
अहन् may optionally be substituted for अह्न in the Locative -7th case singular when a numeral or वि or साय precede it.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.111|6.3.111 Dhralope puurvasya diirgho.aNaH|Dhralope puurvasya diirgho.aNaH|Dhralope puurvasya diirgho.aNaH 6.3.111|ढ्रलोपे पूर्वस्य दीर्घोऽणः|ढ्रलोपे पूर्वस्य दीर्घोऽणः ६.३.१११|६.३.१११|६.३.१११ ढ्रलोपे पूर्वस्य दीर्घोऽणः
When ढ् or र् is elided for the preceding अ , इ and उ a corresponding long vowel is substituted.<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.112|6.3.112 sahivahorodavarNasya|sahivahorodavarNasya|sahivahorodavarNasya 6.3.112|सहिवहोरोदवर्णस्य|सहिवहोरोदवर्णस्य ६.३.११२|६.३.११२|६.३.११२ सहिवहोरोदवर्णस्य
When ढ् or र् are elided, there is the substitution of ओ or आ of the verbs सह् and वह्।<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.113|6.3.113 saaDhyai saaDhvaa saaDheti nigame|saaDhyai saaDhvaa saaDheti nigame|saaDhyai saaDhvaa saaDheti nigame 6.3.113|साढ्यै साढ्वा साढेति निगमे|साढ्यै साढ्वा साढेति निगमे ६.३.११३|६.३.११३|६.३.११३ साढ्यै साढ्वा साढेति निगमे
1. साढ्यै 2. साढ्वा and 3. साढा are irregularly formed in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: Some Substitution

6.3.114|6.3.114 saMhitaayaam|saMhitaayaam|saMhitaayaam 6.3.114|संहितायाम्|संहितायाम् ६.३.११४|६.३.११४|६.३.११४ संहितायाम्
In the following sūtras up to the end of the पाद are to be supplied the words 'in an uninterrupted flow of speech'.<br><br>Terms: संहितायाम्

6.3.115|6.3.115 karNe laxaNasyaaviShTaaShTapancamaNibhinnaChinnaChidrasruvasvastikasya|karNe laxaNasyaaviShTaaShTapancamaNibhinnaChinnaChidrasruvasvastikasya|karNe laxaNasyaaviShTaaShTapancamaNibhinnaChinnaChidrasruvasvastikasya 6.3.115|कर्णे लक्षणस्याविष्टाष्टपञ्चमणिभिन्नछिन्नछिद्रस्रुवस्वस्तिकस्य|कर्णे लक्षणस्याविष्टाष्टपञ्चमणिभिन्नछिन्नछिद्रस्रुवस्वस्तिकस्य ६.३.११५|६.३.११५|६.३.११५ कर्णे लक्षणस्याविष्टाष्टपञ्चमणिभिन्नछिन्नछिद्रस्रुवस्वस्तिकस्य
Before कर्ण there is the substitution of a long vowel for the final of the preceding word when it denotes a proprietorship mark or the ears of cattle, but not when the words 1. विष्ट 2. अष्टन् 3. पञ्चन् 4. मणि 5. भिन्न 6. छिन्न 7. छिद्र 8. स्रुव and 9. स्वस्तिक।<br><br>Terms: संहिता changes

6.3.116|6.3.116 nahivRtivRShivyadhiruchisahitaniShu kvau|nahivRtivRShivyadhiruchisahitaniShu kvau|nahivRtivRShivyadhiruchisahitaniShu kvau 6.3.116|नहिवृतिवृषिव्यधिरुचिसहितनिषु क्वौ|नहिवृतिवृषिव्यधिरुचिसहितनिषु क्वौ ६.३.११६|६.३.११६|६.३.११६ नहिवृतिवृषिव्यधिरुचिसहितनिषु क्वौ
A long vowel is substituted for the final vowel of the preceding word, before the verbs 1. नह् 2. वृत् 3. वृष् 4. व्यध् 5. रुच् 6. सह् and 7. तन् when these roots take the affix क्वि।<br><br>Terms: संहिता changes

6.3.117|6.3.117 vanagiryoH saMJNaayaaM koTarakiMshulakaadiinaam|vanagiryoH saMJNaayaaM koTarakiMshulakaadiinaam|vanagiryoH saMJNaayaaM koTarakiMshulakaadiinaam 6.3.117|वनगिर्योः संज्ञायां कोटरकिंशुलकादीनाम्|वनगिर्योः संज्ञायां कोटरकिंशुलकादीनाम् ६.३.११७|६.३.११७|६.३.११७ वनगिर्योः संज्ञायां कोटरकिंशुलकादीनाम्
For the final vowel of कोटर etc. a long vowel is substituted before वन and also of किंशुलक etc. before गिरि when the compound is a name.<br><br>Terms: संहिता changes

6.3.118|6.3.118 vale|vale|vale 6.3.118|वले|वले ६.३.११८|६.३.११८|६.३.११८ वले
The final of the preceding word is lengthened before the affix वल।<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.119|6.3.119 matau bahvacho.anajiraadiinaam|matau bahvacho.anajiraadiinaam|matau bahvacho.anajiraadiinaam 6.3.119|मतौ बह्वचोऽनजिरादीनाम्|मतौ बह्वचोऽनजिरादीनाम् ६.३.११९|६.३.११९|६.३.११९ मतौ बह्वचोऽनजिरादीनाम्
The final vowel of a word consisting of more than two syllables in lengthened before the affix मत् when it is a name, but not of the words अजिर् etc.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.120|6.3.120 sharaadiinaaM cha|sharaadiinaaM cha|sharaadiinaaM cha 6.3.120|शरादीनां च|शरादीनां च ६.३.१२०|६.३.१२०|६.३.१२० शरादीनां च
The final vowel of शर etc. is lengthened before मत् when it is a name.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.121|6.3.121 ikaH vahe apiiloH|ikaH vahe apiiloH|ikaH vahe apiiloH 6.3.121|इकः वहे अपीलोः|इकः वहे अपीलोः ६.३.१२१|६.३.१२१|६.३.१२१ इकः वहे अपीलोः
The final इ and the उ of a wod with the exception of पीलु are lengthened before वह।<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.122|6.3.122 upasargasya ghaNJyamanuShye bahulam|upasargasya ghaNJyamanuShye bahulam|upasargasya ghaNJyamanuShye bahulam 6.3.122|उपसर्गस्य घञ्यमनुष्ये बहुलम्|उपसर्गस्य घञ्यमनुष्ये बहुलम् ६.३.१२२|६.३.१२२|६.३.१२२ उपसर्गस्य घञ्यमनुष्ये बहुलम्
The final vowel of a preposition is diversely lengthened before a word formed by the कृत् affix घञ् but not when the compound denotes a human being.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.123|6.3.123 ikaH kaashe|ikaH kaashe|ikaH kaashe 6.3.123|इकः काशे|इकः काशे ६.३.१२३|६.३.१२३|६.३.१२३ इकः काशे
A preposition ending in इ or उ lengthens its final before काश।<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.124|6.3.124 dasti|dasti|dasti 6.3.124|दस्ति|दस्ति ६.३.१२४|६.३.१२४|६.३.१२४ दस्ति
A preposition ending in इ or उ lengthens its final before the verb दा when the latter is changed to त।<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.125|6.3.125 aShTanaH saMJNaayaam|aShTanaH saMJNaayaam|aShTanaH saMJNaayaam 6.3.125|अष्टनः संज्ञायाम्|अष्टनः संज्ञायाम् ६.३.१२५|६.३.१२५|६.३.१२५ अष्टनः संज्ञायाम्
A long vowel is substituted for the final of अष्टन् before a second member, when the compound is a Name.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.126|6.3.126 Chandasi cha|Chandasi cha|Chandasi cha 6.3.126|छन्दसि च|छन्दसि च ६.३.१२६|६.३.१२६|६.३.१२६ छन्दसि च
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) also, the long vowel is substituted for the final of अष्टन् before a second member.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.127|6.3.127 chiteH kapi|chiteH kapi|chiteH kapi 6.3.127|चितेः कपि|चितेः कपि ६.३.१२७|६.३.१२७|६.३.१२७ चितेः कपि
The final word of चिति is lengthened before the affix कप्।<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.128|6.3.128 vishvasya vasuraaToH|vishvasya vasuraaToH|vishvasya vasuraaToH 6.3.128|विश्वस्य वसुराटोः|विश्वस्य वसुराटोः ६.३.१२८|६.३.१२८|६.३.१२८ विश्वस्य वसुराटोः
The final vowel of विश्व is lengthened before वसु and राट् (the form assumed by राज्).<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.129|6.3.129 nare saMJNaayaam|nare saMJNaayaam|nare saMJNaayaam 6.3.129|नरे संज्ञायाम्|नरे संज्ञायाम् ६.३.१२९|६.३.१२९|६.३.१२९ नरे संज्ञायाम्
The final vowel of विश्व is lengthened before नर when the compound is a Name.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.130|6.3.130 mitre charShau|mitre charShau|mitre charShau 6.3.130|मित्रे चर्षौ|मित्रे चर्षौ ६.३.१३०|६.३.१३०|६.३.१३० मित्रे चर्षौ
The final vowel of विश्व is lengthened before मित्र when it is the name of a ऋषि।<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.131|6.3.131 mantre somaashvendriyavishvadevyasya matau|mantre somaashvendriyavishvadevyasya matau|mantre somaashvendriyavishvadevyasya matau 6.3.131|मन्त्रे सोमाश्वेन्द्रियविश्वदेव्यस्य मतौ|मन्त्रे सोमाश्वेन्द्रियविश्वदेव्यस्य मतौ ६.३.१३१|६.३.१३१|६.३.१३१ मन्त्रे सोमाश्वेन्द्रियविश्वदेव्यस्य मतौ
In a मन्त्र the final vowels of 1. सोम 2. अश्व 3. इन्द्रिय and 4. विश्वदेव्य are lengthened when the affix मतुप् follows.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.132|6.3.132 oShadheshcha vibhaktaavaprathamaayaam|oShadheshcha vibhaktaavaprathamaayaam|oShadheshcha vibhaktaavaprathamaayaam 6.3.132|ओषधेश्च विभक्तावप्रथमायाम्|ओषधेश्च विभक्तावप्रथमायाम् ६.३.१३२|६.३.१३२|६.३.१३२ ओषधेश्च विभक्तावप्रथमायाम्
In a मन्त्र the final of ओषधि is lengthened before the case-endings but not in the Nominative 1st-Case.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.133|6.3.133 Rchi tunughamaxutankutroruShyaaNaam|Rchi tunughamaxutankutroruShyaaNaam|Rchi tunughamaxutankutroruShyaaNaam 6.3.133|ऋचि तुनुघमक्षुतङ्कुत्रोरुष्याणाम्|ऋचि तुनुघमक्षुतङ्कुत्रोरुष्याणाम् ६.३.१३३|६.३.१३३|६.३.१३३ ऋचि तुनुघमक्षुतङ्कुत्रोरुष्याणाम्
In the ऋग्वेद the finals of the particles 1. तु 2. नु 3. घ 4. मक्षु , the tense-affix तङ् , कु the ending त्र and the word उरुष्य are lengthened.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.134|6.3.134 ikaH suNJi|ikaH suNJi|ikaH suNJi 6.3.134|इकः सुञि|इकः सुञि ६.३.१३४|६.३.१३४|६.३.१३४ इकः सुञि
In a मन्त्र the finals of the preceding member ending in इ or उ are lengthened before the particle सु।<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.135|6.3.135 dvyacho.atastiNGaH|dvyacho.atastiNGaH|dvyacho.atastiNGaH 6.3.135|द्व्यचोऽतस्तिङः|द्व्यचोऽतस्तिङः ६.३.१३५|६.३.१३५|६.३.१३५ द्व्यचोऽतस्तिङः
A tense affix ending in अ is lengthened in the ऋग्वेद when the verb consists of two syllables.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.136|6.3.136 nipaatasya cha|nipaatasya cha|nipaatasya cha 6.3.136|निपातस्य च|निपातस्य च ६.३.१३६|६.३.१३६|६.३.१३६ निपातस्य च
In the ऋग्वेद the final of a particle is lengthened.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.137|6.3.137 anyeShaamapi dRshyate|anyeShaamapi dRshyate|anyeShaamapi dRshyate 6.3.137|अन्येषामपि दृश्यते|अन्येषामपि दृश्यते ६.३.१३७|६.३.१३७|६.३.१३७ अन्येषामपि दृश्यते
The elongation of the final is to be found in other words also.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.138|6.3.138 chau|chau|chau 6.3.138|चौ|चौ ६.३.१३८|६.३.१३८|६.३.१३८ चौ
The final vowel of the preceding member is lengthened before अञ्च when it assumes the form च having lost its nasal and the vowel.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.3.139|6.3.139 samprasaaraNasya|samprasaaraNasya|samprasaaraNasya 6.3.139|सम्प्रसारणस्य|सम्प्रसारणस्य ६.३.१३९|६.३.१३९|६.३.१३९ सम्प्रसारणस्य
The vowel substituted for a semi-vowel is lengthened when it stands as the first member of a compound.<br><br>Terms: संहिता Lengthening

6.4.1|6.4.1 angasya|angasya|angasya 6.4.1|अङ्गस्य|अङ्गस्य ६.४.१|६.४.१|६.४.१ अङ्गस्य
Whatever will be taught here after up to the end of the 7th अध्याय is consequent upon the अङ्ग (stem).<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.2|6.4.2 halaH|halaH|halaH 6.4.2|हलः|हलः ६.४.२|६.४.२|६.४.२ हलः
The long vowel is substituted for a vocalised half-vowel अ , इ and उ at the end of a अङ्ग (stem), when it is preceded by a consonant which is a portion of the stem.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.3|6.4.3 naami|naami|naami 6.4.3|नामि|नामि ६.४.३|६.४.३|६.४.३ नामि
The long vowel is substituted for the final of the stem before the Genitive 6th-Case plural affix नाम् (having the augment नुट्).<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.4|6.4.4 na tisRchatasR|na tisRchatasR|na tisRchatasR 6.4.4|न तिसृचतसृ|न तिसृचतसृ ६.४.४|६.४.४|६.४.४ न तिसृचतसृ
The finals of तिसृ and चतसृ are not lengthened before नाम् (having the augment नुट्).<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.5|6.4.5 Chandasyubhayathaa|Chandasyubhayathaa|Chandasyubhayathaa 6.4.5|छन्दस्युभयथा|छन्दस्युभयथा ६.४.५|६.४.५|६.४.५ छन्दस्युभयथा
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the finals of तिसृ and चतसृ are found in both ways, before the Genitive 6th-Case plural नाम्।<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.6|6.4.6 nR cha|nR cha|nR cha 6.4.6|नृ च|नृ च ६.४.६|६.४.६|६.४.६ नृ च
So also नृ before the Genitive 6th-Case plural नाम् is optionally lengthened.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.7|6.4.7 nopadhaayaaH|nopadhaayaaH|nopadhaayaaH 6.4.7|नोपधायाः|नोपधायाः ६.४.७|६.४.७|६.४.७ नोपधायाः
In a अङ्ग (stem) ending in न् the preceding vowel is lengthened before the affix नाम् ।<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.8|6.4.8 sarvanaamasthaane chaasambuddhau|sarvanaamasthaane chaasambuddhau|sarvanaamasthaane chaasambuddhau 6.4.8|सर्वनामस्थाने चासम्बुद्धौ|सर्वनामस्थाने चासम्बुद्धौ ६.४.८|६.४.८|६.४.८ सर्वनामस्थाने चासम्बुद्धौ
In a अङ्ग (stem) ending in न् the preceding vowel is lengthened in strong cases with the exception of the Vocative Case singular.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.9|6.4.9 vaa Shapuurvasya nigame|vaa Shapuurvasya nigame|vaa Shapuurvasya nigame 6.4.9|वा षपूर्वस्य निगमे|वा षपूर्वस्य निगमे ६.४.९|६.४.९|६.४.९ वा षपूर्वस्य निगमे
The lengthening of the penultimate vowel of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in न् , before the affixes of the strong-case, is optional in the छन्दस् (Vedas) when ष precedes such a vowel.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.10|6.4.10 saantamahataH saMyogasya|saantamahataH saMyogasya|saantamahataH saMyogasya 6.4.10|सान्तमहतः संयोगस्य|सान्तमहतः संयोगस्य ६.४.१०|६.४.१०|६.४.१० सान्तमहतः संयोगस्य
In the strong cases with the exception of Vocative Case singular, the penultimate vowel is lengthened in the case of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in स् with a Nasal consonant preceding it, and of महत्।<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.11|6.4.11 aptRntRchsvasRnaptRneShTRtvaShTRxattRhotRpotRprashaastRRNaam|aptRntRchsvasRnaptRneShTRtvaShTRxattRhotRpotRprashaastRRNaam|aptRntRchsvasRnaptRneShTRtvaShTRxattRhotRpotRprashaastRRNaam 6.4.11|अप्तृन्तृच्स्वसृनप्तृनेष्टृत्वष्टृक्षत्तृहोतृपोतृप्रशास्तॄणाम्|अप्तृन्तृच्स्वसृनप्तृनेष्टृत्वष्टृक्षत्तृहोतृपोतृप्रशास्तॄणाम् ६.४.११|६.४.११|६.४.११ अप्तृन्तृच्स्वसृनप्तृनेष्टृत्वष्टृक्षत्तृहोतृपोतृप्रशास्तॄणाम्
In the strong cases, with the exception of the Vocative Case singular, the penultimate vowel is lengthened in अप् in stems formed by तृन् and तृच् affixes and in 1. स्वसृ 2. नप्तृ 3. नेष्टृ 4. त्वष्टृ 5. क्षत्तृ 6. होतृ 7. पोतृ and 9. प्रशास्तॄ।<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.12|6.4.12 inhanpuuShaaryamNaaM shau|inhanpuuShaaryamNaaM shau|inhanpuuShaaryamNaaM shau 6.4.12|इन्हन्पूषार्यम्णां शौ|इन्हन्पूषार्यम्णां शौ ६.४.१२|६.४.१२|६.४.१२ इन्हन्पूषार्यम्णां शौ
The penultimate vowel is lengthened before the affix शि (Nominative 1st-Case and Accusative -2nd case plural) when the अङ्ग (stem) ends in इन् or हन् or पूषन् or अर्यमन्।<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.13|6.4.13 sau cha|sau cha|sau cha 6.4.13|सौ च|सौ च ६.४.१३|६.४.१३|६.४.१३ सौ च
The penultimate vowels of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in इन् , हन् , पूषन् or अर्यमन् are lengthened before the सु of the Nominative 1st-Case singular but not in Vocative Case singular.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.14|6.4.14 atvasantasya chaadhaatoH|atvasantasya chaadhaatoH|atvasantasya chaadhaatoH 6.4.14|अत्वसन्तस्य चाधातोः|अत्वसन्तस्य चाधातोः ६.४.१४|६.४.१४|६.४.१४ अत्वसन्तस्य चाधातोः
In the Nominative 1st-Case singular (with the exception of the Vocative Case singular) the penultimate vowel is lengthened in a अङ्ग (stem) ending in अतु and अस् when the consonant (अस्) does not belong to a root.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.15|6.4.15 anunaasikasya kvijhaloH kNGiti|anunaasikasya kvijhaloH kNGiti|anunaasikasya kvijhaloH kNGiti 6.4.15|अनुनासिकस्य क्विझलोः क्ङिति|अनुनासिकस्य क्विझलोः क्ङिति ६.४.१५|६.४.१५|६.४.१५ अनुनासिकस्य क्विझलोः क्ङिति
The penultimate vowel of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in a nasal is lengthened before the affix क्वि and before an affix having an indicatory क् or ङ् which begins with a consonant other than a semi-vowel or a nasal.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.16|6.4.16 ajjhanagamaaM sani|ajjhanagamaaM sani|ajjhanagamaaM sani 6.4.16|अज्झनगमां सनि|अज्झनगमां सनि ६.४.१६|६.४.१६|६.४.१६ अज्झनगमां सनि
The lengthening of the vowel takes place in the case of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in a vowel, as well as of हन् and गम् when the Desiderative affix सन् being झलादि (i.e. not taking the augment इट्) follows.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.17|6.4.17 tanotervibhaaShaa|tanotervibhaaShaa|tanotervibhaaShaa 6.4.17|तनोतेर्विभाषा|तनोतेर्विभाषा ६.४.१७|६.४.१७|६.४.१७ तनोतेर्विभाषा
the lengthened of the अङ्ग (stem) of तन् is optional before the Desiderative सन् when it does not take the augment इट्।<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.18|6.4.18 kramashcha ktvi|kramashcha ktvi|kramashcha ktvi 6.4.18|क्रमश्च क्त्वि|क्रमश्च क्त्वि ६.४.१८|६.४.१८|६.४.१८ क्रमश्च क्त्वि
The penultimate of क्रम is optionally lengthened before the affix क्त्वा when it is without the augment इट्।<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.19|6.4.19 chChvoH shuuDanunaasike cha|chChvoH shuuDanunaasike cha|chChvoH shuuDanunaasike cha 6.4.19|च्छ्वोः शूडनुनासिके च|च्छ्वोः शूडनुनासिके च ६.४.१९|६.४.१९|६.४.१९ च्छ्वोः शूडनुनासिके च
For च्छ (including the augment तुक्) is substituted श् and for व् is substituted ऊठ् before an affix beginning with a nasal as well as before क्वि and झलादि ङित् and कित् affixes -- अनुनासिकस्य क्विझलोः क्ङिति ६.४.१५.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.20|6.4.20 jvaratvarashrivyavimavaamupadhaayaashcha|jvaratvarashrivyavimavaamupadhaayaashcha|jvaratvarashrivyavimavaamupadhaayaashcha 6.4.20|ज्वरत्वरश्रिव्यविमवामुपधायाश्च|ज्वरत्वरश्रिव्यविमवामुपधायाश्च ६.४.२०|६.४.२०|६.४.२० ज्वरत्वरश्रिव्यविमवामुपधायाश्च
In 1. ज्वर 2. त्वर् 3. श्रिव् 4. अव and 5. मव् before the above mentioned affixes (क्वि and झलादि ङित् and कित् affixes -- अनुनासिकस्य क्विझलोः क्ङिति ६.४.१५) there is the single substitution of ऊठ् for the and the vowel preceding the final consonant.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.21|6.4.21 raallopaH|raallopaH|raallopaH 6.4.21|राल्लोपः|राल्लोपः ६.४.२१|६.४.२१|६.४.२१ राल्लोपः
After र् there is the elision of छ् and व् before क्वि and झलादि ङित् and कित् affixes -- अनुनासिकस्य क्विझलोः क्ङिति ६.४.१५.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

6.4.22|6.4.22 asiddhavadatraabhaat‌|asiddhavadatraabhaat‌|asiddhavadatraabhaat‌ 6.4.22|असिद्धवदत्राभात्‌|असिद्धवदत्राभात्‌ ६.४.२२|६.४.२२|६.४.२२ असिद्धवदत्राभात्‌
The change which is a अङ्ग (stem) will undergo by the application of any of the rules from this sūtra up to भस्य ६.४.१२९, is to be considered as not to have taken effect when we have to apply any other rule of this very section ६.४.२३ to ६.४.१२९.<br><br>Terms: 

6.4.23|6.4.23 shnaannalopaH|shnaannalopaH|shnaannalopaH 6.4.23|श्नान्नलोपः|श्नान्नलोपः ६.४.२३|६.४.२३|६.४.२३ श्नान्नलोपः
After न which is added to the roots of the रुधादिगणः (7th Conjugation) as a गणविकरण - श्नम् (characteristic), there is the elision of the following न।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.24|6.4.24 aniditaaM hala upadhaayaaH kNGiti|aniditaaM hala upadhaayaaH kNGiti|aniditaaM hala upadhaayaaH kNGiti 6.4.24|अनिदितां हल उपधायाः क्ङिति|अनिदितां हल उपधायाः क्ङिति ६.४.२४|६.४.२४|६.४.२४ अनिदितां हल उपधायाः क्ङिति
In a root-अङ्ग (stem) ending in a consonant preceded by न् - this न not being added to the root owing to its having an indicatory इ -- इदितो नुम् धातोः ७.१.५८, the न् is elided when an affix having an indicatory क् or ङ् follows.<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.25|6.4.25 danshasanjasvanjaaM shapi|danshasanjasvanjaaM shapi|danshasanjasvanjaaM shapi 6.4.25|दन्शसञ्जस्वञ्जां शपि|दन्शसञ्जस्वञ्जां शपि ६.४.२५|६.४.२५|६.४.२५ दन्शसञ्जस्वञ्जां शपि
The nasal of 1. दंश् 2. संज् and 3. स्वञ्ज is elided before the गणविकरण शप् of the roots of the भ्वादिगणः (1st Conjugation).<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.26|6.4.26 ranjeshcha|ranjeshcha|ranjeshcha 6.4.26|रञ्जेश्च|रञ्जेश्च ६.४.२६|६.४.२६|६.४.२६ रञ्जेश्च
The nasal of रञ्ज् is also elided before the गणविकरण शप्।<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.27|6.4.27 ghaNJi cha bhaavakaraNayoH|ghaNJi cha bhaavakaraNayoH|ghaNJi cha bhaavakaraNayoH 6.4.27|घञि च भावकरणयोः|घञि च भावकरणयोः ६.४.२७|६.४.२७|६.४.२७ घञि च भावकरणयोः
The penultimate nasal of रञ्ज् is elided before घञ् when the word formed with it expresses a state or an instrument.<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.28|6.4.28 syado jave|syado jave|syado jave 6.4.28|स्यदो जवे|स्यदो जवे ६.४.२८|६.४.२८|६.४.२८ स्यदो जवे
The word स्यद् is formed by घञ् in the sense of 'speed'.<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.29|6.4.29 avodaidhaudmaprashrathahimashrathaaH|avodaidhaudmaprashrathahimashrathaaH|avodaidhaudmaprashrathahimashrathaaH 6.4.29|अवोदैधौद्मप्रश्रथहिमश्रथाः|अवोदैधौद्मप्रश्रथहिमश्रथाः ६.४.२९|६.४.२९|६.४.२९ अवोदैधौद्मप्रश्रथहिमश्रथाः
1. अवोद 2. एध 3. ओद्म 4. प्रश्रथ and 5. हिमश्रथ are irregularly formed by the elision.<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.30|6.4.30 naanceH puujaayaam|naanceH puujaayaam|naanceH puujaayaam 6.4.30|नाञ्चेः पूजायाम्|नाञ्चेः पूजायाम् ६.४.३०|६.४.३०|६.४.३० नाञ्चेः पूजायाम्
The nasal of अञ्च् is not elided when meaning is to honour.<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.31|6.4.31 ktvi skandisyandoH|ktvi skandisyandoH|ktvi skandisyandoH 6.4.31|क्त्वि स्कन्दिस्यन्दोः|क्त्वि स्कन्दिस्यन्दोः ६.४.३१|६.४.३१|६.४.३१ क्त्वि स्कन्दिस्यन्दोः
स्कन्दि and स्यन्द retain their nasal before the affix क्त।<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.32|6.4.32 jaantanashaaM vibhaaShaa|jaantanashaaM vibhaaShaa|jaantanashaaM vibhaaShaa 6.4.32|जान्तनशां विभाषा|जान्तनशां विभाषा ६.४.३२|६.४.३२|६.४.३२ जान्तनशां विभाषा
The nasal may be optionally elided before क्त्वा in a root ending in ज् and in नश्।<br><br>Terms: Nasal Elision

6.4.33|6.4.33 bhanjeshcha chiNi|bhanjeshcha chiNi|bhanjeshcha chiNi 6.4.33|भञ्जेश्च चिणि|भञ्जेश्च चिणि ६.४.३३|६.४.३३|६.४.३३ भञ्जेश्च चिणि
The nasal may be optionally elided in भञ्ज before the 3rd person passive of the Aorist in चिण् (ई).<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.34|6.4.34 shaasa idaNGhaloH|shaasa idaNGhaloH|shaasa idaNGhaloH 6.4.34|शास इदङ्हलोः|शास इदङ्हलोः ६.४.३४|६.४.३४|६.४.३४ शास इदङ्हलोः
Before the Aorist in अङ् and before an affix beginning with a consonant having an indicatory क् or ङ् there is the substitution of ई for the vowel of शास्।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.35|6.4.35 shaa hau|shaa hau|shaa hau 6.4.35|शा हौ|शा हौ ६.४.३५|६.४.३५|६.४.३५ शा हौ
Before the Imperative affix हि , शा is substituted for शास्।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.36|6.4.36 hanterjaH|hanterjaH|hanterjaH 6.4.36|हन्तेर्जः|हन्तेर्जः ६.४.३६|६.४.३६|६.४.३६ हन्तेर्जः
ज is substituted for हन् before the Imperative affix हि।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.37|6.4.37 anudaattopadeshavanatitanotyaadiinaamanunaasikalopo jhali kNGiti|anudaattopadeshavanatitanotyaadiinaamanunaasikalopo jhali kNGiti|anudaattopadeshavanatitanotyaadiinaamanunaasikalopo jhali kNGiti 6.4.37|अनुदात्तोपदेशवनतितनोत्यादीनामनुनासिकलोपो झलि क्ङिति|अनुदात्तोपदेशवनतितनोत्यादीनामनुनासिकलोपो झलि क्ङिति ६.४.३७|६.४.३७|६.४.३७ अनुदात्तोपदेशवनतितनोत्यादीनामनुनासिकलोपो झलि क्ङिति
The final nasal of those roots which in the धातुपाठ have an accented root-vowel, as well as of वन , तन etc. (तनादिगणः -8th Conjugation) is elided before an affix beginning with a consonant (except a semi-vowel or nasal) when these have an indicatory क् or ङ्।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.38|6.4.38 vaa lyapi|vaa lyapi|vaa lyapi 6.4.38|वा ल्यपि|वा ल्यपि ६.४.३८|६.४.३८|६.४.३८ वा ल्यपि
The nasal above the roots (i.e. अनुदात्त ending in a nasal and वन and तनादि) is optionally elided before the Absolutive affix ल्यप्।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.39|6.4.39 na ktichi diirghashcha|na ktichi diirghashcha|na ktichi diirghashcha 6.4.39|न क्तिचि दीर्घश्च|न क्तिचि दीर्घश्च ६.४.३९|६.४.३९|६.४.३९ न क्तिचि दीर्घश्च
Before the affix क्तिच् the above roots (वन and तनादि) neither drop their nasal nor lengthen their root-vowel.<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.40|6.4.40 gamaH kvau|gamaH kvau|gamaH kvau 6.4.40|गमः क्वौ|गमः क्वौ ६.४.४०|६.४.४०|६.४.४० गमः क्वौ
The nasal of गम् is always elided before क्वि।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.41|6.4.41 viDvanoranunaasikasyaat‌|viDvanoranunaasikasyaat‌|viDvanoranunaasikasyaat‌ 6.4.41|विड्वनोरनुनासिकस्यात्‌|विड्वनोरनुनासिकस्यात्‌ ६.४.४१|६.४.४१|६.४.४१ विड्वनोरनुनासिकस्यात्‌
A stem ending in a nasal and followed by the affix विट् or वन् always substitutes for long आ for its nasal.<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.42|6.4.42 janasanakhanaaM sanJaloH|janasanakhanaaM sanJaloH|janasanakhanaaM sanJaloH 6.4.42|जनसनखनां सञ्झलोः|जनसनखनां सञ्झलोः ६.४.४२|६.४.४२|६.४.४२ जनसनखनां सञ्झलोः
The long आ is substituted for the final of जन् , सन् and खन् before the consonant beginning Desiderative affix सन् and before any other affix beginning with a इल् consonant which has an indicatory क् or ङ्।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.43|6.4.43 ye vibhaaShaa|ye vibhaaShaa|ye vibhaaShaa 6.4.43|ये विभाषा|ये विभाषा ६.४.४३|६.४.४३|६.४.४३ ये विभाषा
There is optionally the substitution of long आ for the finals of जन् , सन् and खन् before the affix beginning with य and marked with an indicatory क् or ङ्।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.44|6.4.44 tanoteryaki|tanoteryaki|tanoteryaki 6.4.44|तनोतेर्यकि|तनोतेर्यकि ६.४.४४|६.४.४४|६.४.४४ तनोतेर्यकि
The long आ is optionally substituted for the final of तन् before the Passive characteristic यक्।<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.45|6.4.45 sanaH ktichi lopashchaasyaanyatarasyaam|sanaH ktichi lopashchaasyaanyatarasyaam|sanaH ktichi lopashchaasyaanyatarasyaam 6.4.45|सनः क्तिचि लोपश्चास्यान्यतरस्याम्|सनः क्तिचि लोपश्चास्यान्यतरस्याम् ६.४.४५|६.४.४५|६.४.४५ सनः क्तिचि लोपश्चास्यान्यतरस्याम्
The long आ is optionally substituted for the final of सन् before the affix क्तिच् and there is also optional elision of the nasal.<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.46|6.4.46 aardhadhaatuke|aardhadhaatuke|aardhadhaatuke 6.4.46|आर्धधातुके|आर्धधातुके ६.४.४६|६.४.४६|६.४.४६ आर्धधातुके
From this up to युप्लुवोर्दीर्घश्छन्दसि ६.४.६८, inclusive, is always to be supplied the words ' before an affix called आर्धधातुक -- आर्द्धधातुकं शेषः ३.४.११४ etc.'<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.47|6.4.47 bhrasjo ropadhayoH ramanyatarasyaam‌|bhrasjo ropadhayoH ramanyatarasyaam‌|bhrasjo ropadhayoH ramanyatarasyaam‌ 6.4.47|भ्रस्जो रोपधयोः रमन्यतरस्याम्‌|भ्रस्जो रोपधयोः रमन्यतरस्याम्‌ ६.४.४७|६.४.४७|६.४.४७ भ्रस्जो रोपधयोः रमन्यतरस्याम्‌
In the room of र् and the penultimate letter स् of the root भ्रस्ज , there is optionally the substitute रम् when an आर्धधातुक affix follows.<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.48|6.4.48 ato lopaH|ato lopaH|ato lopaH 6.4.48|अतो लोपः|अतो लोपः ६.४.४८|६.४.४८|६.४.४८ अतो लोपः
The अ standing at the end of a अङ्ग (stem) is elided before an आर्धधातुक affix.<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.49|6.4.49 yasya halaH|yasya halaH|yasya halaH 6.4.49|यस्य हलः|यस्य हलः ६.४.४९|६.४.४९|६.४.४९ यस्य हलः
When a consonant precedes the final य in a verbal अङ्ग (stem) this य is also elided before an आर्धधातुक affix.<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.50|6.4.50 kyasya vibhaaShaa|kyasya vibhaaShaa|kyasya vibhaaShaa 6.4.50|क्यस्य विभाषा|क्यस्य विभाषा ६.४.५०|६.४.५०|६.४.५० क्यस्य विभाषा
The elision of य of he Denominative अङ्ग (stem) (क्य) is optional when preceded by a consonant and followed by an आर्धधातुक affix.<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.51|6.4.51 NeraniTi|NeraniTi|NeraniTi 6.4.51|णेरनिटि|णेरनिटि ६.४.५१|६.४.५१|६.४.५१ णेरनिटि
The इ of the verbal अङ्ग (stem) formed with the affix णि is elided before an आर्धधातुक affix which does not take the augment इट् ।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.52|6.4.52 niShThaayaaM seTi|niShThaayaaM seTi|niShThaayaaM seTi 6.4.52|निष्ठायां सेटि|निष्ठायां सेटि ६.४.५२|६.४.५२|६.४.५२ निष्ठायां सेटि
The affix णि is elided before the affixes क्त and क्तवतु when these take the augment इट् ।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.53|6.4.53 janitaa mantre|janitaa mantre|janitaa mantre 6.4.53|जनिता मन्त्रे|जनिता मन्त्रे ६.४.५३|६.४.५३|६.४.५३ जनिता मन्त्रे
In a मन्त्र the word जनिता is formed irregularly by the elision of णि before the affix तृ with the augment इट् ।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.54|6.4.54 shamitaa yaJNe|shamitaa yaJNe|shamitaa yaJNe 6.4.54|शमिता यज्ञे|शमिता यज्ञे ६.४.५४|६.४.५४|६.४.५४ शमिता यज्ञे
शमिता is formed irregularly by the elision of णि before an इट् augmented affix when meaning a sacrificial act.<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.55|6.4.55 ayaamantaalvaayyetnviShNuShu|ayaamantaalvaayyetnviShNuShu|ayaamantaalvaayyetnviShNuShu 6.4.55|अयामन्ताल्वाय्येत्न्विष्णुषु|अयामन्ताल्वाय्येत्न्विष्णुषु ६.४.५५|६.४.५५|६.४.५५ अयामन्ताल्वाय्येत्न्विष्णुषु
अय् is substituted for the इ of णि before the affixes 1. आम् 2. अन्त 3. आलु 4. आय्य 5. इत्नु and 6. इष्णु।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.56|6.4.56 lyapi laghupuurvaat‌|lyapi laghupuurvaat‌|lyapi laghupuurvaat‌ 6.4.56|ल्यपि लघुपूर्वात्‌|ल्यपि लघुपूर्वात्‌ ६.४.५६|६.४.५६|६.४.५६ ल्यपि लघुपूर्वात्‌
अय् is substituted for the इ of णि before the Absolutive affix ल्यप् when the vowel preceding the इ is light.<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.57|6.4.57 vibhaaShaa.a.apaH|vibhaaShaa.a.apaH|vibhaaShaa.a.apaH 6.4.57|विभाषाऽऽपः|विभाषाऽऽपः ६.४.५७|६.४.५७|६.४.५७ विभाषाऽऽपः
अय् is optionally substituted for the इ of णि before the Absolutive affix ल्यप् , after the verb आप्।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.58|6.4.58 yupluvordiirghashChandasi|yupluvordiirghashChandasi|yupluvordiirghashChandasi 6.4.58|युप्लुवोर्दीर्घश्छन्दसि|युप्लुवोर्दीर्घश्छन्दसि ६.४.५८|६.४.५८|६.४.५८ युप्लुवोर्दीर्घश्छन्दसि
In यु and प्लु , long is substituted for उ in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.59|6.4.59 xiyaH|xiyaH|xiyaH 6.4.59|क्षियः|क्षियः ६.४.५९|६.४.५९|६.४.५९ क्षियः
A long is substituted for the इ of क्षि before the Absolutive affix ल्यप्।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.60|6.4.60 niShThaayaaM aNyadarthe|niShThaayaaM aNyadarthe|niShThaayaaM aNyadarthe 6.4.60|निष्ठायां अण्यदर्थे|निष्ठायां अण्यदर्थे ६.४.६०|६.४.६०|६.४.६० निष्ठायां अण्यदर्थे
A long is substituted for the इ in क्षि before the Past Participle in क्त when it is not in the sense of the future Passive Participle in ण्यत्।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.61|6.4.61 vaa.a.akroshadainyayoH|vaa.a.akroshadainyayoH|vaa.a.akroshadainyayoH 6.4.61|वाऽऽक्रोशदैन्ययोः|वाऽऽक्रोशदैन्ययोः ६.४.६१|६.४.६१|६.४.६१ वाऽऽक्रोशदैन्ययोः
The long is optionally substituted for the इ in क्षि before the Past Participle in क्त when it is not in the sense of the future Passive Participle in ण्यत् when the word means 'imprecation' or 'a miserable plight'.<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.62|6.4.62 syasichsiiyuTtaasiShu bhaavakarmaNorupadeshe.ajjhanagrahadRshaaM vaa chiNvadiT cha|syasichsiiyuTtaasiShu bhaavakarmaNorupadeshe.ajjhanagrahadRshaaM vaa chiNvadiT cha|syasichsiiyuTtaasiShu bhaavakarmaNorupadeshe.ajjhanagrahadRshaaM vaa chiNvadiT cha 6.4.62|स्यसिच्सीयुट्तासिषु भावकर्मणोरुपदेशेऽज्झनग्रहदृशां वा चिण्वदिट् च|स्यसिच्सीयुट्तासिषु भावकर्मणोरुपदेशेऽज्झनग्रहदृशां वा चिण्वदिट् च ६.४.६२|६.४.६२|६.४.६२ स्यसिच्सीयुट्तासिषु भावकर्मणोरुपदेशेऽज्झनग्रहदृशां वा चिण्वदिट् च
Before the affixes 1. स्य (First future and Conditional) 2. सिच् (S-Aorist) 3. सीयुद् (Benedictive) and 4. तासि (Periphrastic Future), when they are used in the भाव (Impersonal) and कर्म (Passive) voices 1. the verbal stems ending in a vowel in the Grammatical system of instruction (उपदेश), as well as the verbs 2. हन् 'to kill' 3. ग्रह् 'to seize' and 4. दृश् 'to see' are treated optionally in the same way as in the 3rd Person of the Passive Aorist in चिण् and when so treated, they have the augment इट् ।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.63|6.4.63 diiNGo yuDachi kNGiti|diiNGo yuDachi kNGiti|diiNGo yuDachi kNGiti 6.4.63|दीङो युडचि क्ङिति|दीङो युडचि क्ङिति ६.४.६३|६.४.६३|६.४.६३ दीङो युडचि क्ङिति
युट् is the augment of दीङ् of an आर्धधातुक affix beginning with a vowel and having an indicatory क् or ङ्।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.64|6.4.64 aato lopa iTi cha|aato lopa iTi cha|aato lopa iTi cha 6.4.64|आतो लोप इटि च|आतो लोप इटि च ६.४.६४|६.४.६४|६.४.६४ आतो लोप इटि च
The final आ of a root is elided before an आर्धधातुक affix with the augment इट् as well as when it begins with a vowel and has an indicatory क् or ङ्।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.65|6.4.65 iidyati|iidyati|iidyati 6.4.65|ईद्यति|ईद्यति ६.४.६५|६.४.६५|६.४.६५ ईद्यति
The final आ of a अङ्ग (stem) is changed into ई before the कृत् affix यत्।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.66|6.4.66 ghumaasthaagaapaajahaatisaaM hali|ghumaasthaagaapaajahaatisaaM hali|ghumaasthaagaapaajahaatisaaM hali 6.4.66|घुमास्थागापाजहातिसां हलि|घुमास्थागापाजहातिसां हलि ६.४.६६|६.४.६६|६.४.६६ घुमास्थागापाजहातिसां हलि
For the final of the roots of the form of दा and घा (घु), as well as for that of the roots 1. मा 2. स्था 3. गा 4. पा 5. हा (जुहाति) and 6. सा (सो), there is substituted ई before an आर्धधातुक affix beginning with a consonant which has an indicatory क् or ङ्।<br><br>Terms: आर्धधातुक changes

6.4.67|6.4.67 erliNGi|erliNGi|erliNGi 6.4.67|एर्लिङि|एर्लिङि ६.४.६७|६.४.६७|६.४.६७ एर्लिङि
ए is substituted for the आ of the above roots (1. मा 2. स्था 3. गा 4. पा 5. हा (जुहाति) and 6. सा (सो)) in the Benedictive Mood Active.<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.68|6.4.68 vaa.anyasya saMyogaadeH|vaa.anyasya saMyogaadeH|vaa.anyasya saMyogaadeH 6.4.68|वाऽन्यस्य संयोगादेः|वाऽन्यस्य संयोगादेः ६.४.६८|६.४.६८|६.४.६८ वाऽन्यस्य संयोगादेः
For the final आ of any other root than those mentioned in घुमास्थागापाजहातिसां हलि ६.४.६६, ए may optionally be substituted in the Benedictive active, when the root begins with a conjunct consonant.<br><br>Terms: अभीय Rules

6.4.69|6.4.69 na lyapi|na lyapi|na lyapi 6.4.69|न ल्यपि|न ल्यपि ६.४.६९|६.४.६९|६.४.६९ न ल्यपि
The ई substitution for आ under sūtra घुमास्थागापाजहातिसां हलि ६.४.६६ does not apply when the absolutive affix ल्यप् follows 1. मा 2. स्था 3. गा 4. पा 5. हा (जुहाति) 6. सा and 7. घु।<br><br>Terms: अ augment

6.4.70|6.4.70 mayateridanyatarasyaam|mayateridanyatarasyaam|mayateridanyatarasyaam 6.4.70|मयतेरिदन्यतरस्याम्|मयतेरिदन्यतरस्याम् ६.४.७०|६.४.७०|६.४.७० मयतेरिदन्यतरस्याम्
इ may optionally be substituted for the आ of मा (मयति) before ल्यप् ।<br><br>Terms: अ augment

6.4.71|6.4.71 luNGlaNGlRnkShvaDudaattaH|luNGlaNGlRnkShvaDudaattaH|luNGlaNGlRnkShvaDudaattaH 6.4.71|लुङ्लङ्लृङ्क्ष्वडुदात्तः|लुङ्लङ्लृङ्क्ष्वडुदात्तः ६.४.७१|६.४.७१|६.४.७१ लुङ्लङ्लृङ्क्ष्वडुदात्तः
अट् acutely accented (उदात्त) is the augment of the verbal अङ्ग (stem) in the Aorist, Imperfect and the Conditional.<br><br>Terms: अ augment

6.4.72|6.4.72 aaDajaadiinaam|aaDajaadiinaam|aaDajaadiinaam 6.4.72|आडजादीनाम्|आडजादीनाम् ६.४.७२|६.४.७२|६.४.७२ आडजादीनाम्
आट् acutely accented (उदात्त) is the augment of a verbal अङ्ग (stem) beginning with a vowel in the Aorist, Imperfect and the Conditional.<br><br>Terms: अ augment

6.4.73|6.4.73 Chandasyapi dRshyate|Chandasyapi dRshyate|Chandasyapi dRshyate 6.4.73|छन्दस्यपि दृश्यते|छन्दस्यपि दृश्यते ६.४.७३|६.४.७३|६.४.७३ छन्दस्यपि दृश्यते
The आट् augment is found in the छन्दस् (Vedas) also.<br><br>Terms: अ augment

6.4.74|6.4.74 na maaNGyoge|na maaNGyoge|na maaNGyoge 6.4.74|न माङ्योगे|न माङ्योगे ६.४.७४|६.४.७४|६.४.७४ न माङ्योगे
In connection with the prohibitive particle मा the augment अट् or आट् is not added in the Aorist, Imperfect and the Conditional.<br><br>Terms: अ augment

6.4.75|6.4.75 bahulaM ChandasyamaaNGyoge.api|bahulaM ChandasyamaaNGyoge.api|bahulaM ChandasyamaaNGyoge.api 6.4.75|बहुलं छन्दस्यमाङ्योगेऽपि|बहुलं छन्दस्यमाङ्योगेऽपि ६.४.७५|६.४.७५|६.४.७५ बहुलं छन्दस्यमाङ्योगेऽपि
There is diversity in the छन्दस् (Vedas) : the augment अट् or आट् is added even with मा and sometimes not added even there is no मा।<br><br>Terms: अ augment

6.4.76|6.4.76 irayo re|irayo re|irayo re 6.4.76|इरयो रे|इरयो रे ६.४.७६|६.४.७६|६.४.७६ इरयो रे
रे is diversely substituted for इरे in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: छन्दस्

6.4.77|6.4.77 achi shnudhaatubhruvaaM yvoriyaNGuvaNGau|achi shnudhaatubhruvaaM yvoriyaNGuvaNGau|achi shnudhaatubhruvaaM yvoriyaNGuvaNGau 6.4.77|अचि श्नुधातुभ्रुवां य्वोरियङुवङौ|अचि श्नुधातुभ्रुवां य्वोरियङुवङौ ६.४.७७|६.४.७७|६.४.७७ अचि श्नुधातुभ्रुवां य्वोरियङुवङौ
Before an affix beginning with a vowel there are substituted for उ of नु , the characteristic of the roots of the स्वादिगणः (5th Conjugation) for the final इ , ई , उ and ऊ of a root, as well as for ऊ of भ्रू , the इय् (for इ or ई) and उव् (for उ or ऊ).<br><br>Terms: इवङ्-उवङ्

6.4.78|6.4.78 abhyaasasyaasavarNe|abhyaasasyaasavarNe|abhyaasasyaasavarNe 6.4.78|अभ्यासस्यासवर्णे|अभ्यासस्यासवर्णे ६.४.७८|६.४.७८|६.४.७८ अभ्यासस्यासवर्णे
इवङ् and उवङ् are substituted for the इ and उ of a reduplicate, before a non-homogeneous vowel.<br><br>Terms: इवङ्-उवङ्

6.4.79|6.4.79 striyaaH|striyaaH|striyaaH 6.4.79|स्त्रियाः|स्त्रियाः ६.४.७९|६.४.७९|६.४.७९ स्त्रियाः
इवङ् is substituted for the ई of स्त्री before an affix beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: इवङ्-उवङ्

6.4.80|6.4.80 vaa.amshasoH|vaa.amshasoH|vaa.amshasoH 6.4.80|वाऽम्शसोः|वाऽम्शसोः ६.४.८०|६.४.८०|६.४.८० वाऽम्शसोः
The substitution of इवङ् for the ई of स्त्री is optional before the Accusative -2nd case-endings अम् and शस् (अस्).<br><br>Terms: इवङ्-उवङ्

6.4.81|6.4.81 iNo yaN|iNo yaN|iNo yaN 6.4.81|इणो यण्|इणो यण् ६.४.८१|६.४.८१|६.४.८१ इणो यण्
For the इ of the root इण् (एति) is substituted a semi-vowel (य) before the affix beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: इवङ्-उवङ्

6.4.82|6.4.82 eranekaacho.asaMyogapuurvasya|eranekaacho.asaMyogapuurvasya|eranekaacho.asaMyogapuurvasya 6.4.82|एरनेकाचोऽसंयोगपूर्वस्य|एरनेकाचोऽसंयोगपूर्वस्य ६.४.८२|६.४.८२|६.४.८२ एरनेकाचोऽसंयोगपूर्वस्य
A semi-vowel is substituted before an affix beginning with a vowel for the final of इ or ई of a root, not preceded by a conjunct consonant forming part of the root, when the अङ्ग (stem) is mono-syllabic.<br><br>Terms: इवङ्-उवङ्

6.4.83|6.4.83 oH supi|oH supi|oH supi 6.4.83|ओः सुपि|ओः सुपि ६.४.८३|६.४.८३|६.४.८३ ओः सुपि
When a case-affix beginning with a vowel follows, then the semi-vowel व् is substituted for the final ऊ of a अङ्ग (stem) containing more than one syllable if the अङ्ग (stem) ends with a verbal root ending in ऊ not preceded by a conjunct consonant forming part of the root.<br><br>Terms: Semi-vowel substitution

6.4.84|6.4.84 varShaabhvashcha|varShaabhvashcha|varShaabhvashcha 6.4.84|वर्षाभ्वश्च|वर्षाभ्वश्च ६.४.८४|६.४.८४|६.४.८४ वर्षाभ्वश्च
The semi-vowel व् is substituted for the ऊ of वर्षाभू also when a case-affix beginning with a vowel follows.<br><br>Terms: Semi-vowel substitution

6.4.85|6.4.85 na bhuusudhiyoH|na bhuusudhiyoH|na bhuusudhiyoH 6.4.85|न भूसुधियोः|न भूसुधियोः ६.४.८५|६.४.८५|६.४.८५ न भूसुधियोः
The semi-vowel substitution does not take place in the case of अङ्ग (stems) ending in भू or the word सुधी before affixes beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: Semi-vowel substitution

6.4.86|6.4.86 Chandasyubhayathaa|Chandasyubhayathaa|Chandasyubhayathaa 6.4.86|छन्दस्युभयथा|छन्दस्युभयथा ६.४.८६|६.४.८६|६.४.८६ छन्दस्युभयथा
In the छन्दस् (Vedas), in the case of a अङ्ग (stem) in भू or the word सुधी , are found sometimes the इवङ् and उवङ् and sometimes the semi-vowel substitution.<br><br>Terms: Semi-vowel substitution

6.4.87|6.4.87 hushnuvoH saarvadhaatuke|hushnuvoH saarvadhaatuke|hushnuvoH saarvadhaatuke 6.4.87|हुश्नुवोः सार्वधातुके|हुश्नुवोः सार्वधातुके ६.४.८७|६.४.८७|६.४.८७ हुश्नुवोः सार्वधातुके
The semi-vowel व् is substituted for the उ of हु and for that of नु (the characteristic of स्वादिगणः (5th Conjugation), before a सार्वधातुक affix -- तिङ्शित्सार्वधातुकम् ३.४.११३, beginning with a vowel when the अङ्ग (stem) consists of more than one syllable and the उ is not preceded by a conjunct consonant.<br><br>Terms: Semi-vowel substitution

6.4.88|6.4.88 bhuvo vugluNGliToH|bhuvo vugluNGliToH|bhuvo vugluNGliToH 6.4.88|भुवो वुग्लुङ्लिटोः|भुवो वुग्लुङ्लिटोः ६.४.८८|६.४.८८|६.४.८८ भुवो वुग्लुङ्लिटोः
भू gets the augment व् (वुक्) before the tense-affixes of the Aorist and the Perfect, when beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: Semi-vowel substitution

6.4.89|6.4.89 Udupadhaayaa gohaH|Udupadhaayaa gohaH|Udupadhaayaa gohaH 6.4.89|ऊदुपधाया गोहः|ऊदुपधाया गोहः ६.४.८९|६.४.८९|६.४.८९ ऊदुपधाया गोहः
For the penultimate ओ of the गुण-ated अङ्ग (stem) गोह् (from गुह्) there is the substituted ऊ before an affix beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: ऊ substitution

6.4.90|6.4.90 doSho Nau|doSho Nau|doSho Nau 6.4.90|दोषो णौ|दोषो णौ ६.४.९०|६.४.९०|६.४.९० दोषो णौ
The ओ of दोष् is replaced by ऊ before the causative णि।<br><br>Terms: ऊ substitution

6.4.91|6.4.91 vaa chittaviraage|vaa chittaviraage|vaa chittaviraage 6.4.91|वा चित्तविरागे|वा चित्तविरागे ६.४.९१|६.४.९१|६.४.९१ वा चित्तविरागे
The ओ of दोष् is optionally replaced by ऊ when the sense is that of the disturbing of the mind.<br><br>Terms: ऊ substitution

6.4.92|6.4.92 mitaaM hrasvaH|mitaaM hrasvaH|mitaaM hrasvaH 6.4.92|मितां ह्रस्वः|मितां ह्रस्वः ६.४.९२|६.४.९२|६.४.९२ मितां ह्रस्वः
The roots having an indicatory म् retain their penultimate short vowel before the causative णि।<br><br>Terms: ऊ substitution

6.4.93|6.4.93 chiNNamulordiirgho.anyatarasyaam|chiNNamulordiirgho.anyatarasyaam|chiNNamulordiirgho.anyatarasyaam 6.4.93|चिण्णमुलोर्दीर्घोऽन्यतरस्याम्|चिण्णमुलोर्दीर्घोऽन्यतरस्याम् ६.४.९३|६.४.९३|६.४.९३ चिण्णमुलोर्दीर्घोऽन्यतरस्याम्
Optionally a long may be substituted for the penultimate of the causative of मित् roots, before the third person of the Passive Aorist in चिण् (इ) and before the Absolutive affix णमुल् (अम्).<br><br>Terms: ऊ substitution

6.4.94|6.4.94 khachi hrasvaH|khachi hrasvaH|khachi hrasvaH 6.4.94|खचि ह्रस्वः|खचि ह्रस्वः ६.४.९४|६.४.९४|६.४.९४ खचि ह्रस्वः
The penultimate of the Causative अङ्ग (stem) is shortened before the affix खच्।<br><br>Terms: Causative shortening

6.4.95|6.4.95 hlaado niShThaayaam|hlaado niShThaayaam|hlaado niShThaayaam 6.4.95|ह्लादो निष्ठायाम्|ह्लादो निष्ठायाम् ६.४.९५|६.४.९५|६.४.९५ ह्लादो निष्ठायाम्
The penultimate of the Causative of ह्लद् (ह्लादि) is shortened before the Participle affixes क्त and क्तवतु।<br><br>Terms: Causative shortening

6.4.96|6.4.96 Chaaderghe.advyupasargasya|Chaaderghe.advyupasargasya|Chaaderghe.advyupasargasya 6.4.96|छादेर्घेऽद्व्युपसर्गस्य|छादेर्घेऽद्व्युपसर्गस्य ६.४.९६|६.४.९६|६.४.९६ छादेर्घेऽद्व्युपसर्गस्य
The penultimate of चुरादि (10th Conjugation) - छद् is shortened before the affix घ -- पुंसि संज्ञायां घः प्रायेण ३.३.११८, when not preceded by two prepositions (or more).<br><br>Terms: Causative shortening

6.4.97|6.4.97 ismantrankviShu cha|ismantrankviShu cha|ismantrankviShu cha 6.4.97|इस्मन्त्रन्क्विषु च|इस्मन्त्रन्क्विषु च ६.४.९७|६.४.९७|६.४.९७ इस्मन्त्रन्क्विषु च
The penultimate of छादि is shortened before the affixes 1. इस् 2. मन् 3. त्रन् and 4. क्वि।<br><br>Terms: Causative shortening

6.4.98|6.4.98 gamahanajanakhanaghasaaM lopaH kNGityanaNGi|gamahanajanakhanaghasaaM lopaH kNGityanaNGi|gamahanajanakhanaghasaaM lopaH kNGityanaNGi 6.4.98|गमहनजनखनघसां लोपः क्ङित्यनङि|गमहनजनखनघसां लोपः क्ङित्यनङि ६.४.९८|६.४.९८|६.४.९८ गमहनजनखनघसां लोपः क्ङित्यनङि
The root-vowel of 1. गम् 2. जन् 3. खन् and 4. घस् is elided before an affix beginning with a vowel when it has an indicatory क् or ङ् ; but not before the Aorist affix अङ्।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.99|6.4.99 tanipatyoshChandasi|tanipatyoshChandasi|tanipatyoshChandasi 6.4.99|तनिपत्योश्छन्दसि|तनिपत्योश्छन्दसि ६.४.९९|६.४.९९|६.४.९९ तनिपत्योश्छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the root-vowel of तन् and पत् is elided before an affix beginning with a vowel, when it has an indicatory क् or ङ् ।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.100|6.4.100 ghasibhasorhali cha|ghasibhasorhali cha|ghasibhasorhali cha 6.4.100|घसिभसोर्हलि च|घसिभसोर्हलि च ६.४.१००|६.४.१००|६.४.१०० घसिभसोर्हलि च
The root-vowel of घस् and भस् is elided in the छन्दस् (Vedas) before any affix whether beginning with a vowel or a consonant which has an indicatory क् or ङ् ।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.101|6.4.101 hujhalbhyo herdhiH|hujhalbhyo herdhiH|hujhalbhyo herdhiH 6.4.101|हुझल्भ्यो हेर्धिः|हुझल्भ्यो हेर्धिः ६.४.१०१|६.४.१०१|६.४.१०१ हुझल्भ्यो हेर्धिः
After हु and after a consonant (with the exception of semi-vowels and nasals), धि is substituted for the Imperative affix हि when the latter does not take the augment इट् ।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.102|6.4.102 shrushRNupRRkRvRbhyashChandasi|shrushRNupRRkRvRbhyashChandasi|shrushRNupRRkRvRbhyashChandasi 6.4.102|श्रुशृणुपॄकृवृभ्यश्छन्दसि|श्रुशृणुपॄकृवृभ्यश्छन्दसि ६.४.१०२|६.४.१०२|६.४.१०२ श्रुशृणुपॄकृवृभ्यश्छन्दसि
धि is substituted for the Imperative affix हि in the छन्दस् (Vedas) after 1. श्रु 2. शृणु 3. पॄ 4. कृ and 5. वृ।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.103|6.4.103 aNGitashcha|aNGitashcha|aNGitashcha 6.4.103|अङितश्च|अङितश्च ६.४.१०३|६.४.१०३|६.४.१०३ अङितश्च
धि is substituted for the Imperative affix हि when the tense-affix is not ङित्।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.104|6.4.104 chiNo luk|chiNo luk|chiNo luk 6.4.104|चिणो लुक्|चिणो लुक् ६.४.१०४|६.४.१०४|६.४.१०४ चिणो लुक्
The personal endings are elided after चिण् , the 3rd person singular Passive of Aorist.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.105|6.4.105 ato heH|ato heH|ato heH 6.4.105|अतो हेः|अतो हेः ६.४.१०५|६.४.१०५|६.४.१०५ अतो हेः
The Imperative affix हि is elided after a अङ्ग (stem) ending in short अ।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.106|6.4.106 utashcha pratyayaadasaMyogapuurvaat‌|utashcha pratyayaadasaMyogapuurvaat‌|utashcha pratyayaadasaMyogapuurvaat‌ 6.4.106|उतश्च प्रत्ययादसंयोगपूर्वात्‌|उतश्च प्रत्ययादसंयोगपूर्वात्‌ ६.४.१०६|६.४.१०६|६.४.१०६ उतश्च प्रत्ययादसंयोगपूर्वात्‌
The Imperative affix हि is elided after the उ of an affix in the विकरण with which the Present-अङ्ग (stem) (special conjugation) is made, provided that the उ is not preceded by a conjunct consonant.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.107|6.4.107 lopashchaasyaanyatarasyaaM mvoH|lopashchaasyaanyatarasyaaM mvoH|lopashchaasyaanyatarasyaaM mvoH 6.4.107|लोपश्चास्यान्यतरस्यां म्वोः|लोपश्चास्यान्यतरस्यां म्वोः ६.४.१०७|६.४.१०७|६.४.१०७ लोपश्चास्यान्यतरस्यां म्वोः
The पु of the विकरण उ and श्नु when not preceded by a conjunct consonant, may be elided optionally before a personal affix beginning with म् or व्।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.108|6.4.108 nityaM karoteH|nityaM karoteH|nityaM karoteH 6.4.108|नित्यं करोतेः|नित्यं करोतेः ६.४.१०८|६.४.१०८|६.४.१०८ नित्यं करोतेः
The elision of उ is invariable before व् and म् in the case of कृ 'to make' (करोति).<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.109|6.4.109 ye cha|ye cha|ye cha 6.4.109|ये च|ये च ६.४.१०९|६.४.१०९|६.४.१०९ ये च
The affix उ of the अङ्ग (stem) कुरु is always elided before a personal ending beginning with a य्।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.110|6.4.110 ata ut‌ saarvadhaatuke|ata ut‌ saarvadhaatuke|ata ut‌ saarvadhaatuke 6.4.110|अत उत्‌ सार्वधातुके|अत उत्‌ सार्वधातुके ६.४.११०|६.४.११०|६.४.११० अत उत्‌ सार्वधातुके
Before a सार्वधातुक affix with an indicatory क् or ङ् , short उ is substituted for the अ if कृ 'to make' (कर् + उ) when गुण-ated.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.111|6.4.111 shnasorallopaH|shnasorallopaH|shnasorallopaH 6.4.111|श्नसोरल्लोपः|श्नसोरल्लोपः ६.४.१११|६.४.१११|६.४.१११ श्नसोरल्लोपः
Before a सार्वधातुक कित् or ङित् affix, the अ of श्न and अस् is elided.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.112|6.4.112 shnaa.abhyastayoraataH|shnaa.abhyastayoraataH|shnaa.abhyastayoraataH 6.4.112|श्नाऽभ्यस्तयोरातः|श्नाऽभ्यस्तयोरातः ६.४.११२|६.४.११२|६.४.११२ श्नाऽभ्यस्तयोरातः
Before a सार्वधातुक कित् or ङित् affix beginning with a vowel, the long आ of श्ना (the विकरण of the क्र्यादिगणः (9th Conjugation)) and of the reduplicate अङ्ग (stems) is elided.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.113|6.4.113 ii halyaghoH|ii halyaghoH|ii halyaghoH 6.4.113|ई हल्यघोः|ई हल्यघोः ६.४.११३|६.४.११३|६.४.११३ ई हल्यघोः
Before a सार्वधातुक कित् or ङित् affix beginning with a consonant, the आ of श्ना (the विकरण of the क्र्यादिगणः (9th Conjugation)) and of the reduplicate अङ्ग (stems) is replaced by ई except when the root is दा 'to give' or धा (धु).<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.114|6.4.114 iddaridrasya|iddaridrasya|iddaridrasya 6.4.114|इद्दरिद्रस्य|इद्दरिद्रस्य ६.४.११४|६.४.११४|६.४.११४ इद्दरिद्रस्य
इ is substituted for the आ of दरिद्रा before a सार्वधातुक कित् or ङित् affix beginning with a consonant.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.115|6.4.115 bhiyo.anyatarasyaam|bhiyo.anyatarasyaam|bhiyo.anyatarasyaam 6.4.115|भियोऽन्यतरस्याम्|भियोऽन्यतरस्याम् ६.४.११५|६.४.११५|६.४.११५ भियोऽन्यतरस्याम्
इ is substituted for the ई of भी before a सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a consonant and having an indicatory क् or ङ्।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.116|6.4.116 jahaateshcha|jahaateshcha|jahaateshcha 6.4.116|जहातेश्च|जहातेश्च ६.४.११६|६.४.११६|६.४.११६ जहातेश्च
इ is optionally substituted for the आ of हा (जुहोत्यादिगणः (3rd Conjugation)) before a सार्वधातुक affix कित् or ङित् beginning with a consonant.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.117|6.4.117 aa cha hau|aa cha hau|aa cha hau 6.4.117|आ च हौ|आ च हौ ६.४.११७|६.४.११७|६.४.११७ आ च हौ
आ and इ are optionally substituted for the final of the अङ्ग (stem) of हा (जुहोत्यादिगणः (3rd Conjugation)) before the Imperative ending हि।<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.118|6.4.118 lopo yi|lopo yi|lopo yi 6.4.118|लोपो यि|लोपो यि ६.४.११८|६.४.११८|६.४.११८ लोपो यि
The final of the अङ्ग (stem) of हा (जुहोत्यादिगणः (3rd Conjugation)) is elided before an affix beginning with य् being a सार्वधातुक कित् or ङित् affix.<br><br>Terms: कित् and ङित्

6.4.119|6.4.119 ghvasoreddhaavabhyaasalopashcha|ghvasoreddhaavabhyaasalopashcha|ghvasoreddhaavabhyaasalopashcha 6.4.119|घ्वसोरेद्धावभ्यासलोपश्च|घ्वसोरेद्धावभ्यासलोपश्च ६.४.११९|६.४.११९|६.४.११९ घ्वसोरेद्धावभ्यासलोपश्च
For the final vowel of the roots दा and धा (धु) and for the स् of अस् , is substituted ए before the Imperative ending हि and thereby the reduplicated syllable of दा and धा (धु) is elided.<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.120|6.4.120 ata ekahalmadhye.anaadeshaaderliTi|ata ekahalmadhye.anaadeshaaderliTi|ata ekahalmadhye.anaadeshaaderliTi 6.4.120|अत एकहल्मध्येऽनादेशादेर्लिटि|अत एकहल्मध्येऽनादेशादेर्लिटि ६.४.१२०|६.४.१२०|६.४.१२० अत एकहल्मध्येऽनादेशादेर्लिटि
ए is substituted for the short अ standing between two simple consonants of a verbal अङ्ग (stem), before the personal endings of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) which have an indicatory क् -- असंयोगाल्लिट् कित् १.२.५, provided that, at the beginning of the root, in the reduplication, no other consonant has been substituted and when this ए is substituted, the reduplicate is elided.<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.121|6.4.121 thali cha seTi|thali cha seTi|thali cha seTi 6.4.121|थलि च सेटि|थलि च सेटि ६.४.१२१|६.४.१२१|६.४.१२१ थलि च सेटि
ए is substituted for अ of a verbal अङ्ग (stem) standing between two simple consonants, the अङ्ग (stem) not having any different letter substituted in the reduplicate when the ending थल् of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) having the augment इट् follows and thereby the reduplicate is elided.<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.122|6.4.122 tRRphalabhajatrapashcha|tRRphalabhajatrapashcha|tRRphalabhajatrapashcha 6.4.122|तॄफलभजत्रपश्च|तॄफलभजत्रपश्च ६.४.१२२|६.४.१२२|६.४.१२२ तॄफलभजत्रपश्च
ए is substituted for अ of 1. तॄ 2. फल 3. भज and 4. त्रप and the reduplicate is elided when the affixes of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) having an indicatory क् (or ङ्) follow, as well as when थल् of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) having the augment इट् follows.<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.123|6.4.123 raadho hiMsaayaam|raadho hiMsaayaam|raadho hiMsaayaam 6.4.123|राधो हिंसायाम्|राधो हिंसायाम् ६.४.१२३|६.४.१२३|६.४.१२३ राधो हिंसायाम्
ए is substituted for आ of राध when meaning 'to hurt someone' and the reduplicate is elided before the affixes क् (or ङ्) or as well as before थल् of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) having the augment इट्।<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.124|6.4.124 vaa jRRbhramutrasaam|vaa jRRbhramutrasaam|vaa jRRbhramutrasaam 6.4.124|वा जॄभ्रमुत्रसाम्|वा जॄभ्रमुत्रसाम् ६.४.१२४|६.४.१२४|६.४.१२४ वा जॄभ्रमुत्रसाम्
ए is optionally substituted for अ of the अङ्ग (stems) 1. जर् (जॄ) 2. भ्रम and 3. त्रस् and the reduplicate is thereby elided before the affixes of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) having an indicatory क् (or ङ्)<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.125|6.4.125 phaNaaM cha saptaanaam|phaNaaM cha saptaanaam|phaNaaM cha saptaanaam 6.4.125|फणां च सप्तानाम्|फणां च सप्तानाम् ६.४.१२५|६.४.१२५|६.४.१२५ फणां च सप्तानाम्
ए is optionally substituted for अ and आ of the seven roots 1. फण् 2. राज् 3. भ्राज् 4. भ्राश् 5. श्लाश् 6. स्याम् and 7. स्वन् and the reduplicate is elided thereby, before the affixes of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) having an indicatory क् (or ङ्) as well as before थल् of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) having the augment इट्।<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.126|6.4.126 na shasadadavaadiguNaanaam|na shasadadavaadiguNaanaam|na shasadadavaadiguNaanaam 6.4.126|न शसददवादिगुणानाम्|न शसददवादिगुणानाम् ६.४.१२६|६.४.१२६|६.४.१२६ न शसददवादिगुणानाम्
ए is not substituted for अ of शस् , दद् or of roots beginning with a व् or of such verbal अङ्ग (stems) in which the अ results through the substitution being कित् or ङित् follow, of the सेट् थल् of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) nor is the reduplicate elided.<br><br>Terms: ए substitution

6.4.127|6.4.127 arvaNastrasaavanaNJaH|arvaNastrasaavanaNJaH|arvaNastrasaavanaNJaH 6.4.127|अर्वणस्त्रसावनञः|अर्वणस्त्रसावनञः ६.४.१२७|६.४.१२७|६.४.१२७ अर्वणस्त्रसावनञः
तृ (which is changed to न्त् in the strong cases and forms the feminine in ई unaccented) is substituted for the final of the अङ्ग (stem) अर्वन् , except in the Nominative 1st-Case singular or when the word is joined with the Negative particle.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.128|6.4.128 maghavaa bahulam|maghavaa bahulam|maghavaa bahulam 6.4.128|मघवा बहुलम्|मघवा बहुलम् ६.४.१२८|६.४.१२८|६.४.१२८ मघवा बहुलम्
तृ is diversely substituted for the final of मघवन्।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.129|6.4.129 bhasya|bhasya|bhasya 6.4.129|भस्य|भस्य ६.४.१२९|६.४.१२९|६.४.१२९ भस्य
Whatever will be taught in the following up to the end of this अध्याय should be understood to apply to the nominal stems called भ -- यचि भम् १.४.१८, तसौ मत्वर्थे १.४.१९.<br><br>Terms: भ substitution

6.4.130|6.4.130 paadaH pat|paadaH pat|paadaH pat 6.4.130|पादः पत्|पादः पत् ६.४.१३०|६.४.१३०|६.४.१३० पादः पत्
For पाद is substituted पद् when the former is भ।<br><br>Terms: भ substitution

6.4.131|6.4.131 vasoH samprasaaraNam|vasoH samprasaaraNam|vasoH samprasaaraNam 6.4.131|वसोः सम्प्रसारणम्|वसोः सम्प्रसारणम् ६.४.१३१|६.४.१३१|६.४.१३१ वसोः सम्प्रसारणम्
The semi-vowel of the affix वस् (वंस्) is vocalised to उ in a भ अङ्ग (stem).<br><br>Terms: भ substitution

6.4.132|6.4.132 vaaha UTh|vaaha UTh|vaaha UTh 6.4.132|वाह ऊठ्|वाह ऊठ् ६.४.१३२|६.४.१३२|६.४.१३२ वाह ऊठ्
The व is vocalised to ऊ (ऊठ्) when the compound अङ्ग (stem) is भ।<br><br>Terms: भ substitution

6.4.133|6.4.133 shvayuvamaghonaamataddhite|shvayuvamaghonaamataddhite|shvayuvamaghonaamataddhite 6.4.133|श्वयुवमघोनामतद्धिते|श्वयुवमघोनामतद्धिते ६.४.१३३|६.४.१३३|६.४.१३३ श्वयुवमघोनामतद्धिते
The व of 1. श्वन् 2. युवन् and 3. मधवन् becomes vocalised, but not before a तद्धित affix.<br><br>Terms: व vocalisation

6.4.134|6.4.134 allopo.anaH|allopo.anaH|allopo.anaH 6.4.134|अल्लोपोऽनः|अल्लोपोऽनः ६.४.१३४|६.४.१३४|६.४.१३४ अल्लोपोऽनः
Of a भ अङ्ग (stem) ending in अन् , the अ is elided.<br><br>Terms: व vocalisation

6.4.135|6.4.135 ShapuurvahandhRtaraaJNaamaNi|ShapuurvahandhRtaraaJNaamaNi|ShapuurvahandhRtaraaJNaamaNi 6.4.135|षपूर्वहन्धृतराज्ञामणि|षपूर्वहन्धृतराज्ञामणि ६.४.१३५|६.४.१३५|६.४.१३५ षपूर्वहन्धृतराज्ञामणि
Of a भ अङ्ग (stem) ending in अन् with a preceding ष as well as of हन् and धृतराजन् , the अ is elided before the affix अण् ।<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.136|6.4.136 vibhaaShaa NGishyoH|vibhaaShaa NGishyoH|vibhaaShaa NGishyoH 6.4.136|विभाषा ङिश्योः|विभाषा ङिश्योः ६.४.१३६|६.४.१३६|६.४.१३६ विभाषा ङिश्योः
In a अङ्ग (stem) ending in अन् , the अ is optionally elided before the Locative -7th case ending इ before the ending शी (ई) of the Nominative 1st-Case and Accusative-2nd case dual Neuter.<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.137|6.4.137 na saMyogaadvamantaat‌|na saMyogaadvamantaat‌|na saMyogaadvamantaat‌ 6.4.137|न संयोगाद्वमन्तात्‌|न संयोगाद्वमन्तात्‌ ६.४.१३७|६.४.१३७|६.४.१३७ न संयोगाद्वमन्तात्‌
The अ in अन् is not elided when the भ अङ्ग (stem) ends in वन् or मन् with a consonant preceding व् or म्।<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.138|6.4.138 achaH|achaH|achaH 6.4.138|अचः|अचः ६.४.१३८|६.४.१३८|६.४.१३८ अचः
The अ of अच् (अञ्च् ) is elided at the end of a भ अङ्ग (stem).<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.139|6.4.139 uda iit‌|uda iit‌|uda iit‌ 6.4.139|उद ईत्‌|उद ईत्‌ ६.४.१३९|६.४.१३९|६.४.१३९ उद ईत्‌
The long ई is substituted for the अ of अच् (अञ्च् ) after the word उत् when the अङ्ग (stem) is भ।<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.140|6.4.140 aato dhaatoH|aato dhaatoH|aato dhaatoH 6.4.140|आतो धातोः|आतो धातोः ६.४.१४०|६.४.१४०|६.४.१४० आतो धातोः
The final आ of a भ अङ्ग (stem) is elided when it ends in a root.<br><br>Terms: आ elision

6.4.141|6.4.141 mantreShvaaNGyaaderaatmanaH|mantreShvaaNGyaaderaatmanaH|mantreShvaaNGyaaderaatmanaH 6.4.141|मन्त्रेष्वाङ्यादेरात्मनः|मन्त्रेष्वाङ्यादेरात्मनः ६.४.१४१|६.४.१४१|६.४.१४१ मन्त्रेष्वाङ्यादेरात्मनः
In the मन्त्र-s , the beginning of आत्मन् is elided when the affix of the Instrumental -3rd case singular follows.<br><br>Terms: आ elision

6.4.142|6.4.142 ti viMshaterDiti|ti viMshaterDiti|ti viMshaterDiti 6.4.142|ति विंशतेर्डिति|ति विंशतेर्डिति ६.४.१४२|६.४.१४२|६.४.१४२ ति विंशतेर्डिति
Of the भ अङ्ग (stem) विंशति , before an affix having an indicatory ड् the ति is elided.<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.143|6.4.143 TeH|TeH|TeH 6.4.143|टेः|टेः ६.४.१४३|६.४.१४३|६.४.१४३ टेः
Before an affix having an indicatory ड् , the last vowel, with the consonant, if any, that follows it, is elided.<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.144|6.4.144 nastaddhite|nastaddhite|nastaddhite 6.4.144|नस्तद्धिते|नस्तद्धिते ६.४.१४४|६.४.१४४|६.४.१४४ नस्तद्धिते
Of the भ अङ्ग (stem) the final न् with the vowel that precedes it, is elided before a तद्धित affix.<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.145|6.4.145 ahnaShTakhoreva|ahnaShTakhoreva|ahnaShTakhoreva 6.4.145|अह्नष्टखोरेव|अह्नष्टखोरेव ६.४.१४५|६.४.१४५|६.४.१४५ अह्नष्टखोरेव
The अ of अहन् is elided only before the affixes ट and ख।<br><br>Terms: अ elision

6.4.146|6.4.146 orguNaH|orguNaH|orguNaH 6.4.146|ओर्गुणः|ओर्गुणः ६.४.१४६|६.४.१४६|६.४.१४६ ओर्गुणः
For उ of ऊ of a भ अङ्ग (stem) there is substituted गुण before a तद्धित affix.<br><br>Terms: अ & इ elision

6.4.147|6.4.147 Dhe lopo.akadrvaaH|Dhe lopo.akadrvaaH|Dhe lopo.akadrvaaH 6.4.147|ढे लोपोऽकद्र्वाः|ढे लोपोऽकद्र्वाः ६.४.१४७|६.४.१४७|६.४.१४७ ढे लोपोऽकद्र्वाः
For उ of ऊ of a भ अङ्ग (stem) is elided before the affix एय (ढ) but not of the अङ्ग (stem) कट्रू<br><br>Terms: अ & इ elision

6.4.148|6.4.148 yasyeti cha|yasyeti cha|yasyeti cha 6.4.148|यस्येति च|यस्येति च ६.४.१४८|६.४.१४८|६.४.१४८ यस्येति च
The final अ and इ (both long and short) of a भ अङ्ग (stem) are elided before a तद्धित affix.<br><br>Terms: अ & इ elision

6.4.149|6.4.149 suuryatiShyaagastyamatsyaanaaM ya upadhaayaaH|suuryatiShyaagastyamatsyaanaaM ya upadhaayaaH|suuryatiShyaagastyamatsyaanaaM ya upadhaayaaH 6.4.149|सूर्यतिष्यागस्त्यमत्स्यानां य उपधायाः|सूर्यतिष्यागस्त्यमत्स्यानां य उपधायाः ६.४.१४९|६.४.१४९|६.४.१४९ सूर्यतिष्यागस्त्यमत्स्यानां य उपधायाः
Of the भ अङ्ग (stems) 1. सूर्य 2. तिष्य 3. अगस्त्य and 4. मत्स्य (and their derivatives when they are भ) the penultimate य् is also is also elided before a तद्धित affix.<br><br>Terms: य elision

6.4.150|6.4.150 halastaddhitasya|halastaddhitasya|halastaddhitasya 6.4.150|हलस्तद्धितस्य|हलस्तद्धितस्य ६.४.१५०|६.४.१५०|६.४.१५० हलस्तद्धितस्य
The य् of a तद्धित affix when preceded by a consonant and penultimate in a अङ्ग (stem), is elided before the feminine ई।<br><br>Terms: य elision

6.4.151|6.4.151 aapatyasya cha taddhite.anaati|aapatyasya cha taddhite.anaati|aapatyasya cha taddhite.anaati 6.4.151|आपत्यस्य च तद्धितेऽनाति|आपत्यस्य च तद्धितेऽनाति ६.४.१५१|६.४.१५१|६.४.१५१ आपत्यस्य च तद्धितेऽनाति
The य् of a Patronymic affix, preceded by a consonant, is elided before a तद्धित when it does not begin with an आ।<br><br>Terms: य elision

6.4.152|6.4.152 kyachvyoshcha|kyachvyoshcha|kyachvyoshcha 6.4.152|क्यच्व्योश्च|क्यच्व्योश्च ६.४.१५२|६.४.१५२|६.४.१५२ क्यच्व्योश्च
The य् of a Patronymic affix, preceded by a consonant, is elided before the Denominative affix क्य and the adverbial affix च्वि।<br><br>Terms: य elision

6.4.153|6.4.153 bilvakaadibhyashChasya luk|bilvakaadibhyashChasya luk|bilvakaadibhyashChasya luk 6.4.153|बिल्वकादिभ्यश्छस्य लुक्|बिल्वकादिभ्यश्छस्य लुक् ६.४.१५३|६.४.१५३|६.४.१५३ बिल्वकादिभ्यश्छस्य लुक्
The affix छ of the भ अङ्ग (stems) बिल्वक etc. is elided before a तद्धित affix.<br><br>Terms: छ elision

6.4.154|6.4.154 turiShThemeyassu|turiShThemeyassu|turiShThemeyassu 6.4.154|तुरिष्ठेमेयस्सु|तुरिष्ठेमेयस्सु ६.४.१५४|६.४.१५४|६.४.१५४ तुरिष्ठेमेयस्सु
The affix तृ is elided before the affixes 1. इष्ठन् 2. इमनिव् and 3. ईयसुन्।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.155|6.4.155 TeH|TeH|TeH 6.4.155|टेः|टेः ६.४.१५५|६.४.१५५|६.४.१५५ टेः
The last vowel, with the consonant, if any, that follows it, is elided when the affixes 1. इष्ठ 2. इमन् and ईयस् follow.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.156|6.4.156 sthuuladuurayuvahrasvaxipraxudraaNaaM yaNaadiparaM puurvasya cha guNaH|sthuuladuurayuvahrasvaxipraxudraaNaaM yaNaadiparaM puurvasya cha guNaH|sthuuladuurayuvahrasvaxipraxudraaNaaM yaNaadiparaM puurvasya cha guNaH 6.4.156|स्थूलदूरयुवह्रस्वक्षिप्रक्षुद्राणां यणादिपरं पूर्वस्य च गुणः|स्थूलदूरयुवह्रस्वक्षिप्रक्षुद्राणां यणादिपरं पूर्वस्य च गुणः ६.४.१५६|६.४.१५६|६.४.१५६ स्थूलदूरयुवह्रस्वक्षिप्रक्षुद्राणां यणादिपरं पूर्वस्य च गुणः
Before the affixes 1. इष्ठ 2. इमन् and 3. ईयस् the last semi-vowel is elided with that which follows it and for the first vowel, a गुण is substituted in 1. स्थूल 2. दूर 3. युवन् 4. ह्रस्व 5. क्षिप्र and 6. क्षुद्र।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.157|6.4.157 priyasthirasphirorubahulaguruvRddhatRpradiirghavRndaarakaaNaaM prasthasphavarbaMhigarvarShitrabdraaghivRndaaH|priyasthirasphirorubahulaguruvRddhatRpradiirghavRndaarakaaNaaM prasthasphavarbaMhigarvarShitrabdraaghivRndaaH|priyasthirasphirorubahulaguruvRddhatRpradiirghavRndaarakaaNaaM prasthasphavarbaMhigarvarShitrabdraaghivRndaaH 6.4.157|प्रियस्थिरस्फिरोरुबहुलगुरुवृद्धतृप्रदीर्घवृन्दारकाणां प्रस्थस्फवर्बंहिगर्वर्षित्रब्द्राघिवृन्दाः|प्रियस्थिरस्फिरोरुबहुलगुरुवृद्धतृप्रदीर्घवृन्दारकाणां प्रस्थस्फवर्बंहिगर्वर्षित्रब्द्राघिवृन्दाः ६.४.१५७|६.४.१५७|६.४.१५७ प्रियस्थिरस्फिरोरुबहुलगुरुवृद्धतृप्रदीर्घवृन्दारकाणां प्रस्थस्फवर्बंहिगर्वर्षित्रब्द्राघिवृन्दाः
Before the affixes 1. इष्ठ 2. इमन् and ईयस् the following substitutions take place 1. प्र for प्रिय 2. स्थ for स्थिर 3. स्फ for स्फिर 4. वर् for उरु 5. बह for बहुल 6. गर् for गुरु 7. वर्ष for वृद्ध 8. त्रप् for तृप् 9. द्राघ for दीर्घ and 10. वृन्द for वृन्दारक।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.158|6.4.158 bahorlopo bhuu cha bahoH|bahorlopo bhuu cha bahoH|bahorlopo bhuu cha bahoH 6.4.158|बहोर्लोपो भू च बहोः|बहोर्लोपो भू च बहोः ६.४.१५८|६.४.१५८|६.४.१५८ बहोर्लोपो भू च बहोः
The इ and ई of these affixes (इमन् and ईयस्) are elided after बहु , and for बहु is substituted भू।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.159|6.4.159 iShThasya yiT cha|iShThasya yiT cha|iShThasya yiT cha 6.4.159|इष्ठस्य यिट् च|इष्ठस्य यिट् च ६.४.१५९|६.४.१५९|६.४.१५९ इष्ठस्य यिट् च
After बहु , the augment यिट् is added to इष्ठ and भू is the substitute of बहु।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.160|6.4.160 jyaadaadiiyasaH|jyaadaadiiyasaH|jyaadaadiiyasaH 6.4.160|ज्यादादीयसः|ज्यादादीयसः ६.४.१६०|६.४.१६०|६.४.१६० ज्यादादीयसः
आ is substituted for the first letter of ईयस् after ज्य।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.161|6.4.161 ra Rto halaaderlaghoH|ra Rto halaaderlaghoH|ra Rto halaaderlaghoH 6.4.161|र ऋतो हलादेर्लघोः|र ऋतो हलादेर्लघोः ६.४.१६१|६.४.१६१|६.४.१६१ र ऋतो हलादेर्लघोः
Before the affixes 1. इष्ठ 2. इमन् and 3. ईयस् , र् is substituted for ऋ in a अङ्ग (stem), when this ऋ is preceded by a consonant and is not prosodially long (on account of being followed by a double consonant).<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

6.4.162|6.4.162 vibhaaSharjoshChandasi|vibhaaSharjoshChandasi|vibhaaSharjoshChandasi 6.4.162|विभाषर्जोश्छन्दसि|विभाषर्जोश्छन्दसि ६.४.१६२|६.४.१६२|६.४.१६२ विभाषर्जोश्छन्दसि
Before the affixes 1. इष्ठ 2. इमन् and 3. ईयस् , the ऋ of ऋजु may optionally be changed to र् , in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: र् substitution

6.4.163|6.4.163 prakRtyaikaach|prakRtyaikaach|prakRtyaikaach 6.4.163|प्रकृत्यैकाच्|प्रकृत्यैकाच् ६.४.१६३|६.४.१६३|६.४.१६३ प्रकृत्यैकाच्
A monosyllabic भ अङ्ग (stem) retains its original form without undergoing any change before the affixes 1. इष्ठ 2. इमन् and 3. ईयस् ।<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.164|6.4.164 inaNyanapatye|inaNyanapatye|inaNyanapatye 6.4.164|इनण्यनपत्ये|इनण्यनपत्ये ६.४.१६४|६.४.१६४|६.४.१६४ इनण्यनपत्ये
The final इन् of a भ अङ्ग (stem) remains unaltered before the non-Patronymic अण् affix.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.165|6.4.165 gaathividathikeshigaNipaNinashcha|gaathividathikeshigaNipaNinashcha|gaathividathikeshigaNipaNinashcha 6.4.165|गाथिविदथिकेशिगणिपणिनश्च|गाथिविदथिकेशिगणिपणिनश्च ६.४.१६५|६.४.१६५|६.४.१६५ गाथिविदथिकेशिगणिपणिनश्च
1. गाथिन् 2. विदथिन् 3. केशिन् 4. गणिन् and 5. पणिन् remain unchanged before the Patronymic also.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.166|6.4.166 saMyogaadishcha|saMyogaadishcha|saMyogaadishcha 6.4.166|संयोगादिश्च|संयोगादिश्च ६.४.१६६|६.४.१६६|६.४.१६६ संयोगादिश्च
The syllable इन् of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in इन् remains unchanged before अण् when a conjunct consonant precedes it.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.167|6.4.167 an|an|an 6.4.167|अन्|अन् ६.४.१६७|६.४.१६७|६.४.१६७ अन्
The syllable अन् of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in अन् remains unchanged before अण् affix whether Patronymic or otherwise.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.168|6.4.168 ye chaabhaavakarmaNoH|ye chaabhaavakarmaNoH|ye chaabhaavakarmaNoH 6.4.168|ये चाभावकर्मणोः|ये चाभावकर्मणोः ६.४.१६८|६.४.१६८|६.४.१६८ ये चाभावकर्मणोः
The syllable अन् of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in अन् remains unchanged before a तद्धित affix beginning with य् when it does not denote existence in abstract of the avocation of someone.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.169|6.4.169 aatmaadhvaanau khe|aatmaadhvaanau khe|aatmaadhvaanau khe 6.4.169|आत्माध्वानौ खे|आत्माध्वानौ खे ६.४.१६९|६.४.१६९|६.४.१६९ आत्माध्वानौ खे
The finals of the अङ्ग (stems) आत्मन् and अध्वन् remain unchanged before the affix ख।<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.170|6.4.170 na mapuurvo.apatye.avarmaNaH|na mapuurvo.apatye.avarmaNaH|na mapuurvo.apatye.avarmaNaH 6.4.170|न मपूर्वोऽपत्येऽवर्मणः|न मपूर्वोऽपत्येऽवर्मणः ६.४.१७०|६.४.१७०|६.४.१७० न मपूर्वोऽपत्येऽवर्मणः
In a अङ्ग (stem) in अन् with a preceding म् with the exception of वर्मन् , the ending अन् does not remain unchanged before the Patronymic affix अण् ।<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.171|6.4.171 braahmoajaatau|braahmoajaatau|braahmoajaatau 6.4.171|ब्राह्मोअजातौ|ब्राह्मोअजातौ ६.४.१७१|६.४.१७१|६.४.१७१ ब्राह्मोअजातौ
ब्राह्म is irregularly formed from ब्रह्मन् when not meaning 'a kind of जाति'.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.172|6.4.172 kaarmastaachChiilye|kaarmastaachChiilye|kaarmastaachChiilye 6.4.172|कार्मस्ताच्छील्ये|कार्मस्ताच्छील्ये ६.४.१७२|६.४.१७२|६.४.१७२ कार्मस्ताच्छील्ये
कार्म is irregularly formed from कर्मन् by the elision of the final अन् when the sense is 'accustomed to such occupation or prompt therein'.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.173|6.4.173 auxamanapatye|auxamanapatye|auxamanapatye 6.4.173|औक्षमनपत्ये|औक्षमनपत्ये ६.४.१७३|६.४.१७३|६.४.१७३ औक्षमनपत्ये
From उक्षन् is formed औक्ष when not meaning a descendant.<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.174|6.4.174 daaNDinaayanahaastinaayanaatharvaNikajaihmaashineyavaashinaayanibhrauNahatyadhaivatyasaaravaixvaakamaitreyahiraNmayaani|daaNDinaayanahaastinaayanaatharvaNikajaihmaashineyavaashinaayanibhrauNahatyadhaivatyasaaravaixvaakamaitreyahiraNmayaani|daaNDinaayanahaastinaayanaatharvaNikajaihmaashineyavaashinaayanibhrauNahatyadhaivatyasaaravaixvaakamaitreyahiraNmayaani 6.4.174|दाण्डिनायनहास्तिनायनाथर्वणिकजैह्माशिनेयवाशिनायनिभ्रौणहत्यधैवत्यसारवैक्ष्वाकमैत्रेयहिरण्मयानि|दाण्डिनायनहास्तिनायनाथर्वणिकजैह्माशिनेयवाशिनायनिभ्रौणहत्यधैवत्यसारवैक्ष्वाकमैत्रेयहिरण्मयानि ६.४.१७४|६.४.१७४|६.४.१७४ दाण्डिनायनहास्तिनायनाथर्वणिकजैह्माशिनेयवाशिनायनिभ्रौणहत्यधैवत्यसारवैक्ष्वाकमैत्रेयहिरण्मयानि
The following are irregularly formed - 1. दाण्डिनायन 2. हास्तिनायन 3. अथर्वणिक 4. जैह्माशिनेय 5. वाशिनायनि 6. भ्रौणहत्य 7. धैवत्य 8. सरवै 9. अक्ष्वाक 10. मैत्रेय and 11. हिरण्मया।<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

6.4.175|6.4.175 RtvyavaastvyavaastvamaadhviihiraNyayaani chChandasi|RtvyavaastvyavaastvamaadhviihiraNyayaani chChandasi|RtvyavaastvyavaastvamaadhviihiraNyayaani chChandasi 6.4.175|ऋत्व्यवास्त्व्यवास्त्वमाध्वीहिरण्ययानि च्छन्दसि|ऋत्व्यवास्त्व्यवास्त्वमाध्वीहिरण्ययानि च्छन्दसि ६.४.१७५|६.४.१७५|६.४.१७५ ऋत्व्यवास्त्व्यवास्त्वमाध्वीहिरण्ययानि च्छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the following are irregularly formed 1. ऋत्व्य 2. वास्त्व्य 3. 4. वास्त्व 5. माध्वी and 6. हिरण्यय।<br><br>Terms: प्रकृति भाव

7.1.1|7.1.1 yuvoranaakau|yuvoranaakau|yuvoranaakau 7.1.1|युवोरनाकौ|युवोरनाकौ ७.१.१|७.१.१|७.१.१ युवोरनाकौ
For यु and वु (nasalized) in an affix, are substituted, respectively, अन and अक।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.1.2|7.1.2 aayaneyiiniiyiyaH phaDhakhachChaghaaM pratyayaadiinaam‌|aayaneyiiniiyiyaH phaDhakhachChaghaaM pratyayaadiinaam‌|aayaneyiiniiyiyaH phaDhakhachChaghaaM pratyayaadiinaam‌ 7.1.2|आयनेयीनीयियः फढखच्छघां प्रत्ययादीनाम्‌|आयनेयीनीयियः फढखच्छघां प्रत्ययादीनाम्‌ ७.१.२|७.१.२|७.१.२ आयनेयीनीयियः फढखच्छघां प्रत्ययादीनाम्‌
आयन् for 1. फ् 2. एय् for ढ् 3. ईन् for ख् 4. ईय् for छ् and इय् for घ are substituted when these consonants stand in the beginning of an affix.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.1.3|7.1.3 jho.antaH|jho.antaH|jho.antaH 7.1.3|झोऽन्तः|झोऽन्तः ७.१.३|७.१.३|७.१.३ झोऽन्तः
अन्त् is substituted for झ of an affix.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.1.4|7.1.4 adabhyastaat‌|adabhyastaat‌|adabhyastaat‌ 7.1.4|अदभ्यस्तात्‌|अदभ्यस्तात्‌ ७.१.४|७.१.४|७.१.४ अदभ्यस्तात्‌
अत् is the substitute of झ after a reduplicated verbal अङ्ग (stem).<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.1.5|7.1.5 aatmanepadeShvanataH|aatmanepadeShvanataH|aatmanepadeShvanataH 7.1.5|आत्मनेपदेष्वनतः|आत्मनेपदेष्वनतः ७.१.५|७.१.५|७.१.५ आत्मनेपदेष्वनतः
अत् is always the substitute of झ in the आत्मनेपद when it is not preceded by a verbal अङ्ग (stem) ending in अ।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

