7.1.37|7.1.37 samaase.anaNJpuurve ktvo lyap‌|samaase.anaNJpuurve ktvo lyap‌|samaase.anaNJpuurve ktvo lyap‌ 7.1.37|समासेऽनञ्पूर्वे क्त्वो ल्यप्‌|समासेऽनञ्पूर्वे क्त्वो ल्यप्‌ ७.१.३७|७.१.३७|७.१.३७ समासेऽनञ्पूर्वे क्त्वो ल्यप्‌
In a compound, the first member of which is an indeclinable but not नञ् ; ल्यप् is substituted for क्त्वा।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.1.38|7.1.38 ktvaa.api Chandasi|ktvaa.api Chandasi|ktvaa.api Chandasi 7.1.38|क्त्वाऽपि छन्दसि|क्त्वाऽपि छन्दसि ७.१.३८|७.१.३८|७.१.३८ क्त्वाऽपि छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the क्त्वा also, as well as ल्यप् is substituted for क्त्वा after an indeclinable compound, other than one preceded by the Negative नञ् ।<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.39|7.1.39 supaaM sulukpuurvasavarNaa.a.achCheyaaDaaDyaayaajaalaH|supaaM sulukpuurvasavarNaa.a.achCheyaaDaaDyaayaajaalaH|supaaM sulukpuurvasavarNaa.a.achCheyaaDaaDyaayaajaalaH 7.1.39|सुपां सुलुक्पूर्वसवर्णाऽऽच्छेयाडाड्यायाजालः|सुपां सुलुक्पूर्वसवर्णाऽऽच्छेयाडाड्यायाजालः ७.१.३९|७.१.३९|७.१.३९ सुपां सुलुक्पूर्वसवर्णाऽऽच्छेयाडाड्यायाजालः
The following irregularly endings are substituted for the various case endings in the छन्दस् (Vedas) 1. स् of the Nominative 1st-Case singular for अस् of the plural 2. the लुक् elision of the case-endings 3. the single substitution of the homogeneous long vowel of the अङ्ग (stem) 4. आ 5. आत् 6. ए (शे) for the ending of the Nominative 1st-Case plural 7. या 8. आ (डा) with the elision of the last vowel and the consonant, if any, that follows it in the अङ्ग (stem) 9. या (ड्या) with a similar shortening of the अङ्ग (stem) 10. या (याच्) and आ (accent of ल).<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.40|7.1.40 amo mash|amo mash|amo mash 7.1.40|अमो मश्|अमो मश् ७.१.४०|७.१.४०|७.१.४० अमो मश्
For the personal ending अम् of the 1st person singular (in the Aorist) म -- अनेकाल्शित्सर्वस्य १.१.५५ is substituted in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.41|7.1.41 lopasta aatmanepadeShu|lopasta aatmanepadeShu|lopasta aatmanepadeShu 7.1.41|लोपस्त आत्मनेपदेषु|लोपस्त आत्मनेपदेषु ७.१.४१|७.१.४१|७.१.४१ लोपस्त आत्मनेपदेषु
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the त of the आत्मनेपद personal ending is elided.<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.42|7.1.42 dhvamo dhvaat‌|dhvamo dhvaat‌|dhvamo dhvaat‌ 7.1.42|ध्वमो ध्वात्‌|ध्वमो ध्वात्‌ ७.१.४२|७.१.४२|७.१.४२ ध्वमो ध्वात्‌
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) ध्वात्‌ is substituted for the personal ending ध्वम्।<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.43|7.1.43 yajadhvainamiti cha|yajadhvainamiti cha|yajadhvainamiti cha 7.1.43|यजध्वैनमिति च|यजध्वैनमिति च ७.१.४३|७.१.४३|७.१.४३ यजध्वैनमिति च
यजध्वैनम् is irregularly formed in the छन्दस् (Vedas) for यजध्वनमेनम्।<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.44|7.1.44 tasya taat‌|tasya taat‌|tasya taat‌ 7.1.44|तस्य तात्‌|तस्य तात्‌ ७.१.४४|७.१.४४|७.१.४४ तस्य तात्‌
For the ending त of the 2nd person plural Imperative is substituted तात्‌ in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.45|7.1.45 taptanaptanathanaashcha|taptanaptanathanaashcha|taptanaptanathanaashcha 7.1.45|तप्तनप्तनथनाश्च|तप्तनप्तनथनाश्च ७.१.४५|७.१.४५|७.१.४५ तप्तनप्तनथनाश्च
Also त and तन (before both, on account of the indicatory प् the preceding vowel of the verbal अङ्ग (stem) is strengthened or if weak not shortened) तन and थन are substituted for the त of the 2nd person plural Imperative in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.46|7.1.46 idanto masi|idanto masi|idanto masi 7.1.46|इदन्तो मसि|इदन्तो मसि ७.१.४६|७.१.४६|७.१.४६ इदन्तो मसि
The personal ending मस् becomes in the छन्दस् (Vedas) मसि ending with a इ।<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.47|7.1.47 ktvo yak|ktvo yak|ktvo yak 7.1.47|क्त्वो यक्|क्त्वो यक् ७.१.४७|७.१.४७|७.१.४७ क्त्वो यक्
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the Absolutive affix क्त्वा gets at the end the augment य।<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.48|7.1.48 iShTviinamiti cha|iShTviinamiti cha|iShTviinamiti cha 7.1.48|इष्ट्वीनमिति च|इष्ट्वीनमिति च ७.१.४८|७.१.४८|७.१.४८ इष्ट्वीनमिति च
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the Absolutive इष्ट्वीनम् is irregularly formed for इष्ट्वा।<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.49|7.1.49 snaatvyaadayashcha|snaatvyaadayashcha|snaatvyaadayashcha 7.1.49|स्नात्व्यादयश्च|स्नात्व्यादयश्च ७.१.४९|७.१.४९|७.१.४९ स्नात्व्यादयश्च
स्नात्व्यी etc. are irregularly formed in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.50|7.1.50 aajjaserasuk|aajjaserasuk|aajjaserasuk 7.1.50|आज्जसेरसुक्|आज्जसेरसुक् ७.१.५०|७.१.५०|७.१.५० आज्जसेरसुक्
After a अङ्ग (stem) ending in अ or आ the affix अस् of the Nominative 1st-Case plural gets, in the छन्दस् (Vedas), the augment अस् (असुक्) at the end.<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.51|7.1.51 ashvaxiiravRShalavaNaanaamaatmapriitau kyachi|ashvaxiiravRShalavaNaanaamaatmapriitau kyachi|ashvaxiiravRShalavaNaanaamaatmapriitau kyachi 7.1.51|अश्वक्षीरवृषलवणानामात्मप्रीतौ क्यचि|अश्वक्षीरवृषलवणानामात्मप्रीतौ क्यचि ७.१.५१|७.१.५१|७.१.५१ अश्वक्षीरवृषलवणानामात्मप्रीतौ क्यचि
The same augment अस् (असुक्) is added after the words 1. अश्व 2. क्षीर 3. वृष and 4. लवण before the Denominative affix क्यचि when the delight of the subject in these things is to be expressed.<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.52|7.1.52 aami sarvanaamnaH suT|aami sarvanaamnaH suT|aami sarvanaamnaH suT 7.1.52|आमि सर्वनाम्नः सुट्|आमि सर्वनाम्नः सुट् ७.१.५२|७.१.५२|७.१.५२ आमि सर्वनाम्नः सुट्
After a Pronominal अङ्ग (stem) ending in a अ or आ the affix आम् of the Genitive 6th-Case plural gets the augment स् at the beginning.<br><br>Terms: छन्दस् substitution

7.1.53|7.1.53 trestrayaH|trestrayaH|trestrayaH 7.1.53|त्रेस्त्रयः|त्रेस्त्रयः ७.१.५३|७.१.५३|७.१.५३ त्रेस्त्रयः
त्रय is substituted for त्रि before the Genitive 6th-Case plural affix.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.1.54|7.1.54 hrasvanadyaapo nuT|hrasvanadyaapo nuT|hrasvanadyaapo nuT 7.1.54|ह्रस्वनद्यापो नुट्|ह्रस्वनद्यापो नुट् ७.१.५४|७.१.५४|७.१.५४ ह्रस्वनद्यापो नुट्
The augment न् is added before the Genitive 6th-Case plural ending आम् after the अङ्ग (stems) ending in a short vowel after अङ्ग (stems) called नदी -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३ etc., and after the अङ्ग (stems) ending in the feminine affix आ।<br><br>Terms: नुम् / नुट् augment

7.1.55|7.1.55 ShaTchaturbhyashcha|ShaTchaturbhyashcha|ShaTchaturbhyashcha 7.1.55|षट्चतुर्भ्यश्च|षट्चतुर्भ्यश्च ७.१.५५|७.१.५५|७.१.५५ षट्चतुर्भ्यश्च
The augment न् is added before the Genitive 6th-Case plural ending आम् after the numerals called षष् and after चतुर्।<br><br>Terms: नुम् / नुट् augment

7.1.56|7.1.56 shriigraamaNyoshChandasi|shriigraamaNyoshChandasi|shriigraamaNyoshChandasi 7.1.56|श्रीग्रामण्योश्छन्दसि|श्रीग्रामण्योश्छन्दसि ७.१.५६|७.१.५६|७.१.५६ श्रीग्रामण्योश्छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) after the words श्री and ग्रामणी the Genitive 6th-Case plural आम् gets the augment न्।<br><br>Terms: नुम् / नुट् augment

7.1.57|7.1.57 goH paadaante|goH paadaante|goH paadaante 7.1.57|गोः पादान्ते|गोः पादान्ते ७.१.५७|७.१.५७|७.१.५७ गोः पादान्ते
After गो when standing at the end of a ऋक् verse, the augment न् comes before the Genitive 6th-Case plural आम् ।<br><br>Terms: नुम् / नुट् augment

7.1.58|7.1.58 idito num dhaatoH|idito num dhaatoH|idito num dhaatoH 7.1.58|इदितो नुम् धातोः|इदितो नुम् धातोः ७.१.५८|७.१.५८|७.१.५८ इदितो नुम् धातोः
न् is added after the vowel of a root in a root which has an indicatory इ in the धातुपाठ।<br><br>Terms: नुम् / नुट् augment

7.1.59|7.1.59 she muchaadiinaam|she muchaadiinaam|she muchaadiinaam 7.1.59|शे मुचादीनाम्|शे मुचादीनाम् ७.१.५९|७.१.५९|७.१.५९ शे मुचादीनाम्
In मुच् etc. Before the characteristic श of the तुदादिगणः (6th Conjugation) the न् is added after the vowel of the root.<br><br>Terms: नुम् / नुट् augment

7.1.60|7.1.60 masjinashorjhali|masjinashorjhali|masjinashorjhali 7.1.60|मस्जिनशोर्झलि|मस्जिनशोर्झलि ७.१.६०|७.१.६०|७.१.६० मस्जिनशोर्झलि
The augment नुम् is added after the vowel of the roots मस्ज् and नश् before an affix beginning with any consonant other than a semi-vowel or a nasal.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.61|7.1.61 radhijabhorachi|radhijabhorachi|radhijabhorachi 7.1.61|रधिजभोरचि|रधिजभोरचि ७.१.६१|७.१.६१|७.१.६१ रधिजभोरचि
The augment नुम् is added after the root-vowel in रध् and जभ् before affixes beginning with a consonant.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.62|7.1.62 neTyaliTi radheH|neTyaliTi radheH|neTyaliTi radheH 7.1.62|नेट्यलिटि रधेः|नेट्यलिटि रधेः ७.१.६२|७.१.६२|७.१.६२ नेट्यलिटि रधेः
The augment नुम् is not added to रध् before an affix beginning with the augment इट् , except in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.63|7.1.63 rabherashabliToH|rabherashabliToH|rabherashabliToH 7.1.63|रभेरशब्लिटोः|रभेरशब्लिटोः ७.१.६३|७.१.६३|७.१.६३ रभेरशब्लिटोः
The augment नुम् is added after the vowel of the root रभ् 'to begin' before an affix beginning with a vowel but not before the विकरण शप् or the affixes of the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.64|7.1.64 labheshcha|labheshcha|labheshcha 7.1.64|लभेश्च|लभेश्च ७.१.६४|७.१.६४|७.१.६४ लभेश्च
So also लभ् 'to get' before an affix beginning with a vowel with the exception of शप् and लिट् , there is no augment नुम् ।<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.65|7.1.65 aaNGo yi|aaNGo yi|aaNGo yi 7.1.65|आङो यि|आङो यि ७.१.६५|७.१.६५|७.१.६५ आङो यि
The augment नुम् is added to लभ् 'to get' preceded by आ before an affix beginning with य।<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.66|7.1.66 upaat‌ prashaMsaayaam|upaat‌ prashaMsaayaam|upaat‌ prashaMsaayaam 7.1.66|उपात्‌ प्रशंसायाम्|उपात्‌ प्रशंसायाम् ७.१.६६|७.१.६६|७.१.६६ उपात्‌ प्रशंसायाम्
The augment नुम् is added to लभ् 'to get' preceded by उप before य when the reference is to something praise-worthy.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.67|7.1.67 upasargaat‌ khalghaNJoH|upasargaat‌ khalghaNJoH|upasargaat‌ khalghaNJoH 7.1.67|उपसर्गात्‌ खल्घञोः|उपसर्गात्‌ खल्घञोः ७.१.६७|७.१.६७|७.१.६७ उपसर्गात्‌ खल्घञोः
The augment नुम् is added to लभ् 'to get' preceded by a Preposition before the affixes खल् -- ईषद्दुःसुषु कृच्छ्राकृच्छ्रार्थेषु खल् ३.३.१२६, and घञ्।<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.68|7.1.68 na sudurbhyaaM kevalaabhyaam|na sudurbhyaaM kevalaabhyaam|na sudurbhyaaM kevalaabhyaam 7.1.68|न सुदुर्भ्यां केवलाभ्याम्|न सुदुर्भ्यां केवलाभ्याम् ७.१.६८|७.१.६८|७.१.६८ न सुदुर्भ्यां केवलाभ्याम्
The augment नुम् is added to लभ् 'to get' preceded by a Preposition before the affixes खल् -- ईषद्दुःसुषु कृच्छ्राकृच्छ्रार्थेषु खल् ३.३.१२६, and घञ् when सु or दुः alone (without another Preposition along with them) precede the root.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.69|7.1.69 vibhaaShaa chiNNamuloH|vibhaaShaa chiNNamuloH|vibhaaShaa chiNNamuloH 7.1.69|विभाषा चिण्णमुलोः|विभाषा चिण्णमुलोः ७.१.६९|७.१.६९|७.१.६९ विभाषा चिण्णमुलोः
The augment नुम् is optionally added to लभ् 'to get' not preceded by a Preposition before the चिण् Aorist and the Absolutive णमुल्।<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.70|7.1.70 ugidachaaM sarvanaamasthaane.adhaatoH|ugidachaaM sarvanaamasthaane.adhaatoH|ugidachaaM sarvanaamasthaane.adhaatoH 7.1.70|उगिदचां सर्वनामस्थानेऽधातोः|उगिदचां सर्वनामस्थानेऽधातोः ७.१.७०|७.१.७०|७.१.७० उगिदचां सर्वनामस्थानेऽधातोः
Whatever has an indicatory उ , ऋ and ऌ (with the exception of a root) and the अङ्ग (stem) अच् (अञ्चि) get the augment नुम् in the strong cases.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.71|7.1.71 yujerasamaase|yujerasamaase|yujerasamaase 7.1.71|युजेरसमासे|युजेरसमासे ७.१.७१|७.१.७१|७.१.७१ युजेरसमासे
The प्रातिपदिक (Nominal Stem) युज् before the strong cases gets the augment (नुम्) न् when it does not stand in a compound.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.72|7.1.72 napuMsakasya jhalachaH|napuMsakasya jhalachaH|napuMsakasya jhalachaH 7.1.72|नपुंसकस्य झलचः|नपुंसकस्य झलचः ७.१.७२|७.१.७२|७.१.७२ नपुंसकस्य झलचः
The augment (नुम्) न् is added in the strong cases to a Neuter अङ्ग (stem) ending in a consonant (other than a nasal or a semi-vowel) or ending in a vowel.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.73|7.1.73 iko.achi vibhaktau|iko.achi vibhaktau|iko.achi vibhaktau 7.1.73|इकोऽचि विभक्तौ|इकोऽचि विभक्तौ ७.१.७३|७.१.७३|७.१.७३ इकोऽचि विभक्तौ
The augment (नुम्) न् is added to a Neuter अङ्ग (stem) ending in a simple vowel, except अ , before a case-affix beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.74|7.1.74 tRtiiyaa.a.adiShu bhaaShitapuMskaM puMvadgaalavasya|tRtiiyaa.a.adiShu bhaaShitapuMskaM puMvadgaalavasya|tRtiiyaa.a.adiShu bhaaShitapuMskaM puMvadgaalavasya 7.1.74|तृतीयाऽऽदिषु भाषितपुंस्कं पुंवद्गालवस्य|तृतीयाऽऽदिषु भाषितपुंस्कं पुंवद्गालवस्य ७.१.७४|७.१.७४|७.१.७४ तृतीयाऽऽदिषु भाषितपुंस्कं पुंवद्गालवस्य
A Neuter अङ्ग (stem) ending in a vowel except अ , of which there exists an equivalent, uniform masculine, is treated like the masculine, in the opinion of गावल before the vowel beginning affixes of the Instrumental -3rd case and the cases that follow it.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.75|7.1.75 asthidadhisakthyaxNaamanaNGudaattaH|asthidadhisakthyaxNaamanaNGudaattaH|asthidadhisakthyaxNaamanaNGudaattaH 7.1.75|अस्थिदधिसक्थ्यक्ष्णामनङुदात्तः|अस्थिदधिसक्थ्यक्ष्णामनङुदात्तः ७.१.७५|७.१.७५|७.१.७५ अस्थिदधिसक्थ्यक्ष्णामनङुदात्तः
The acutely accented (उदात्त) अन् (अनङ्) is substituted for the finals of 1. अस्थि 2. दधि 3. सक्थि and 4. अक्षि, before the affixes of the Instrumental -3rd case and the cases that follow it, which begin with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: अनङ् augment

7.1.76|7.1.76 Chandasyapi dRshyate|Chandasyapi dRshyate|Chandasyapi dRshyate 7.1.76|छन्दस्यपि दृश्यते|छन्दस्यपि दृश्यते ७.१.७६|७.१.७६|७.१.७६ छन्दस्यपि दृश्यते
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) also, the अङ्ग (stems) 1. अस्थि 2. दधि 3. सक्थि and 4. अक्षि are found to take the substitute अन् (अनङ्) before the endings other than those mentioned above.<br><br>Terms: अनङ् augment

7.1.77|7.1.77 ii cha dvivachane|ii cha dvivachane|ii cha dvivachane 7.1.77|ई च द्विवचने|ई च द्विवचने ७.१.७७|७.१.७७|७.१.७७ ई च द्विवचने
The acutely accented (उदात्त) ई is substituted for the final of 1. अस्थि 2. दधि 3. सक्थि and 4. अक्षि in the छन्दस् (Vedas) when the case-affixes of the dual follow.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.78|7.1.78 naabhyastaachChatuH|naabhyastaachChatuH|naabhyastaachChatuH 7.1.78|नाभ्यस्ताच्छतुः|नाभ्यस्ताच्छतुः ७.१.७८|७.१.७८|७.१.७८ नाभ्यस्ताच्छतुः
The participle affix शतृ (अत्-अन्त्) does not take the augment नुम् after a reduplicate अङ्ग (stem).<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.79|7.1.79 vaa napuMsakasya|vaa napuMsakasya|vaa napuMsakasya 7.1.79|वा नपुंसकस्य|वा नपुंसकस्य ७.१.७९|७.१.७९|७.१.७९ वा नपुंसकस्य
The participle affix शतृ (अत्-अन्त्) optionally takes the augment नुम् after a reduplicate अङ्ग (stem) in Neuter nouns.<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.80|7.1.80 aachChiinadyornum|aachChiinadyornum|aachChiinadyornum 7.1.80|आच्छीनद्योर्नुम्|आच्छीनद्योर्नुम् ७.१.८०|७.१.८०|७.१.८० आच्छीनद्योर्नुम्
When the affix शतृ (अत्-अन्त्) comes after a verbal अङ्ग (stem) ending in अ or आ, it may optionally take the augment नुम् before the Neutral case-ending शी and before the feminine affix ई।<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.81|7.1.81 shapshyanornityam|shapshyanornityam|shapshyanornityam 7.1.81|शप्श्यनोर्नित्यम्|शप्श्यनोर्नित्यम् ७.१.८१|७.१.८१|७.१.८१ शप्श्यनोर्नित्यम्
When the affix शतृ (अत्-अन्त्) comes after a verbal अङ्ग (stem) ending in विकरण-s शप् and श्यन् it invariably takes the augment नुम् before the Neutral शी (ई) and the feminine ending ई (नदी).<br><br>Terms: नुम् augment

7.1.82|7.1.82 saavanaDuhaH|saavanaDuhaH|saavanaDuhaH 7.1.82|सावनडुहः|सावनडुहः ७.१.८२|७.१.८२|७.१.८२ सावनडुहः
अनडुह् gets the augment नुम् before the ending सु of the Nominative 1st-Case singular (and Vocative Case).<br><br>Terms: अनडुह् augment

7.1.83|7.1.83 dRksvavassvatavasaaM Chandasi|dRksvavassvatavasaaM Chandasi|dRksvavassvatavasaaM Chandasi 7.1.83|दृक्स्ववस्स्वतवसां छन्दसि|दृक्स्ववस्स्वतवसां छन्दसि ७.१.८३|७.१.८३|७.१.८३ दृक्स्ववस्स्वतवसां छन्दसि
1. दृक् 2. स्वस् and 3. स्वतवस् take the augment नुम् before the affix सु (Nominative 1st-Case and Vocative Case singular) in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

