The word क्रोष्टु 'a jackal' is treated as if it ended in तृच् (तृ), in the feminine, before all case-endings.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.1.97|7.1.97 vibhaaShaa tRtiiyaa.a.adiShvachi|vibhaaShaa tRtiiyaa.a.adiShvachi|vibhaaShaa tRtiiyaa.a.adiShvachi 7.1.97|विभाषा तृतीयाऽऽदिष्वचि|विभाषा तृतीयाऽऽदिष्वचि ७.१.९७|७.१.९७|७.१.९७ विभाषा तृतीयाऽऽदिष्वचि
