7.1.100|7.1.100 RRta iddhaatoH|RRta iddhaatoH|RRta iddhaatoH 7.1.100|ॠत इद्धातोः|ॠत इद्धातोः ७.१.१००|७.१.१००|७.१.१०० ॠत इद्धातोः
For the final long ॠ of a root, there is substituted इर् -- उरण् रपरः १.१.५१.<br><br>Terms: इ substitution

7.1.101|7.1.101 upadhaayaashcha|upadhaayaashcha|upadhaayaashcha 7.1.101|उपधायाश्च|उपधायाश्च ७.१.१०१|७.१.१०१|७.१.१०१ उपधायाश्च
इर् is also substituted for the penultimate long ॠ of a root.<br><br>Terms: इ substitution

7.1.102|7.1.102 udoShThyapuurvasya|udoShThyapuurvasya|udoShThyapuurvasya 7.1.102|उदोष्ठ्यपूर्वस्य|उदोष्ठ्यपूर्वस्य ७.१.१०२|७.१.१०२|७.१.१०२ उदोष्ठ्यपूर्वस्य
उर् is substituted for the long ॠ of a root when it is preceded by a labial consonant belonging to the root.<br><br>Terms: उ substitution

7.1.103|7.1.103 bahulaM Chandasi|bahulaM Chandasi|bahulaM Chandasi 7.1.103|बहुलं छन्दसि|बहुलं छन्दसि ७.१.१०३|७.१.१०३|७.१.१०३ बहुलं छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas), the उर् substitution for ॠ of a root-stem is diverse.<br><br>Terms: उ substitution

7.2.1|7.2.1 sichi vRddhiH parasmaipadeShu|sichi vRddhiH parasmaipadeShu|sichi vRddhiH parasmaipadeShu 7.2.1|सिचि वृद्धिः परस्मैपदेषु|सिचि वृद्धिः परस्मैपदेषु ७.२.१|७.२.१|७.२.१ सिचि वृद्धिः परस्मैपदेषु
Before the Aorist-characteristic स् (सिच्), वृद्धि is substituted in the परस्मैपद for the final of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in इ , उ , ऋ (long or short -- इको गुणवृद्धी १.१.३).<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.2.2|7.2.2 ato rlaantasya|ato rlaantasya|ato rlaantasya 7.2.2|अतो र्लान्तस्य|अतो र्लान्तस्य ७.२.२|७.२.२|७.२.२ अतो र्लान्तस्य
वृद्धि is substituted for the short अ when it is immediately followed by the final र् or ल् of a root, before the परस्मैपद s-Aorist.<br><br>Terms: Aorist वृद्धि

7.2.3|7.2.3 vadavrajahalantasyaachaH|vadavrajahalantasyaachaH|vadavrajahalantasyaachaH 7.2.3|वदव्रजहलन्तस्याचः|वदव्रजहलन्तस्याचः ७.२.३|७.२.३|७.२.३ वदव्रजहलन्तस्याचः
In the परस्मैपद s-Aorist there is वृद्धि of the अ of वद , व्रज् and of any vowel, without distinction, of the अङ्ग (stems) ending in a consonant.<br><br>Terms: Aorist वृद्धि

7.2.4|7.2.4 neTi|neTi|neTi 7.2.4|नेटि|नेटि ७.२.४|७.२.४|७.२.४ नेटि
The vowel of a अङ्ग (stem) ending in a consonant does not get वृद्धि when the स् (सिच्) takes the augment इट् ।<br><br>Terms: Aorist वृद्धि

7.2.5|7.2.5 hmyantaxaNashvasajaagRNishvyeditaam|hmyantaxaNashvasajaagRNishvyeditaam|hmyantaxaNashvasajaagRNishvyeditaam 7.2.5|ह्म्यन्तक्षणश्वसजागृणिश्व्येदिताम्|ह्म्यन्तक्षणश्वसजागृणिश्व्येदिताम् ७.२.५|७.२.५|७.२.५ ह्म्यन्तक्षणश्वसजागृणिश्व्येदिताम्
The वृद्धि of the vowel of the following अङ्ग (stems), does not take place before the इट् augment s-Aorist in the परस्मैपद ; namely - the अङ्ग (stems) ending in 1. ह् 2. म् or 3. य् , the roots 1. क्षण् 2. श्वस् 3. जागृ , a stem formed with णि, the root श्वि and the roots having an indicatory ए in the धातुपाठ।<br><br>Terms: Aorist वृद्धि

7.2.6|7.2.6 UrNotervibhaaShaa|UrNotervibhaaShaa|UrNotervibhaaShaa 7.2.6|ऊर्णोतेर्विभाषा|ऊर्णोतेर्विभाषा ७.२.६|७.२.६|७.२.६ ऊर्णोतेर्विभाषा
Before an इट् beginning substituted-Aorist of the परस्मैपद there is optional वृद्धि of the vowel of ऊर्णु।<br><br>Terms: Aorist वृद्धि

7.2.7|7.2.7 ato halaaderlaghoH|ato halaaderlaghoH|ato halaaderlaghoH 7.2.7|अतो हलादेर्लघोः|अतो हलादेर्लघोः ७.२.७|७.२.७|७.२.७ अतो हलादेर्लघोः
Before the इट् beginning s-Aorist of the परस्मैपद the short अ of the root gets optionally वृद्धि when the अङ्ग (stem) begins with a consonant and the अ is prosodially short by being followed by a simple consonant.<br><br>Terms: Aorist वृद्धि

7.2.8|7.2.8 neD vashi kRti|neD vashi kRti|neD vashi kRti 7.2.8|नेड् वशि कृति|नेड् वशि कृति ७.२.८|७.२.८|७.२.८ नेड् वशि कृति
The augment इट् is not added to a कृत् affix beginning with a sonant consonant (वश् प्रत्यहार).<br><br>Terms: Aorist वृद्धि

7.2.9|7.2.9 titutratathasisusarakaseShu cha|titutratathasisusarakaseShu cha|titutratathasisusarakaseShu cha 7.2.9|तितुत्रतथसिसुसरकसेषु च|तितुत्रतथसिसुसरकसेषु च ७.२.९|७.२.९|७.२.९ तितुत्रतथसिसुसरकसेषु च
The इट् augment is not taken by the following कृत् affixes - 1. ति 2. तु 3. त्र 4. त 5. थ 6. सि 7. सु 8. सर 9. क and 10. स।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.10|7.2.10 ekaacha upadeshe.anudaattaat‌|ekaacha upadeshe.anudaattaat‌|ekaacha upadeshe.anudaattaat‌ 7.2.10|एकाच उपदेशेऽनुदात्तात्‌|एकाच उपदेशेऽनुदात्तात्‌ ७.२.१०|७.२.१०|७.२.१० एकाच उपदेशेऽनुदात्तात्‌
The augment इट् is not added to that affix which is joined to a root which is joined to a root, which in the Grammatical system of Instruction (i.e. in the धातुपाठ) is one syllable and is without accent (अनुदात्त).<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.11|7.2.11 shryukaH kiti|shryukaH kiti|shryukaH kiti 7.2.11|श्र्युकः किति|श्र्युकः किति ७.२.११|७.२.११|७.२.११ श्र्युकः किति
The augment इट् is not added to an affix having an indicatory फ् when it comes after the root श्रि or after a mono-syllabic root ending in 1. उ 2. ऊ 3. ऋ or 4. ॠ in the धातुपाठ।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.12|7.2.12 sani grahaguhoshcha|sani grahaguhoshcha|sani grahaguhoshcha 7.2.12|सनि ग्रहगुहोश्च|सनि ग्रहगुहोश्च ७.२.१२|७.२.१२|७.२.१२ सनि ग्रहगुहोश्च
The Desiderative affix सन् does not get the augment इट् , not only after roots ending in 1. उ 2. ऊ 3. ऋ and 4. ॠ but also after ग्रह and गुह।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.13|7.2.13 kRsRbhRvRstudrusrushruvo liTi|kRsRbhRvRstudrusrushruvo liTi|kRsRbhRvRstudrusrushruvo liTi 7.2.13|कृसृभृवृस्तुद्रुस्रुश्रुवो लिटि|कृसृभृवृस्तुद्रुस्रुश्रुवो लिटि ७.२.१३|७.२.१३|७.२.१३ कृसृभृवृस्तुद्रुस्रुश्रुवो लिटि
The personal endings of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) do not get the augment इट् after 1 कृ 2. सृ 3. भृ 4. वृ 5. स्तु 6. द्रु 7. स्रु 8.श्रु।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.14|7.2.14 shviidito niShThaayaam|shviidito niShThaayaam|shviidito niShThaayaam 7.2.14|श्वीदितो निष्ठायाम्|श्वीदितो निष्ठायाम् ७.२.१४|७.२.१४|७.२.१४ श्वीदितो निष्ठायाम्
The participial affixes त and तथत् (क्त and क्तवतु) do not get the इट् augment after श्वि and after the root which has an indicatory ई।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.15|7.2.15 yasya vibhaaShaa|yasya vibhaaShaa|yasya vibhaaShaa 7.2.15|यस्य विभाषा|यस्य विभाषा ७.२.१५|७.२.१५|७.२.१५ यस्य विभाषा
The participial affixes do not take the इट् augment after those roots, to which another suffix can optionally be added, with or without this augment इ।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.16|7.2.16 aaditashcha|aaditashcha|aaditashcha 7.2.16|आदितश्च|आदितश्च ७.२.१६|७.२.१६|७.२.१६ आदितश्च
The participial affixes do not take the इट् augment after a root which has an indicatory आ।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.17|7.2.17 vibhaaShaa bhaavaadikarmaNoH|vibhaaShaa bhaavaadikarmaNoH|vibhaaShaa bhaavaadikarmaNoH 7.2.17|विभाषा भावादिकर्मणोः|विभाषा भावादिकर्मणोः ७.२.१७|७.२.१७|७.२.१७ विभाषा भावादिकर्मणोः
The participial affixes optionally take the इट् augment after roots having an indicatory आ when the affixes have an Impersonal sense or denote the beginning of an action.<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.18|7.2.18 xubdhasvaantadhvaantalagnamliShTaviribdhaphaaNTabaaDhaani manthamanastamaHsaktaavispaShTasvaraanaayaasabhRsheShu|xubdhasvaantadhvaantalagnamliShTaviribdhaphaaNTabaaDhaani manthamanastamaHsaktaavispaShTasvaraanaayaasabhRsheShu|xubdhasvaantadhvaantalagnamliShTaviribdhaphaaNTabaaDhaani manthamanastamaHsaktaavispaShTasvaraanaayaasabhRsheShu 7.2.18|क्षुब्धस्वान्तध्वान्तलग्नम्लिष्टविरिब्धफाण्टबाढानि मन्थमनस्तमःसक्ताविस्पष्टस्वरानायासभृशेषु|क्षुब्धस्वान्तध्वान्तलग्नम्लिष्टविरिब्धफाण्टबाढानि मन्थमनस्तमःसक्ताविस्पष्टस्वरानायासभृशेषु ७.२.१८|७.२.१८|७.२.१८ क्षुब्धस्वान्तध्वान्तलग्नम्लिष्टविरिब्धफाण्टबाढानि मन्थमनस्तमःसक्ताविस्पष्टस्वरानायासभृशेषु
The following words are made without the इट् augment in the senses given against them - 1. क्षुब्ध 'a churning stick' 2. स्वान्तः 'the mind' 3. ध्वान्तः 'darkness' 4. लग्नः 'attached' 5. म्लिष्टः 'indistinct or unintelligible' 6. विरिब्धः 'a note or a tone' 7. फाण्टः 'made without an effort or by an easy process' and 8. बाढः 'excessive'.<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.19|7.2.19 dhRShishasii vaiyaatye|dhRShishasii vaiyaatye|dhRShishasii vaiyaatye 7.2.19|धृषिशसी वैयात्ये|धृषिशसी वैयात्ये ७.२.१९|७.२.१९|७.२.१९ धृषिशसी वैयात्ये
The participial affix does not get इट् augment after the roots 1. धृष् and 2. शस् when meaning 'bold, impudent and arrogant'.<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.20|7.2.20 dRDhaH sthuulabalayoH|dRDhaH sthuulabalayoH|dRDhaH sthuulabalayoH 7.2.20|दृढः स्थूलबलयोः|दृढः स्थूलबलयोः ७.२.२०|७.२.२०|७.२.२० दृढः स्थूलबलयोः
