7.2.23|7.2.23 ghuShiravishabdane|ghuShiravishabdane|ghuShiravishabdane 7.2.23|घुषिरविशब्दने|घुषिरविशब्दने ७.२.२३|७.२.२३|७.२.२३ घुषिरविशब्दने
The participial affix does not take the augment इट् after the root घुष् in any sense other than that of 'proclaimed'.<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.2.24|7.2.24 ardeH saMnivibhyaH|ardeH saMnivibhyaH|ardeH saMnivibhyaH 7.2.24|अर्देः संनिविभ्यः|अर्देः संनिविभ्यः ७.२.२४|७.२.२४|७.२.२४ अर्देः संनिविभ्यः
