7.2.111|7.2.111 ido.ay puMsi|ido.ay puMsi|ido.ay puMsi 7.2.111|इदोऽय् पुंसि|इदोऽय् पुंसि ७.२.१११|७.२.१११|७.२.१११ इदोऽय् पुंसि
अय् is substituted for the इद् of इदम् in the Nominative 1st-Case singular masculine.<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम इदम्

7.2.112|7.2.112 anaapyakaH|anaapyakaH|anaapyakaH 7.2.112|अनाप्यकः|अनाप्यकः ७.२.११२|७.२.११२|७.२.११२ अनाप्यकः
अन is substituted for the इद् of इदम् in the Instrumental -3rd case singular and the cases that follow, provided that the augment अकच् is not added.<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम इदम्

7.2.113|7.2.113 hali lopaH|hali lopaH|hali lopaH 7.2.113|हलि लोपः|हलि लोपः ७.२.११३|७.२.११३|७.२.११३ हलि लोपः
The इद् of इदम् is elided before a विभक्ति affix beginning with a consonant.<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम इदम्

7.2.114|7.2.114 mRjervRddhiH|mRjervRddhiH|mRjervRddhiH 7.2.114|मृजेर्वृद्धिः|मृजेर्वृद्धिः ७.२.११४|७.२.११४|७.२.११४ मृजेर्वृद्धिः
The वृद्धि (आर्) is substituted for the root vowel (ऋ) of the अङ्ग (stem) मृज् before an affix.<br><br>Terms: तद्धित वृद्धि

7.2.115|7.2.115 acho NJNiti|acho NJNiti|acho NJNiti 7.2.115|अचो ञ्णिति|अचो ञ्णिति ७.२.११५|७.२.११५|७.२.११५ अचो ञ्णिति
Before the affixes having an indicatory ञ् or ण् , वृद्धि is substituted for the end-vowel of a अङ्ग (stem).<br><br>Terms: तद्धित वृद्धि

7.2.116|7.2.116 ata upadhaayaaH|ata upadhaayaaH|ata upadhaayaaH 7.2.116|अत उपधायाः|अत उपधायाः ७.२.११६|७.२.११६|७.२.११६ अत उपधायाः
In a अङ्ग (stem) ending in a consonant with an अ immediately preceding it, the वृद्धि is substituted for such अ when followed by an indicatory ञ् or ण्।<br><br>Terms: तद्धित वृद्धि

7.2.117|7.2.117 taddhiteShvachaamaadeH|taddhiteShvachaamaadeH|taddhiteShvachaamaadeH 7.2.117|तद्धितेष्वचामादेः|तद्धितेष्वचामादेः ७.२.११७|७.२.११७|७.२.११७ तद्धितेष्वचामादेः
The वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowel of the अङ्ग (stem) when a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् or ण् follows.<br><br>Terms: तद्धित वृद्धि

7.2.118|7.2.118 kiti cha|kiti cha|kiti cha 7.2.118|किति च|किति च ७.२.११८|७.२.११८|७.२.११८ किति च
The वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowel of the अङ्ग (stem) when a तद्धित affix with an indicatory क् follows.<br><br>Terms: तद्धित वृद्धि

7.3.1|7.3.1 devikaashiMshapaadityavaaDdiirghasatrashreyasaamaat‌|devikaashiMshapaadityavaaDdiirghasatrashreyasaamaat‌|devikaashiMshapaadityavaaDdiirghasatrashreyasaamaat‌ 7.3.1|देविकाशिंशपादित्यवाड्दीर्घसत्रश्रेयसामात्‌|देविकाशिंशपादित्यवाड्दीर्घसत्रश्रेयसामात्‌ ७.३.१|७.३.१|७.३.१ देविकाशिंशपादित्यवाड्दीर्घसत्रश्रेयसामात्‌
When a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् follows, आ is substituted instead of वृद्धि for the first vowels of the following - 1. देविका 2. शिंशपा 3. दित्यवाट् 4. दीर्घसत्र and 5. श्रेयस।<br><br>Terms: तद्धित changes

7.3.2|7.3.2 kekayamittrayupralayaanaaM yaaderiyaH|kekayamittrayupralayaanaaM yaaderiyaH|kekayamittrayupralayaanaaM yaaderiyaH 7.3.2|केकयमित्त्रयुप्रलयानां यादेरियः|केकयमित्त्रयुप्रलयानां यादेरियः ७.३.२|७.३.२|७.३.२ केकयमित्त्रयुप्रलयानां यादेरियः
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् the वृद्धि is not substituted for the first vowel in a compound when it follows a word ending in य् or व् but ऐ and औ are respectively placed before the semi-vowels.<br><br>Terms: तद्धित changes

7.3.3|7.3.3 na yvaabhyaaM padaantaabhyaam puurvau tu taabhyaamaich|na yvaabhyaaM padaantaabhyaam puurvau tu taabhyaamaich|na yvaabhyaaM padaantaabhyaam puurvau tu taabhyaamaich 7.3.3|न य्वाभ्यां पदान्ताभ्याम् पूर्वौ तु ताभ्यामैच्|न य्वाभ्यां पदान्ताभ्याम् पूर्वौ तु ताभ्यामैच् ७.३.३|७.३.३|७.३.३ न य्वाभ्यां पदान्ताभ्याम् पूर्वौ तु ताभ्यामैच्
Before a तद्धित affix with an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् the वृद्धि is not substituted for the first vowel in a compound when it follows a word ending in य् or व् but ऐ and औ are respectively placed before the semi-vowels.<br><br>Terms: तद्धित changes

7.3.4|7.3.4 dvaaraadiinaaM cha|dvaaraadiinaaM cha|dvaaraadiinaaM cha 7.3.4|द्वारादीनां च|द्वारादीनां च ७.३.४|७.३.४|७.३.४ द्वारादीनां च
Before a तद्धित affix with an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् the वृद्धि is not substituted for the first vowel after य् or व् but ऐ and औ are respectively placed before the semi-vowels in द्वार etc.<br><br>Terms: तद्धित changes

7.3.5|7.3.5 nyagrodhasya cha kevalasya|nyagrodhasya cha kevalasya|nyagrodhasya cha kevalasya 7.3.5|न्यग्रोधस्य च केवलस्य|न्यग्रोधस्य च केवलस्य ७.३.५|७.३.५|७.३.५ न्यग्रोधस्य च केवलस्य
ऐ is placed before the य् of न्यग्रोध instead of वृद्धि when the word stands alone and is not a member of a compound and is followed by a तद्धित affix with the indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् ।<br><br>Terms: Peculiar वृद्धि

7.3.6|7.3.6 na karmavyatihaare|na karmavyatihaare|na karmavyatihaare 7.3.6|न कर्मव्यतिहारे|न कर्मव्यतिहारे ७.३.६|७.३.६|७.३.६ न कर्मव्यतिहारे
The prohibition and the augment ordained by न य्वाभ्यां पदान्ताभ्याम् पूर्वौ तु ताभ्यामैच् ७.३.३, do not apply to a word which expresses the reciprocity of an action.<br><br>Terms: Peculiar वृद्धि

7.3.7|7.3.7 svaagataadiinaaM cha|svaagataadiinaaM cha|svaagataadiinaaM cha 7.3.7|स्वागतादीनां च|स्वागतादीनां च ७.३.७|७.३.७|७.३.७ स्वागतादीनां च
The prohibition and the augment ordained by न य्वाभ्यां पदान्ताभ्याम् पूर्वौ तु ताभ्यामैच् ७.३.३, do not apply also to स्वागत etc.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.8|7.3.8 shvaaderiNJi|shvaaderiNJi|shvaaderiNJi 7.3.8|श्वादेरिञि|श्वादेरिञि ७.३.८|७.३.८|७.३.८ श्वादेरिञि
A compound beginning with श्वन् and followed by the तद्धित affix इञ् is not governed by the prohibition nor takes the augment taught in द्वारादीनां च ७.३.४.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.9|7.3.9 padaantasyaanyatarasyaam|padaantasyaanyatarasyaam|padaantasyaanyatarasyaam 7.3.9|पदान्तस्यान्यतरस्याम्|पदान्तस्यान्यतरस्याम् ७.३.९|७.३.९|७.३.९ पदान्तस्यान्यतरस्याम्
The sūtra द्वारादीनां च ७.३.४ is optionally applied to श्वन् followed by पद।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.10|7.3.10 uttarapadasya|uttarapadasya|uttarapadasya 7.3.10|उत्तरपदस्य|उत्तरपदस्य ७.३.१०|७.३.१०|७.३.१० उत्तरपदस्य
Up to यथातथयथापुरयोः पर्यायेण ७.३.३१ inclusive, the substitution of वृद्धि will take place for the first vowel of the second member in a compound.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.11|7.3.11 avayavaadRtoH|avayavaadRtoH|avayavaadRtoH 7.3.11|अवयवादृतोः|अवयवादृतोः ७.३.११|७.३.११|७.३.११ अवयवादृतोः
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowel of a word denoting season when it is preceded by a word denoting a part.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.12|7.3.12 susarvaardhaajjanapadasya|susarvaardhaajjanapadasya|susarvaardhaajjanapadasya 7.3.12|सुसर्वार्धाज्जनपदस्य|सुसर्वार्धाज्जनपदस्य ७.३.१२|७.३.१२|७.३.१२ सुसर्वार्धाज्जनपदस्य
After 1. सु 2. सर्व and 3. अर्ध the first vowel of the name of a country gets the वृद्धि when a तद्धित affix with an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् follows.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.13|7.3.13 disho.amadraaNaam|disho.amadraaNaam|disho.amadraaNaam 7.3.13|दिशोऽमद्राणाम्|दिशोऽमद्राणाम् ७.३.१३|७.३.१३|७.३.१३ दिशोऽमद्राणाम्
After a word denoting direction, the first vowel of the name of a country with the exception of मद्र gets वृद्धि before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.14|7.3.14 praachaaM graamanagaraaNaam|praachaaM graamanagaraaNaam|praachaaM graamanagaraaNaam 7.3.14|प्राचां ग्रामनगराणाम्|प्राचां ग्रामनगराणाम् ७.३.१४|७.३.१४|७.३.१४ प्राचां ग्रामनगराणाम्
After a word denoting direction, the first vowel of the name of a village or city in the land of the Eastern people, gets the वृद्धि before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.15|7.3.15 saMkhyaayaaH saMvatsarasaMkhyasya cha|saMkhyaayaaH saMvatsarasaMkhyasya cha|saMkhyaayaaH saMvatsarasaMkhyasya cha 7.3.15|संख्यायाः संवत्सरसंख्यस्य च|संख्यायाः संवत्सरसंख्यस्य च ७.३.१५|७.३.१५|७.३.१५ संख्यायाः संवत्सरसंख्यस्य च
After a numeral, the first vowel of संवत्सर and of a numeral, gets वृद्धि before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.16|7.3.16 varShasyaabhaviShyati|varShasyaabhaviShyati|varShasyaabhaviShyati 7.3.16|वर्षस्याभविष्यति|वर्षस्याभविष्यति ७.३.१६|७.३.१६|७.३.१६ वर्षस्याभविष्यति
After a numeral, the first vowel of वर्ष gets वृद्धि before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् when the affix does not refer to a Future time.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.17|7.3.17 parimaaNaantasyaasaMJNaashaaNayoH|parimaaNaantasyaasaMJNaashaaNayoH|parimaaNaantasyaasaMJNaashaaNayoH 7.3.17|परिमाणान्तस्यासंज्ञाशाणयोः|परिमाणान्तस्यासंज्ञाशाणयोः ७.३.१७|७.३.१७|७.३.१७ परिमाणान्तस्यासंज्ञाशाणयोः
After a numeral, the first vowel of a word denoting mass in its widest sense (with the exception of शाण) gets the वृद्धि before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् when the word so formed does not mean a Name.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.18|7.3.18 je proShThapadaanaam|je proShThapadaanaam|je proShThapadaanaam 7.3.18|जे प्रोष्ठपदानाम्|जे प्रोष्ठपदानाम् ७.३.१८|७.३.१८|७.३.१८ जे प्रोष्ठपदानाम्
In प्रोष्ठपद and its synonyms, the first vowel of the second member gets the वृद्धि before a तद्धित affix meaning 'born in that time' and having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.19|7.3.19 hRdbhagasindhvante puurvapadasya cha|hRdbhagasindhvante puurvapadasya cha|hRdbhagasindhvante puurvapadasya cha 7.3.19|हृद्भगसिन्ध्वन्ते पूर्वपदस्य च|हृद्भगसिन्ध्वन्ते पूर्वपदस्य च ७.३.१९|७.३.१९|७.३.१९ हृद्भगसिन्ध्वन्ते पूर्वपदस्य च
The वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowels of both (the first and second) members in a compound ending with 1. हृद् 2. भग and 3. सिन्धु before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.20|7.3.20 anushatikaadiinaaM cha|anushatikaadiinaaM cha|anushatikaadiinaaM cha 7.3.20|अनुशतिकादीनां च|अनुशतिकादीनां च ७.३.२०|७.३.२०|७.३.२० अनुशतिकादीनां च
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् , the वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowel of both members of the compounds अनुशतिका etc.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.21|7.3.21 devataadvaMdve cha|devataadvaMdve cha|devataadvaMdve cha 7.3.21|देवताद्वंद्वे च|देवताद्वंद्वे च ७.३.२१|७.३.२१|७.३.२१ देवताद्वंद्वे च
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् , the वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowels of both members of द्वन्द समास of the names of देवता-s।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.22|7.3.22 nendrasya parasya|nendrasya parasya|nendrasya parasya 7.3.22|नेन्द्रस्य परस्य|नेन्द्रस्य परस्य ७.३.२२|७.३.२२|७.३.२२ नेन्द्रस्य परस्य
But the वृद्धि of the first vowel of इन्द्र when it stands as the second member of a द्वन्द समास , does not take place before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.23|7.3.23 diirghaachcha varuNasya|diirghaachcha varuNasya|diirghaachcha varuNasya 7.3.23|दीर्घाच्च वरुणस्य|दीर्घाच्च वरुणस्य ७.३.२३|७.३.२३|७.३.२३ दीर्घाच्च वरुणस्य
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् in a द्वन्द समास of god-names, the वृद्धि is not substituted for the first vowel of वरुण when a long vowel precedes it.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.24|7.3.24 praachaaM nagaraante|praachaaM nagaraante|praachaaM nagaraante 7.3.24|प्राचां नगरान्ते|प्राचां नगरान्ते ७.३.२४|७.३.२४|७.३.२४ प्राचां नगरान्ते
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् the वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowels of both members of the compound which is the name of a city of the Eastern people and which ends in the word नगर।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.25|7.3.25 jangaladhenuvalajaantasya vibhaaShitamuttaram‌|jangaladhenuvalajaantasya vibhaaShitamuttaram‌|jangaladhenuvalajaantasya vibhaaShitamuttaram‌ 7.3.25|जङ्गलधेनुवलजान्तस्य विभाषितमुत्तरम्‌|जङ्गलधेनुवलजान्तस्य विभाषितमुत्तरम्‌ ७.३.२५|७.३.२५|७.३.२५ जङ्गलधेनुवलजान्तस्य विभाषितमुत्तरम्‌
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् the वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowel of the compound ending in 1. जङ्गल 2. धेनु and 3. बलज and optionally for the first vowel of these second members also.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.26|7.3.26 ardhaat‌ parimaaNasya puurvasya tu vaa|ardhaat‌ parimaaNasya puurvasya tu vaa|ardhaat‌ parimaaNasya puurvasya tu vaa 7.3.26|अर्धात्‌ परिमाणस्य पूर्वस्य तु वा|अर्धात्‌ परिमाणस्य पूर्वस्य तु वा ७.३.२६|७.३.२६|७.३.२६ अर्धात्‌ परिमाणस्य पूर्वस्य तु वा
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् the वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowel of the second member, denoting a mass in its widest sense when the word अर्ध precedes it, but optionally for the first vowel of अर्ध।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.27|7.3.27 naataH parasya|naataH parasya|naataH parasya 7.3.27|नातः परस्य|नातः परस्य ७.३.२७|७.३.२७|७.३.२७ नातः परस्य
When the first vowel of the second member preceded by अर्ध and denoting mass is short अ before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् and optionally so for the first vowel of the first member (i.e. अर्ध).<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.28|7.3.28 pravaahaNasya Dhe|pravaahaNasya Dhe|pravaahaNasya Dhe 7.3.28|प्रवाहणस्य ढे|प्रवाहणस्य ढे ७.३.२८|७.३.२८|७.३.२८ प्रवाहणस्य ढे
Before the affix ढ (एय), the वृद्धि is substituted for the first vowel of the second member of प्रवाहण but optionally so for the first member (i.e. प्र).<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.29|7.3.29 tatpratyayasya cha|tatpratyayasya cha|tatpratyayasya cha 7.3.29|तत्प्रत्ययस्य च|तत्प्रत्ययस्य च ७.३.२९|७.३.२९|७.३.२९ तत्प्रत्ययस्य च
Even so from a new derivative from this stem ending in ढ, formed with a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् there is वृद्धि substitution for the first vowel of the second member and optionally for the first vowel of the first member in प्रवाहणेय and प्रावाहणेय।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.30|7.3.30 naNJaH shuchiishvaraxetraJNakushalanipuNaanaam|naNJaH shuchiishvaraxetraJNakushalanipuNaanaam|naNJaH shuchiishvaraxetraJNakushalanipuNaanaam 7.3.30|नञः शुचीश्वरक्षेत्रज्ञकुशलनिपुणानाम्|नञः शुचीश्वरक्षेत्रज्ञकुशलनिपुणानाम् ७.३.३०|७.३.३०|७.३.३० नञः शुचीश्वरक्षेत्रज्ञकुशलनिपुणानाम्
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् , the वृद्धि is always substituted for the first vowel of 1. शुचि 2. ईश्वर 3. क्षेत्रज्ञ 4. कुशल and 4. निपुण when preceded by the Negative particle, but this substitution is optional for the vowel of the Negative particles.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.31|7.3.31 yathaatathayathaapurayoH paryaayeNa|yathaatathayathaapurayoH paryaayeNa|yathaatathayathaapurayoH paryaayeNa 7.3.31|यथातथयथापुरयोः पर्यायेण|यथातथयथापुरयोः पर्यायेण ७.३.३१|७.३.३१|७.३.३१ यथातथयथापुरयोः पर्यायेण
Before a तद्धित affix having an indicatory ञ् , ण् or क् , the words यथातथ and यथापुर may have वृद्धि of the first vowel of their first member or that of the second member, in alteration.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.32|7.3.32 hanasto.achiNNaloH|hanasto.achiNNaloH|hanasto.achiNNaloH 7.3.32|हनस्तोऽचिण्णलोः|हनस्तोऽचिण्णलोः ७.३.३२|७.३.३२|७.३.३२ हनस्तोऽचिण्णलोः
त् is substituted for the न् of the root हन् 'to kill' before an affix with a indicatory ञ् or ण् which also causes वृद्धि of the penultimate अ , but the augment is not added before the Aorist sign nor before the Personal ending णल् of the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.33|7.3.33 aato yuk chiNkRtoH|aato yuk chiNkRtoH|aato yuk chiNkRtoH 7.3.33|आतो युक् चिण्कृतोः|आतो युक् चिण्कृतोः ७.३.३३|७.३.३३|७.३.३३ आतो युक् चिण्कृतोः
A root-अङ्ग (stem) ending in आ gets the augment युक् (य्) before the Aorist sign चिण् which causes also the वृद्धि of the root-vowel.<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.34|7.3.34 nodaattopadeshasya maantasyaanaachameH|nodaattopadeshasya maantasyaanaachameH|nodaattopadeshasya maantasyaanaachameH 7.3.34|नोदात्तोपदेशस्य मान्तस्यानाचमेः|नोदात्तोपदेशस्य मान्तस्यानाचमेः ७.३.३४|७.३.३४|७.३.३४ नोदात्तोपदेशस्य मान्तस्यानाचमेः
The वृद्धि is not substituted before the Aorist sign चिण् or a कृत् affix with an indicatory ञ् or ण् for the vowel of that root which ends in म and is acutely accented (उदात्त) in its original enunciation (धातुपाठ), but not so in चम् after आ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.35|7.3.35 janivadhyoshcha|janivadhyoshcha|janivadhyoshcha 7.3.35|जनिवध्योश्च|जनिवध्योश्च ७.३.३५|७.३.३५|७.३.३५ जनिवध्योश्च
The वृद्धि is not substituted for the vowels of जन् 'to produce' and वधे before the Aorist sign चिण् and the कृत् affixes with an indicatory ञ् or ण् ।<br><br>Terms: वृद्धि

7.3.36|7.3.36 arttihriibliiriiknuuyiixmaayyaataaM puNGNau|arttihriibliiriiknuuyiixmaayyaataaM puNGNau|arttihriibliiriiknuuyiixmaayyaataaM puNGNau 7.3.36|अर्त्तिह्रीब्लीरीक्नूयीक्ष्माय्यातां पुङ्णौ|अर्त्तिह्रीब्लीरीक्नूयीक्ष्माय्यातां पुङ्णौ ७.३.३६|७.३.३६|७.३.३६ अर्त्तिह्रीब्लीरीक्नूयीक्ष्माय्यातां पुङ्णौ
The augment पुक् (प्) is added to the roots 1. ऋ 2. ह्री 3. व्ली 4. री 5. क्नुय् 6. क्ष्माय and to a root ending in long आ when the affix णि (the Causative) follows.<br><br>Terms: पुक् augment

7.3.37|7.3.37 shaachChaasaahvaavyaavepaaM yuk|shaachChaasaahvaavyaavepaaM yuk|shaachChaasaahvaavyaavepaaM yuk 7.3.37|शाच्छासाह्वाव्यावेपां युक्|शाच्छासाह्वाव्यावेपां युक् ७.३.३७|७.३.३७|७.३.३७ शाच्छासाह्वाव्यावेपां युक्
The augment युक् (य्) is added to the verbal stems 1. शा 2. छा 3. सा 4. ह्वा 5. वे and 6. पा before the affix णि (Causative).<br><br>Terms: युक् augment

7.3.38|7.3.38 vo vidhuunane juk|vo vidhuunane juk|vo vidhuunane juk 7.3.38|वो विधूनने जुक्|वो विधूनने जुक् ७.३.३८|७.३.३८|७.३.३८ वो विधूनने जुक्
वा gets the augment जुक् (ज्) before the affix णि when the Causative has the sense of 'shaking'.<br><br>Terms: जुक् augment

7.3.39|7.3.39 liilornuglukaavanyatarasyaaM snehavipaatane|liilornuglukaavanyatarasyaaM snehavipaatane|liilornuglukaavanyatarasyaaM snehavipaatane 7.3.39|लीलोर्नुग्लुकावन्यतरस्यां स्नेहविपातने|लीलोर्नुग्लुकावन्यतरस्यां स्नेहविपातने ७.३.३९|७.३.३९|७.३.३९ लीलोर्नुग्लुकावन्यतरस्यां स्नेहविपातने
The roots ली and ला optionally get नुक् and लुक् augment respectively before the affix णि when the Causative means 'the melting of a fatty substance'.<br><br>Terms: नुक् and लुक् augment

7.3.40|7.3.40 bhiyo hetubhaye Shuk|bhiyo hetubhaye Shuk|bhiyo hetubhaye Shuk 7.3.40|भियो हेतुभये षुक्|भियो हेतुभये षुक् ७.३.४०|७.३.४०|७.३.४० भियो हेतुभये षुक्
The augment षुक् is added to the root भी before the affix णि when fear is caused immediately owing to the agent of the Causative.<br><br>Terms: षुक् augment

7.3.41|7.3.41 sphaayo vaH|sphaayo vaH|sphaayo vaH 7.3.41|स्फायो वः|स्फायो वः ७.३.४१|७.३.४१|७.३.४१ स्फायो वः
For the final of the stem स्फाय् is substituted व् in the Causative.<br><br>Terms: augment

7.3.42|7.3.42 shaderagatau taH|shaderagatau taH|shaderagatau taH 7.3.42|शदेरगतौ तः|शदेरगतौ तः ७.३.४२|७.३.४२|७.३.४२ शदेरगतौ तः
For the final of शद् is substituted त् in the Causative, when it does not mean 'to drive'.<br><br>Terms: augment

7.3.43|7.3.43 ruhaH po.anyatarasyaam|ruhaH po.anyatarasyaam|ruhaH po.anyatarasyaam 7.3.43|रुहः पोऽन्यतरस्याम्|रुहः पोऽन्यतरस्याम् ७.३.४३|७.३.४३|७.३.४३ रुहः पोऽन्यतरस्याम्
प् may optionally be substituted for the final of रुह् 'to mount' in the Causative.<br><br>Terms: augment

7.3.44|7.3.44 pratyayasthaat‌ kaat‌ puurvasyaata idaapyasupaH|pratyayasthaat‌ kaat‌ puurvasyaata idaapyasupaH|pratyayasthaat‌ kaat‌ puurvasyaata idaapyasupaH 7.3.44|प्रत्ययस्थात्‌ कात्‌ पूर्वस्यात इदाप्यसुपः|प्रत्ययस्थात्‌ कात्‌ पूर्वस्यात इदाप्यसुपः ७.३.४४|७.३.४४|७.३.४४ प्रत्ययस्थात्‌ कात्‌ पूर्वस्यात इदाप्यसुपः
इ is substituted for the अ which stands before the क् belonging to an affix when the feminine ending आ follows, provided that, it does not come after a case-affix (i.e. when such a word in अक does not stand at the end of a बहुव्रीहि समास).<br><br>Terms: Feminine इ

7.3.45|7.3.45 na yaasayoH|na yaasayoH|na yaasayoH 7.3.45|न यासयोः|न यासयोः ७.३.४५|७.३.४५|७.३.४५ न यासयोः
The इ is not substituted for the अ of य् and स् with the augment क् when the feminine आ follows.<br><br>Terms: Feminine इ

7.3.46|7.3.46 udiichaamaataH sthaane yakapuurvaayaaH|udiichaamaataH sthaane yakapuurvaayaaH|udiichaamaataH sthaane yakapuurvaayaaH 7.3.46|उदीचामातः स्थाने यकपूर्वायाः|उदीचामातः स्थाने यकपूर्वायाः ७.३.४६|७.३.४६|७.३.४६ उदीचामातः स्थाने यकपूर्वायाः
According to the opinion of Northern Grammarians इ is not substituted for that अ which is obtained by shortening the long आ of the feminine (under sūtra केऽणः ७.४.१३ before the affix क) which is preceded by य् or a क्।<br><br>Terms: Feminine इ

7.3.47|7.3.47 bhastraiShaa.ajaaJNaadvaasvaanaNJpuurvaaNaamapi|bhastraiShaa.ajaaJNaadvaasvaanaNJpuurvaaNaamapi|bhastraiShaa.ajaaJNaadvaasvaanaNJpuurvaaNaamapi 7.3.47|भस्त्रैषाऽजाज्ञाद्वास्वानञ्पूर्वाणामपि|भस्त्रैषाऽजाज्ञाद्वास्वानञ्पूर्वाणामपि ७.३.४७|७.३.४७|७.३.४७ भस्त्रैषाऽजाज्ञाद्वास्वानञ्पूर्वाणामपि
According to the opinion of Northern Grammarians इ is not substituted for that अ which is obtained by shortening the long आ of the feminine (under sūtra केऽणः ७.४.१३) of 1. भस्त्रा 2. एषा 3. अजा 4. ज्ञा 5. द्वा -- त्यदादीनामः ७.२.१०२, and 6. स्वा even not then when the negative particle precedes them.<br><br>Terms: Feminine इ

7.3.48|7.3.48 abhaaShitapuMskaachcha|abhaaShitapuMskaachcha|abhaaShitapuMskaachcha 7.3.48|अभाषितपुंस्काच्च|अभाषितपुंस्काच्च ७.३.४८|७.३.४८|७.३.४८ अभाषितपुंस्काच्च
According to the opinion of Northern Grammarians इ is not substituted for that अ which is obtained by shortening the long आ of the feminine (under sūtra केऽणः ७.४.१३) when to the feminine in long आ there is no equivalent masculine, even when the negative particle precedes.<br><br>Terms: Feminine इ

7.3.49|7.3.49 aadaachaaryaaNaam|aadaachaaryaaNaam|aadaachaaryaaNaam 7.3.49|आदाचार्याणाम्|आदाचार्याणाम् ७.३.४९|७.३.४९|७.३.४९ आदाचार्याणाम्
According to the opinion of other Teachers, आ is substituted for the which is obtained by shortening the long आ of the feminine (under sūtra केऽणः ७.४.१३) of a word which has no corresponding masculine form.<br><br>Terms: Feminine इ

7.3.50|7.3.50 ThasyekaH|ThasyekaH|ThasyekaH 7.3.50|ठस्येकः|ठस्येकः ७.३.५०|७.३.५०|७.३.५० ठस्येकः
For ठ at the beginning of a तद्धित affix there is substituted इक्।<br><br>Terms: इ - इक्

7.3.51|7.3.51 isusuktaantaat‌ kaH|isusuktaantaat‌ kaH|isusuktaantaat‌ kaH 7.3.51|इसुसुक्तान्तात्‌ कः|इसुसुक्तान्तात्‌ कः ७.३.५१|७.३.५१|७.३.५१ इसुसुक्तान्तात्‌ कः
क is substituted for ठ after a अङ्ग (stem) ending in 1. इस् 2. उस् 3. उ or ऊ 4. ॠ and 5. त्।<br><br>Terms: इ - इक्

7.3.52|7.3.52 chajoH ku ghinNyatoH|chajoH ku ghinNyatoH|chajoH ku ghinNyatoH 7.3.52|चजोः कु घिन्ण्यतोः|चजोः कु घिन्ण्यतोः ७.३.५२|७.३.५२|७.३.५२ चजोः कु घिन्ण्यतोः
For the final च् or ज् of a root, there is substituted a corresponding guttural, before an affix having an indicatory ध् and before णयत्।<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.53|7.3.53 nyankvaadiinaaM cha|nyankvaadiinaaM cha|nyankvaadiinaaM cha 7.3.53|न्यङ्क्वादीनां च|न्यङ्क्वादीनां च ७.३.५३|७.३.५३|७.३.५३ न्यङ्क्वादीनां च
The guttural is substituted in न्यङ्क्वु etc..<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.54|7.3.54 ho hanterNJNinneShu|ho hanterNJNinneShu|ho hanterNJNinneShu 7.3.54|हो हन्तेर्ञ्णिन्नेषु|हो हन्तेर्ञ्णिन्नेषु ७.३.५४|७.३.५४|७.३.५४ हो हन्तेर्ञ्णिन्नेषु
A guttural is substituted for the ह् in हन् 'to kill' before an affix having an indicatory ञ् or ण् and before न्।<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.55|7.3.55 abhyaasaachcha|abhyaasaachcha|abhyaasaachcha 7.3.55|अभ्यासाच्च|अभ्यासाच्च ७.३.५५|७.३.५५|७.३.५५ अभ्यासाच्च
A guttural is substituted for the ह् in हन् 'to kill' after reduplication also.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.56|7.3.56 herachaNGi|herachaNGi|herachaNGi 7.3.56|हेरचङि|हेरचङि ७.३.५६|७.३.५६|७.३.५६ हेरचङि
A guttural is substituted for the ह् of हि (हिनोति) after a reduplication, but not in the reduplicated Aorist.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.57|7.3.57 sanliTorjeH|sanliTorjeH|sanliTorjeH 7.3.57|सन्लिटोर्जेः|सन्लिटोर्जेः ७.३.५७|७.३.५७|७.३.५७ सन्लिटोर्जेः
ज् in जि 'to conquer' after a reduplication before the Desiderative affix सन् and in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.58|7.3.58 vibhaaShaa cheH|vibhaaShaa cheH|vibhaaShaa cheH 7.3.58|विभाषा चेः|विभाषा चेः ७.३.५८|७.३.५८|७.३.५८ विभाषा चेः
A guttural is optionally substituted for the च् of चि 'to collect' after a reduplication in Desiderative and लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.59|7.3.59 na kvaadeH|na kvaadeH|na kvaadeH 7.3.59|न क्वादेः|न क्वादेः ७.३.५९|७.३.५९|७.३.५९ न क्वादेः
A guttural is not substituted for the final च् or ज् of a root which begins with a guttral, before the affix having an indicatory ध् and before ण्यत्।<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.60|7.3.60 ajivRjyoshcha|ajivRjyoshcha|ajivRjyoshcha 7.3.60|अजिवृज्योश्च|अजिवृज्योश्च ७.३.६०|७.३.६०|७.३.६० अजिवृज्योश्च
A guttural is not substituted for the final ज् of अज् and व्रज् before an affix having an indicatory ध् and before ण्यत्।<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.61|7.3.61 bhujanyubjau paaNyupataapayoH|bhujanyubjau paaNyupataapayoH|bhujanyubjau paaNyupataapayoH 7.3.61|भुजन्युब्जौ पाण्युपतापयोः|भुजन्युब्जौ पाण्युपतापयोः ७.३.६१|७.३.६१|७.३.६१ भुजन्युब्जौ पाण्युपतापयोः
भुज 'an arm' and न्युब्ज 'a kind of bodily disease' are irregularly formed without any change of their ज् before घञ्।<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.62|7.3.62 prayaajaanuyaajau yaJNaange|prayaajaanuyaajau yaJNaange|prayaajaanuyaajau yaJNaange 7.3.62|प्रयाजानुयाजौ यज्ञाङ्गे|प्रयाजानुयाजौ यज्ञाङ्गे ७.३.६२|७.३.६२|७.३.६२ प्रयाजानुयाजौ यज्ञाङ्गे
प्रयाज and अनुयाज are irregularly formed with घञ् when meaning 'a portion of a sacrificial offering'.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.63|7.3.63 vancergatau|vancergatau|vancergatau 7.3.63|वञ्चेर्गतौ|वञ्चेर्गतौ ७.३.६३|७.३.६३|७.३.६३ वञ्चेर्गतौ
A guttural is not substituted for the palatal of वञ्च् in the sense of 'going'.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.64|7.3.64 oka uchaH ke|oka uchaH ke|oka uchaH ke 7.3.64|ओक उचः के|ओक उचः के ७.३.६४|७.३.६४|७.३.६४ ओक उचः के
ओक is irregularly formed from the root उच् with the affix क (अ).<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.65|7.3.65 Nya aavashyake|Nya aavashyake|Nya aavashyake 7.3.65|ण्य आवश्यके|ण्य आवश्यके ७.३.६५|७.३.६५|७.३.६५ ण्य आवश्यके
A guttural is not substituted for the palatal before the affix ण्य when it means 'to do as absolute necessity'.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.66|7.3.66 yajayaacharuchapravacharchashcha|yajayaacharuchapravacharchashcha|yajayaacharuchapravacharchashcha 7.3.66|यजयाचरुचप्रवचर्चश्च|यजयाचरुचप्रवचर्चश्च ७.३.६६|७.३.६६|७.३.६६ यजयाचरुचप्रवचर्चश्च
A guttural is not substituted for the final palatals of 1. यज् 2. याच् 3. रुच् 4. प्र-वच् and 5. ऋच् before the affix ण्यत्।<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.67|7.3.67 vacho.ashabdasaMJNaayaam|vacho.ashabdasaMJNaayaam|vacho.ashabdasaMJNaayaam 7.3.67|वचोऽशब्दसंज्ञायाम्|वचोऽशब्दसंज्ञायाम् ७.३.६७|७.३.६७|७.३.६७ वचोऽशब्दसंज्ञायाम्
A guttural is not substituted for the final of वच् before ण्यत् when it does not mean 'a word or speech'.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.68|7.3.68 prayojyaniyojyau shakyaarthe|prayojyaniyojyau shakyaarthe|prayojyaniyojyau shakyaarthe 7.3.68|प्रयोज्यनियोज्यौ शक्यार्थे|प्रयोज्यनियोज्यौ शक्यार्थे ७.३.६८|७.३.६८|७.३.६८ प्रयोज्यनियोज्यौ शक्यार्थे
प्रयोज्य and नियोज्य preserve their palatal in the sense of 'capable to do this'.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.69|7.3.69 bhojyaM bhaxye|bhojyaM bhaxye|bhojyaM bhaxye 7.3.69|भोज्यं भक्ष्ये|भोज्यं भक्ष्ये ७.३.६९|७.३.६९|७.३.६९ भोज्यं भक्ष्ये
भोज्य preserves its palatal in the sense of 'eatable'.<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.70|7.3.70 ghorlopo leTi vaa|ghorlopo leTi vaa|ghorlopo leTi vaa 7.3.70|घोर्लोपो लेटि वा|घोर्लोपो लेटि वा ७.३.७०|७.३.७०|७.३.७० घोर्लोपो लेटि वा
The final of दा and धा (धु roots) may optionally be elided in the लेट् (Vedic Subjunctive).<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.71|7.3.71 otaH shyani|otaH shyani|otaH shyani 7.3.71|ओतः श्यनि|ओतः श्यनि ७.३.७१|७.३.७१|७.३.७१ ओतः श्यनि
A अङ्ग (stem) ending in ओ loses its final before the Present characteristic श्यन् of the दिवादिगणः (4th Conjugation).<br><br>Terms: Guttarlisation

7.3.72|7.3.72 ksasyaachi|ksasyaachi|ksasyaachi 7.3.72|क्सस्याचि|क्सस्याचि ७.३.७२|७.३.७२|७.३.७२ क्सस्याचि
The अ of the Aorist characteristic कस् is elided before an affix beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: कस् affix

7.3.73|7.3.73 lugvaa duhadihalihaguhaamaatmanepade dantye|lugvaa duhadihalihaguhaamaatmanepade dantye|lugvaa duhadihalihaguhaamaatmanepade dantye 7.3.73|लुग्वा दुहदिहलिहगुहामात्मनेपदे दन्त्ये|लुग्वा दुहदिहलिहगुहामात्मनेपदे दन्त्ये ७.३.७३|७.३.७३|७.३.७३ लुग्वा दुहदिहलिहगुहामात्मनेपदे दन्त्ये
The whole of the affix कस् is optionally elided before the personal endings of आत्मनेपद beginning with a dental, after 1. दुह् 2. दिह् 3. लिह् and 4. गुह्।<br><br>Terms: कस् affix

7.3.74|7.3.74 shamaamaShTaanaaM diirghaH shyani|shamaamaShTaanaaM diirghaH shyani|shamaamaShTaanaaM diirghaH shyani 7.3.74|शमामष्टानां दीर्घः श्यनि|शमामष्टानां दीर्घः श्यनि ७.३.७४|७.३.७४|७.३.७४ शमामष्टानां दीर्घः श्यनि
Before the Present characteristic श्यन् , a long is substituted for the root-vowel in शम् and the seven roots that follow it.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.3.75|7.3.75 ShThivuklamyaachamaaM shiti|ShThivuklamyaachamaaM shiti|ShThivuklamyaachamaaM shiti 7.3.75|ष्ठिवुक्लम्याचमां शिति|ष्ठिवुक्लम्याचमां शिति ७.३.७५|७.३.७५|७.३.७५ ष्ठिवुक्लम्याचमां शिति
Before any other Present character (शित्) the root vowel of 1. ष्ठिव् 2. क्लम् and 3.आ-चम् is lengthened.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.3.76|7.3.76 kramaH parasmaipadeShu|kramaH parasmaipadeShu|kramaH parasmaipadeShu 7.3.76|क्रमः परस्मैपदेषु|क्रमः परस्मैपदेषु ७.३.७६|७.३.७६|७.३.७६ क्रमः परस्मैपदेषु
The long is substituted in क्रम् before a शित् affix, in the परस्मैपद ।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.3.77|7.3.77 iShugamiyamaaM ChaH|iShugamiyamaaM ChaH|iShugamiyamaaM ChaH 7.3.77|इषुगमियमां छः|इषुगमियमां छः ७.३.७७|७.३.७७|७.३.७७ इषुगमियमां छः
छ् is substituted for the final of 1. इष् 2. गम् and 3. यम् before a Present-character (शित्).<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.3.78|7.3.78 paaghraadhmaasthaamnaadaaNdRshyarttisarttishadasadaaM pibajighradhamatiShThamanayachChapashyarchChadhaushiiyasiidaaH|paaghraadhmaasthaamnaadaaNdRshyarttisarttishadasadaaM pibajighradhamatiShThamanayachChapashyarchChadhaushiiyasiidaaH|paaghraadhmaasthaamnaadaaNdRshyarttisarttishadasadaaM pibajighradhamatiShThamanayachChapashyarchChadhaushiiyasiidaaH 7.3.78|पाघ्राध्मास्थाम्नादाण्दृश्यर्त्तिसर्त्तिशदसदां पिबजिघ्रधमतिष्ठमनयच्छपश्यर्च्छधौशीयसीदाः|पाघ्राध्मास्थाम्नादाण्दृश्यर्त्तिसर्त्तिशदसदां पिबजिघ्रधमतिष्ठमनयच्छपश्यर्च्छधौशीयसीदाः ७.३.७८|७.३.७८|७.३.७८ पाघ्राध्मास्थाम्नादाण्दृश्यर्त्तिसर्त्तिशदसदां पिबजिघ्रधमतिष्ठमनयच्छपश्यर्च्छधौशीयसीदाः
Before a Present-character (शित्) the following substitutions take place - 1. पिब् for पा 2. जिघ्र for घ्रा 3. धम् for ध्मा 4. तिष्ठ् for स्था 5. मन् for म्ना 6. यछ् for दा (दाण्) 7. पश्य for दृश् 8. ऋच्छ् for ऋ 9. धौ for सृ 10. शीय् for शद् and 11. सीद् for सद्।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.3.79|7.3.79 JNaajanorjaa|JNaajanorjaa|JNaajanorjaa 7.3.79|ज्ञाजनोर्जा|ज्ञाजनोर्जा ७.३.७९|७.३.७९|७.३.७९ ज्ञाजनोर्जा
Before a शित् affix, जा is substituted for ज्ञा and जन्।<br><br>Terms: 

7.3.80|7.3.80 pvaadiinaaM hrasvaH|pvaadiinaaM hrasvaH|pvaadiinaaM hrasvaH 7.3.80|प्वादीनां ह्रस्वः|प्वादीनां ह्रस्वः ७.३.८०|७.३.८०|७.३.८० प्वादीनां ह्रस्वः
A short is substituted for पू etc. before a शित् affix.<br><br>Terms: shortening

7.3.81|7.3.81 miinaaternigame|miinaaternigame|miinaaternigame 7.3.81|मीनातेर्निगमे|मीनातेर्निगमे ७.३.८१|७.३.८१|७.३.८१ मीनातेर्निगमे
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) मी is shortened before a शित् affix.<br><br>Terms: shortening

7.3.82|7.3.82 miderguNaH|miderguNaH|miderguNaH 7.3.82|मिदेर्गुणः|मिदेर्गुणः ७.३.८२|७.३.८२|७.३.८२ मिदेर्गुणः
For इ in मिद् there is substituted a गुण before a शित् affix.<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.83|7.3.83 jusi cha|jusi cha|jusi cha 7.3.83|जुसि च|जुसि च ७.३.८३|७.३.८३|७.३.८३ जुसि च
Before a personal ending जुस् (उस्) of the Imperfect, गुण is substituted for the final 1. इ 2. ई 3. उ. 4. ऊ 5. ऋ 6. ॠ and 7. ऌ।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.84|7.3.84 saarvadhaatukaardhadhaatukayoH|saarvadhaatukaardhadhaatukayoH|saarvadhaatukaardhadhaatukayoH 7.3.84|सार्वधातुकार्धधातुकयोः|सार्वधातुकार्धधातुकयोः ७.३.८४|७.३.८४|७.३.८४ सार्वधातुकार्धधातुकयोः
The गुण is substituted for the final इक् vowel of a अङ्ग (stem) before the affixes called सार्वधातुक and आर्धधातुक -- तिङ्शित्सार्वधातुकम् ३.४.११३ etc.<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.85|7.3.85 jaagro.avichiNNalNGitsu|jaagro.avichiNNalNGitsu|jaagro.avichiNNalNGitsu 7.3.85|जाग्रोऽविचिण्णल्ङित्सु|जाग्रोऽविचिण्णल्ङित्सु ७.३.८५|७.३.८५|७.३.८५ जाग्रोऽविचिण्णल्ङित्सु
The गुण is substituted for the ऋ of the अङ्ग (stem) जागृ , except before the affix वि , before the Aorist character (चिण्) before the personal ending णल् of the लिट् (Perfect Tense) and before an affix with an indicatory ङ्।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.86|7.3.86 pugantalaghuupadhasya cha|pugantalaghuupadhasya cha|pugantalaghuupadhasya cha 7.3.86|पुगन्तलघूपधस्य च|पुगन्तलघूपधस्य च ७.३.८६|७.३.८६|७.३.८६ पुगन्तलघूपधस्य च
गुण is substituted before a सार्वधातुक and an आर्धधातुक affix for the इक् vowels of the Causative अङ्ग (stems) which take the augment प् -- अर्त्तिह्रीब्लीरीक्नूयीक्ष्माय्यातां पुङ्णौ ७.३.३६, and for the short penultimate vowel of a root which ends in a single consonant.<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.87|7.3.87 naabhyastasyaachi piti saarvadhaatuke|naabhyastasyaachi piti saarvadhaatuke|naabhyastasyaachi piti saarvadhaatuke 7.3.87|नाभ्यस्तस्याचि पिति सार्वधातुके|नाभ्यस्तस्याचि पिति सार्वधातुके ७.३.८७|७.३.८७|७.३.८७ नाभ्यस्तस्याचि पिति सार्वधातुके
The गुण is not substituted for the penultimate light इक् vowel in the reduplicated form of a root, before a सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a vowel and having an indicatory प्।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.88|7.3.88 bhuusuvostiNGi|bhuusuvostiNGi|bhuusuvostiNGi 7.3.88|भूसुवोस्तिङि|भूसुवोस्तिङि ७.३.८८|७.३.८८|७.३.८८ भूसुवोस्तिङि
भू and सु get not गुण before an immediately following personal ending which is सार्वधातुक ।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.89|7.3.89 uto vRddhirluki hali|uto vRddhirluki hali|uto vRddhirluki hali 7.3.89|उतो वृद्धिर्लुकि हलि|उतो वृद्धिर्लुकि हलि ७.३.८९|७.३.८९|७.३.८९ उतो वृद्धिर्लुकि हलि
A root ending in short उ , which has no Present characteristic (i.e. the विकरण is dropped by लुक् elision) gets वृद्धि before a पित् सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a consonant, but not if the अङ्ग (stem) is reduplicated.<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.90|7.3.90 UrNotervibhaaShaa|UrNotervibhaaShaa|UrNotervibhaaShaa 7.3.90|ऊर्णोतेर्विभाषा|ऊर्णोतेर्विभाषा ७.३.९०|७.३.९०|७.३.९० ऊर्णोतेर्विभाषा
Before a पित् सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a consonant, the final उ of ऊर्णु optionally gets वृद्धि ।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.91|7.3.91 guNo.apRkte|guNo.apRkte|guNo.apRkte 7.3.91|गुणोऽपृक्ते|गुणोऽपृक्ते ७.३.९१|७.३.९१|७.३.९१ गुणोऽपृक्ते
Before a पित् सार्वधातुक affix which is a single consonant, गुण is substituted for the final of ऊर्णु ।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.92|7.3.92 tRNaha im|tRNaha im|tRNaha im 7.3.92|तृणह इम्|तृणह इम् ७.३.९२|७.३.९२|७.३.९२ तृणह इम्
Before a पित् सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a consonant, इ is added after अ of the verbal stem तृणह्।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.3.93|7.3.93 bruva iiT|bruva iiT|bruva iiT 7.3.93|ब्रुव ईट्|ब्रुव ईट् ७.३.९३|७.३.९३|७.३.९३ ब्रुव ईट्
Before a पित् सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a consonant, the augment इट् is placed after ब्रू।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.3.94|7.3.94 yaNGo vaa|yaNGo vaa|yaNGo vaa 7.3.94|यङो वा|यङो वा ७.३.९४|७.३.९४|७.३.९४ यङो वा
The पित् सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a consonant, optionally get the augment इट् in the Intensive.<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.3.95|7.3.95 turustushamyamaH saarvadhaatuke|turustushamyamaH saarvadhaatuke|turustushamyamaH saarvadhaatuke 7.3.95|तुरुस्तुशम्यमः सार्वधातुके|तुरुस्तुशम्यमः सार्वधातुके ७.३.९५|७.३.९५|७.३.९५ तुरुस्तुशम्यमः सार्वधातुके
A सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a consonant, optionally get the augment इट् after the roots 1. तु 2. रु 3. स्तु 4. शम् and 5. अम्।<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

7.3.96|7.3.96 astisicho.apRkte|astisicho.apRkte|astisicho.apRkte 7.3.96|अस्तिसिचोऽपृक्ते|अस्तिसिचोऽपृक्ते ७.३.९६|७.३.९६|७.३.९६ अस्तिसिचोऽपृक्ते
A single consonantal सार्वधातुक affix gets the augment ईट् after अस् (अस्ति) and after the Aorist character सिच् ।<br><br>Terms: ईट् augment

7.3.97|7.3.97 bahulaM Chandasi|bahulaM Chandasi|bahulaM Chandasi 7.3.97|बहुलं छन्दसि|बहुलं छन्दसि ७.३.९७|७.३.९७|७.३.९७ बहुलं छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas), a single consonantal सार्वधातुक affix gets diversely the augment after अस् (अस्ति) and after the Aorist character सिच् ।<br><br>Terms: ईट् augment

7.3.98|7.3.98 rudashcha pancabhyaH|rudashcha pancabhyaH|rudashcha pancabhyaH 7.3.98|रुदश्च पञ्चभ्यः|रुदश्च पञ्चभ्यः ७.३.९८|७.३.९८|७.३.९८ रुदश्च पञ्चभ्यः
After रुद् and the four roots that follow it, comes the augment ईट् consisting of a single consonant.<br><br>Terms: ईट् augment

7.3.99|7.3.99 aDgaargyagaalavayoH|aDgaargyagaalavayoH|aDgaargyagaalavayoH 7.3.99|अड्गार्ग्यगालवयोः|अड्गार्ग्यगालवयोः ७.३.९९|७.३.९९|७.३.९९ अड्गार्ग्यगालवयोः
According to the opinion of गार्ग्य and गालाव , the augment अट् comes before a सार्वधातुक affix consisting of single consonant, after the above five roots रुद् etc.<br><br>Terms: अट् augment

7.3.100|7.3.100 adaH sarveShaam|adaH sarveShaam|adaH sarveShaam 7.3.100|अदः सर्वेषाम्|अदः सर्वेषाम् ७.३.१००|७.३.१००|७.३.१०० अदः सर्वेषाम्
After अद् 'to eat' , comes the augment अट् before a सार्वधातुक affix consisting of a single consonant, according to the opinion of all grammarians.<br><br>Terms: अट् augment

7.3.101|7.3.101 ato diirgho yaNJi|ato diirgho yaNJi|ato diirgho yaNJi 7.3.101|अतो दीर्घो यञि|अतो दीर्घो यञि ७.३.१०१|७.३.१०१|७.३.१०१ अतो दीर्घो यञि
The long आ is substituted for the final अ of a tense अङ्ग (stem) before a सार्वधातुक affix beginning with a व् or म् (literally a consonant of यञ् प्रत्यहार).<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.3.102|7.3.102 supi cha|supi cha|supi cha 7.3.102|सुपि च|सुपि च ७.३.१०२|७.३.१०२|७.३.१०२ सुपि च
Before a case-ending beginning with य् or भ् (literally a consonant of the यञ् प्रत्यहार) the final of a Nominal-stem is lengthened.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.3.103|7.3.103 bahuvachane jhalyet‌|bahuvachane jhalyet‌|bahuvachane jhalyet‌ 7.3.103|बहुवचने झल्येत्‌|बहुवचने झल्येत्‌ ७.३.१०३|७.३.१०३|७.३.१०३ बहुवचने झल्येत्‌
Before a case-ending beginning with भ् or स् (literally a consonant of the झल् प्रत्यहार) in the plural, ए is substituted for the final अ of Nominal-stem.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.3.104|7.3.104 osi cha|osi cha|osi cha 7.3.104|ओसि च|ओसि च ७.३.१०४|७.३.१०४|७.३.१०४ ओसि च
Before the case-ending ओस् , ए is substituted for the final अ of Nominal-stem.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.3.105|7.3.105 aaNGi chaapaH|aaNGi chaapaH|aaNGi chaapaH 7.3.105|आङि चापः|आङि चापः ७.३.१०५|७.३.१०५|७.३.१०५ आङि चापः
Before the case-ending ओस् and before आ of the Instrumental -3rd case, ए is substituted for the final आ of the feminine affix.<br><br>Terms: गुण in Feminine

7.3.106|7.3.106 sambuddhau cha|sambuddhau cha|sambuddhau cha 7.3.106|सम्बुद्धौ च|सम्बुद्धौ च ७.३.१०६|७.३.१०६|७.३.१०६ सम्बुद्धौ च
ए is substituted for the final आ of the feminine affix, in the Vocative Case singular.<br><br>Terms: गुण in Feminine

7.3.107|7.3.107 ambaa.arthanadyorhrasvaH|ambaa.arthanadyorhrasvaH|ambaa.arthanadyorhrasvaH 7.3.107|अम्बाऽर्थनद्योर्ह्रस्वः|अम्बाऽर्थनद्योर्ह्रस्वः ७.३.१०७|७.३.१०७|७.३.१०७ अम्बाऽर्थनद्योर्ह्रस्वः
A short vowel is substituted in the Vocative Case singular for the final आ of the feminine affix, in the sense of 'mother, mother-dear' and also for the long vowel of the feminines called नदी -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३ etc.<br><br>Terms: गुण in Feminine

7.3.108|7.3.108 hrasvasya guNaH|hrasvasya guNaH|hrasvasya guNaH 7.3.108|ह्रस्वस्य गुणः|ह्रस्वस्य गुणः ७.३.१०८|७.३.१०८|७.३.१०८ ह्रस्वस्य गुणः
For the short इ and उ final in a nominal-stem, a गुण is substituted in the Vocative Case singular.<br><br>Terms: गुण in Feminine

7.3.109|7.3.109 jasi cha|jasi cha|jasi cha 7.3.109|जसि च|जसि च ७.३.१०९|७.३.१०९|७.३.१०९ जसि च
Before the affix अस् of the Nominative 1st-Case plural गुण is substituted for the final short vowel of a Nominal-stem.<br><br>Terms: गुण in Feminine

7.3.110|7.3.110 Rto NGisarvanaamasthaanayoH|Rto NGisarvanaamasthaanayoH|Rto NGisarvanaamasthaanayoH 7.3.110|ऋतो ङिसर्वनामस्थानयोः|ऋतो ङिसर्वनामस्थानयोः ७.३.११०|७.३.११०|७.३.११० ऋतो ङिसर्वनामस्थानयोः
गुण is substituted for the final ऋ of a अङ्ग (stem) in the Locative -7th case singular and in the strong cases.<br><br>Terms: गुण in Feminine

7.3.111|7.3.111 gherNGiti|gherNGiti|gherNGiti 7.3.111|घेर्ङिति|घेर्ङिति ७.३.१११|७.३.१११|७.३.१११ घेर्ङिति
For the इ and उ of the stems called घि -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३, गुण is substituted in the Dative -4th Case, Ablative -5th case and Genitive 6th-Case singular.<br><br>Terms: गुण in Feminine

7.3.112|7.3.112 aaNnadyaaH|aaNnadyaaH|aaNnadyaaH 7.3.112|आण्नद्याः|आण्नद्याः ७.३.११२|७.३.११२|७.३.११२ आण्नद्याः
The augment आट् is added to the case-endings of the Dative -4th Case, Ablative -5th case and Genitive 6th-Case singular after the stem called नदी -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३ etc.<br><br>Terms: आट् augment

7.3.113|7.3.113 yaaDaapaH|yaaDaapaH|yaaDaapaH 7.3.113|याडापः|याडापः ७.३.११३|७.३.११३|७.३.११३ याडापः
The augment याट् is added to the case-endings of the Dative -4th Case, Ablative -5th case and Genitive 6th-Case singular after a feminine अङ्ग (stem) ending in आ।<br><br>Terms: याट् augment

7.3.114|7.3.114 sarvanaamnaH syaaDDhrasvashcha|sarvanaamnaH syaaDDhrasvashcha|sarvanaamnaH syaaDDhrasvashcha 7.3.114|सर्वनाम्नः स्याड्ढ्रस्वश्च|सर्वनाम्नः स्याड्ढ्रस्वश्च ७.३.११४|७.३.११४|७.३.११४ सर्वनाम्नः स्याड्ढ्रस्वश्च
After a Pronominal अङ्ग (stem) ending in long आ of the feminine, the Dative -4th Case, Ablative -5th case and Genitive 6th-Case singular get the augment स्याट् and the आ of the अङ्ग (stem) is shortened.<br><br>Terms: स्याट् augment

7.3.115|7.3.115 vibhaaShaa dvitiiyaatRtiiyaabhyaam|vibhaaShaa dvitiiyaatRtiiyaabhyaam|vibhaaShaa dvitiiyaatRtiiyaabhyaam 7.3.115|विभाषा द्वितीयातृतीयाभ्याम्|विभाषा द्वितीयातृतीयाभ्याम् ७.३.११५|७.३.११५|७.३.११५ विभाषा द्वितीयातृतीयाभ्याम्
After द्वितीया and तृतीया the Dative -4th Case, Ablative -5th case and Genitive 6th-Case singular may optionally get the augment स्याट् before which the आ of the अङ्ग (stem) is shortened.<br><br>Terms: स्याट् augment

7.3.116|7.3.116 NGeraamnadyaamniibhyaH|NGeraamnadyaamniibhyaH|NGeraamnadyaamniibhyaH 7.3.116|ङेराम्नद्याम्नीभ्यः|ङेराम्नद्याम्नीभ्यः ७.३.११६|७.३.११६|७.३.११६ ङेराम्नद्याम्नीभ्यः
For the ending इ of the Locative -7th case singular there is substituted आम् after a अङ्ग (stem) called नदी -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३ etc., after the feminines in आ and after नी।<br><br>Terms: आम् augment

7.3.117|7.3.117 idudbhyaam|idudbhyaam|idudbhyaam 7.3.117|इदुद्भ्याम्|इदुद्भ्याम् ७.३.११७|७.३.११७|७.३.११७ इदुद्भ्याम्
After all the feminine नदी -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३ etc., words ending in a short इ and उ , आम् is substituted for the इ of the Locative -7th case singular.<br><br>Terms: नदी विभक्ति

7.3.118|7.3.118 aut‌|aut‌|aut‌ 7.3.118|औत्‌|औत्‌ ७.३.११८|७.३.११८|७.३.११८ औत्‌
After a अङ्ग (stem) ending in short इ and उ and which is not नदी -- यू स्त्र्याख्यौ नदी १.४.३ or घि -- शेषो घ्यसखि १.४.७, औ is substituted for the इ of the Locative -7th case singular.<br><br>Terms: घि विभक्ति

7.3.119|7.3.119 achcha gheH|achcha gheH|achcha gheH 7.3.119|अच्च घेः|अच्च घेः ७.३.११९|७.३.११९|७.३.११९ अच्च घेः
After a घि -- शेषो घ्यसखि १.४.७, अङ्ग (stem) ending in short इ or उ , औ is substituted for the इ of the Locative -7th case singular and अ is substituted for the final of such a घि अङ्ग (stem).<br><br>Terms: घि विभक्ति

7.3.120|7.3.120 aaNGo naa.astriyaam|aaNGo naa.astriyaam|aaNGo naa.astriyaam 7.3.120|आङो नाऽस्त्रियाम्|आङो नाऽस्त्रियाम् ७.३.१२०|७.३.१२०|७.३.१२० आङो नाऽस्त्रियाम्
ना is substituted for the ending आ of the Instrumental -3rd case singular, after the घि अङ्ग (stems) when they are not feminine.<br><br>Terms: घि विभक्ति

7.4.1|7.4.1 Nau chaNGyupadhaayaa hrasvaH|Nau chaNGyupadhaayaa hrasvaH|Nau chaNGyupadhaayaa hrasvaH 7.4.1|णौ चङ्युपधाया ह्रस्वः|णौ चङ्युपधाया ह्रस्वः ७.४.१|७.४.१|७.४.१ णौ चङ्युपधाया ह्रस्वः
A short is substituted for the vowel, standing in a penultimate position, the Causative अङ्ग (stem), when the affix चङ् (sign of the Reduplicate Aorist of the Causatives) follows.<br><br>Terms: Aorist shortening

7.4.2|7.4.2 naaglopishaasvRditaam|naaglopishaasvRditaam|naaglopishaasvRditaam 7.4.2|नाग्लोपिशास्वृदिताम्|नाग्लोपिशास्वृदिताम् ७.४.२|७.४.२|७.४.२ नाग्लोपिशास्वृदिताम्
The shortening of the penultimate of the stem, before the causative affix in the reduplicated Aorist, does not take place, when it is a (Denominative) अङ्ग (stem), which has lost a simple (end vowel of the Nominal stem) before the Causative sign and also not, when it is the verb शास् , or a root which has an indicatory ऋ।<br><br>Terms: Aorist shortening

7.4.3|7.4.3 bhraajabhaasabhaaShadiipajiivamiilapiiDaamanyatarasyaam‌|bhraajabhaasabhaaShadiipajiivamiilapiiDaamanyatarasyaam‌|bhraajabhaasabhaaShadiipajiivamiilapiiDaamanyatarasyaam‌ 7.4.3|भ्राजभासभाषदीपजीवमीलपीडामन्यतरस्याम्‌|भ्राजभासभाषदीपजीवमीलपीडामन्यतरस्याम्‌ ७.४.३|७.४.३|७.४.३ भ्राजभासभाषदीपजीवमीलपीडामन्यतरस्याम्‌
The shortening of the penultimate of the Causative अङ्ग (stem) in the reduplicated Aorist, is optional in the following - 1. भ्राज् 2. भास् 3. भाष् 4. दीप् 5. जीव् 6. मील् and 7. पीड् ।<br><br>Terms: Aorist shortening

7.4.4|7.4.4 lopaH pibateriichchaabhyaasasya|lopaH pibateriichchaabhyaasasya|lopaH pibateriichchaabhyaasasya 7.4.4|लोपः पिबतेरीच्चाभ्यासस्य|लोपः पिबतेरीच्चाभ्यासस्य ७.४.४|७.४.४|७.४.४ लोपः पिबतेरीच्चाभ्यासस्य
The penultimate vowel in the Causative अङ्ग (stem) पा 'to drink' is elided in the Aorist and for the vowel of the reduplicate there is substituted long ई।<br><br>Terms: Aorist shortening

7.4.5|7.4.5 tiShThaterit‌|tiShThaterit‌|tiShThaterit‌ 7.4.5|तिष्ठतेरित्‌|तिष्ठतेरित्‌ ७.४.५|७.४.५|७.४.५ तिष्ठतेरित्‌
Short इ is substituted for the penultimate vowel of the Causative अङ्ग (stem) स्था in the Aorist.<br><br>Terms: इ substitute

7.4.6|7.4.6 jighratervaa|jighratervaa|jighratervaa 7.4.6|जिघ्रतेर्वा|जिघ्रतेर्वा ७.४.६|७.४.६|७.४.६ जिघ्रतेर्वा
Short इ is optionally substituted for the penultimate vowel of the Causative अङ्ग (stem) of घ्रा in the Aorist.<br><br>Terms: इ substitute

7.4.7|7.4.7 urRt‌|urRt‌|urRt‌ 7.4.7|उर्ऋत्‌|उर्ऋत्‌ ७.४.७|७.४.७|७.४.७ उर्ऋत्‌
Short ऋ is optionally substituted for the penultimate ऋ and ॠ of a Causative अङ्ग (stem) in the reduplicated Aorist.<br><br>Terms: ऋ substitute

7.4.8|7.4.8 nityaM Chandasi|nityaM Chandasi|nityaM Chandasi 7.4.8|नित्यं छन्दसि|नित्यं छन्दसि ७.४.८|७.४.८|७.४.८ नित्यं छन्दसि
Short ऋ is invariably substituted in the छन्दस् (Vedas) for the penultimate ऋ or ॠ of a Causative अङ्ग (stem) in the reduplicated Aorist.<br><br>Terms: ऋ substitute

7.4.9|7.4.9 dayaterdigi liTi|dayaterdigi liTi|dayaterdigi liTi 7.4.9|दयतेर्दिगि लिटि|दयतेर्दिगि लिटि ७.४.९|७.४.९|७.४.९ दयतेर्दिगि लिटि
दिगि is substituted for दे (दयते) in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.4.10|7.4.10 Rtashcha saMyogaaderguNaH|Rtashcha saMyogaaderguNaH|Rtashcha saMyogaaderguNaH 7.4.10|ऋतश्च संयोगादेर्गुणः|ऋतश्च संयोगादेर्गुणः ७.४.१०|७.४.१०|७.४.१० ऋतश्च संयोगादेर्गुणः
A root ending in short ऋ and preceded by a conjunct consonant gets गुण in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.4.11|7.4.11 RchChatyRRtaam|RchChatyRRtaam|RchChatyRRtaam 7.4.11|ऋच्छत्यॄताम्|ऋच्छत्यॄताम् ७.४.११|७.४.११|७.४.११ ऋच्छत्यॄताम्
There is गुण in the लिट् (Perfect Tense) of 1. ऋच्छ् 2. ॠ and roots ending in long ॠ।<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.4.12|7.4.12 shRdRRpraaM hrasvo vaa|shRdRRpraaM hrasvo vaa|shRdRRpraaM hrasvo vaa 7.4.12|शृदॄप्रां ह्रस्वो वा|शृदॄप्रां ह्रस्वो वा ७.४.१२|७.४.१२|७.४.१२ शृदॄप्रां ह्रस्वो वा
In 1. शॄ 'to injure' 2. दॄ 'to tear' and 3. पॄ 'to protect'-- all belonging to क्र्यादिगणः (9th Conjugation), the vowel may be optionally shortened in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.13|7.4.13 ke.aNaH|ke.aNaH|ke.aNaH 7.4.13|केऽणः|केऽणः ७.४.१३|७.४.१३|७.४.१३ केऽणः
Before the affix क the preceding आ , ई and ऊ are shortened.<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.14|7.4.14 na kapi|na kapi|na kapi 7.4.14|न कपि|न कपि ७.४.१४|७.४.१४|७.४.१४ न कपि
But before the समासान्त affix कप् coming after बहुव्रीहि समास , the अण् vowels are not shortened.<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.15|7.4.15 aapo.anyatarasyaam|aapo.anyatarasyaam|aapo.anyatarasyaam 7.4.15|आपोऽन्यतरस्याम्|आपोऽन्यतरस्याम् ७.४.१५|७.४.१५|७.४.१५ आपोऽन्यतरस्याम्
Optionally the feminine अङ्ग (stem) in आ is not shortened before the affix कप्।<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.16|7.4.16 RdRsho.aNGi guNaH|RdRsho.aNGi guNaH|RdRsho.aNGi guNaH 7.4.16|ऋदृशोऽङि गुणः|ऋदृशोऽङि गुणः ७.४.१६|७.४.१६|७.४.१६ ऋदृशोऽङि गुणः
गुण is substituted for the vowel of the root before the affix अङ् in the roots ending in ऋ or ॠ as well as दृश् 'to see'.<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.17|7.4.17 asyatesthuk|asyatesthuk|asyatesthuk 7.4.17|अस्यतेस्थुक्|अस्यतेस्थुक् ७.४.१७|७.४.१७|७.४.१७ अस्यतेस्थुक्
The अङ्ग (stem) अस् 'to be' (अस्यते) gets the augment थुक् before this Aorist अङ्।<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.18|7.4.18 shvayateraH|shvayateraH|shvayateraH 7.4.18|श्वयतेरः|श्वयतेरः ७.४.१८|७.४.१८|७.४.१८ श्वयतेरः
The अ is substituted for the final of श्वि in the Aorist अङ्।<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.19|7.4.19 pataH pum|pataH pum|pataH pum 7.4.19|पतः पुम्|पतः पुम् ७.४.१९|७.४.१९|७.४.१९ पतः पुम्
The augment प् is added after the vowel of a root पत् 'to fall' in the Aorist अङ्।<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.20|7.4.20 vacha um|vacha um|vacha um 7.4.20|वच उम्|वच उम् ७.४.२०|७.४.२०|७.४.२० वच उम्
The augment उ is added after the अ of वच् in the Aorist अङ्।<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.21|7.4.21 shiiNGaH saarvadhaatuke guNaH|shiiNGaH saarvadhaatuke guNaH|shiiNGaH saarvadhaatuke guNaH 7.4.21|शीङः सार्वधातुके गुणः|शीङः सार्वधातुके गुणः ७.४.२१|७.४.२१|७.४.२१ शीङः सार्वधातुके गुणः
For the vowel of शी there is substituted गुण when a सार्वधातुक affix follows.<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.22|7.4.22 ayaNG yi kNGiti|ayaNG yi kNGiti|ayaNG yi kNGiti 7.4.22|अयङ् यि क्ङिति|अयङ् यि क्ङिति ७.४.२२|७.४.२२|७.४.२२ अयङ् यि क्ङिति
Before an affix beginning with a य् and having an indicatory क् or ङ् there is substituted अय् for the ई of शी।<br><br>Terms: अयङ्

7.4.23|7.4.23 upasargaaddhrasva UhateH|upasargaaddhrasva UhateH|upasargaaddhrasva UhateH 7.4.23|उपसर्गाद्ध्रस्व ऊहतेः|उपसर्गाद्ध्रस्व ऊहतेः ७.४.२३|७.४.२३|७.४.२३ उपसर्गाद्ध्रस्व ऊहतेः
The short is substituted for the ऊ of ऊह् when a preposition precedes it and an affix beginning with य् with an indicatory क् or ङ् follows.<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.24|7.4.24 eterliNGi|eterliNGi|eterliNGi 7.4.24|एतेर्लिङि|एतेर्लिङि ७.४.२४|७.४.२४|७.४.२४ एतेर्लिङि
The short is substituted for the vowel of the अङ्ग (stem) इ (एति) before the augment यास् in the Benedictive, when a preposition precedes it.<br><br>Terms: Shortening

7.4.25|7.4.25 akRtsaarvadhaatukayordiirghaH|akRtsaarvadhaatukayordiirghaH|akRtsaarvadhaatukayordiirghaH 7.4.25|अकृत्सार्वधातुकयोर्दीर्घः|अकृत्सार्वधातुकयोर्दीर्घः ७.४.२५|७.४.२५|७.४.२५ अकृत्सार्वधातुकयोर्दीर्घः
A long is substituted for the final vowel of the अङ्ग (stem) before an affix beginning with य् having an indicatory क् or ङ् , when it is not a कृत् or a सार्वधातुक affix.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.4.26|7.4.26 chvau cha|chvau cha|chvau cha 7.4.26|च्वौ च|च्वौ च ७.४.२६|७.४.२६|७.४.२६ च्वौ च
A long is substituted for the final vowel of the अङ्ग (stem) before the Adverbial affix च्वि -- अभूततद्भावे कृभ्वस्तियोगे सम्पद्यकर्तरि च्विः ५.४.५०.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.4.27|7.4.27 riiNG RtaH|riiNG RtaH|riiNG RtaH 7.4.27|रीङ् ऋतः|रीङ् ऋतः ७.४.२७|७.४.२७|७.४.२७ रीङ् ऋतः
री is substituted for the final short ऋ of a अङ्ग (stem) before an affix beginning with य् when it is not a कृत् or a सार्वधातुक affix and the Adverbial affix च्वि -- अभूततद्भावे कृभ्वस्तियोगे सम्पद्यकर्तरि च्विः ५.४.५०.<br><br>Terms: Lengthening

7.4.28|7.4.28 riNG shayaglinkShu|riNG shayaglinkShu|riNG shayaglinkShu 7.4.28|रिङ् शयग्लिङ्क्षु|रिङ् शयग्लिङ्क्षु ७.४.२८|७.४.२८|७.४.२८ रिङ् शयग्लिङ्क्षु
For the final short ऋ of a root, there is substituted रि before the present character अ (श) before the Passive character य् and before the augment यास् in the Benedictive.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

7.4.29|7.4.29 guNo.artisaMyogaadyoH|guNo.artisaMyogaadyoH|guNo.artisaMyogaadyoH 7.4.29|गुणोऽर्तिसंयोगाद्योः|गुणोऽर्तिसंयोगाद्योः ७.४.२९|७.४.२९|७.४.२९ गुणोऽर्तिसंयोगाद्योः
गुण is substituted for the final ऋ in the root ऋ (अर्ति) and in those roots ending in ऋ in which the vowel is preceded by a conjunct consonant, when the Passive character यक् or the Benedictive augment यास् follows.<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.4.30|7.4.30 yaNGi cha|yaNGi cha|yaNGi cha 7.4.30|यङि च|यङि च ७.४.३०|७.४.३०|७.४.३० यङि च
गुण is substituted for the final ऋ in those roots ending in ऋ in which the vowel is preceded by a conjunct consonant, when the Intensive character यङ् follows.<br><br>Terms: गुण

7.4.31|7.4.31 ii ghraadhmoH|ii ghraadhmoH|ii ghraadhmoH 7.4.31|ई घ्राध्मोः|ई घ्राध्मोः ७.४.३१|७.४.३१|७.४.३१ ई घ्राध्मोः
Long ई is substituted for the vowel of the roots 1. घ्रा and 2. ध्मा in the Intensive.<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.32|7.4.32 asya chvau|asya chvau|asya chvau 7.4.32|अस्य च्वौ|अस्य च्वौ ७.४.३२|७.४.३२|७.४.३२ अस्य च्वौ
Long ई is substituted for the final of अ or आ of a Nominal stem, before the Adverbial affix च्वि -- अभूततद्भावे कृभ्वस्तियोगे सम्पद्यकर्तरि च्विः ५.४.५०।<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.33|7.4.33 kyachi cha|kyachi cha|kyachi cha 7.4.33|क्यचि च|क्यचि च ७.४.३३|७.४.३३|७.४.३३ क्यचि च
Long ई is substituted for the final of अ or आ of a Nominal stem, before the Denominative affix क्यच् ।<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.34|7.4.34 ashanaayodanyadhanaayaa bubhuxaapipaasaagarddheShu|ashanaayodanyadhanaayaa bubhuxaapipaasaagarddheShu|ashanaayodanyadhanaayaa bubhuxaapipaasaagarddheShu 7.4.34|अशनायोदन्यधनाया बुभुक्षापिपासागर्द्धेषु|अशनायोदन्यधनाया बुभुक्षापिपासागर्द्धेषु ७.४.३४|७.४.३४|७.४.३४ अशनायोदन्यधनाया बुभुक्षापिपासागर्द्धेषु
The Denominative roots 1. अशनाय 2. उदन्य and 3. धनाय are irregularly formed when they respectively mean 1. 'to be hungry' 2. 'to be thirsty' and 3. 'to be greedy'.<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.35|7.4.35 na chChandasyaputrasya|na chChandasyaputrasya|na chChandasyaputrasya 7.4.35|न च्छन्दस्यपुत्रस्य|न च्छन्दस्यपुत्रस्य ७.४.३५|७.४.३५|७.४.३५ न च्छन्दस्यपुत्रस्य
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the above rules causing lengthening or the substitution of long ई for the final vowel of the अङ्ग (stem), do not apply, except in the case of पुत्र।<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.36|7.4.36 durasyurdraviNasyurvRShaNyatiriShaNyati|durasyurdraviNasyurvRShaNyatiriShaNyati|durasyurdraviNasyurvRShaNyatiriShaNyati 7.4.36|दुरस्युर्द्रविणस्युर्वृषण्यतिरिषण्यति|दुरस्युर्द्रविणस्युर्वृषण्यतिरिषण्यति ७.४.३६|७.४.३६|७.४.३६ दुरस्युर्द्रविणस्युर्वृषण्यतिरिषण्यति
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) 1. दुरस्यु 2. द्रविणस्यु 3. वृषण्यति and 4. रिषण्यति are irregularly formed<br><br>Terms: Irregular

7.4.37|7.4.37 ashvaaghasyaat‌|ashvaaghasyaat‌|ashvaaghasyaat‌ 7.4.37|अश्वाघस्यात्‌|अश्वाघस्यात्‌ ७.४.३७|७.४.३७|७.४.३७ अश्वाघस्यात्‌
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) long आ is substituted for the final of 1. अश्व and 2. अघ before the Denominative क्यच् ।<br><br>Terms: क्यच् affix

7.4.38|7.4.38 devasumnayoryajuShi kaaThake|devasumnayoryajuShi kaaThake|devasumnayoryajuShi kaaThake 7.4.38|देवसुम्नयोर्यजुषि काठके|देवसुम्नयोर्यजुषि काठके ७.४.३८|७.४.३८|७.४.३८ देवसुम्नयोर्यजुषि काठके
Long आ is substituted for the final of देव and सुम्न before the Denominative क्यच् in यजुष काठक।<br><br>Terms: क्यच् affix

7.4.39|7.4.39 kavyadhvarapRtanasyarchi lopaH|kavyadhvarapRtanasyarchi lopaH|kavyadhvarapRtanasyarchi lopaH 7.4.39|कव्यध्वरपृतनस्यर्चि लोपः|कव्यध्वरपृतनस्यर्चि लोपः ७.४.३९|७.४.३९|७.४.३९ कव्यध्वरपृतनस्यर्चि लोपः
In the ऋग् वेद the final of 1. कवि 2. अध्वर and 3. पृतना is dropped before the Denominative affix क्यच् ।<br><br>Terms: क्यच् affix

7.4.40|7.4.40 dyatisyatimaasthaamitti kiti|dyatisyatimaasthaamitti kiti|dyatisyatimaasthaamitti kiti 7.4.40|द्यतिस्यतिमास्थामित्ति किति|द्यतिस्यतिमास्थामित्ति किति ७.४.४०|७.४.४०|७.४.४० द्यतिस्यतिमास्थामित्ति किति
Short इ is substituted for the final of 1. दो 2. सो 3. मा and 4. स्था before an affix beginning with त् and having an indicatory क् ।<br><br>Terms: इ substitution

7.4.41|7.4.41 shaaChoranyatarasyaam|shaaChoranyatarasyaam|shaaChoranyatarasyaam 7.4.41|शाछोरन्यतरस्याम्|शाछोरन्यतरस्याम् ७.४.४१|७.४.४१|७.४.४१ शाछोरन्यतरस्याम्
Short इ is optionally substituted for the final of 1. शा (शो) and 2. छा (छो) before an affix beginning with त् and having an indicatory क् ।<br><br>Terms: इ substitution

7.4.42|7.4.42 dadhaaterhiH|dadhaaterhiH|dadhaaterhiH 7.4.42|दधातेर्हिः|दधातेर्हिः ७.४.४२|७.४.४२|७.४.४२ दधातेर्हिः
हि is optionally substituted for धा (दधाति) before an affix beginning with त् and having an indicatory क् ।<br><br>Terms: हि substitution

7.4.43|7.4.43 jahaateshcha ktvi|jahaateshcha ktvi|jahaateshcha ktvi 7.4.43|जहातेश्च क्त्वि|जहातेश्च क्त्वि ७.४.४३|७.४.४३|७.४.४३ जहातेश्च क्त्वि
हि is optionally substituted for हा (जहाति) before क्त्वा।<br><br>Terms: हि substitution

7.4.44|7.4.44 vibhaaShaa Chandasi|vibhaaShaa Chandasi|vibhaaShaa Chandasi 7.4.44|विभाषा छन्दसि|विभाषा छन्दसि ७.४.४४|७.४.४४|७.४.४४ विभाषा छन्दसि
हि is optionally substituted for हा (जहाति) before क्त्वा in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: हि substitution

7.4.45|7.4.45 sudhitavasudhitanemadhitadhiShvadhiShiiya cha|sudhitavasudhitanemadhitadhiShvadhiShiiya cha|sudhitavasudhitanemadhitadhiShvadhiShiiya cha 7.4.45|सुधितवसुधितनेमधितधिष्वधिषीय च|सुधितवसुधितनेमधितधिष्वधिषीय च ७.४.४५|७.४.४५|७.४.४५ सुधितवसुधितनेमधितधिष्वधिषीय च
These five Vedic forms are irregularly formed - 1. सुधित 2. वसुधित 3. नेमधित 4. धिष्व and 3. धिषीय।<br><br>Terms: Irregular छन्दस्

7.4.46|7.4.46 do dad ghoH|do dad ghoH|do dad ghoH 7.4.46|दो दद् घोः|दो दद् घोः ७.४.४६|७.४.४६|७.४.४६ दो दद् घोः
For दा , when it is a घु - दाधा घ्वदाप् १.१.२०, there is substituted दद् before a कित् affix beginning with त् ।<br><br>Terms: घु declension

7.4.47|7.4.47 acha upasargaattaH|acha upasargaattaH|acha upasargaattaH 7.4.47|अच उपसर्गात्तः|अच उपसर्गात्तः ७.४.४७|७.४.४७|७.४.४७ अच उपसर्गात्तः
त् is substituted for the घु - दाधा घ्वदाप् १.१.२०, before a कित् affix beginning with त when a preposition ending in a vowel preceded it.<br><br>Terms: घु declension

7.4.48|7.4.48 apo bhi|apo bhi|apo bhi 7.4.48|अपो भि|अपो भि ७.४.४८|७.४.४८|७.४.४८ अपो भि
त् is substituted for the final of the अङ्ग (stem) अप् before a case-ending beginning with भ्।<br><br>Terms: त् substitution

7.4.49|7.4.49 saH syaarddhadhaatuke|saH syaarddhadhaatuke|saH syaarddhadhaatuke 7.4.49|सः स्यार्द्धधातुके|सः स्यार्द्धधातुके ७.४.४९|७.४.४९|७.४.४९ सः स्यार्द्धधातुके
त् is substituted for the final स् of a root before an आर्द्धधातुक affix beginning with a स्।<br><br>Terms: त् substitution

7.4.50|7.4.50 taasastyorlopaH|taasastyorlopaH|taasastyorlopaH 7.4.50|तासस्त्योर्लोपः|तासस्त्योर्लोपः ७.४.५०|७.४.५०|७.४.५० तासस्त्योर्लोपः
The final स् of तास् (the character of the second future) and अस् 'to be' is elided before an affix beginning with स् ।<br><br>Terms: Elision

7.4.51|7.4.51 ri cha|ri cha|ri cha 7.4.51|रि च|रि च ७.४.५१|७.४.५१|७.४.५१ रि च
The final स् of तास् (the character of the second future) and अस् 'to be' is elided before an affix beginning with र्।<br><br>Terms: Elision

7.4.52|7.4.52 ha eti|ha eti|ha eti 7.4.52|ह एति|ह एति ७.४.५२|७.४.५२|७.४.५२ ह एति
The स् of तास् (the character of the second future) and अस् 'to be' is substituted ह् before the personal-ending ए।<br><br>Terms: Elision

7.4.53|7.4.53 yiivarNayordiidhiivevyoH|yiivarNayordiidhiivevyoH|yiivarNayordiidhiivevyoH 7.4.53|यीवर्णयोर्दीधीवेव्योः|यीवर्णयोर्दीधीवेव्योः ७.४.५३|७.४.५३|७.४.५३ यीवर्णयोर्दीधीवेव्योः
The final of दीधी and वेवी falls before an affix beginning with य् , इ or ई।<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.54|7.4.54 sani miimaaghurabhalabhashakapatapadaamacha is|sani miimaaghurabhalabhashakapatapadaamacha is|sani miimaaghurabhalabhashakapatapadaamacha is 7.4.54|सनि मीमाघुरभलभशकपतपदामच इस्|सनि मीमाघुरभलभशकपतपदामच इस् ७.४.५४|७.४.५४|७.४.५४ सनि मीमाघुरभलभशकपतपदामच इस्
इस् is substituted for the root-vowel of 1. मी 2. मा 3. धा (घु) 4. रभ् 5. लभ् 6. शक् 7. पत् 8. पद् and 9. दा when the Desiderative सन् follows beginning with स् (i.e. not taking the augment इ) follows.<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.55|7.4.55 aapJNapyRdhaamiit‌|aapJNapyRdhaamiit‌|aapJNapyRdhaamiit‌ 7.4.55|आप्ज्ञप्यृधामीत्‌|आप्ज्ञप्यृधामीत्‌ ७.४.५५|७.४.५५|७.४.५५ आप्ज्ञप्यृधामीत्‌
For the vowel of the roots 1. आप् 2. ज्ञपि and 3. ऋध् there is substituted long ई before सन् of the Desiderative when it begins with स्।<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.56|7.4.56 dambha ichcha|dambha ichcha|dambha ichcha 7.4.56|दम्भ इच्च|दम्भ इच्च ७.४.५६|७.४.५६|७.४.५६ दम्भ इच्च
For the vowel of the root दम्भ् there is substituted इ as well as ई before सन् of the Desiderative when it begins with स्।<br><br>Terms: Long ई

7.4.57|7.4.57 mucho.akarmakasya guNo vaa|mucho.akarmakasya guNo vaa|mucho.akarmakasya guNo vaa 7.4.57|मुचोऽकर्मकस्य गुणो वा|मुचोऽकर्मकस्य गुणो वा ७.४.५७|७.४.५७|७.४.५७ मुचोऽकर्मकस्य गुणो वा
When मुच् has an Intransitive signification गुण is optionally substituted for its vowel before the अनिट् सन् of the Desiderative.<br><br>Terms: 

7.4.58|7.4.58 atra lopo.abhyaasasya|atra lopo.abhyaasasya|atra lopo.abhyaasasya 7.4.58|अत्र लोपोऽभ्यासस्य|अत्र लोपोऽभ्यासस्य ७.४.५८|७.४.५८|७.४.५८ अत्र लोपोऽभ्यासस्य
The reduplicate is elided under the circumstances mentioned in the foregoing sūtras सनि मीमाघुरभलभशकपतपदामच इस् ७.४.५४ to मुचोऽकर्मकस्य गुणो वा ७.४.५७.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate elision

7.4.59|7.4.59 hrasvaH|hrasvaH|hrasvaH 7.4.59|ह्रस्वः|ह्रस्वः ७.४.५९|७.४.५९|७.४.५९ ह्रस्वः
A short is substituted for the long vowel of the reduplicate.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.60|7.4.60 halaadiH sheShaH|halaadiH sheShaH|halaadiH sheShaH 7.4.60|हलादिः शेषः|हलादिः शेषः ७.४.६०|७.४.६०|७.४.६० हलादिः शेषः
Of the consonants of the reduplicate, only the first is retained, the remainders are elided.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.61|7.4.61 sharpuurvaaH khayaH|sharpuurvaaH khayaH|sharpuurvaaH khayaH 7.4.61|शर्पूर्वाः खयः|शर्पूर्वाः खयः ७.४.६१|७.४.६१|७.४.६१ शर्पूर्वाः खयः
Of a reduplicate, the hard compound (aspirate and un-aspirate) when preceded by a sibilant, are only retained, the other consonants are elided.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.62|7.4.62 kuhoshchuH|kuhoshchuH|kuhoshchuH 7.4.62|कुहोश्चुः|कुहोश्चुः ७.४.६२|७.४.६२|७.४.६२ कुहोश्चुः
For the guttural and ह् of a reduplicate there is substituted a Platal.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.63|7.4.63 na kavateryaNGi|na kavateryaNGi|na kavateryaNGi 7.4.63|न कवतेर्यङि|न कवतेर्यङि ७.४.६३|७.४.६३|७.४.६३ न कवतेर्यङि
The Palatal is not substituted for the Guttural of the reduplicate of कु (कवते) in the intensive.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.64|7.4.64 kRSheshChandasi|kRSheshChandasi|kRSheshChandasi 7.4.64|कृषेश्छन्दसि|कृषेश्छन्दसि ७.४.६४|७.४.६४|७.४.६४ कृषेश्छन्दसि
The Palatal is not substituted for the Guttural of the reduplicate of कृष् 'to draw' in the छन्दस् (Vedas) when in the Intensive.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.65|7.4.65 daadhartidardhartidardharShibobhuututetikte.alarShyaapaniiphaNatsaMsaniShyadatkarikratkanikradadbharibhraddavidhvatodavidyutattaritrataHsariisRpataMvariivRjanmarmRjyaaganiigantiiti cha|daadhartidardhartidardharShibobhuututetikte.alarShyaapaniiphaNatsaMsaniShyadatkarikratkanikradadbharibhraddavidhvatodavidyutattaritrataHsariisRpataMvariivRjanmarmRjyaaganiigantiiti cha|daadhartidardhartidardharShibobhuututetikte.alarShyaapaniiphaNatsaMsaniShyadatkarikratkanikradadbharibhraddavidhvatodavidyutattaritrataHsariisRpataMvariivRjanmarmRjyaaganiigantiiti cha 7.4.65|दाधर्तिदर्धर्तिदर्धर्षिबोभूतुतेतिक्तेऽलर्ष्यापनीफणत्संसनिष्यदत्करिक्रत्कनिक्रदद्भरिभ्रद्दविध्वतोदविद्युतत्तरित्रतःसरीसृपतंवरीवृजन्मर्मृज्यागनीगन्तीति च|दाधर्तिदर्धर्तिदर्धर्षिबोभूतुतेतिक्तेऽलर्ष्यापनीफणत्संसनिष्यदत्करिक्रत्कनिक्रदद्भरिभ्रद्दविध्वतोदविद्युतत्तरित्रतःसरीसृपतंवरीवृजन्मर्मृज्यागनीगन्तीति च ७.४.६५|७.४.६५|७.४.६५ दाधर्तिदर्धर्तिदर्धर्षिबोभूतुतेतिक्तेऽलर्ष्यापनीफणत्संसनिष्यदत्करिक्रत्कनिक्रदद्भरिभ्रद्दविध्वतोदविद्युतत्तरित्रतःसरीसृपतंवरीवृजन्मर्मृज्यागनीगन्तीति च
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) are found the following eighteen irregularly reduplicated forms - 1. दाधर्ति 2. दर्धर्ति 3. दर्धर्षि 4. बोभूतु 5. तेतिक्ते 6. अलर्षि 7. आपनीफणत् 8. संसनिष्यदत् 9. करिक्रत् 10. कनिक्रदत् 11.भरिभ्रत् 12. द्दविध्वतः 13. दविद्युतत् 14. तरित्रतः 15. सरीसृपतम् 16. वरीवृजत् 17. मर्मृज्य and 18. आगनीगन्ति।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.66|7.4.66 urat‌|urat‌|urat‌ 7.4.66|उरत्‌|उरत्‌ ७.४.६६|७.४.६६|७.४.६६ उरत्‌
अर् -- उरण् रपरः १.१.५१ is substituted for the ऋ or ॠ of the reduplicate.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.67|7.4.67 dyutisvaapyoH samprasaaraNam|dyutisvaapyoH samprasaaraNam|dyutisvaapyoH samprasaaraNam 7.4.67|द्युतिस्वाप्योः सम्प्रसारणम्|द्युतिस्वाप्योः सम्प्रसारणम् ७.४.६७|७.४.६७|७.४.६७ द्युतिस्वाप्योः सम्प्रसारणम्
There is vocalisation of the half-vowel of the reduplicate of द्युत् and स्वापि (Causative of स्वप्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.68|7.4.68 vyatho liTi|vyatho liTi|vyatho liTi 7.4.68|व्यथो लिटि|व्यथो लिटि ७.४.६८|७.४.६८|७.४.६८ व्यथो लिटि
There is vocalisation of the half-vowel of the reduplicate of व्यथ् in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.69|7.4.69 diirgha iNaH kiti|diirgha iNaH kiti|diirgha iNaH kiti 7.4.69|दीर्घ इणः किति|दीर्घ इणः किति ७.४.६९|७.४.६९|७.४.६९ दीर्घ इणः किति
A long vowel is substituted in the reduplicate of the root इ (एति) before a personal ending of the लिट् (Perfect Tense), which has an indicatory क्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.70|7.4.70 ata aadeH|ata aadeH|ata aadeH 7.4.70|अत आदेः|अत आदेः ७.४.७०|७.४.७०|७.४.७० अत आदेः
A long vowel is substituted in the लिट् (Perfect Tense) for the initial अ of the reduplicate.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.71|7.4.71 tasmaannuD dvihalaH|tasmaannuD dvihalaH|tasmaannuD dvihalaH 7.4.71|तस्मान्नुड् द्विहलः|तस्मान्नुड् द्विहलः ७.४.७१|७.४.७१|७.४.७१ तस्मान्नुड् द्विहलः
After such a lengthened आ of the reduplicate there is added the augment नुट् (न्) to the short अ of the root which ends in a double consonant.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.72|7.4.72 ashnoteshcha|ashnoteshcha|ashnoteshcha 7.4.72|अश्नोतेश्च|अश्नोतेश्च ७.४.७२|७.४.७२|७.४.७२ अश्नोतेश्च
After the lengthened आ of the reduplicate of अश् (अश्नोति) comes the augment नुट् (न्) before the short अ in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.73|7.4.73 bhavateraH|bhavateraH|bhavateraH 7.4.73|भवतेरः|भवतेरः ७.४.७३|७.४.७३|७.४.७३ भवतेरः
अ is substituted for the vowel of the reduplicate of भू 'to be' in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.74|7.4.74 sasuuveti nigame|sasuuveti nigame|sasuuveti nigame 7.4.74|ससूवेति निगमे|ससूवेति निगमे ७.४.७४|७.४.७४|७.४.७४ ससूवेति निगमे
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) ससूव is irregularly formed in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.75|7.4.75 nijaaM trayaaNaaM guNaH shlau|nijaaM trayaaNaaM guNaH shlau|nijaaM trayaaNaaM guNaH shlau 7.4.75|निजां त्रयाणां गुणः श्लौ|निजां त्रयाणां गुणः श्लौ ७.४.७५|७.४.७५|७.४.७५ निजां त्रयाणां गुणः श्लौ
गुण is substituted for the vowel of the reduplicate in the Reduplicated Present form (श्लु) of निज् , विज् and विष्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.76|7.4.76 bhRNJaamit‌|bhRNJaamit‌|bhRNJaamit‌ 7.4.76|भृञामित्‌|भृञामित्‌ ७.४.७६|७.४.७६|७.४.७६ भृञामित्‌
In the Reduplicated Present form (श्लु) of the three roots 1. भृ 2. मा (माङ्) and 3. हा (ओहाङ्), इ is substituted for the vowel of the reduplicate.‌ <br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.77|7.4.77 artipipartyoshcha|artipipartyoshcha|artipipartyoshcha 7.4.77|अर्तिपिपर्त्योश्च|अर्तिपिपर्त्योश्च ७.४.७७|७.४.७७|७.४.७७ अर्तिपिपर्त्योश्च
इ is substituted for the vowel of the reduplicate of ऋ and पृ in the reduplicated Present form.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.78|7.4.78 bahulaM Chandasi|bahulaM Chandasi|bahulaM Chandasi 7.4.78|बहुलं छन्दसि|बहुलं छन्दसि ७.४.७८|७.४.७८|७.४.७८ बहुलं छन्दसि
इ is diversely substituted in the छन्दस् (Vedas) for the vowel of the reduplicate, in the Reduplicated Present-form.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.79|7.4.79 sanyataH|sanyataH|sanyataH 7.4.79|सन्यतः|सन्यतः ७.४.७९|७.४.७९|७.४.७९ सन्यतः
इ is substituted for the final short अ of the reduplicate in the Desiderative.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.80|7.4.80 oH puyaNjyapare|oH puyaNjyapare|oH puyaNjyapare 7.4.80|ओः पुयण्ज्यपरे|ओः पुयण्ज्यपरे ७.४.८०|७.४.८०|७.४.८० ओः पुयण्ज्यपरे
इ is substituted for the final उ or ऊ of a reduplicate before a labial, a semi-vowel and before ज् when अ or आ follows these consonants, in the Desiderative.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.81|7.4.81 sravatishRNotidravatipravatiplavatichyavatiinaaM vaa|sravatishRNotidravatipravatiplavatichyavatiinaaM vaa|sravatishRNotidravatipravatiplavatichyavatiinaaM vaa 7.4.81|स्रवतिशृणोतिद्रवतिप्रवतिप्लवतिच्यवतीनां वा|स्रवतिशृणोतिद्रवतिप्रवतिप्लवतिच्यवतीनां वा ७.४.८१|७.४.८१|७.४.८१ स्रवतिशृणोतिद्रवतिप्रवतिप्लवतिच्यवतीनां वा
इ is optionally substituted for the final उ of a reduplicate of 1. स्रु 2. श्रु 3. द्रु 4. प्रु 5. प्लु and 6. च्यु when the semi-vowel is followed by a अ or आ in the Desiderative.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.82|7.4.82 guNo yaNGlukoH|guNo yaNGlukoH|guNo yaNGlukoH 7.4.82|गुणो यङ्लुकोः|गुणो यङ्लुकोः ७.४.८२|७.४.८२|७.४.८२ गुणो यङ्लुकोः
गुण is substituted for the final of इ and उ (with their long) of a reduplicate when the Intensive character यङ् follows and also when it is elided.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.83|7.4.83 diirgho.akitaH|diirgho.akitaH|diirgho.akitaH 7.4.83|दीर्घोऽकितः|दीर्घोऽकितः ७.४.८३|७.४.८३|७.४.८३ दीर्घोऽकितः
A long vowel is substituted for the अ of the reduplicate in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्) when the reduplicate receives no augment having an indicatory क् ।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.84|7.4.84 niigvancusraMsudhvaMsubhraMsukasapatapadaskandaam|niigvancusraMsudhvaMsubhraMsukasapatapadaskandaam|niigvancusraMsudhvaMsubhraMsukasapatapadaskandaam 7.4.84|नीग्वञ्चुस्रंसुध्वंसुभ्रंसुकसपतपदस्कन्दाम्|नीग्वञ्चुस्रंसुध्वंसुभ्रंसुकसपतपदस्कन्दाम् ७.४.८४|७.४.८४|७.४.८४ नीग्वञ्चुस्रंसुध्वंसुभ्रंसुकसपतपदस्कन्दाम्
The augment नीक् is added to the reduplicate of the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्) in the following - 1. वञ्च् 2. संस्र 3. ध्वंस् 3. भ्रंश् 4. कस् 5. पत् 6. पद् and 7. स्कन्द्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.85|7.4.85 nugato.anunaasikaantasya|nugato.anunaasikaantasya|nugato.anunaasikaantasya 7.4.85|नुगतोऽनुनासिकान्तस्य|नुगतोऽनुनासिकान्तस्य ७.४.८५|७.४.८५|७.४.८५ नुगतोऽनुनासिकान्तस्य
The augment नुक् (न्) is added after the short अ of a reduplicate in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्) when the root ends in a nasal.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.86|7.4.86 japajabhadahadashabhanjapashaaM cha|japajabhadahadashabhanjapashaaM cha|japajabhadahadashabhanjapashaaM cha 7.4.86|जपजभदहदशभञ्जपशां च|जपजभदहदशभञ्जपशां च ७.४.८६|७.४.८६|७.४.८६ जपजभदहदशभञ्जपशां च
The augment नुक् (न्) comes after the reduplicates of 1. जप 2. जभ 3. दह 4. दश 5. भञ्ज and 6. पश in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.87|7.4.87 charaphaloshcha|charaphaloshcha|charaphaloshcha 7.4.87|चरफलोश्च|चरफलोश्च ७.४.८७|७.४.८७|७.४.८७ चरफलोश्च
The augment नुक् (न्) comes after the reduplicates of चर् and फल् in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.88|7.4.88 ut‌ parasyaataH|ut‌ parasyaataH|ut‌ parasyaataH 7.4.88|उत्‌ परस्यातः|उत्‌ परस्यातः ७.४.८८|७.४.८८|७.४.८८ उत्‌ परस्यातः
For the subsequent अ (i.e. for the अ of the root and not of the reduplicate), there is substituted उ in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.89|7.4.89 ti cha|ti cha|ti cha 7.4.89|ति च|ति च ७.४.८९|७.४.८९|७.४.८९ ति च
उ is substituted for the vowel of चर् and फल् before an affix beginning with त्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.90|7.4.90 riigRdupadhasya cha|riigRdupadhasya cha|riigRdupadhasya cha 7.4.90|रीगृदुपधस्य च|रीगृदुपधस्य च ७.४.९०|७.४.९०|७.४.९० रीगृदुपधस्य च
The reduplicate of a root which has ऋ at the penultimate position, gets the augment री in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.91|7.4.91 rugrikau cha luki|rugrikau cha luki|rugrikau cha luki 7.4.91|रुग्रिकौ च लुकि|रुग्रिकौ च लुकि ७.४.९१|७.४.९१|७.४.९१ रुग्रिकौ च लुकि
The augments come after the reduplicate of a root which has ऋ at the penultimate position, only when the यङ् of the Intensive is elided.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.92|7.4.92 Rtashcha|Rtashcha|Rtashcha 7.4.92|ऋतश्च|ऋतश्च ७.४.९२|७.४.९२|७.४.९२ ऋतश्च
The reduplicate of a root which ends in short ऋ gets, in the Intensive without यङ् the above augments (1. रीक् 2. रुक् and 3. रिक्), 1. रि 2. र् and 3. रि।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.93|7.4.93 sanvallaghuni chaNGpare.anaglope|sanvallaghuni chaNGpare.anaglope|sanvallaghuni chaNGpare.anaglope 7.4.93|सन्वल्लघुनि चङ्परेऽनग्लोपे|सन्वल्लघुनि चङ्परेऽनग्लोपे ७.४.९३|७.४.९३|७.४.९३ सन्वल्लघुनि चङ्परेऽनग्लोपे
In the reduplicated Aorist of the Causative, the reduplicate adapts itself to that of the Desiderative when the vowel of the root is light and the root has not lost its end-vowel before the Causative affix.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.94|7.4.94 diirgho laghoH|diirgho laghoH|diirgho laghoH 7.4.94|दीर्घो लघोः|दीर्घो लघोः ७.४.९४|७.४.९४|७.४.९४ दीर्घो लघोः
In the reduplicative syllable, a prosodially short vowel is lengthened in the reduplicated Aorist of the Causative when the vowel of the root is light and the root has not lost its end-vowel before the Causative णि।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.95|7.4.95 at‌ smRdRtvaraprathamradastRRspashaam|at‌ smRdRtvaraprathamradastRRspashaam|at‌ smRdRtvaraprathamradastRRspashaam 7.4.95|अत्‌ स्मृदृत्वरप्रथम्रदस्तॄस्पशाम्|अत्‌ स्मृदृत्वरप्रथम्रदस्तॄस्पशाम् ७.४.९५|७.४.९५|७.४.९५ अत्‌ स्मृदृत्वरप्रथम्रदस्तॄस्पशाम्
Short अ is substituted for the vowel of the reduplicate in the reduplicated Aorist of the Causative of the roots 1. स्मृ 2. दॄ 3. त्वर 4. प्रथ 5. म्रद 6. स्तॄ and 7. स्पश्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.96|7.4.96 vibhaaShaa veShTicheShTyoH|vibhaaShaa veShTicheShTyoH|vibhaaShaa veShTicheShTyoH 7.4.96|विभाषा वेष्टिचेष्ट्योः|विभाषा वेष्टिचेष्ट्योः ७.४.९६|७.४.९६|७.४.९६ विभाषा वेष्टिचेष्ट्योः
Short अ is optionally substituted for the vowel of the reduplicate in the reduplicated Aorist of the Causative of वेष्ट् and चेष्ट्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

7.4.97|7.4.97 ii cha gaNaH|ii cha gaNaH|ii cha gaNaH 7.4.97|ई च गणः|ई च गणः ७.४.९७|७.४.९७|७.४.९७ ई च गणः
In the reduplicated Aorist of the Causative, ई is substituted optionally for the vowel of the reduplicate in गण्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

8.1.1|8.1.1 sarvasya dve|sarvasya dve|sarvasya dve 8.1.1|सर्वस्य द्वे|सर्वस्य द्वे ८.१.१|८.१.१|८.१.१ सर्वस्य द्वे
From here up to यथास्वे यथायथम् ८.१.१५, inclusive, is to be supplied always the phrase 'the whole word is repeated'.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.2|8.1.2 tasya paramaamreDitam‌|tasya paramaamreDitam‌|tasya paramaamreDitam‌ 8.1.2|तस्य परमाम्रेडितम्‌|तस्य परमाम्रेडितम्‌ ८.१.२|८.१.२|८.१.२ तस्य परमाम्रेडितम्‌
Of that which is twice uttered, the latter form is called अम्रेडित (repeated).<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.3|8.1.3 anudaattaM cha|anudaattaM cha|anudaattaM cha 8.1.3|अनुदात्तं च|अनुदात्तं च ८.१.३|८.१.३|८.१.३ अनुदात्तं च
That which is called अम्रेडित (repeated) is gravely accented.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.4|8.1.4 nityaviipsayoH|nityaviipsayoH|nityaviipsayoH 8.1.4|नित्यवीप्सयोः|नित्यवीप्सयोः ८.१.४|८.१.४|८.१.४ नित्यवीप्सयोः
The whole word is अम्रेडित (repeated) when the sense is of 'always' and 'each'.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.5|8.1.5 parervarjane|parervarjane|parervarjane 8.1.5|परेर्वर्जने|परेर्वर्जने ८.१.५|८.१.५|८.१.५ परेर्वर्जने
The word परि is repeated when used in the sense of 'with the exception or exclusion of''.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.6|8.1.6 prasamupodaH paadapuuraNe|prasamupodaH paadapuuraNe|prasamupodaH paadapuuraNe 8.1.6|प्रसमुपोदः पादपूरणे|प्रसमुपोदः पादपूरणे ८.१.६|८.१.६|८.१.६ प्रसमुपोदः पादपूरणे
1. प्र 2. सम् 3. उ and 4. उत् are repeated when by so doubling, the foot of a verse is completed.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.7|8.1.7 uparyadhyadhasaH saamiipye|uparyadhyadhasaH saamiipye|uparyadhyadhasaH saamiipye 8.1.7|उपर्यध्यधसः सामीप्ये|उपर्यध्यधसः सामीप्ये ८.१.७|८.१.७|८.१.७ उपर्यध्यधसः सामीप्ये
1. उपरि 2. अधि and 3. अधस् are repeated when it expresses uninterrupted nearness.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.8|8.1.8 vaakyaaderaamantritasyaasuuyaasammatikopakutsanabhartsaneShu|vaakyaaderaamantritasyaasuuyaasammatikopakutsanabhartsaneShu|vaakyaaderaamantritasyaasuuyaasammatikopakutsanabhartsaneShu 8.1.8|वाक्यादेरामन्त्रितस्यासूयासम्मतिकोपकुत्सनभर्त्सनेषु|वाक्यादेरामन्त्रितस्यासूयासम्मतिकोपकुत्सनभर्त्सनेषु ८.१.८|८.१.८|८.१.८ वाक्यादेरामन्त्रितस्यासूयासम्मतिकोपकुत्सनभर्त्सनेषु
A Vocative, at the beginning of a sentence, is repeated, when envy, praise, anger, blame, or threat is meant by the speaker.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.9|8.1.9 ekaM bahuvriihivat‌|ekaM bahuvriihivat‌|ekaM bahuvriihivat‌ 8.1.9|एकं बहुव्रीहिवत्‌|एकं बहुव्रीहिवत्‌ ८.१.९|८.१.९|८.१.९ एकं बहुव्रीहिवत्‌
When एक is repeated, it is treated like a member of a बहुव्रीहि समास ।<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.10|8.1.10 aabaadhe cha|aabaadhe cha|aabaadhe cha 8.1.10|आबाधे च|आबाधे च ८.१.१०|८.१.१०|८.१.१० आबाधे च
A word is repeated and is treated like a member of a बहुव्रीहि समास when a mental distress over something is expressed.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.11|8.1.11 karmadhaarayavat‌ uttareShu|karmadhaarayavat‌ uttareShu|karmadhaarayavat‌ uttareShu 8.1.11|कर्मधारयवत्‌ उत्तरेषु|कर्मधारयवत्‌ उत्तरेषु ८.१.११|८.१.११|८.१.११ कर्मधारयवत्‌ उत्तरेषु
In the following rules, the double-word is treated like a कर्मधारय समास ।<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.12|8.1.12 prakaare guNavachanasya|prakaare guNavachanasya|prakaare guNavachanasya 8.1.12|प्रकारे गुणवचनस्य|प्रकारे गुणवचनस्य ८.१.१२|८.१.१२|८.१.१२ प्रकारे गुणवचनस्य
An adjective is repeated, when it is meant to express that the said attribute belongs to a thing only to a limited degree and the double word is treated like a कर्मधारय समास ।<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.13|8.1.13 akRchChre priyasukhayoranyatarasyaam|akRchChre priyasukhayoranyatarasyaam|akRchChre priyasukhayoranyatarasyaam 8.1.13|अकृच्छ्रे प्रियसुखयोरन्यतरस्याम्|अकृच्छ्रे प्रियसुखयोरन्यतरस्याम् ८.१.१३|८.१.१३|८.१.१३ अकृच्छ्रे प्रियसुखयोरन्यतरस्याम्
The words प्रिय and सुख are repeated optionally when they mean 'easily, without any difficulty'.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.14|8.1.14 yathaasve yathaayatham|yathaasve yathaayatham|yathaasve yathaayatham 8.1.14|यथास्वे यथायथम्|यथास्वे यथायथम् ८.१.१४|८.१.१४|८.१.१४ यथास्वे यथायथम्
The word यथायथम् is irregularly formed in the sense of 'respectively, fitly, properly'.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.15|8.1.15 dvandvaM rahasyamaryaadaavachanavyutkramaNayaJNapaatraprayogaabhivyaktiShu|dvandvaM rahasyamaryaadaavachanavyutkramaNayaJNapaatraprayogaabhivyaktiShu|dvandvaM rahasyamaryaadaavachanavyutkramaNayaJNapaatraprayogaabhivyaktiShu 8.1.15|द्वन्द्वं रहस्यमर्यादावचनव्युत्क्रमणयज्ञपात्रप्रयोगाभिव्यक्तिषु|द्वन्द्वं रहस्यमर्यादावचनव्युत्क्रमणयज्ञपात्रप्रयोगाभिव्यक्तिषु ८.१.१५|८.१.१५|८.१.१५ द्वन्द्वं रहस्यमर्यादावचनव्युत्क्रमणयज्ञपात्रप्रयोगाभिव्यक्तिषु
The word द्वन्द्वम् is irregularly formed in the sense of 'secret' and when it expresses a 'limit', 'a separation', 'employing in a sacrificial vessel' and 'manifestation'.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.16|8.1.16 padasya|padasya|padasya 8.1.16|पदस्य|पदस्य ८.१.१६|८.१.१६|८.१.१६ पदस्य
Up to इडाया वा ८.३.५४, inclusive, should be always supplied in every subsequent sūtra the phrase 'of a word' or 'to the whole of a word'.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.17|8.1.17 padaat‌|padaat‌|padaat‌ 8.1.17|पदात्‌|पदात्‌ ८.१.१७|८.१.१७|८.१.१७ पदात्‌
Up to सगतिरपि तिङ् ८.१.६८, inclusive, should always be supplied the phrase 'after a पद'.<br><br>Terms: Doubling of Words

8.1.18|8.1.18 anudaattaM sarvamapaadaadau|anudaattaM sarvamapaadaadau|anudaattaM sarvamapaadaadau 8.1.18|अनुदात्तं सर्वमपादादौ|अनुदात्तं सर्वमपादादौ ८.१.१८|८.१.१८|८.१.१८ अनुदात्तं सर्वमपादादौ
Up to (सामान्यवचनं) विभाषितं विशेषवचने (बहुवचनम्) ८.१.७४, inclusive, should always be supplied the phrase 'the whole is unaccented, if it does not stand at the beginning of the foot of a verse'.<br><br>Terms: अनुदात्त

8.1.19|8.1.19 aamantritasya cha|aamantritasya cha|aamantritasya cha 8.1.19|आमन्त्रितस्य च|आमन्त्रितस्य च ८.१.१९|८.१.१९|८.१.१९ आमन्त्रितस्य च
All the syllables of the Vocative Case are unaccented when a word precedes them and they do not stand at the beginning of a hemistich.<br><br>Terms: अनुदात्त

8.1.20|8.1.20 yuShmadasmadoH ShaShThiichaturthiidvitiiyaasthayorvaannaavau|yuShmadasmadoH ShaShThiichaturthiidvitiiyaasthayorvaannaavau|yuShmadasmadoH ShaShThiichaturthiidvitiiyaasthayorvaannaavau 8.1.20|युष्मदस्मदोः षष्ठीचतुर्थीद्वितीयास्थयोर्वान्नावौ|युष्मदस्मदोः षष्ठीचतुर्थीद्वितीयास्थयोर्वान्नावौ ८.१.२०|८.१.२०|८.१.२० युष्मदस्मदोः षष्ठीचतुर्थीद्वितीयास्थयोर्वान्नावौ
dual of युष्मद् and अस्मद् are substituted वाम and नौ respectively ।<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.21|8.1.21 bahuvachane vasnasau|bahuvachane vasnasau|bahuvachane vasnasau 8.1.21|बहुवचने वस्नसौ|बहुवचने वस्नसौ ८.१.२१|८.१.२१|८.१.२१ बहुवचने वस्नसौ
For (the Genitive 6th-Case, Dative -4th Case and Accusative -2nd case) plural of युष्मद् and अस्मद् are substituted वस् and नस् respectively (when a word precedes and these substitutes are अनुदात्त).<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.22|8.1.22 temayaavekavachanasya|temayaavekavachanasya|temayaavekavachanasya 8.1.22|तेमयावेकवचनस्य|तेमयावेकवचनस्य ८.१.२२|८.१.२२|८.१.२२ तेमयावेकवचनस्य
For the Genitive 6th-Case and Dative -4th Case singular (of युष्मद् and अस्मद् are substituted) ते and मे respectively (when a word precedes and these substitutes are अनुदात्त).<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.23|8.1.23 tvaamau dvitiiyaayaaH|tvaamau dvitiiyaayaaH|tvaamau dvitiiyaayaaH 8.1.23|त्वामौ द्वितीयायाः|त्वामौ द्वितीयायाः ८.१.२३|८.१.२३|८.१.२३ त्वामौ द्वितीयायाः
For the Accusative -2nd case singular of युष्मद् and अस्मद् are substituted त्वा and मा respectively (when a word precedes and these substitutes are अनुदात्त).<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.24|8.1.24 na chavaahaahaivayukte|na chavaahaahaivayukte|na chavaahaahaivayukte 8.1.24|न चवाहाहैवयुक्ते|न चवाहाहैवयुक्ते ८.१.२४|८.१.२४|८.१.२४ न चवाहाहैवयुक्ते
when there is in connection with the सर्वनाम any of these - 1. च 'and' 2. वा 'or' 3. ह 'Oh!' 4. अह 'wonderful' or 5. एव 'only'.<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.25|8.1.25 pashyaarthaishchaanaalochane|pashyaarthaishchaanaalochane|pashyaarthaishchaanaalochane 8.1.25|पश्यार्थैश्चानालोचने|पश्यार्थैश्चानालोचने ८.१.२५|८.१.२५|८.१.२५ पश्यार्थैश्चानालोचने
The above substitutions do not take place also in connection with verbs having the sense of 'seeing' when physical seeing is not denoted.<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.26|8.1.26 sapuurvaayaaH prathamaayaa vibhaaShaa|sapuurvaayaaH prathamaayaa vibhaaShaa|sapuurvaayaaH prathamaayaa vibhaaShaa 8.1.26|सपूर्वायाः प्रथमाया विभाषा|सपूर्वायाः प्रथमाया विभाषा ८.१.२६|८.१.२६|८.१.२६ सपूर्वायाः प्रथमाया विभाषा
When the सर्वनाम follows a Nominative 1st-Case, which itself is preceded by another word, then the above substitutions may take place optionally.<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.27|8.1.27 tiNGo gotraadiini kutsanaabhiixNyayoH|tiNGo gotraadiini kutsanaabhiixNyayoH|tiNGo gotraadiini kutsanaabhiixNyayoH 8.1.27|तिङो गोत्रादीनि कुत्सनाभीक्ष्ण्ययोः|तिङो गोत्रादीनि कुत्सनाभीक्ष्ण्ययोः ८.१.२७|८.१.२७|८.१.२७ तिङो गोत्रादीनि कुत्सनाभीक्ष्ण्ययोः
The words गोत्र etc. become unaccented after a finite verb when a contempt or a repetition in intended.<br><br>Terms: सर्वनाम

8.1.28|8.1.28 tiNGNGatiNGaH|tiNGNGatiNGaH|tiNGNGatiNGaH 8.1.28|तिङ्ङतिङः|तिङ्ङतिङः ८.१.२८|८.१.२८|८.१.२८ तिङ्ङतिङः
A finite verb is unaccented when a word precedes it which is not a finite verb.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.29|8.1.29 na luT|na luT|na luT 8.1.29|न लुट्|न लुट् ८.१.२९|८.१.२९|८.१.२९ न लुट्
By the लुट् (Periphrastic Future) is not unaccented when it is preceded by a word which is not a finite verb.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.30|8.1.30 nipaatairyadyadihantakuvinnechchechchaNkachchidyatrayuktam|nipaatairyadyadihantakuvinnechchechchaNkachchidyatrayuktam|nipaatairyadyadihantakuvinnechchechchaNkachchidyatrayuktam 8.1.30|निपातैर्यद्यदिहन्तकुविन्नेच्चेच्चण्कच्चिद्यत्रयुक्तम्|निपातैर्यद्यदिहन्तकुविन्नेच्चेच्चण्कच्चिद्यत्रयुक्तम् ८.१.३०|८.१.३०|८.१.३० निपातैर्यद्यदिहन्तकुविन्नेच्चेच्चण्कच्चिद्यत्रयुक्तम्
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with the particles 1. यत् 'that', 'because' 2. यदि 'if' 3. हन्त 'also', 'O!' 4. कुवित् 'well' 5. नेत् 'not' 6. चेत् 'if' 7. च 'if' 8. कच्चित् (interrogative particle implying 'I hope' or 'I hope not') and 9. यत्र 'where'. <br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.31|8.1.31 naha pratyaarambhe|naha pratyaarambhe|naha pratyaarambhe 8.1.31|नह प्रत्यारम्भे|नह प्रत्यारम्भे ८.१.३१|८.१.३१|८.१.३१ नह प्रत्यारम्भे
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with नह when used in the sense of forbidding.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.32|8.1.32 satyaM prashne|satyaM prashne|satyaM prashne 8.1.32|सत्यं प्रश्ने|सत्यं प्रश्ने ८.१.३२|८.१.३२|८.१.३२ सत्यं प्रश्ने
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with सत्य when used in asking a question.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.33|8.1.33 angaapraatilomye|angaapraatilomye|angaapraatilomye 8.1.33|अङ्गाप्रातिलोम्ये|अङ्गाप्रातिलोम्ये ८.१.३३|८.१.३३|८.१.३३ अङ्गाप्रातिलोम्ये
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with अङ्ग when used in a friendly assertion.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.34|8.1.34 hi cha|hi cha|hi cha 8.1.34|हि च|हि च ८.१.३४|८.१.३४|८.१.३४ हि च
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with हि when used in a friendly assertion.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.35|8.1.35 Chandasyanekamapi saakaankSham‌|Chandasyanekamapi saakaankSham‌|Chandasyanekamapi saakaankSham‌ 8.1.35|छन्दस्यनेकमपि साकाङ्क्षम्‌|छन्दस्यनेकमपि साकाङ्क्षम्‌ ८.१.३५|८.१.३५|८.१.३५ छन्दस्यनेकमपि साकाङ्क्षम्‌
In the छन्दस् (Vedas), the finite verb retains its accent (but not always) in connection with हि when it stands in correlation to another verb, even more than one.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.36|8.1.36 yaavadyathaabhyaam|yaavadyathaabhyaam|yaavadyathaabhyaam 8.1.36|यावद्यथाभ्याम्|यावद्यथाभ्याम् ८.१.३६|८.१.३६|८.१.३६ यावद्यथाभ्याम्
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with यावत् and यथा।<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.37|8.1.37 puujaayaaM naanantaram|puujaayaaM naanantaram|puujaayaaM naanantaram 8.1.37|पूजायां नानन्तरम्|पूजायां नानन्तरम् ८.१.३७|८.१.३७|८.१.३७ पूजायां नानन्तरम्
But not so when these particles यावत् and यथा immediately precede the verb an denote 'praise'.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.38|8.1.38 upasargavyapetaM cha|upasargavyapetaM cha|upasargavyapetaM cha 8.1.38|उपसर्गव्यपेतं च|उपसर्गव्यपेतं च ८.१.३८|८.१.३८|८.१.३८ उपसर्गव्यपेतं च
A finite verb loses its accent when it denotes 'praise' and is joined immediately with यावत् and यथा through the intervention of an उपसर्ग (verbal Preposition).<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.39|8.1.39 tupashyapashyataahaiH puujaayaam|tupashyapashyataahaiH puujaayaam|tupashyapashyataahaiH puujaayaam 8.1.39|तुपश्यपश्यताहैः पूजायाम्|तुपश्यपश्यताहैः पूजायाम् ८.१.३९|८.१.३९|८.१.३९ तुपश्यपश्यताहैः पूजायाम्
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with 1. तु 2. पश्य 3. पश्यत and 4. अह when meaning 'praise'.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.40|8.1.40 aho cha|aho cha|aho cha 8.1.40|अहो च|अहो च ८.१.४०|८.१.४०|८.१.४० अहो च
The finite verb retains its accent in connection with अहो when meaning 'praise'.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.41|8.1.41 sheShe vibhaaShaa|sheShe vibhaaShaa|sheShe vibhaaShaa 8.1.41|शेषे विभाषा|शेषे विभाषा ८.१.४१|८.१.४१|८.१.४१ शेषे विभाषा
The finite verb optionally retains its accent in connection with अहो in the remaining cases (i.e. where it does not mean 'praise').<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.42|8.1.42 puraa cha pariipsaayaam|puraa cha pariipsaayaam|puraa cha pariipsaayaam 8.1.42|पुरा च परीप्सायाम्|पुरा च परीप्सायाम् ८.१.४२|८.१.४२|८.१.४२ पुरा च परीप्सायाम्
The finite verb optionally retains its accent in connection with पुरा when it means 'haste' (i.e. when पुरा means 'before').<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.43|8.1.43 nanvityanuJNaiShaNaayaam|nanvityanuJNaiShaNaayaam|nanvityanuJNaiShaNaayaam 8.1.43|नन्वित्यनुज्ञैषणायाम्|नन्वित्यनुज्ञैषणायाम् ८.१.४३|८.१.४३|८.१.४३ नन्वित्यनुज्ञैषणायाम्
The finite verb optionally retains its accent in connection with ननु when with this particle, permission is asked.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.44|8.1.44 kiM kriyaaprashne.anupasargamapratiShiddham‌|kiM kriyaaprashne.anupasargamapratiShiddham‌|kiM kriyaaprashne.anupasargamapratiShiddham‌ 8.1.44|किं क्रियाप्रश्नेऽनुपसर्गमप्रतिषिद्धम्‌|किं क्रियाप्रश्नेऽनुपसर्गमप्रतिषिद्धम्‌ ८.१.४४|८.१.४४|८.१.४४ किं क्रियाप्रश्नेऽनुपसर्गमप्रतिषिद्धम्‌
The finite verb optionally retains its accent in connection with किम् when with this is asked a question relating to an action and when the verb is not preceded by a preposition or a negation.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.45|8.1.45 lope vibhaaShaa|lope vibhaaShaa|lope vibhaaShaa 8.1.45|लोपे विभाषा|लोपे विभाषा ८.१.४५|८.१.४५|८.१.४५ लोपे विभाषा
When however किम् is not added in asking such a question, the finite verb may optionally retain its accent.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.46|8.1.46 ehimanye prahaase lRT|ehimanye prahaase lRT|ehimanye prahaase lRT 8.1.46|एहिमन्ये प्रहासे लृट्|एहिमन्ये प्रहासे लृट् ८.१.४६|८.१.४६|८.१.४६ एहिमन्ये प्रहासे लृट्
In connection with एहिमन्ये used diversely in the लृट् (I Future) that follows it, retains its accent.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.47|8.1.47 jaatvapuurvam|jaatvapuurvam|jaatvapuurvam 8.1.47|जात्वपूर्वम्|जात्वपूर्वम् ८.१.४७|८.१.४७|८.१.४७ जात्वपूर्वम्
The finite verb optionally retains its accent after जातु when this जातु is not preceded by another word.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.48|8.1.48 kimvRttaM cha chiduttaram|kimvRttaM cha chiduttaram|kimvRttaM cha chiduttaram 8.1.48|किम्वृत्तं च चिदुत्तरम्|किम्वृत्तं च चिदुत्तरम् ८.१.४८|८.१.४८|८.१.४८ किम्वृत्तं च चिदुत्तरम्
Also after a form of किम् when the particle चित् follows it and when no other word precedes such form of किम् the finite verb retains its accent.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.49|8.1.49 aaho utaaho chaanantaram|aaho utaaho chaanantaram|aaho utaaho chaanantaram 8.1.49|आहो उताहो चानन्तरम्|आहो उताहो चानन्तरम् ८.१.४९|८.१.४९|८.१.४९ आहो उताहो चानन्तरम्
Also after an immediately preceding आहो and उताहो when these follow, no other word, the verb retains its accent.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.50|8.1.50 sheShe vibhaaShaa|sheShe vibhaaShaa|sheShe vibhaaShaa 8.1.50|शेषे विभाषा|शेषे विभाषा ८.१.५०|८.१.५०|८.१.५० शेषे विभाषा
When the above mentioned particles आहो and उताहो do not immediately precede the verb, the verb may optionally retain its accent.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.51|8.1.51 gatyarthaloTaa lRNna chet‌ kaarakaM sarvaanyat‌|gatyarthaloTaa lRNna chet‌ kaarakaM sarvaanyat‌|gatyarthaloTaa lRNna chet‌ kaarakaM sarvaanyat‌ 8.1.51|गत्यर्थलोटा लृण्न चेत्‌ कारकं सर्वान्यत्‌|गत्यर्थलोटा लृण्न चेत्‌ कारकं सर्वान्यत्‌ ८.१.५१|८.१.५१|८.१.५१ गत्यर्थलोटा लृण्न चेत्‌ कारकं सर्वान्यत्‌
The लृट् (I Future) retains its accent in connection with the Imperative of a verb denoting 'motion' ('to go', 'to come', 'to start' etc.) but only in that case, when the subject and object of both the verbs are not wholly different one from another.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.52|8.1.52 loT cha|loT cha|loT cha 8.1.52|लोट् च|लोट् च ८.१.५२|८.१.५२|८.१.५२ लोट् च
Also an लोट् (Imperative Mood), following after an Imperative of verbs of 'motion' retains its accent when the subject or object of both the verbs is not wholly different.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.53|8.1.53 vibhaaShitaM sopasargamanuttamam‌|vibhaaShitaM sopasargamanuttamam‌|vibhaaShitaM sopasargamanuttamam‌ 8.1.53|विभाषितं सोपसर्गमनुत्तमम्‌|विभाषितं सोपसर्गमनुत्तमम्‌ ८.१.५३|८.१.५३|८.१.५३ विभाषितं सोपसर्गमनुत्तमम्‌
An Imperative preceded by a preposition and not in the 1st person, following an Imperative of verbs of 'motion', may optionally retain its accent when the कारक is not wholly different.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.54|8.1.54 hanta cha|hanta cha|hanta cha 8.1.54|हन्त च|हन्त च ८.१.५४|८.१.५४|८.१.५४ हन्त च
An Imperative with a preposition preceding it, may optionally retain its accent, in connection with हन्त , but not in the 1st person.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.55|8.1.55 aama ekaantaramaamantritamanantike|aama ekaantaramaamantritamanantike|aama ekaantaramaamantritamanantike 8.1.55|आम एकान्तरमामन्त्रितमनन्तिके|आम एकान्तरमामन्त्रितमनन्तिके ८.१.५५|८.१.५५|८.१.५५ आम एकान्तरमामन्त्रितमनन्तिके
After आम् , but separated from it by not more than one word, the Vocative retains its accent when the person addressed is not near.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.56|8.1.56 yaddhituparaM Chandasi|yaddhituparaM Chandasi|yaddhituparaM Chandasi 8.1.56|यद्धितुपरं छन्दसि|यद्धितुपरं छन्दसि ८.१.५६|८.१.५६|८.१.५६ यद्धितुपरं छन्दसि
A finite verb followed by यत् or हि or तु retains its accent in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.57|8.1.57 chanachidivagotraaditaddhitaamreDiteShvagateH|chanachidivagotraaditaddhitaamreDiteShvagateH|chanachidivagotraaditaddhitaamreDiteShvagateH 8.1.57|चनचिदिवगोत्रादितद्धिताम्रेडितेष्वगतेः|चनचिदिवगोत्रादितद्धिताम्रेडितेष्वगतेः ८.१.५७|८.१.५७|८.१.५७ चनचिदिवगोत्रादितद्धिताम्रेडितेष्वगतेः
A finite verb retains its accent when it is not preceded by a गति Particle -- गतिश्च १.४.६० etc., and when it is followed by 1. चन 2. चिद् 3. इव 4. गोत्र etc., a तद्धित affix, or by its own doubled form.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.58|8.1.58 chaadiShu cha|chaadiShu cha|chaadiShu cha 8.1.58|चादिषु च|चादिषु च ८.१.५८|८.१.५८|८.१.५८ चादिषु च
A finite verb, not preceded by a गति , retains its accent before the particles च (1. वा 2. ह 3. अह and 4. एव -- न चवाहाहैवयुक्ते ८.१.२४).<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.59|8.1.59 chavaayoge prathamaa|chavaayoge prathamaa|chavaayoge prathamaa 8.1.59|चवायोगे प्रथमा|चवायोगे प्रथमा ८.१.५९|८.१.५९|८.१.५९ चवायोगे प्रथमा
The first finite verb only retains its accent in connection with च and वा।<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.60|8.1.60 heti xiyaayaam|heti xiyaayaam|heti xiyaayaam 8.1.60|हेति क्षियायाम्|हेति क्षियायाम् ८.१.६०|८.१.६०|८.१.६० हेति क्षियायाम्
In connection with ह , the first finite verb retains its accent when an offence against custom is reprimanded.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.61|8.1.61 aheti viniyoge cha|aheti viniyoge cha|aheti viniyoge cha 8.1.61|अहेति विनियोगे च|अहेति विनियोगे च ८.१.६१|८.१.६१|८.१.६१ अहेति विनियोगे च
In connection with अह , the first finite verb retains its accent when it refers to various commissions (as well as when a breach of good manners is condemned).<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.62|8.1.62 chaahalopa evetyavadhaaraNam|chaahalopa evetyavadhaaraNam|chaahalopa evetyavadhaaraNam 8.1.62|चाहलोप एवेत्यवधारणम्|चाहलोप एवेत्यवधारणम् ८.१.६२|८.१.६२|८.१.६२ चाहलोप एवेत्यवधारणम्
When च and अह are elided, the first finite verb still retains its accent when एव with the force of limitation, takes their place.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.63|8.1.63 chaadilope vibhaaShaa|chaadilope vibhaaShaa|chaadilope vibhaaShaa 8.1.63|चादिलोपे विभाषा|चादिलोपे विभाषा ८.१.६३|८.१.६३|८.१.६३ चादिलोपे विभाषा
When च (1. वा 2. ह 3. अह and 4. एव -- न चवाहाहैवयुक्ते ८.१.२४) are elided the first verb optionally retains its accent.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.64|8.1.64 vaivaaveti cha chChandasi|vaivaaveti cha chChandasi|vaivaaveti cha chChandasi 8.1.64|वैवावेति च च्छन्दसि|वैवावेति च च्छन्दसि ८.१.६४|८.१.६४|८.१.६४ वैवावेति च च्छन्दसि
Also in connection with वै and वाव , may optionally, in the छन्दस् (Vedas), the first verb retains its accent.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.65|8.1.65 ekaanyaabhyaaM samarthaabhyaam|ekaanyaabhyaaM samarthaabhyaam|ekaanyaabhyaaM samarthaabhyaam 8.1.65|एकान्याभ्यां समर्थाभ्याम्|एकान्याभ्यां समर्थाभ्याम् ८.१.६५|८.१.६५|८.१.६५ एकान्याभ्यां समर्थाभ्याम्
Also in connection with एक and अन्य , optionally in the छन्दस् (Vedas), the first verb retains its accent, when these word have the same meaning ('the one - the other').<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.66|8.1.66 yadvRttaannityaM|yadvRttaannityaM|yadvRttaannityaM 8.1.66|यद्वृत्तान्नित्यं|यद्वृत्तान्नित्यं ८.१.६६|८.१.६६|८.१.६६ यद्वृत्तान्नित्यं
In connection with यद् in all its forms, the verb retains its accent always.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.67|8.1.67 puujanaat‌ puujitamanudaattam (kaaShThaadibhyaH)|puujanaat‌ puujitamanudaattam (kaaShThaadibhyaH)|puujanaat‌ puujitamanudaattam (kaaShThaadibhyaH) 8.1.67|पूजनात्‌ पूजितमनुदात्तम् (काष्ठादिभ्यः)|पूजनात्‌ पूजितमनुदात्तम् (काष्ठादिभ्यः) ८.१.६७|८.१.६७|८.१.६७ पूजनात्‌ पूजितमनुदात्तम् (काष्ठादिभ्यः)
After a word denoting praise belonging to काष्ठादि class the word whose praise is denoted, becomes अनुदात्त ।<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.68|8.1.68 sagatirapi tiNG|sagatirapi tiNG|sagatirapi tiNG 8.1.68|सगतिरपि तिङ्|सगतिरपि तिङ् ८.१.६८|८.१.६८|८.१.६८ सगतिरपि तिङ्
(After such words denoting praise) the finite verb (which is praised) becomes अनुदात्त even along with the गति , if any, that may precede it.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.69|8.1.69 kutsane cha supyagotraadau|kutsane cha supyagotraadau|kutsane cha supyagotraadau 8.1.69|कुत्सने च सुप्यगोत्रादौ|कुत्सने च सुप्यगोत्रादौ ८.१.६९|८.१.६९|८.१.६९ कुत्सने च सुप्यगोत्रादौ
A finite verb along with its preceding गति , if any, become अनुदात्त when a noun denoting the fault of the action follows, with the exception of गोत्र etc.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.70|8.1.70 gatirgatau|gatirgatau|gatirgatau 8.1.70|गतिर्गतौ|गतिर्गतौ ८.१.७०|८.१.७०|८.१.७० गतिर्गतौ
A गति becomes unaccented when followed by another गति .<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.71|8.1.71 tiNGi chodaattavati|tiNGi chodaattavati|tiNGi chodaattavati 8.1.71|तिङि चोदात्तवति|तिङि चोदात्तवति ८.१.७१|८.१.७१|८.१.७१ तिङि चोदात्तवति
A गति becomes अनुदात्त when followed by an accented finite verb.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.72|8.1.72 aamantritaM puurvam avidyamaanavat‌|aamantritaM puurvam avidyamaanavat‌|aamantritaM puurvam avidyamaanavat‌ 8.1.72|आमन्त्रितं पूर्वम् अविद्यमानवत्‌|आमन्त्रितं पूर्वम् अविद्यमानवत्‌ ८.१.७२|८.१.७२|८.१.७२ आमन्त्रितं पूर्वम् अविद्यमानवत्‌
A preceding Vocative is considered as non-existent (for the purposes of the accent of the following word and the enclitic forms of युष्मद् and अस्मद्).<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.73|8.1.73 naamantrite samaanaadhikaraNe (saamaanyavachanam)|naamantrite samaanaadhikaraNe (saamaanyavachanam)|naamantrite samaanaadhikaraNe (saamaanyavachanam) 8.1.73|नामन्त्रिते समानाधिकरणे (सामान्यवचनम्)|नामन्त्रिते समानाधिकरणे (सामान्यवचनम्) ८.१.७३|८.१.७३|८.१.७३ नामन्त्रिते समानाधिकरणे (सामान्यवचनम्)
A preceding Vocative, when it conveys a general idea, is not to be considered as if non-existent for the purposes of the subsequent Vocative, which stands in apposition with the former.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.1.74|8.1.74 vibhaaShitaM visheShavachane bahuvachanam|vibhaaShitaM visheShavachane bahuvachanam|vibhaaShitaM visheShavachane bahuvachanam 8.1.74|विभाषितं विशेषवचने बहुवचनम्|विभाषितं विशेषवचने बहुवचनम् ८.१.७४|८.१.७४|८.१.७४ विभाषितं विशेषवचने बहुवचनम्
When the preceding Vocative is in the plural number, it is optionally considered as non-existent, if the subsequent Vocative, in apposition with it, is a specific term.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.2.1|8.2.1 puurvatraasiddham|puurvatraasiddham|puurvatraasiddham 8.2.1|पूर्वत्रासिद्धम्|पूर्वत्रासिद्धम् ८.२.१|८.२.१|८.२.१ पूर्वत्रासिद्धम्
Whatever will be taught hereafter, up to the end of the work, is to be considered as not taken effect, in relation to the application of a preceding rule.<br><br>Terms: असिद्ध

8.2.2|8.2.2 nalopaH supsvarasaMJNaatugvidhiShu kRti|nalopaH supsvarasaMJNaatugvidhiShu kRti|nalopaH supsvarasaMJNaatugvidhiShu kRti 8.2.2|नलोपः सुप्स्वरसंज्ञातुग्विधिषु कृति|नलोपः सुप्स्वरसंज्ञातुग्विधिषु कृति ८.२.२|८.२.२|८.२.२ नलोपः सुप्स्वरसंज्ञातुग्विधिषु कृति
The elision of a final न् -- नलोपः प्रातिपदिकान्तस्य ८.२.७, is considered as if not to have taken effect, in applying the following rules - 1. rules regarding case-endings 2. rules regarding accents 3. rules regarding any technical term of Grammar and 4. rules regarding the augment त् before a कृत् affix.<br><br>Terms: असिद्ध

8.2.3|8.2.3 na mu ne|na mu ne|na mu ne 8.2.3|न मु ने|न मु ने ८.२.३|८.२.३|८.२.३ न मु ने
The sūtra अदसोऽसेर्दादु दो मः ८.२.८०, teaching the substitution of मु for the दस् of the pronoun अदस् is however not treated as असिद्ध in relation to the case-ending ना।<br><br>Terms: असिद्ध

8.2.4|8.2.4 udaattasvaritayoryaNaH svarito.anudaattasya|udaattasvaritayoryaNaH svarito.anudaattasya|udaattasvaritayoryaNaH svarito.anudaattasya 8.2.4|उदात्तस्वरितयोर्यणः स्वरितोऽनुदात्तस्य|उदात्तस्वरितयोर्यणः स्वरितोऽनुदात्तस्य ८.२.४|८.२.४|८.२.४ उदात्तस्वरितयोर्यणः स्वरितोऽनुदात्तस्य
A स्वरित vowel is the substitute of an अनुदात्त vowel when the latter follows after such a semi-vowel which has replaced an उदात्त (acute accent) or a स्वरित vowel.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.2.5|8.2.5 ekaadesha udaattenodaattaH|ekaadesha udaattenodaattaH|ekaadesha udaattenodaattaH 8.2.5|एकादेश उदात्तेनोदात्तः|एकादेश उदात्तेनोदात्तः ८.२.५|८.२.५|८.२.५ एकादेश उदात्तेनोदात्तः
The single substitute of an unaccented with an उदात्त (acute accent) vowel is उदात्त।<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.2.6|8.2.6 svarito vaa.anudaatte padaadau|svarito vaa.anudaatte padaadau|svarito vaa.anudaatte padaadau 8.2.6|स्वरितो वाऽनुदात्ते पदादौ|स्वरितो वाऽनुदात्ते पदादौ ८.२.६|८.२.६|८.२.६ स्वरितो वाऽनुदात्ते पदादौ
The single substitute of an unaccented vowel standing at the beginning of a word, with an उदात्त (acute accent) vowel may optionally be a स्वरित or उदात्त (acute accent).<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.2.7|8.2.7 nalopaH praatipadikaantasya|nalopaH praatipadikaantasya|nalopaH praatipadikaantasya 8.2.7|नलोपः प्रातिपदिकान्तस्य|नलोपः प्रातिपदिकान्तस्य ८.२.७|८.२.७|८.२.७ नलोपः प्रातिपदिकान्तस्य
The न् at the end of a nominal-stem, which is a पद -- शेषो घ्यसखि १.४.७, is elided.<br><br>Terms: Accent

8.2.8|8.2.8 na NGisambuddhyoH|na NGisambuddhyoH|na NGisambuddhyoH 8.2.8|न ङिसम्बुद्ध्योः|न ङिसम्बुद्ध्योः ८.२.८|८.२.८|८.२.८ न ङिसम्बुद्ध्योः
(But such न्) is not elided in the Locative -7th case and Vocative Case singular.<br><br>Terms: न् Elision

8.2.9|8.2.9 maadupadhaayaashcha matorvo.ayavaadibhyaH|maadupadhaayaashcha matorvo.ayavaadibhyaH|maadupadhaayaashcha matorvo.ayavaadibhyaH 8.2.9|मादुपधायाश्च मतोर्वोऽयवादिभ्यः|मादुपधायाश्च मतोर्वोऽयवादिभ्यः ८.२.९|८.२.९|८.२.९ मादुपधायाश्च मतोर्वोऽयवादिभ्यः
For the म् of the affix मत् is substituted व if the अङ्ग (stem) ends in म् or अ ( and आ) or if these are in the penultimate position; but not after यव etc.<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

8.2.10|8.2.10 jhayaH|jhayaH|jhayaH 8.2.10|झयः|झयः ८.२.१०|८.२.१०|८.२.१० झयः
The व् is substituted for the म् of मत् after a अङ्ग (stem) ending in a mute consonant.<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

8.2.11|8.2.11 saMJNaayaam|saMJNaayaam|saMJNaayaam 8.2.11|संज्ञायाम्|संज्ञायाम् ८.२.११|८.२.११|८.२.११ संज्ञायाम्
The व् is substituted for the म् of मत् when the word so formed is a Name.<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

8.2.12|8.2.12 aasandiivadaShThiivachchakriivatkaxiivadrumaNvachcharmaNvatii|aasandiivadaShThiivachchakriivatkaxiivadrumaNvachcharmaNvatii|aasandiivadaShThiivachchakriivatkaxiivadrumaNvachcharmaNvatii 8.2.12|आसन्दीवदष्ठीवच्चक्रीवत्कक्षीवद्रुमण्वच्चर्मण्वती|आसन्दीवदष्ठीवच्चक्रीवत्कक्षीवद्रुमण्वच्चर्मण्वती ८.२.१२|८.२.१२|८.२.१२ आसन्दीवदष्ठीवच्चक्रीवत्कक्षीवद्रुमण्वच्चर्मण्वती
The following names are irregularly formed 1. आसन्दीवत् 2. अष्ठीवत् 3. चक्रीवत् 4. कक्षीवत् 5. रुमण्वत् and 6. चर्मण्वती। (Reference श्लोक - आसन्दीवति धान्यादं रुक्मिणं हरितस्रजम्। अश्वं बबन्ध सारङ्गं देवेभ्यो अनमेजयः।)<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

8.2.13|8.2.13 udanvaanudadhau cha|udanvaanudadhau cha|udanvaanudadhau cha 8.2.13|उदन्वानुदधौ च|उदन्वानुदधौ च ८.२.१३|८.२.१३|८.२.१३ उदन्वानुदधौ च
The word उदन्वान् is irregularly formed in the sense of 'a sea'.<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

8.2.14|8.2.14 raajanvaan sauraajye|raajanvaan sauraajye|raajanvaan sauraajye 8.2.14|राजन्वान् सौराज्ये|राजन्वान् सौराज्ये ८.२.१४|८.२.१४|८.२.१४ राजन्वान् सौराज्ये
Also राजन्वान् when the sense is of a good government.<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

8.2.15|8.2.15 ChandasiiraH|ChandasiiraH|ChandasiiraH 8.2.15|छन्दसीरः|छन्दसीरः ८.२.१५|८.२.१५|८.२.१५ छन्दसीरः
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) व् is substituted for the म् of मत् after a अङ्ग (stem) ending in इ (or ई) or र्।<br><br>Terms: मतुप्

8.2.16|8.2.16 ano nuT|ano nuT|ano nuT 8.2.16|अनो नुट्|अनो नुट् ८.२.१६|८.२.१६|८.२.१६ अनो नुट्
The affix मत् gets the augment नुट् in the छन्दस् (Vedas) after a अङ्ग (stem) ending in अन्।<br><br>Terms: नुट् augment

8.2.17|8.2.17 naadghasya|naadghasya|naadghasya 8.2.17|नाद्घस्य|नाद्घस्य ८.२.१७|८.२.१७|८.२.१७ नाद्घस्य
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) the affixes तर and तम get the augment नुट् after a stem in न्।<br><br>Terms: नुट् augment

8.2.18|8.2.18 kRpo ro laH|kRpo ro laH|kRpo ro laH 8.2.18|कृपो रो लः|कृपो रो लः ८.२.१८|८.२.१८|८.२.१८ कृपो रो लः
For the र् of the root कृप् there is substituted ल्।<br><br>Terms: र् changed to ल्

8.2.19|8.2.19 upasargasyaayatau|upasargasyaayatau|upasargasyaayatau 8.2.19|उपसर्गस्यायतौ|उपसर्गस्यायतौ ८.२.१९|८.२.१९|८.२.१९ उपसर्गस्यायतौ
ल् is substituted for the र् of a preposition when अयते follows.<br><br>Terms: र् changed to ल्

8.2.20|8.2.20 gro yaNGi|gro yaNGi|gro yaNGi 8.2.20|ग्रो यङि|ग्रो यङि ८.२.२०|८.२.२०|८.२.२० ग्रो यङि
ल् is substituted for the र् of गॄ in the intensive.<br><br>Terms: र् changed to ल्

8.2.21|8.2.21 achi vibhaaShaa|achi vibhaaShaa|achi vibhaaShaa 8.2.21|अचि विभाषा|अचि विभाषा ८.२.२१|८.२.२१|८.२.२१ अचि विभाषा
ल् is optionally changed to ल् before an affix beginning with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: र् changed to ल्

8.2.22|8.2.22 pareshcha ghaankayoH|pareshcha ghaankayoH|pareshcha ghaankayoH 8.2.22|परेश्च घाङ्कयोः|परेश्च घाङ्कयोः ८.२.२२|८.२.२२|८.२.२२ परेश्च घाङ्कयोः
The र् of परि is changed to ल् before घ and अङ्क।<br><br>Terms: र् changed to ल्

8.2.23|8.2.23 saMyogaantasya lopaH|saMyogaantasya lopaH|saMyogaantasya lopaH 8.2.23|संयोगान्तस्य लोपः|संयोगान्तस्य लोपः ८.२.२३|८.२.२३|८.२.२३ संयोगान्तस्य लोपः
When a word ends in a double consonant the last consonant is dropped.<br><br>Terms: र् changed to ल्

8.2.24|8.2.24 raat‌ sasya|raat‌ sasya|raat‌ sasya 8.2.24|रात्‌ सस्य|रात्‌ सस्य ८.२.२४|८.२.२४|८.२.२४ रात्‌ सस्य
Of a word ending in a conjunct consonant, only स् is elided if it comes after र् (but any other consonant coming after र् is not elided).<br><br>Terms: स् changed to ल्

8.2.25|8.2.25 dhi cha|dhi cha|dhi cha 8.2.25|धि च|धि च ८.२.२५|८.२.२५|८.२.२५ धि च
The स् is elided before an affix beginning with ध।<br><br>Terms: स् Elision

8.2.26|8.2.26 jhalo jhali|jhalo jhali|jhalo jhali 8.2.26|झलो झलि|झलो झलि ८.२.२६|८.२.२६|८.२.२६ झलो झलि
The स् is elided when it is preceded by a झल् consonant (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) and is followed by an affix beginning with a झल् consonant.<br><br>Terms: स् Elision

8.2.27|8.2.27 hrasvaadangaat‌|hrasvaadangaat‌|hrasvaadangaat‌ 8.2.27|ह्रस्वादङ्गात्‌|ह्रस्वादङ्गात्‌ ८.२.२७|८.२.२७|८.२.२७ ह्रस्वादङ्गात्‌
The स् is elided before an affix beginning with झल् consonant (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) when it is preceded by a अङ्ग (stem) ending in a short vowel.<br><br>Terms: स् Elision

8.2.28|8.2.28 iTa iiTi|iTa iiTi|iTa iiTi 8.2.28|इट ईटि|इट ईटि ८.२.२८|८.२.२८|८.२.२८ इट ईटि
The स् is elided after the augment इट् if after this स् the augment ईट् follows.<br><br>Terms: स् Elision

8.2.29|8.2.29 skoH saMyogaadyorante cha|skoH saMyogaadyorante cha|skoH saMyogaadyorante cha 8.2.29|स्कोः संयोगाद्योरन्ते च|स्कोः संयोगाद्योरन्ते च ८.२.२९|८.२.२९|८.२.२९ स्कोः संयोगाद्योरन्ते च
The स् or क् , when initial in a conjunct consonant, are elided before a झल् (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) affix and at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: Guttural

8.2.30|8.2.30 choH kuH|choH kuH|choH kuH 8.2.30|चोः कुः|चोः कुः ८.२.३०|८.२.३०|८.२.३० चोः कुः
A Guttural is substituted for a palatal before a झल् (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) affix or at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: Guttural

8.2.31|8.2.31 ho DhaH|ho DhaH|ho DhaH 8.2.31|हो ढः|हो ढः ८.२.३१|८.२.३१|८.२.३१ हो ढः
ढ is substituted for ह before a झल् (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) letter and at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: ह changed to ढ

8.2.32|8.2.32 daaderdhaatorghaH|daaderdhaatorghaH|daaderdhaatorghaH 8.2.32|दादेर्धातोर्घः|दादेर्धातोर्घः ८.२.३२|८.२.३२|८.२.३२ दादेर्धातोर्घः
Of a root beginning with द , the ध is substituted for ह before a झल् (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) letter or at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: ह changed to ध

8.2.33|8.2.33 vaa druhamuhaShNuhaShNihaam|vaa druhamuhaShNuhaShNihaam|vaa druhamuhaShNuhaShNihaam 8.2.33|वा द्रुहमुहष्णुहष्णिहाम्|वा द्रुहमुहष्णुहष्णिहाम् ८.२.३३|८.२.३३|८.२.३३ वा द्रुहमुहष्णुहष्णिहाम्
The ह of 1. द्रुह् 2. मुह् 3.ष्णुह् and 4. ष्णिह् is optionally changed to ध before a झल् (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) letter or at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: ह changed to ध

8.2.34|8.2.34 naho dhaH|naho dhaH|naho dhaH 8.2.34|नहो धः|नहो धः ८.२.३४|८.२.३४|८.२.३४ नहो धः
The ह of नह् is changed to ध before a before a झल् (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) letter or at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: ह changed to ध

8.2.35|8.2.35 aahasthaH|aahasthaH|aahasthaH 8.2.35|आहस्थः|आहस्थः ८.२.३५|८.२.३५|८.२.३५ आहस्थः
For the ह of the root आह् there is substituted थ before a झल् (all consonant except semi-vowels and nasals) letter.<br><br>Terms: ह changed to थ

8.2.36|8.2.36 vrashchabhrasjasRjamRjayajaraajabhraajachChashaaM ShaH|vrashchabhrasjasRjamRjayajaraajabhraajachChashaaM ShaH|vrashchabhrasjasRjamRjayajaraajabhraajachChashaaM ShaH 8.2.36|व्रश्चभ्रस्जसृजमृजयजराजभ्राजच्छशां षः|व्रश्चभ्रस्जसृजमृजयजराजभ्राजच्छशां षः ८.२.३६|८.२.३६|८.२.३६ व्रश्चभ्रस्जसृजमृजयजराजभ्राजच्छशां षः
For the final consonants of 1. व्रश्च् 2. भ्रस्ज् 3. सृज् 4. मृज् 5. यज् 6. राज् and 7. भ्राज् and for the final छ and श , there is substituted ष् or at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

8.2.37|8.2.37 ekaacho basho bhaSh jhaShantasya sdhvoH|ekaacho basho bhaSh jhaShantasya sdhvoH|ekaacho basho bhaSh jhaShantasya sdhvoH 8.2.37|एकाचो बशो भष् झषन्तस्य स्ध्वोः|एकाचो बशो भष् झषन्तस्य स्ध्वोः ८.२.३७|८.२.३७|८.२.३७ एकाचो बशो भष् झषन्तस्य स्ध्वोः
For the letters 1. ब 2. ग 3. ड or 4. द in the beginning of a mono-syllable and belonging to a root, and which ends in 1. झ 2. भ 3. घ 4. ढ or 5. ध there is substituted 1. भ 2. घ 3. ढ or 4. ध respectively before स् or ध्व or at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

8.2.38|8.2.38 dadhastathoshcha|dadhastathoshcha|dadhastathoshcha 8.2.38|दधस्तथोश्च|दधस्तथोश्च ८.२.३८|८.२.३८|८.२.३८ दधस्तथोश्च
For the द of दध (the reduplicated form of धा) is substituted ध before the affixes beginning with त, थ, स and before ध्वम्।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

8.2.39|8.2.39 jhalaaM jasho.ante|jhalaaM jasho.ante|jhalaaM jasho.ante 8.2.39|झलां जशोऽन्ते|झलां जशोऽन्ते ८.२.३९|८.२.३९|८.२.३९ झलां जशोऽन्ते
A corresponding ज, ब, ग, ड or द is substituted for all consonants (with the exception of semi-vowels and nasals) at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: हल् सन्धिः

8.2.40|8.2.40 jhaShastathordho.adhaH|jhaShastathordho.adhaH|jhaShastathordho.adhaH 8.2.40|झषस्तथोर्धोऽधः|झषस्तथोर्धोऽधः ८.२.४०|८.२.४०|८.२.४० झषस्तथोर्धोऽधः
ध is substituted for त or थ coming after झष् (झ, भ, घ, ढ, ध) but not after the root धा (दध).<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

8.2.41|8.2.41 ShaDhoH kaH si|ShaDhoH kaH si|ShaDhoH kaH si 8.2.41|षढोः कः सि|षढोः कः सि ८.२.४१|८.२.४१|८.२.४१ षढोः कः सि
क is substituted for ष or ढ before स।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

8.2.42|8.2.42 radaabhyaaM niShThaato naH puurvasya cha daH|radaabhyaaM niShThaato naH puurvasya cha daH|radaabhyaaM niShThaato naH puurvasya cha daH 8.2.42|रदाभ्यां निष्ठातो नः पूर्वस्य च दः|रदाभ्यां निष्ठातो नः पूर्वस्य च दः ८.२.४२|८.२.४२|८.२.४२ रदाभ्यां निष्ठातो नः पूर्वस्य च दः
After र and द for the त of the Participial suffix त and तवत् there is substituted न and the same substitution takes place also for the preceding द।<br><br>Terms: Some substitution

8.2.43|8.2.43 saMyogaaderaato dhaatoryaNvataH|saMyogaaderaato dhaatoryaNvataH|saMyogaaderaato dhaatoryaNvataH 8.2.43|संयोगादेरातो धातोर्यण्वतः|संयोगादेरातो धातोर्यण्वतः ८.२.४३|८.२.४३|८.२.४३ संयोगादेरातो धातोर्यण्वतः
For the त of the निष्ठा there is substituted न after a root ending in आ and commencing with a conjunct consonant, if the latter contains a semi-vowel.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.44|8.2.44 lvaadibhyaH|lvaadibhyaH|lvaadibhyaH 8.2.44|ल्वादिभ्यः|ल्वादिभ्यः ८.२.४४|८.२.४४|८.२.४४ ल्वादिभ्यः
For the त of the निष्ठा there is substituted न after the roots लू and those that follow it.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.45|8.2.45 oditashcha|oditashcha|oditashcha 8.2.45|ओदितश्च|ओदितश्च ८.२.४५|८.२.४५|८.२.४५ ओदितश्च
For the त of the निष्ठा there is substituted न after a root which has an indicatory ओ in the धातुपाठ।<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.46|8.2.46 xiyo diirghaat‌|xiyo diirghaat‌|xiyo diirghaat‌ 8.2.46|क्षियो दीर्घात्‌|क्षियो दीर्घात्‌ ८.२.४६|८.२.४६|८.२.४६ क्षियो दीर्घात्‌
For the त of the निष्ठा there is substituted न after क्षि when the root-vowel is lengthened.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.47|8.2.47 shyo.asparshe|shyo.asparshe|shyo.asparshe 8.2.47|श्योऽस्पर्शे|श्योऽस्पर्शे ८.२.४७|८.२.४७|८.२.४७ श्योऽस्पर्शे
The निष्ठा त is changed to न after श्यै but not when the participle denotes 'cold'.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.48|8.2.48 anco.anapaadaane|anco.anapaadaane|anco.anapaadaane 8.2.48|अञ्चोऽनपादाने|अञ्चोऽनपादाने ८.२.४८|८.२.४८|८.२.४८ अञ्चोऽनपादाने
The निष्ठा त is changed to न after अञ्च् but not when it is in connection with an Ablative -5th case.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.49|8.2.49 divo.avijigiiShaayaam|divo.avijigiiShaayaam|divo.avijigiiShaayaam 8.2.49|दिवोऽविजिगीषायाम्|दिवोऽविजिगीषायाम् ८.२.४९|८.२.४९|८.२.४९ दिवोऽविजिगीषायाम्
The निष्ठा त is changed to न after दिव् when the sense is not that of 'play'.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.50|8.2.50 nirvaaNo.avaate|nirvaaNo.avaate|nirvaaNo.avaate 8.2.50|निर्वाणोऽवाते|निर्वाणोऽवाते ८.२.५०|८.२.५०|८.२.५० निर्वाणोऽवाते
The word निर्वाण is irregularly formed by changing the निष्ठा त is changed to न when the sense is not that of 'wind'.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.51|8.2.51 shuShaH kaH|shuShaH kaH|shuShaH kaH 8.2.51|शुषः कः|शुषः कः ८.२.५१|८.२.५१|८.२.५१ शुषः कः
क is substituted for the निष्ठा त after the root शुष्।<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.52|8.2.52 pacho vaH|pacho vaH|pacho vaH 8.2.52|पचो वः|पचो वः ८.२.५२|८.२.५२|८.२.५२ पचो वः
व is substituted for the निष्ठा त after the root पच् 'to cook' ।<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.53|8.2.53 xaayo maH|xaayo maH|xaayo maH 8.2.53|क्षायो मः|क्षायो मः ८.२.५३|८.२.५३|८.२.५३ क्षायो मः
म is substituted for the निष्ठा त after the root क्षै।<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.54|8.2.54 prastyo.anyatarasyaam|prastyo.anyatarasyaam|prastyo.anyatarasyaam 8.2.54|प्रस्त्योऽन्यतरस्याम्|प्रस्त्योऽन्यतरस्याम् ८.२.५४|८.२.५४|८.२.५४ प्रस्त्योऽन्यतरस्याम्
म is optionally substituted for the निष्ठा त after the root स्तयै preceded by प्र।<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.55|8.2.55 anupasargaat‌ phullaxiibakRshollaaghaaH|anupasargaat‌ phullaxiibakRshollaaghaaH|anupasargaat‌ phullaxiibakRshollaaghaaH 8.2.55|अनुपसर्गात्‌ फुल्लक्षीबकृशोल्लाघाः|अनुपसर्गात्‌ फुल्लक्षीबकृशोल्लाघाः ८.२.५५|८.२.५५|८.२.५५ अनुपसर्गात्‌ फुल्लक्षीबकृशोल्लाघाः
The irregular participles 1. फुल्ल 2. क्षीब 3. कृश and 4. उल्लाघ are formed then only, when no preposition precedes them.<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.56|8.2.56 nudavidondatraaghraahriibhyo.anyatarasyaam|nudavidondatraaghraahriibhyo.anyatarasyaam|nudavidondatraaghraahriibhyo.anyatarasyaam 8.2.56|नुदविदोन्दत्राघ्राह्रीभ्योऽन्यतरस्याम्|नुदविदोन्दत्राघ्राह्रीभ्योऽन्यतरस्याम् ८.२.५६|८.२.५६|८.२.५६ नुदविदोन्दत्राघ्राह्रीभ्योऽन्यतरस्याम्
The निष्ठा त is optionally changed to न after 1. नुद 2. विद 3. उन्द 4. त्रा 5. घ्रा and 6. ह्री।<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.57|8.2.57 na dhyaakhyaapRRmuurChimadaam|na dhyaakhyaapRRmuurChimadaam|na dhyaakhyaapRRmuurChimadaam 8.2.57|न ध्याख्यापॄमूर्छिमदाम्|न ध्याख्यापॄमूर्छिमदाम् ८.२.५७|८.२.५७|८.२.५७ न ध्याख्यापॄमूर्छिमदाम्
The निष्ठा त is not changed to न after 1. ध्या 2. ख्या 3. पॄ 4. मूर्छि and 5. मद।<br><br>Terms: निष्ठा changes

8.2.58|8.2.58 vitto bhogapratyayayoH|vitto bhogapratyayayoH|vitto bhogapratyayayoH 8.2.58|वित्तो भोगप्रत्यययोः|वित्तो भोगप्रत्यययोः ८.२.५८|८.२.५८|८.२.५८ वित्तो भोगप्रत्यययोः
The irregularly formed participle वित्त denotes 'possessions' and 'renowned'.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

8.2.59|8.2.59 bhittaM shakalam|bhittaM shakalam|bhittaM shakalam 8.2.59|भित्तं शकलम्|भित्तं शकलम् ८.२.५९|८.२.५९|८.२.५९ भित्तं शकलम्
The word भित्त is irregularly formed in the sense of 'a fragment, a portion'.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

8.2.60|8.2.60 RNamaadhamarNye|RNamaadhamarNye|RNamaadhamarNye 8.2.60|ऋणमाधमर्ण्ये|ऋणमाधमर्ण्ये ८.२.६०|८.२.६०|८.२.६० ऋणमाधमर्ण्ये
The word ऋण is irregularly formed in the sense of 'debt.<br><br>Terms: Irregular

8.2.61|8.2.61 nasattaniShattaanuttapratuurtasuurtaguurtaani Chandasi|nasattaniShattaanuttapratuurtasuurtaguurtaani Chandasi|nasattaniShattaanuttapratuurtasuurtaguurtaani Chandasi 8.2.61|नसत्तनिषत्तानुत्तप्रतूर्तसूर्तगूर्तानि छन्दसि|नसत्तनिषत्तानुत्तप्रतूर्तसूर्तगूर्तानि छन्दसि ८.२.६१|८.२.६१|८.२.६१ नसत्तनिषत्तानुत्तप्रतूर्तसूर्तगूर्तानि छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas) we have the following irregular participles - 1. नसत्त 2. निषत्त 3. अनुत्त 4. प्रतूर्त 5. सूर्त्त and 6. गूर्त्त।<br><br>Terms: छन्दस्

8.2.62|8.2.62 kvinpratyayasya kuH|kvinpratyayasya kuH|kvinpratyayasya kuH 8.2.62|क्विन्प्रत्ययस्य कुः|क्विन्प्रत्ययस्य कुः ८.२.६२|८.२.६२|८.२.६२ क्विन्प्रत्ययस्य कुः
A अङ्ग (stem) formed with the affix क्विन् under स्पृशोऽनुदके क्विन् ३.२.५८ etc. substitutes, at the end of a word, a guttural for the final consonant.<br><br>Terms: Guttural

8.2.63|8.2.63 nashervaa|nashervaa|nashervaa 8.2.63|नशेर्वा|नशेर्वा ८.२.६३|८.२.६३|८.२.६३ नशेर्वा
The final नश् at the end of a word is optionally changed to guttural.<br><br>Terms: Final Changes

8.2.64|8.2.64 mo no dhaatoH|mo no dhaatoH|mo no dhaatoH 8.2.64|मो नो धातोः|मो नो धातोः ८.२.६४|८.२.६४|८.२.६४ मो नो धातोः
न is substituted, at the end of a word, for the final म of a root.<br><br>Terms: Final Changes

8.2.65|8.2.65 mvoshcha|mvoshcha|mvoshcha 8.2.65|म्वोश्च|म्वोश्च ८.२.६५|८.२.६५|८.२.६५ म्वोश्च
न is substituted for the म of a root before the affixes beginning with म and व।<br><br>Terms: Final Changes

8.2.66|8.2.66 sasajuSho ruँH|sasajuSho ruँH|sasajuSho ruँH 8.2.66|ससजुषो रुँः|ससजुषो रुँः ८.२.६६|८.२.६६|८.२.६६ ससजुषो रुँः
For the final स् and for the ष् of ससजुष् is substituted रु , at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: रु substitution

8.2.67|8.2.67 avayaaHshvetavaaHpuroDaashcha|avayaaHshvetavaaHpuroDaashcha|avayaaHshvetavaaHpuroDaashcha 8.2.67|अवयाःश्वेतवाःपुरोडाश्च|अवयाःश्वेतवाःपुरोडाश्च ८.२.६७|८.२.६७|८.२.६७ अवयाःश्वेतवाःपुरोडाश्च
The same substitution takes place for the final Nominatives of 1. अवयाः 2. श्वेतवाः and 3. पुरोडाः।<br><br>Terms: रु substitution

8.2.68|8.2.68 ahan|ahan|ahan 8.2.68|अहन्|अहन् ८.२.६८|८.२.६८|८.२.६८ अहन्
रु is also substituted for the न् of अहन् at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: रु substitution

8.2.69|8.2.69 ro.asupi|ro.asupi|ro.asupi 8.2.69|रोऽसुपि|रोऽसुपि ८.२.६९|८.२.६९|८.२.६९ रोऽसुपि
When no case-ending follows (i.e. at the end of a word, in the narrower sense), र् is substituted for the न् of अहन्।<br><br>Terms: रु substitution

8.2.70|8.2.70 amnaruudharavarityubhayathaa Chandasi|amnaruudharavarityubhayathaa Chandasi|amnaruudharavarityubhayathaa Chandasi 8.2.70|अम्नरूधरवरित्युभयथा छन्दसि|अम्नरूधरवरित्युभयथा छन्दसि ८.२.७०|८.२.७०|८.२.७० अम्नरूधरवरित्युभयथा छन्दसि
In the छन्दस् (Vedas), both रु and र् are substituted for the final 1. अमनस् 2. ऊधस् and 3. अवस्।<br><br>Terms: Final Changes

8.2.71|8.2.71 bhuvashcha mahaavyaahRteH|bhuvashcha mahaavyaahRteH|bhuvashcha mahaavyaahRteH 8.2.71|भुवश्च महाव्याहृतेः|भुवश्च महाव्याहृतेः ८.२.७१|८.२.७१|८.२.७१ भुवश्च महाव्याहृतेः
In the छन्दस् (Vedas), both रु and र् may replace the final of the word भुवस् when used as a महाव्याहृति।<br><br>Terms: Final Changes

8.2.72|8.2.72 vasusraMsudhvaMsvanaDuhaaM daH|vasusraMsudhvaMsvanaDuhaaM daH|vasusraMsudhvaMsvanaDuhaaM daH 8.2.72|वसुस्रंसुध्वंस्वनडुहां दः|वसुस्रंसुध्वंस्वनडुहां दः ८.२.७२|८.२.७२|८.२.७२ वसुस्रंसुध्वंस्वनडुहां दः
द is substituted for the final स् of a word ending in the affix वस् and for the final of 1. स्रंस् 2. ध्वंस् and 3. अनडुह् at the end of a word (in the wider sense निपात एकाजनाङ् १.१.१४, उञः १.१.१७).<br><br>Terms: Final Changes

8.2.73|8.2.73 tipyanasteH|tipyanasteH|tipyanasteH 8.2.73|तिप्यनस्तेः|तिप्यनस्तेः ८.२.७३|८.२.७३|८.२.७३ तिप्यनस्तेः
द is substituted for the final स् of a root with the exception of अस् 'to be' , before the personal ending ति (त्) when it stands at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: स् change

8.2.74|8.2.74 sipi dhaato rurvaa|sipi dhaato rurvaa|sipi dhaato rurvaa 8.2.74|सिपि धातो रुर्वा|सिपि धातो रुर्वा ८.२.७४|८.२.७४|८.२.७४ सिपि धातो रुर्वा
 द् or रु may optionally be substituted for the स् of a root, , before the personal ending सि (स्) when such स् stands at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: स् change

8.2.75|8.2.75 dashcha|dashcha|dashcha 8.2.75|दश्च|दश्च ८.२.७५|८.२.७५|८.२.७५ दश्च
द् or रु may optionally be substituted for the द् of a root, , before the personal ending सि (स्) when such द् stands at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: स् change

8.2.76|8.2.76 rvorupadhaayaa diirgha ikaH|rvorupadhaayaa diirgha ikaH|rvorupadhaayaa diirgha ikaH 8.2.76|र्वोरुपधाया दीर्घ इकः|र्वोरुपधाया दीर्घ इकः ८.२.७६|८.२.७६|८.२.७६ र्वोरुपधाया दीर्घ इकः
A penultimate इ or उ is lengthened, when the र् or व् of a root can stand at the end of a word.<br><br>Terms: penultimate lengthening

8.2.77|8.2.77 hali cha|hali cha|hali cha 8.2.77|हलि च|हलि च ८.२.७७|८.२.७७|८.२.७७ हलि च
Of a root ending in र् or व् , the penultimate इ or उ is lengthened before a consonantal beginning affix.<br><br>Terms: penultimate lengthening

8.2.78|8.2.78 upadhaayaaM cha|upadhaayaaM cha|upadhaayaaM cha 8.2.78|उपधायां च|उपधायां च ८.२.७८|८.२.७८|८.२.७८ उपधायां च
The short इ or उ is lengthened, when the verb has र् or व् as its penultimate letter and is followed by a consonant.<br><br>Terms: penultimate lengthening

8.2.79|8.2.79 na bhakurChuraam|na bhakurChuraam|na bhakurChuraam 8.2.79|न भकुर्छुराम्|न भकुर्छुराम् ८.२.७९|८.२.७९|८.२.७९ न भकुर्छुराम्
The lengthening of a vowel does not take place under हलि च ८.२.७७ when the nominal अङ्ग (stem) ending in र् or व् is called भ (i.e. when a य् follows) and also not in कुर् and छुर्।<br><br>Terms: penultimate lengthening

8.2.80|8.2.80 adaso.aserdaadu do maH|adaso.aserdaadu do maH|adaso.aserdaadu do maH 8.2.80|अदसोऽसेर्दादु दो मः|अदसोऽसेर्दादु दो मः ८.२.८०|८.२.८०|८.२.८० अदसोऽसेर्दादु दो मः
When the सर्वनाम अदस् does not end in स् then there is substituted उ or ऊ for the vowel after द् , and म् for द्।<br><br>Terms: अदस् declension

8.2.81|8.2.81 eta iidbahuvachane|eta iidbahuvachane|eta iidbahuvachane 8.2.81|एत ईद्बहुवचने|एत ईद्बहुवचने ८.२.८१|८.२.८१|८.२.८१ एत ईद्बहुवचने
For the ए coming after the द् of अदस् , there is substituted ई , and द् is changed to म् when plurality is to be expressed.<br><br>Terms: अदस् declension

8.2.82|8.2.82 vaakyasya TeH pluta udaattaH|vaakyasya TeH pluta udaattaH|vaakyasya TeH pluta udaattaH 8.2.82|वाक्यस्य टेः प्लुत उदात्तः|वाक्यस्य टेः प्लुत उदात्तः ८.२.८२|८.२.८२|८.२.८२ वाक्यस्य टेः प्लुत उदात्तः
Up to the close of this chapter (पाद), is always to be supplied the words 'the last vowel of a sentence is प्लुत and has the acute'.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.83|8.2.83 pratyabhivaadeashuudre|pratyabhivaadeashuudre|pratyabhivaadeashuudre 8.2.83|प्रत्यभिवादेअशूद्रे|प्रत्यभिवादेअशूद्रे ८.२.८३|८.२.८३|८.२.८३ प्रत्यभिवादेअशूद्रे
In answer to a salutation, but not when it refers to शुद्र , the last vowel of a sentence becomes प्लुत and gets an acute accent (उदात्त).<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.84|8.2.84 duuraaddhuute cha|duuraaddhuute cha|duuraaddhuute cha 8.2.84|दूराद्धूते च|दूराद्धूते च ८.२.८४|८.२.८४|८.२.८४ दूराद्धूते च
The final vowel of a sentence becomes प्लुत and acutely accented (उदात्त) when used in calling a person from a distance.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.85|8.2.85 haiheprayoge haihayoH|haiheprayoge haihayoH|haiheprayoge haihayoH 8.2.85|हैहेप्रयोगे हैहयोः|हैहेप्रयोगे हैहयोः ८.२.८५|८.२.८५|८.२.८५ हैहेप्रयोगे हैहयोः
When the words है and हे are used in addressing a person from a distance, there the है and हे alone get the प्लुत and the accent.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.86|8.2.86 guroranRto.anantyasyaapyekaikasya praachaam|guroranRto.anantyasyaapyekaikasya praachaam|guroranRto.anantyasyaapyekaikasya praachaam 8.2.86|गुरोरनृतोऽनन्त्यस्याप्येकैकस्य प्राचाम्|गुरोरनृतोऽनन्त्यस्याप्येकैकस्य प्राचाम् ८.२.८६|८.२.८६|८.२.८६ गुरोरनृतोऽनन्त्यस्याप्येकैकस्य प्राचाम्
In the room of a prosodially long vowel (with the exception of ऋ) though it may not stand at the end, there is substituted a प्लुत for one at a time, under the above circumstances -- प्रत्यभिवादेशूद्रे ८.२.८३ & दूराद्धूते च ८.२.८४, in the opinion of Eastern Grammarians.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.87|8.2.87 omabhyaadaane|omabhyaadaane|omabhyaadaane 8.2.87|ओमभ्यादाने|ओमभ्यादाने ८.२.८७|८.२.८७|८.२.८७ ओमभ्यादाने
The vowel in ओम् is प्लुत in the beginning of a sacred text.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.88|8.2.88 ye yaJNakarmaNi|ye yaJNakarmaNi|ye yaJNakarmaNi 8.2.88|ये यज्ञकर्मणि|ये यज्ञकर्मणि ८.२.८८|८.२.८८|८.२.८८ ये यज्ञकर्मणि
The vowel of ये becomes प्लुत in a sacred text when it is used in a sacrificial work.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.89|8.2.89 praNavaShTeH|praNavaShTeH|praNavaShTeH 8.2.89|प्रणवष्टेः|प्रणवष्टेः ८.२.८९|८.२.८९|८.२.८९ प्रणवष्टेः
In a sacrificial work ओ3म् is substituted for the final vowel with the consonant, if any, that may follow it, in a sentence.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.90|8.2.90 yaajyaa.antaH|yaajyaa.antaH|yaajyaa.antaH 8.2.90|याज्याऽन्तः|याज्याऽन्तः ८.२.९०|८.२.९०|८.२.९० याज्याऽन्तः
The last vowel at the end of मन्त्र-s called याज्य , when used in sacrificial works is प्लुत and has the acute accent (उदात्त).<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.91|8.2.91 bruuhipresyashrauShaDvauShaDaavahaanaamaadeH|bruuhipresyashrauShaDvauShaDaavahaanaamaadeH|bruuhipresyashrauShaDvauShaDaavahaanaamaadeH 8.2.91|ब्रूहिप्रेस्यश्रौषड्वौषडावहानामादेः|ब्रूहिप्रेस्यश्रौषड्वौषडावहानामादेः ८.२.९१|८.२.९१|८.२.९१ ब्रूहिप्रेस्यश्रौषड्वौषडावहानामादेः
In a sacrificial work, the first syllable of 1. ब्रूहि 2. प्रेष्य 3. श्रौषट् and 4.आवह is प्लुत।<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.92|8.2.92 agniitpreShaNe parasya cha|agniitpreShaNe parasya cha|agniitpreShaNe parasya cha 8.2.92|अग्नीत्प्रेषणे परस्य च|अग्नीत्प्रेषणे परस्य च ८.२.९२|८.२.९२|८.२.९२ अग्नीत्प्रेषणे परस्य च
In an order given to अग्नीध्र priest, the first syllable as well as the succeeding syllable is प्लुत.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.93|8.2.93 vibhaaShaa pRShTaprativachane heH|vibhaaShaa pRShTaprativachane heH|vibhaaShaa pRShTaprativachane heH 8.2.93|विभाषा पृष्टप्रतिवचने हेः|विभाषा पृष्टप्रतिवचने हेः ८.२.९३|८.२.९३|८.२.९३ विभाषा पृष्टप्रतिवचने हेः
हि at the end of an answer to a question may optionally be प्लुत।<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.94|8.2.94 nigRhyaanuyoge cha|nigRhyaanuyoge cha|nigRhyaanuyoge cha 8.2.94|निगृह्यानुयोगे च|निगृह्यानुयोगे च ८.२.९४|८.२.९४|८.२.९४ निगृह्यानुयोगे च
The end syllable of that sentence is optionally प्लुत when it asserts something which has been refuted and is used by the victor by way of censure.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.95|8.2.95 aamreDitaM bhartsane|aamreDitaM bhartsane|aamreDitaM bhartsane 8.2.95|आम्रेडितं भर्त्सने|आम्रेडितं भर्त्सने ८.२.९५|८.२.९५|८.२.९५ आम्रेडितं भर्त्सने
The end syllable of an आम्रेडित Vocative Case is प्लुत when threat is expressed.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.96|8.2.96 angayuktaM tiNG aakaankSham|angayuktaM tiNG aakaankSham|angayuktaM tiNG aakaankSham 8.2.96|अङ्गयुक्तं तिङ् आकाङ्क्षम्|अङ्गयुक्तं तिङ् आकाङ्क्षम् ८.२.९६|८.२.९६|८.२.९६ अङ्गयुक्तं तिङ् आकाङ्क्षम्
The final syllable of a finite verb used as a threat becomes प्लुत when the word अङ्ग is joined with it and it demands another sentence to complete the conclusion.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.97|8.2.97 vichaaryamaaNaanaam|vichaaryamaaNaanaam|vichaaryamaaNaanaam 8.2.97|विचार्यमाणानाम्|विचार्यमाणानाम् ८.२.९७|८.२.९७|८.२.९७ विचार्यमाणानाम्
The end syllable of those sentences is प्लुत which denote acts of reflection (or balancing between two alternatives).<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.98|8.2.98 puurvaM tu bhaaShaayaam|puurvaM tu bhaaShaayaam|puurvaM tu bhaaShaayaam 8.2.98|पूर्वं तु भाषायाम्|पूर्वं तु भाषायाम् ८.२.९८|८.२.९८|८.२.९८ पूर्वं तु भाषायाम्
In the common speech, the end vowel of the first alternative is only प्लुत।<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.99|8.2.99 pratishravaNe cha|pratishravaNe cha|pratishravaNe cha 8.2.99|प्रतिश्रवणे च|प्रतिश्रवणे च ८.२.९९|८.२.९९|८.२.९९ प्रतिश्रवणे च
The end syllable of the sentence which expresses assent or promise or listening to, is प्लुत।<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.100|8.2.100 anudaattaM prashnaantaabhipuujitayoH|anudaattaM prashnaantaabhipuujitayoH|anudaattaM prashnaantaabhipuujitayoH 8.2.100|अनुदात्तं प्रश्नान्ताभिपूजितयोः|अनुदात्तं प्रश्नान्ताभिपूजितयोः ८.२.१००|८.२.१००|८.२.१०० अनुदात्तं प्रश्नान्ताभिपूजितयोः
The end vowel at the end of a question or of a praise is प्लुत, but unaccented.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.101|8.2.101 chiditi chopamaa.arthe prayujyamaane|chiditi chopamaa.arthe prayujyamaane|chiditi chopamaa.arthe prayujyamaane 8.2.101|चिदिति चोपमाऽर्थे प्रयुज्यमाने|चिदिति चोपमाऽर्थे प्रयुज्यमाने ८.२.१०१|८.२.१०१|८.२.१०१ चिदिति चोपमाऽर्थे प्रयुज्यमाने
The end vowel at the end of a sentence becomes अनुदात्त and प्लुत when the particle चित् is used, denoting comparison.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.102|8.2.102 uparisvidaasiiditi cha|uparisvidaasiiditi cha|uparisvidaasiiditi cha 8.2.102|उपरिस्विदासीदिति च|उपरिस्विदासीदिति च ८.२.१०२|८.२.१०२|८.२.१०२ उपरिस्विदासीदिति च
In 1. उपरि 2. स्विद् and 3. आसीद् the end vowel is अनुदात्त and प्लुत।<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.103|8.2.103 svaritamaamreDite.asuuyaasammatikopakutsaneShu|svaritamaamreDite.asuuyaasammatikopakutsaneShu|svaritamaamreDite.asuuyaasammatikopakutsaneShu 8.2.103|स्वरितमाम्रेडितेऽसूयासम्मतिकोपकुत्सनेषु|स्वरितमाम्रेडितेऽसूयासम्मतिकोपकुत्सनेषु ८.२.१०३|८.२.१०३|८.२.१०३ स्वरितमाम्रेडितेऽसूयासम्मतिकोपकुत्सनेषु
Of the two Vocatives of the same form standing at the beginning of a sentence, the end vowel of the first becomes प्लुत and स्वरित when envy, praise, anger or blame is expressed.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.104|8.2.104 xiyaa.a.ashiiHpraiSheShu tiNG aakaankSham|xiyaa.a.ashiiHpraiSheShu tiNG aakaankSham|xiyaa.a.ashiiHpraiSheShu tiNG aakaankSham 8.2.104|क्षियाऽऽशीःप्रैषेषु तिङ् आकाङ्क्षम्|क्षियाऽऽशीःप्रैषेषु तिङ् आकाङ्क्षम् ८.२.१०४|८.२.१०४|८.२.१०४ क्षियाऽऽशीःप्रैषेषु तिङ् आकाङ्क्षम्
When an error against polite usage is censured or when a benediction or a bidding is intended, the end syllable of a finite verb becomes प्लुत and स्वरित , if this requires another sentence to complete the sense.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.105|8.2.105 anantyasyaapi prashnaakhyaanayoH|anantyasyaapi prashnaakhyaanayoH|anantyasyaapi prashnaakhyaanayoH 8.2.105|अनन्त्यस्यापि प्रश्नाख्यानयोः|अनन्त्यस्यापि प्रश्नाख्यानयोः ८.२.१०५|८.२.१०५|८.२.१०५ अनन्त्यस्यापि प्रश्नाख्यानयोः
In a question or narration, the end vowel of a word, though not final in a sentence, becomes प्लुत and स्वरित , as well as the word which is final in a sentence.<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.106|8.2.106 plutaavaicha idutau|plutaavaicha idutau|plutaavaicha idutau 8.2.106|प्लुतावैच इदुतौ|प्लुतावैच इदुतौ ८.२.१०६|८.२.१०६|८.२.१०६ प्लुतावैच इदुतौ
In forming the प्लुत of the diphthongs s ए and ओ , their last element इ and उ get the प्लुत।<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.107|8.2.107 echo.apragRhyasyaaduuraaddhuute puurvasyaardhasyaaduttarasyedutau|echo.apragRhyasyaaduuraaddhuute puurvasyaardhasyaaduttarasyedutau|echo.apragRhyasyaaduuraaddhuute puurvasyaardhasyaaduttarasyedutau 8.2.107|एचोऽप्रगृह्यस्यादूराद्धूते पूर्वस्यार्धस्यादुत्तरस्येदुतौ|एचोऽप्रगृह्यस्यादूराद्धूते पूर्वस्यार्धस्यादुत्तरस्येदुतौ ८.२.१०७|८.२.१०७|८.२.१०७ एचोऽप्रगृह्यस्यादूराद्धूते पूर्वस्यार्धस्यादुत्तरस्येदुतौ
In the diphthongs which are not प्रगृह्य -- ईदूदेद्द्विवचनं प्रगृह्यम् १.१.११ etc. and which become प्लुत under the circumstances mentioned in प्रत्यभिवादेशूद्रे ८.२.८३ etc., but not when that circumstance is a call from a distance -- दूराद्धूते च ८.२.८४; for the first half, there is substituted the prolated आ and for the second portion इ or उ।<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.2.108|8.2.108 tayoryvaavachi saMhitaayaam|tayoryvaavachi saMhitaayaam|tayoryvaavachi saMhitaayaam 8.2.108|तयोर्य्वावचि संहितायाम्|तयोर्य्वावचि संहितायाम् ८.२.१०८|८.२.१०८|८.२.१०८ तयोर्य्वावचि संहितायाम्
For these vowels इ or उ are substituted य् and व् when a vowel follows them in a संहिता (in an unbroken flow of speech).<br><br>Terms: प्लुत

8.3.1|8.3.1 matuvaso ru sambuddhau Chandasi|matuvaso ru sambuddhau Chandasi|matuvaso ru sambuddhau Chandasi 8.3.1|मतुवसो रु सम्बुद्धौ छन्दसि|मतुवसो रु सम्बुद्धौ छन्दसि ८.३.१|८.३.१|८.३.१ मतुवसो रु सम्बुद्धौ छन्दसि
For the final affixes मत् and वस् there is substituted रु in the Vocative Case singular, in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.2|8.3.2 atraanunaasikaH puurvasya tu vaa|atraanunaasikaH puurvasya tu vaa|atraanunaasikaH puurvasya tu vaa 8.3.2|अत्रानुनासिकः पूर्वस्य तु वा|अत्रानुनासिकः पूर्वस्य तु वा ८.३.२|८.३.२|८.३.२ अत्रानुनासिकः पूर्वस्य तु वा
In the following sūtras up to कानाम्रेडिते ८.३.१२, this always to be supplied - 'But here a nasal vowel after which रु has been ordained'.<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.3|8.3.3 aato.aTi nityam|aato.aTi nityam|aato.aTi nityam 8.3.3|आतोऽटि नित्यम्|आतोऽटि नित्यम् ८.३.३|८.३.३|८.३.३ आतोऽटि नित्यम्
A nasal vowel is ALWAYS substituted for आ before रु when it is followed by a letter of अट् प्रत्यहार (i.e. when it is followed by a vowel or ह , य , व or र).<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.4|8.3.4 anunaasikaat‌ paro.anusvaaraH|anunaasikaat‌ paro.anusvaaraH|anunaasikaat‌ paro.anusvaaraH 8.3.4|अनुनासिकात्‌ परोऽनुस्वारः|अनुनासिकात्‌ परोऽनुस्वारः ८.३.४|८.३.४|८.३.४ अनुनासिकात्‌ परोऽनुस्वारः
After what precedes रु , if we omit to substitute the nasal, then अनुस्वार shall be the augment.<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.5|8.3.5 samaH suTi|samaH suTi|samaH suTi 8.3.5|समः सुटि|समः सुटि ८.३.५|८.३.५|८.३.५ समः सुटि
रु is substituted for the म् of स्म् (and thereby अँ or अं is substituted for अ) when the augment स् follows in a संहिता ।<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.6|8.3.6 pumaH khayyampare|pumaH khayyampare|pumaH khayyampare 8.3.6|पुमः खय्यम्परे|पुमः खय्यम्परे ८.३.६|८.३.६|८.३.६ पुमः खय्यम्परे
रु is substituted for the म् of पुम् (whereby the उ is changed to उँ or उं) before a surd mute (खय्) which is followed by a vowel, semi-vowel or a nasal (अम् प्रत्यहार).<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.7|8.3.7 nashChavyaprashaan|nashChavyaprashaan|nashChavyaprashaan 8.3.7|नश्छव्यप्रशान्|नश्छव्यप्रशान् ८.३.७|८.३.७|८.३.७ नश्छव्यप्रशान्
रु is substituted for the final न् of a word, with the exception of न् of प्रशान् before a छव् letter (छ ठ थ च ट त) which is followed by an अम् letter (vowel, semi-vowel and nasal).<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.8|8.3.8 ubhayatharxu|ubhayatharxu|ubhayatharxu 8.3.8|उभयथर्क्षु|उभयथर्क्षु ८.३.८|८.३.८|८.३.८ उभयथर्क्षु
In both ways in the ऋग् verses.<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.9|8.3.9 diirghaadaTi samaanapade|diirghaadaTi samaanapade|diirghaadaTi samaanapade 8.3.9|दीर्घादटि समानपदे|दीर्घादटि समानपदे ८.३.९|८.३.९|८.३.९ दीर्घादटि समानपदे
रु is optionally substituted for that final न् of a word which is preceded by a long vowel and is followed by a letter of the अट् प्रत्यहार (vowel or semi-vowel with the exception of ल्) when these (न् and अट्) come in contact with each other in the same stanza of the ऋग्वेद।<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.10|8.3.10 nRRn pe|nRRn pe|nRRn pe 8.3.10|नॄन् पे|नॄन् पे ८.३.१०|८.३.१०|८.३.१० नॄन् पे
रु is optionally substituted for the न् of नॄन् before प्।<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.11|8.3.11 svatavaan paayau|svatavaan paayau|svatavaan paayau 8.3.11|स्वतवान् पायौ|स्वतवान् पायौ ८.३.११|८.३.११|८.३.११ स्वतवान् पायौ
रु is substituted for the न् of स्वतवान् before पायु।<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.12|8.3.12 kaanaamreDite|kaanaamreDite|kaanaamreDite 8.3.12|कानाम्रेडिते|कानाम्रेडिते ८.३.१२|८.३.१२|८.३.१२ कानाम्रेडिते
रु is substituted for the न् of कान् when it is followed by another कान् which is an अम्रेडित (repeated).<br><br>Terms: Nasal रु

8.3.13|8.3.13 Dho Dhe lopaH|Dho Dhe lopaH|Dho Dhe lopaH 8.3.13|ढो ढे लोपः|ढो ढे लोपः ८.३.१३|८.३.१३|८.३.१३ ढो ढे लोपः
There is elision of ढ् when ढ् follows.<br><br>Terms: ढ् elision

8.3.14|8.3.14 ro ri|ro ri|ro ri 8.3.14|रो रि|रो रि ८.३.१४|८.३.१४|८.३.१४ रो रि
There is elision of र् when र् follows.<br><br>Terms: र् elision

8.3.15|8.3.15 kharavasaanayorvisarjaniiyaH|kharavasaanayorvisarjaniiyaH|kharavasaanayorvisarjaniiyaH 8.3.15|खरवसानयोर्विसर्जनीयः|खरवसानयोर्विसर्जनीयः ८.३.१५|८.३.१५|८.३.१५ खरवसानयोर्विसर्जनीयः
The विसर्जनीय is substituted for र् before a खर् consonant or when there is a Pause.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग

8.3.16|8.3.16 roH supi|roH supi|roH supi 8.3.16|रोः सुपि|रोः सुपि ८.३.१६|८.३.१६|८.३.१६ रोः सुपि
The विसर्जनीय is substituted for रु called र (and not any other र) before the Locative -7th case plural case-affix सु।<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग

8.3.17|8.3.17 bhobhagoaghoapuurvasya yo.ashi|bhobhagoaghoapuurvasya yo.ashi|bhobhagoaghoapuurvasya yo.ashi 8.3.17|भोभगोअघोअपूर्वस्य योऽशि|भोभगोअघोअपूर्वस्य योऽशि ८.३.१७|८.३.१७|८.३.१७ भोभगोअघोअपूर्वस्य योऽशि
य् is substituted for the रु called र (and not any other र) when it is preceded by 1. भो 2. भगो 3. अघो 4. अ or 5. आ before an अश् letter (vowels and soft-consonants).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग

8.3.18|8.3.18 vyorlaghuprayatnataraH shaakaTaayanasya|vyorlaghuprayatnataraH shaakaTaayanasya|vyorlaghuprayatnataraH shaakaTaayanasya 8.3.18|व्योर्लघुप्रयत्नतरः शाकटायनस्य|व्योर्लघुप्रयत्नतरः शाकटायनस्य ८.३.१८|८.३.१८|८.३.१८ व्योर्लघुप्रयत्नतरः शाकटायनस्य
व् and य् (in भगोय् etc. and after अ or आ , at the end of a पद) are pronounced with a lighter articulation before an अश् letter (vowels and soft-consonants) according the opinion of शाकटायन।<br><br>Terms: व् and य् elision

8.3.19|8.3.19 lopaH shaakalyasya|lopaH shaakalyasya|lopaH shaakalyasya 8.3.19|लोपः शाकल्यस्य|लोपः शाकल्यस्य ८.३.१९|८.३.१९|८.३.१९ लोपः शाकल्यस्य
व् and य् preceded by अ or आ and the end of a पद are elided before an अश् letter (vowels and soft-consonants) according the opinion of शाकल्य।<br><br>Terms: व् and य् elision

8.3.20|8.3.20 oto gaargyasya|oto gaargyasya|oto gaargyasya 8.3.20|ओतो गार्ग्यस्य|ओतो गार्ग्यस्य ८.३.२०|८.३.२०|८.३.२० ओतो गार्ग्यस्य
य् preceded by ओ is elided before an अश् letter (vowels and soft-consonants) according the opinion of गार्ग्य ।<br><br>Terms: व् and य् elision

8.3.21|8.3.21 uNJi cha pade|uNJi cha pade|uNJi cha pade 8.3.21|उञि च पदे|उञि च पदे ८.३.२१|८.३.२१|८.३.२१ उञि च पदे
व् and य् (preceded by अ or आ and the end of a पद) and followed by उ , when it is a word, are elided necessarily.<br><br>Terms: व् and य् elision

8.3.22|8.3.22 hali sarveShaam|hali sarveShaam|hali sarveShaam 8.3.22|हलि सर्वेषाम्|हलि सर्वेषाम् ८.३.२२|८.३.२२|८.३.२२ हलि सर्वेषाम्
(The य् when preceded by 1. भो 2. भगो 3. अघो 4. अ or 5. आ , is elided) before a consonant according to the opinion of all आचार्रचा-s.<br><br>Terms: व् and य् elision

8.3.23|8.3.23 mo.anusvaaraH|mo.anusvaaraH|mo.anusvaaraH 8.3.23|मोऽनुस्वारः|मोऽनुस्वारः ८.३.२३|८.३.२३|८.३.२३ मोऽनुस्वारः
The अनुस्वार is substituted for म् at the end of a word, before a consonant.<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.24|8.3.24 nashchaapadaantasya jhali|nashchaapadaantasya jhali|nashchaapadaantasya jhali 8.3.24|नश्चापदान्तस्य झलि|नश्चापदान्तस्य झलि ८.३.२४|८.३.२४|८.३.२४ नश्चापदान्तस्य झलि
The अनुस्वार is substituted for न् and not म् final in a word, before all consonants, with the exception<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.25|8.3.25 mo raaji samaH kvau|mo raaji samaH kvau|mo raaji samaH kvau 8.3.25|मो राजि समः क्वौ|मो राजि समः क्वौ ८.३.२५|८.३.२५|८.३.२५ मो राजि समः क्वौ
म् is substituted for म् of स्म् before the word राज् ending with the affix क्विप्।<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.26|8.3.26 he mapare vaa|he mapare vaa|he mapare vaa 8.3.26|हे मपरे वा|हे मपरे वा ८.३.२६|८.३.२६|८.३.२६ हे मपरे वा
म् is optionally substituted for म् before ह which itself is followed by म्।<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.27|8.3.27 napare naH|napare naH|napare naH 8.3.27|नपरे नः|नपरे नः ८.३.२७|८.३.२७|८.३.२७ नपरे नः
न् is optionally substituted for म् when it is followed by ह which has a न after it.<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.28|8.3.28 NGNoH kukTuk shari|NGNoH kukTuk shari|NGNoH kukTuk shari 8.3.28|ङ्णोः कुक्टुक् शरि|ङ्णोः कुक्टुक् शरि ८.३.२८|८.३.२८|८.३.२८ ङ्णोः कुक्टुक् शरि
The augment क् is added to a final ङ् and the augment ट् to a final ण् before a sibilant, optionally.<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.29|8.3.29 DaH si dhuT|DaH si dhuT|DaH si dhuT 8.3.29|डः सि धुट्|डः सि धुट् ८.३.२९|८.३.२९|८.३.२९ डः सि धुट्
After a word ending in ड् there may optionally be added the augment ध् to a word beginning with स्।<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.30|8.3.30 nashcha|nashcha|nashcha 8.3.30|नश्च|नश्च ८.३.३०|८.३.३०|८.३.३० नश्च
After a word ending in न् , धुट् is optionally the augment to a word beginning with स्।<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.31|8.3.31 shi tuk|shi tuk|shi tuk 8.3.31|शि तुक्|शि तुक् ८.३.३१|८.३.३१|८.३.३१ शि तुक्
The augment त् may optionally be added to a word ending in न् , when a word beginning with श् follows.<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.32|8.3.32 NGamo hrasvaadachi NGamuNnityam|NGamo hrasvaadachi NGamuNnityam|NGamo hrasvaadachi NGamuNnityam 8.3.32|ङमो ह्रस्वादचि ङमुण्नित्यम्|ङमो ह्रस्वादचि ङमुण्नित्यम् ८.३.३२|८.३.३२|८.३.३२ ङमो ह्रस्वादचि ङमुण्नित्यम्
After a word ending in ङ् ण् or न् which is preceded by a light vowel, the same consonant ङ् ण् or न् is added invariably at the beginning of the next word, which commences with a vowel.<br><br>Terms: Nasal

8.3.33|8.3.33 maya uNJo vo vaa|maya uNJo vo vaa|maya uNJo vo vaa 8.3.33|मय उञो वो वा|मय उञो वो वा ८.३.३३|८.३.३३|८.३.३३ मय उञो वो वा
व् is optionally the substitute of the Particle उ when it is preceded by मय् consonant (all consonants with the exception of the semi-vowels, sibilants, ह and ञ) and is followed by a vowel.<br><br>Terms: व् substitution

8.3.34|8.3.34 visarjaniiyasya saH|visarjaniiyasya saH|visarjaniiyasya saH 8.3.34|विसर्जनीयस्य सः|विसर्जनीयस्य सः ८.३.३४|८.३.३४|८.३.३४ विसर्जनीयस्य सः
स् is the substitute of a विसर्ग when it is followed by a hard consonant (खर्) which itself is followed by a sibilant (शर्).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.35|8.3.35 sharpare visarjaniiyaH|sharpare visarjaniiyaH|sharpare visarjaniiyaH 8.3.35|शर्परे विसर्जनीयः|शर्परे विसर्जनीयः ८.३.३५|८.३.३५|८.३.३५ शर्परे विसर्जनीयः
The विसर्ग is the substitute when it is followed by a hard consonant (खर्) which itself is followed by a sibilant (शर्).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.36|8.3.36 vaa shari|vaa shari|vaa shari 8.3.36|वा शरि|वा शरि ८.३.३६|८.३.३६|८.३.३६ वा शरि
The विसर्ग is optionally the substitute of विसर्ग when followed by a sibilant (शर्).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.37|8.3.37 kupvoH XkaXpau cha|kupvoH XkaXpau cha|kupvoH XkaXpau cha 8.3.37|कुप्वोः XकXपौ च|कुप्वोः XकXपौ च ८.३.३७|८.३.३७|८.३.३७ कुप्वोः XकXपौ च
Xक and Xप are optionally substituted for the विसर्ग when followed by a hard Guttural or a hard labial.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.38|8.3.38 so.apadaadau|so.apadaadau|so.apadaadau 8.3.38|सोऽपदादौ|सोऽपदादौ ८.३.३८|८.३.३८|८.३.३८ सोऽपदादौ
स् is the substitute of a विसर्ग before an affix beginning with a hard guttural or labial.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.39|8.3.39 iNaH ShaH|iNaH ShaH|iNaH ShaH 8.3.39|इणः षः|इणः षः ८.३.३९|८.३.३९|८.३.३९ इणः षः
ष् is the substitute of a विसर्ग when is preceded by इ or उ and is followed by an affix beginning with a hard guttural or a labial.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.40|8.3.40 namaspurasorgatyoH|namaspurasorgatyoH|namaspurasorgatyoH 8.3.40|नमस्पुरसोर्गत्योः|नमस्पुरसोर्गत्योः ८.३.४०|८.३.४०|८.३.४० नमस्पुरसोर्गत्योः
For the विसर्ग of नमस् and पुरस् there is substituted स् before a hard guttural or a labial when these words are गति -- पुरोऽव्ययम् १.४.६७ and साक्षात्प्रभृतीनि च १.४.७४.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.41|8.3.41 idudupadhasya chaapratyayasya|idudupadhasya chaapratyayasya|idudupadhasya chaapratyayasya 8.3.41|इदुदुपधस्य चाप्रत्ययस्य|इदुदुपधस्य चाप्रत्ययस्य ८.३.४१|८.३.४१|८.३.४१ इदुदुपधस्य चाप्रत्ययस्य
ष् is substituted before a hard guttural or a labial for the विसर्ग which is preceded इ or उ and not part of an affix.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.42|8.3.42 tiraso.anyatarasyaam|tiraso.anyatarasyaam|tiraso.anyatarasyaam 8.3.42|तिरसोऽन्यतरस्याम्|तिरसोऽन्यतरस्याम् ८.३.४२|८.३.४२|८.३.४२ तिरसोऽन्यतरस्याम्
The विसर्ग of गति तिरस् is optionally changed to स् before a hard guttural or a labial.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.43|8.3.43 dvistrishchaturiti kRtvo.arthe|dvistrishchaturiti kRtvo.arthe|dvistrishchaturiti kRtvo.arthe 8.3.43|द्विस्त्रिश्चतुरिति कृत्वोऽर्थे|द्विस्त्रिश्चतुरिति कृत्वोऽर्थे ८.३.४३|८.३.४३|८.३.४३ द्विस्त्रिश्चतुरिति कृत्वोऽर्थे
ष् is optionally the substitute of the विसर्ग of 1. द्विस् 2. त्रिस् and 3. चतुर् when they are used as numeral adverbs (before a hard guttural or a labial).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.44|8.3.44 isusoH saamarthye|isusoH saamarthye|isusoH saamarthye 8.3.44|इसुसोः सामर्थ्ये|इसुसोः सामर्थ्ये ८.३.४४|८.३.४४|८.३.४४ इसुसोः सामर्थ्ये
For the विसर्ग of words ending in इस् and उस् before a hard guttural or a labial, there is optionally substituted ष् when the two words stand in correlation with one another.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.45|8.3.45 nityaM samaase.anuttarapadasthasya|nityaM samaase.anuttarapadasthasya|nityaM samaase.anuttarapadasthasya 8.3.45|नित्यं समासेऽनुत्तरपदस्थस्य|नित्यं समासेऽनुत्तरपदस्थस्य ८.३.४५|८.३.४५|८.३.४५ नित्यं समासेऽनुत्तरपदस्थस्य
The विसर्ग of इस् or उस् ending word which is not preceded by any other word is invariably changed to ष् in a compound when followed by a hard consonant or a labial.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.46|8.3.46 ataH kRkamikaMsakumbhapaatrakushaakarNiiShvanavyayasya|ataH kRkamikaMsakumbhapaatrakushaakarNiiShvanavyayasya|ataH kRkamikaMsakumbhapaatrakushaakarNiiShvanavyayasya 8.3.46|अतः कृकमिकंसकुम्भपात्रकुशाकर्णीष्वनव्ययस्य|अतः कृकमिकंसकुम्भपात्रकुशाकर्णीष्वनव्ययस्य ८.३.४६|८.३.४६|८.३.४६ अतः कृकमिकंसकुम्भपात्रकुशाकर्णीष्वनव्ययस्य
For the विसर्ग of a word ending in अस् with the exception of an indeclinable, स् is substituted in a compound when a form of कृ and कम् or the words 1. कंस 2. कुम्भ 3. पात्र 4. कुशा and 5. कर्णी follow and the first word is not preceded by another word.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.47|8.3.47 adhaHshirasii pade|adhaHshirasii pade|adhaHshirasii pade 8.3.47|अधःशिरसी पदे|अधःशिरसी पदे ८.३.४७|८.३.४७|८.३.४७ अधःशिरसी पदे
For the विसर्ग of अधस् or शिरस् when not preceded by another word and followed by the word पद in composition with it, there is substituted स्।<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.48|8.3.48 kaskaadiShu cha|kaskaadiShu cha|kaskaadiShu cha 8.3.48|कस्कादिषु च|कस्कादिषु च ८.३.४८|८.३.४८|८.३.४८ कस्कादिषु च
स् or ष् is substituted for the विसर्ग before a hard guttural or a labial in the words कस्क etc.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.49|8.3.49 Chandasi vaa.apraamreDitayoH|Chandasi vaa.apraamreDitayoH|Chandasi vaa.apraamreDitayoH 8.3.49|छन्दसि वाऽप्राम्रेडितयोः|छन्दसि वाऽप्राम्रेडितयोः ८.३.४९|८.३.४९|८.३.४९ छन्दसि वाऽप्राम्रेडितयोः
स् may optionally be substituted for the विसर्ग before a hard guttural or a labial in the छन्दस् (Vedas); but neither before प्र , nor before a doubled word.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.50|8.3.50 kaHkaratkaratikRdhikRteShvanaditeH|kaHkaratkaratikRdhikRteShvanaditeH|kaHkaratkaratikRdhikRteShvanaditeH 8.3.50|कःकरत्करतिकृधिकृतेष्वनदितेः|कःकरत्करतिकृधिकृतेष्वनदितेः ८.३.५०|८.३.५०|८.३.५० कःकरत्करतिकृधिकृतेष्वनदितेः
The विसर्ग is changed to स् in the छन्दस् (Vedas) before 1. कः 2. करत् 3. करति 4. कृधि and 5. कृतः but not so in the विसर्ग of अदितिः।<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.51|8.3.51 pancamyaaH paraavadhyarthe|pancamyaaH paraavadhyarthe|pancamyaaH paraavadhyarthe 8.3.51|पञ्चम्याः परावध्यर्थे|पञ्चम्याः परावध्यर्थे ८.३.५१|८.३.५१|८.३.५१ पञ्चम्याः परावध्यर्थे
The विसर्ग of the Ablative -5th case is changed to स् before परि meaning 'over'.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.52|8.3.52 paatau cha bahulam|paatau cha bahulam|paatau cha bahulam 8.3.52|पातौ च बहुलम्|पातौ च बहुलम् ८.३.५२|८.३.५२|८.३.५२ पातौ च बहुलम्
स् may diversely be substituted for the विसर्ग of the Ablative -5th case before the verb पातु in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.53|8.3.53 ShaShThyaaH patiputrapRShThapaarapadapayaspoSheShu|ShaShThyaaH patiputrapRShThapaarapadapayaspoSheShu|ShaShThyaaH patiputrapRShThapaarapadapayaspoSheShu 8.3.53|षष्ठ्याः पतिपुत्रपृष्ठपारपदपयस्पोषेषु|षष्ठ्याः पतिपुत्रपृष्ठपारपदपयस्पोषेषु ८.३.५३|८.३.५३|८.३.५३ षष्ठ्याः पतिपुत्रपृष्ठपारपदपयस्पोषेषु
For the विसर्ग  of the Genitive 6th-Case there is substituted स् in the छन्दस् (Vedas) before 1. पति 2. पुत्र 3. पृष्ठ 4. पार 5. पद 6. पयस्  and 7. पोष।<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.54|8.3.54 iDaayaa vaa|iDaayaa vaa|iDaayaa vaa 8.3.54|इडाया वा|इडाया वा ८.३.५४|८.३.५४|८.३.५४ इडाया वा
स् is optionally substituted for the विसर्ग of इडाया before पति etc. -- षष्ठ्याः पतिपुत्रपृष्ठपारपदपयस्पोषेषु ८.३.५३, in the छन्दस् (Vedas).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.55|8.3.55 apadaantasya muurdhanyaH|apadaantasya muurdhanyaH|apadaantasya muurdhanyaH 8.3.55|अपदान्तस्य मूर्धन्यः|अपदान्तस्य मूर्धन्यः ८.३.५५|८.३.५५|८.३.५५ अपदान्तस्य मूर्धन्यः
Up to the end of the पद , is throughout to be supplied the following - 'A cerebral letter substituted always in the room of …, when this letter does not stand at the end of a word'.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.56|8.3.56 saheH saaDaH saH|saheH saaDaH saH|saheH saaDaH saH 8.3.56|सहेः साडः सः|सहेः साडः सः ८.३.५६|८.३.५६|८.३.५६ सहेः साडः सः
ष् is substituted for the स् in साह when this occurs in the form of साड (साट्).<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.57|8.3.57 iNkoH|iNkoH|iNkoH 8.3.57|इण्कोः|इण्कोः ८.३.५७|८.३.५७|८.३.५७ इण्कोः
From this, up to the end of the chapter should be supplied, in every sūtra, the following - 'when a vowel (with the exception of अ or आ) or a र् or a guttural precedes'.<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.58|8.3.58 numvisarjaniiyasharvyavaaye.api|numvisarjaniiyasharvyavaaye.api|numvisarjaniiyasharvyavaaye.api 8.3.58|नुम्विसर्जनीयशर्व्यवायेऽपि|नुम्विसर्जनीयशर्व्यवायेऽपि ८.३.५८|८.३.५८|८.३.५८ नुम्विसर्जनीयशर्व्यवायेऽपि
The substitution of for स् takes place then also, when the augment नुम् (न्) the विसर्जनीय or a sibilant occurs between the said इण् and कु letters or the स्।<br><br>Terms: विसर्ग सन्धि

8.3.59|8.3.59 aadeshapratyayayoH|aadeshapratyayayoH|aadeshapratyayayoH 8.3.59|आदेशप्रत्यययोः|आदेशप्रत्यययोः ८.३.५९|८.३.५९|८.३.५९ आदेशप्रत्यययोः
ष् is substituted for that स् which is a substitute (of the ष् of a root in the धातुपाठ by धात्वादेः षः सः ६.१.६४) or which is (the portion of) an affix, under the above mentioned conditions -- इण्कोः ८.३.५७, नुम्विसर्जनीयशर्व्यवायेऽपि ८.३.५८, of being preceded by an इण् vowel or a guttural.<br><br>Terms: ष् change

8.3.60|8.3.60 shaasivasighasiinaaM cha|shaasivasighasiinaaM cha|shaasivasighasiinaaM cha 8.3.60|शासिवसिघसीनां च|शासिवसिघसीनां च ८.३.६०|८.३.६०|८.३.६० शासिवसिघसीनां च
ष् is substituted for the स् of 1. शास् 2. वस् 'to dwell' and 3. घस् when it is preceded by an इण् vowel or a guttural.<br><br>Terms: ष् change

8.3.61|8.3.61 stautiNyoreva ShaNyabhyaasaat‌|stautiNyoreva ShaNyabhyaasaat‌|stautiNyoreva ShaNyabhyaasaat‌ 8.3.61|स्तौतिण्योरेव षण्यभ्यासात्‌|स्तौतिण्योरेव षण्यभ्यासात्‌ ८.३.६१|८.३.६१|८.३.६१ स्तौतिण्योरेव षण्यभ्यासात्‌
ष् is substituted for the स् after इ or उ in the reduplication of a Desiderative, if the स् of सन् is changed to ष् but only in स्तु and in Causative of roots which in the धातुपाठ begin with ष्।<br><br>Terms: ष् change

8.3.62|8.3.62 saH svidisvadisahiinaaM cha|saH svidisvadisahiinaaM cha|saH svidisvadisahiinaaM cha 8.3.62|सः स्विदिस्वदिसहीनां च|सः स्विदिस्वदिसहीनां च ८.३.६२|८.३.६२|८.३.६२ सः स्विदिस्वदिसहीनां च
स is substituted for the स् after the reduplicate of षण् Desiderative of the Causatives of 1. स्विद् 2. स्वद्  and 3. सह्।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.63|8.3.63 praaksitaadaDvyavaaye.api|praaksitaadaDvyavaaye.api|praaksitaadaDvyavaaye.api 8.3.63|प्राक्सितादड्व्यवायेऽपि|प्राक्सितादड्व्यवायेऽपि ८.३.६३|८.३.६३|८.३.६३ प्राक्सितादड्व्यवायेऽपि
(The substitution of ष् for स् to be taught hereafter, will take place) for all roots up to सित्  exclusive in परिनिविभ्यः सेवसितसयसिवुसहसुट्स्तुस्वञ्जाम् ८.३.७०, even when the augment अट् intervenes (between the स and the efficient letter).<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.64|8.3.64 sthaa.a.adiShvabhyaasena chaabhyaasaya|sthaa.a.adiShvabhyaasena chaabhyaasaya|sthaa.a.adiShvabhyaasena chaabhyaasaya 8.3.64|स्थाऽऽदिष्वभ्यासेन चाभ्यासय|स्थाऽऽदिष्वभ्यासेन चाभ्यासय ८.३.६४|८.३.६४|८.३.६४ स्थाऽऽदिष्वभ्यासेन चाभ्यासय
In स्था etc. up to सित् exclusive -- उपसर्गात्‌ सुनोतिसुवतिस्यतिस्तौतिस्तोभतिस्थासेनय सेधसिचसञ्जस्वञ्जाम् ८.३.६५ to परिनिविभ्यः सेवसितसयसिवुसहसुट्स्तुस्वञ्जाम् ८.३.७०, this substitution of ष् takes place then also, when the reduplicate intervenes and the स of the reduplicate is also changed to ष।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.65|8.3.65 upasargaat‌ sunotisuvatisyatistautistobhatisthaasenayasedhasichasanjasvanjaam|upasargaat‌ sunotisuvatisyatistautistobhatisthaasenayasedhasichasanjasvanjaam|upasargaat‌ sunotisuvatisyatistautistobhatisthaasenayasedhasichasanjasvanjaam 8.3.65|उपसर्गात्‌ सुनोतिसुवतिस्यतिस्तौतिस्तोभतिस्थासेनयसेधसिचसञ्जस्वञ्जाम्|उपसर्गात्‌ सुनोतिसुवतिस्यतिस्तौतिस्तोभतिस्थासेनयसेधसिचसञ्जस्वञ्जाम् ८.३.६५|८.३.६५|८.३.६५ उपसर्गात्‌ सुनोतिसुवतिस्यतिस्तौतिस्तोभतिस्थासेनयसेधसिचसञ्जस्वञ्जाम्
ष् is substituted for स् after an इ and उ of an उपसर्ग (Preposition) in the following verbs - 1. सू (सुनोति) 2. सू (सवति) 3. सो (स्यति -- ओतः श्यनि ७.३.७१) 5. स्तु (स्तौति - उतो वृद्धिर्लुकि हलि ७.३.८९) 6. स्तुभ (स्तोभते) 7. स्था 8. सेनय (Denominative) 9. सिध् (सेधति) 10.  सिच् 11. सञ्ज्  and 12. स्वञ्ज्।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.66|8.3.66 sadiraprateH|sadiraprateH|sadiraprateH 8.3.66|सदिरप्रतेः|सदिरप्रतेः ८.३.६६|८.३.६६|८.३.६६ सदिरप्रतेः
The  स् of सद् is changed to ष after an उपसर्ग (Preposition) having an इ or उ , but not after प्रति।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.67|8.3.67 stambheH|stambheH|stambheH 8.3.67|स्तम्भेः|स्तम्भेः ८.३.६७|८.३.६७|८.३.६७ स्तम्भेः
having an इ or उ।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.68|8.3.68 avaachchaalambanaaviduuryayoH|avaachchaalambanaaviduuryayoH|avaachchaalambanaaviduuryayoH 8.3.68|अवाच्चालम्बनाविदूर्ययोः|अवाच्चालम्बनाविदूर्ययोः ८.३.६८|८.३.६८|८.३.६८ अवाच्चालम्बनाविदूर्ययोः
The  स् of स्तम्भ् is changed into to ष after the उपसर्ग (Preposition) अव in the sense of 'support' and 'contiguity'.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.69|8.3.69 veshcha svano bhojane|veshcha svano bhojane|veshcha svano bhojane 8.3.69|वेश्च स्वनो भोजने|वेश्च स्वनो भोजने ८.३.६९|८.३.६९|८.३.६९ वेश्च स्वनो भोजने
The ष् is substituted for the स् of स्वन् after वि  and अव when the sense is 'to smack while eating'.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.70|8.3.70 parinivibhyaH sevasitasayasivusahasuTstusvanjaam|parinivibhyaH sevasitasayasivusahasuTstusvanjaam|parinivibhyaH sevasitasayasivusahasuTstusvanjaam 8.3.70|परिनिविभ्यः सेवसितसयसिवुसहसुट्स्तुस्वञ्जाम्|परिनिविभ्यः सेवसितसयसिवुसहसुट्स्तुस्वञ्जाम् ८.३.७०|८.३.७०|८.३.७० परिनिविभ्यः सेवसितसयसिवुसहसुट्स्तुस्वञ्जाम्
ष् is substituted for the स् of 1. सेव् 2. सित 3. सय 4. सिव् 5. सह 6. the augment सुट् 7.  स्तु  and 8. स्वज् after the उपसर्ग (Prepositions)  परि , नि  and वि।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.71|8.3.71 sivaadiinaaM vaa.aDvyavaaye.api|sivaadiinaaM vaa.aDvyavaaye.api|sivaadiinaaM vaa.aDvyavaaye.api 8.3.71|सिवादीनां वाऽड्व्यवायेऽपि|सिवादीनां वाऽड्व्यवायेऽपि ८.३.७१|८.३.७१|८.३.७१ सिवादीनां वाऽड्व्यवायेऽपि
The ष् change may take place optionally in the सिव् and the rest (of the last sūtra) even when the augment अ intervenes between the उपसर्ग (Prepositions)  परि , नि  and वि and the verb.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.72|8.3.72 anuviparyabhinibhyaH syandaterapraaNiShu|anuviparyabhinibhyaH syandaterapraaNiShu|anuviparyabhinibhyaH syandaterapraaNiShu 8.3.72|अनुविपर्यभिनिभ्यः स्यन्दतेरप्राणिषु|अनुविपर्यभिनिभ्यः स्यन्दतेरप्राणिषु ८.३.७२|८.३.७२|८.३.७२ अनुविपर्यभिनिभ्यः स्यन्दतेरप्राणिषु
ष् is optionally the substitute of the स् of स्यन्द् after the उपसर्ग (Prepositions) अनु , वि , परि , अभि  and वि when the subject is not a living being.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.73|8.3.73 veH skanderaniShThaayaam|veH skanderaniShThaayaam|veH skanderaniShThaayaam 8.3.73|वेः स्कन्देरनिष्ठायाम्|वेः स्कन्देरनिष्ठायाम् ८.३.७३|८.३.७३|८.३.७३ वेः स्कन्देरनिष्ठायाम्
ष् is optionally the substitute of the स् of स्कन्द् after the उपसर्ग (Preposition) वि but not in the participles in त and तवत।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.74|8.3.74 pareshcha|pareshcha|pareshcha 8.3.74|परेश्च|परेश्च ८.३.७४|८.३.७४|८.३.७४ परेश्च
ष् is optionally the substitute of the स् of स्कन्द् after the उपसर्ग (Preposition) परि everywhere.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.75|8.3.75 pariskandaH praachyabharateShu|pariskandaH praachyabharateShu|pariskandaH praachyabharateShu 8.3.75|परिस्कन्दः प्राच्यभरतेषु|परिस्कन्दः प्राच्यभरतेषु ८.३.७५|८.३.७५|८.३.७५ परिस्कन्दः प्राच्यभरतेषु
The word परिस्कन्द is used without the cerebral change in the country of Eastern Bharata.<br><br>Terms: cerebral change

8.3.76|8.3.76 sphuratisphulatyornirnivibhyaH|sphuratisphulatyornirnivibhyaH|sphuratisphulatyornirnivibhyaH 8.3.76|स्फुरतिस्फुलत्योर्निर्निविभ्यः|स्फुरतिस्फुलत्योर्निर्निविभ्यः ८.३.७६|८.३.७६|८.३.७६ स्फुरतिस्फुलत्योर्निर्निविभ्यः
ष् is optionally the substitute of the स् of स्फुर् and स्फुल् after the उपसर्ग (Prepositions) निस् , नि  and वि।<br><br>Terms: cerebral change

8.3.77|8.3.77 veH skabhnaaternityam|veH skabhnaaternityam|veH skabhnaaternityam 8.3.77|वेः स्कभ्नातेर्नित्यम्|वेः स्कभ्नातेर्नित्यम् ८.३.७७|८.३.७७|८.३.७७ वेः स्कभ्नातेर्नित्यम्
ष् is always the substitute of the स् of स्कम्भ after the उपसर्ग (Preposition) वि।<br><br>Terms: cerebral change

8.3.78|8.3.78 iNaH ShiidhvaMluNG‌liTaaM dho.angaat‌|iNaH ShiidhvaMluNG‌liTaaM dho.angaat‌|iNaH ShiidhvaMluNG‌liTaaM dho.angaat‌ 8.3.78|इणः षीध्वंलुङ्‌लिटां धोऽङ्गात्‌|इणः षीध्वंलुङ्‌लिटां धोऽङ्गात्‌ ८.३.७८|८.३.७८|८.३.७८ इणः षीध्वंलुङ्‌लिटां धोऽङ्गात्‌
The cerebral sound is substituted in the room of ध् of षीध्वम्  and of the personal-endings of the Aorist and the लिट् (Perfect Tense), after a अङ्ग (stem) ending in इण् (a vowel other than अ).<br><br>Terms: cerebral change

8.3.79|8.3.79 vibhaaSheTaH|vibhaaSheTaH|vibhaaSheTaH 8.3.79|विभाषेटः|विभाषेटः ८.३.७९|८.३.७९|८.३.७९ विभाषेटः
The cerebral sound is optionally substituted for the ध् of षीध्वम्  and of the Aorist and the लिट् (Perfect Tense) after the augment इट् when the stem ends in inn<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.80|8.3.80 samaase.anguleH sangaH|samaase.anguleH sangaH|samaase.anguleH sangaH 8.3.80|समासेऽङ्गुलेः सङ्गः|समासेऽङ्गुलेः सङ्गः ८.३.८०|८.३.८०|८.३.८० समासेऽङ्गुलेः सङ्गः
ष् is substituted for the स् of सङ्ग after the word अङ्गुलि in a compound.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.81|8.3.81 bhiiroH sthaanam|bhiiroH sthaanam|bhiiroH sthaanam 8.3.81|भीरोः स्थानम्|भीरोः स्थानम् ८.३.८१|८.३.८१|८.३.८१ भीरोः स्थानम्
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्थानम् when preceded by भीरु in a compound.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.82|8.3.82 agneH stutstomasomaaH|agneH stutstomasomaaH|agneH stutstomasomaaH 8.3.82|अग्नेः स्तुत्स्तोमसोमाः|अग्नेः स्तुत्स्तोमसोमाः ८.३.८२|८.३.८२|८.३.८२ अग्नेः स्तुत्स्तोमसोमाः
ष् is substituted for the स् of 1. स्तुत 2. स्तोम  and 3. सोम when preceded by अग्नि in a compound.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.83|8.3.83 jyotiraayuShaH stomaH|jyotiraayuShaH stomaH|jyotiraayuShaH stomaH 8.3.83|ज्योतिरायुषः स्तोमः|ज्योतिरायुषः स्तोमः ८.३.८३|८.३.८३|८.३.८३ ज्योतिरायुषः स्तोमः
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्तोम after ज्योतिस्  and  आयुस् in a compound.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.84|8.3.84 maatRpitRbhyaaM svasaa|maatRpitRbhyaaM svasaa|maatRpitRbhyaaM svasaa 8.3.84|मातृपितृभ्यां स्वसा|मातृपितृभ्यां स्वसा ८.३.८४|८.३.८४|८.३.८४ मातृपितृभ्यां स्वसा
ष् is optionally substituted for the स् of स्वसृ after मातृ  and पितृ in a compound.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.85|8.3.85 maatuHpiturbhyaamanyatarasyaam‌|maatuHpiturbhyaamanyatarasyaam‌|maatuHpiturbhyaamanyatarasyaam‌ 8.3.85|मातुःपितुर्भ्यामन्यतरस्याम्‌|मातुःपितुर्भ्यामन्यतरस्याम्‌ ८.३.८५|८.३.८५|८.३.८५ मातुःपितुर्भ्यामन्यतरस्याम्‌
ष् is optionally substituted for the स् of स्वसृ after मातुर्  and पितुर् in a compound.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.86|8.3.86 abhinisaH stanaH shabdasaMJNaayaam|abhinisaH stanaH shabdasaMJNaayaam|abhinisaH stanaH shabdasaMJNaayaam 8.3.86|अभिनिसः स्तनः शब्दसंज्ञायाम्|अभिनिसः स्तनः शब्दसंज्ञायाम् ८.३.८६|८.३.८६|८.३.८६ अभिनिसः स्तनः शब्दसंज्ञायाम्
ष् is optionally substituted for the स् of स्तन् after the double उपसर्ग (Preposition) अभि निस् when the word so formed is the name of a particular letter (विसर्ग).<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.87|8.3.87 upasargapraadurbhyaamastiryachparaH|upasargapraadurbhyaamastiryachparaH|upasargapraadurbhyaamastiryachparaH 8.3.87|उपसर्गप्रादुर्भ्यामस्तिर्यच्परः|उपसर्गप्रादुर्भ्यामस्तिर्यच्परः ८.३.८७|८.३.८७|८.३.८७ उपसर्गप्रादुर्भ्यामस्तिर्यच्परः
ष् is substituted for the स् of the verb अस् 'to be' when it is followed by a vowel or य् and is preceded by प्रादुः or an उपसर्ग (Preposition) इ or उ having in it.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.88|8.3.88 suvinirdurbhyaH supisuutisamaaH|suvinirdurbhyaH supisuutisamaaH|suvinirdurbhyaH supisuutisamaaH 8.3.88|सुविनिर्दुर्भ्यः सुपिसूतिसमाः|सुविनिर्दुर्भ्यः सुपिसूतिसमाः ८.३.८८|८.३.८८|८.३.८८ सुविनिर्दुर्भ्यः सुपिसूतिसमाः
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्वप् , सूति  and सम after सु , वि , निर्  and दुर्।<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.89|8.3.89 ninadiibhyaaM snaateH kaushale|ninadiibhyaaM snaateH kaushale|ninadiibhyaaM snaateH kaushale 8.3.89|निनदीभ्यां स्नातेः कौशले|निनदीभ्यां स्नातेः कौशले ८.३.८९|८.३.८९|८.३.८९ निनदीभ्यां स्नातेः कौशले
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्ना after नि and नदी when the word so formed denotes 'dexterous'.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.90|8.3.90 suutraM pratiShNaatam‌|suutraM pratiShNaatam‌|suutraM pratiShNaatam‌ 8.3.90|सूत्रं प्रतिष्णातम्‌|सूत्रं प्रतिष्णातम्‌ ८.३.९०|८.३.९०|८.३.९० सूत्रं प्रतिष्णातम्‌
The word प्रतिष्णात is irregularly formed when meaning 'sūtra'.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.91|8.3.91 kapiShThalo gotre|kapiShThalo gotre|kapiShThalo gotre 8.3.91|कपिष्ठलो गोत्रे|कपिष्ठलो गोत्रे ८.३.९१|८.३.९१|८.३.९१ कपिष्ठलो गोत्रे
The word कपिष्ठल is irregularly formed denoting the founder of a गोत्र (Patronymic) of that name.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.92|8.3.92 praShTho.agragaamini|praShTho.agragaamini|praShTho.agragaamini 8.3.92|प्रष्ठोऽग्रगामिनि|प्रष्ठोऽग्रगामिनि ८.३.९२|८.३.९२|८.३.९२ प्रष्ठोऽग्रगामिनि
The word प्रष्ठ is irregularly formed when denoting 'a chief' or 'one who goes in front'.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.93|8.3.93 vRxaasanayorviShTaraH|vRxaasanayorviShTaraH|vRxaasanayorviShTaraH 8.3.93|वृक्षासनयोर्विष्टरः|वृक्षासनयोर्विष्टरः ८.३.९३|८.३.९३|८.३.९३ वृक्षासनयोर्विष्टरः
The word विष्टर is irregularly formed in the sense of 'tree' and 'seat'.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.94|8.3.94 Chandonaamni cha|Chandonaamni cha|Chandonaamni cha 8.3.94|छन्दोनाम्नि च|छन्दोनाम्नि च ८.३.९४|८.३.९४|८.३.९४ छन्दोनाम्नि च
Also when it is the name of a meter, the irregular form विष्टर is used.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.95|8.3.95 gaviyudhibhyaaM sthiraH|gaviyudhibhyaaM sthiraH|gaviyudhibhyaaM sthiraH 8.3.95|गवियुधिभ्यां स्थिरः|गवियुधिभ्यां स्थिरः ८.३.९५|८.३.९५|८.३.९५ गवियुधिभ्यां स्थिरः
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्थिरः after the words गवि  and  युधि।<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.96|8.3.96 vikushamiparibhyaH sthalam|vikushamiparibhyaH sthalam|vikushamiparibhyaH sthalam 8.3.96|विकुशमिपरिभ्यः स्थलम्|विकुशमिपरिभ्यः स्थलम् ८.३.९६|८.३.९६|८.३.९६ विकुशमिपरिभ्यः स्थलम्
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्थल after वि , कु , शमि  and परि।<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.97|8.3.97 ambaambagobhuumisavyaapadvitrikushekushankvangumanjipunjiparamebarhirdivyagnibhyaH sthaH|ambaambagobhuumisavyaapadvitrikushekushankvangumanjipunjiparamebarhirdivyagnibhyaH sthaH|ambaambagobhuumisavyaapadvitrikushekushankvangumanjipunjiparamebarhirdivyagnibhyaH sthaH 8.3.97|अम्बाम्बगोभूमिसव्यापद्वित्रिकुशेकुशङ्क्वङ्गुमञ्जिपुञ्जिपरमेबर्हिर्दिव्यग्निभ्यः स्थः|अम्बाम्बगोभूमिसव्यापद्वित्रिकुशेकुशङ्क्वङ्गुमञ्जिपुञ्जिपरमेबर्हिर्दिव्यग्निभ्यः स्थः ८.३.९७|८.३.९७|८.३.९७ अम्बाम्बगोभूमिसव्यापद्वित्रिकुशेकुशङ्क्वङ्गुमञ्जिपुञ्जिपरमेबर्हिर्दिव्यग्निभ्यः स्थः
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्थ after 1. अम्ब 2. आम्ब 3. गो 4. भूमि 5. सव्य 6. अप 7. द्वि 8. त्रि 9. कु 10. शेकु 11. शङ्क्वु 12. अङ्गु 13. मञ्जि 14. पुञ्जि 15. परमे 16. बर्हिस् 17. दिवि  and 18 अग्नि।<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.98|8.3.98 suShaamaadiShu cha|suShaamaadiShu cha|suShaamaadiShu cha 8.3.98|सुषामादिषु च|सुषामादिषु च ८.३.९८|८.३.९८|८.३.९८ सुषामादिषु च
ष् is substituted for the स् of the words सुषामान् etc.<br><br>Terms: ष change

8.3.99|8.3.99 aiti saMJNaayaamagaat‌|aiti saMJNaayaamagaat‌|aiti saMJNaayaamagaat‌ 8.3.99|ऐति संज्ञायामगात्‌|ऐति संज्ञायामगात्‌ ८.३.९९|८.३.९९|८.३.९९ ऐति संज्ञायामगात्‌
ष् is substituted for the स् when followed by ए and preceded by इण् or कु , when the word is a name and when the स् is not preceded by ग्।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.100|8.3.100 naxatraadvaa|naxatraadvaa|naxatraadvaa 8.3.100|नक्षत्राद्वा|नक्षत्राद्वा ८.३.१००|८.३.१००|८.३.१०० नक्षत्राद्वा
ष् is optionally substituted for the स् when the preceding word is the name of a Lunar mansion.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.101|8.3.101 hrasvaat‌ taadau taddhite|hrasvaat‌ taadau taddhite|hrasvaat‌ taadau taddhite 8.3.101|ह्रस्वात्‌ तादौ तद्धिते|ह्रस्वात्‌ तादौ तद्धिते ८.३.१०१|८.३.१०१|८.३.१०१ ह्रस्वात्‌ तादौ तद्धिते
ष् is substituted for the final स् preceded by a उ before a तद्धित affix beginning with त।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.102|8.3.102 nisastapataavanaasevane|nisastapataavanaasevane|nisastapataavanaasevane 8.3.102|निसस्तपतावनासेवने|निसस्तपतावनासेवने ८.३.१०२|८.३.१०२|८.३.१०२ निसस्तपतावनासेवने
ष् is substituted for the स् of निस् before the verb तप् when meaning is not that of 'repeatedly making red hot'.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.103|8.3.103 yuShmattattataxuHShvantaHpaadam|yuShmattattataxuHShvantaHpaadam|yuShmattattataxuHShvantaHpaadam 8.3.103|युष्मत्तत्ततक्षुःष्वन्तःपादम्|युष्मत्तत्ततक्षुःष्वन्तःपादम् ८.३.१०३|८.३.१०३|८.३.१०३ युष्मत्तत्ततक्षुःष्वन्तःपादम्
The स् standing in the inner half of a stanza is changed to ष्  before the त of त्वम् etc. and युष्मद्।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.104|8.3.104 yajuShyekeShaam|yajuShyekeShaam|yajuShyekeShaam 8.3.104|यजुष्येकेषाम्|यजुष्येकेषाम् ८.३.१०४|८.३.१०४|८.३.१०४ यजुष्येकेषाम्
In the opinion of some, the above change takes place in the यजुर्वेद also.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.105|8.3.105 stutastomayoshChandasi|stutastomayoshChandasi|stutastomayoshChandasi 8.3.105|स्तुतस्तोमयोश्छन्दसि|स्तुतस्तोमयोश्छन्दसि ८.३.१०५|८.३.१०५|८.३.१०५ स्तुतस्तोमयोश्छन्दसि
ष् is substituted for the स् of स्तुत in the छन्दस् (Vedas), in the opinion of some.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.106|8.3.106 puurvapadaat‌|puurvapadaat‌|puurvapadaat‌ 8.3.106|पूर्वपदात्‌|पूर्वपदात्‌ ८.३.१०६|८.३.१०६|८.३.१०६ पूर्वपदात्‌
In the छन्दस् (Vedas), ष् is substituted for the स् when it stands in the beginning of a second word, preceded by a word ending in इ etc.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.107|8.3.107 suNJaH|suNJaH|suNJaH 8.3.107|सुञः|सुञः ८.३.१०७|८.३.१०७|८.३.१०७ सुञः
In the छन्दस् (Vedas),  ष् is substituted for the स् of the particle सु when preceded by a word having in it the change-effecting letter इ etc.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.108|8.3.108 sanoteranaH|sanoteranaH|sanoteranaH 8.3.108|सनोतेरनः|सनोतेरनः ८.३.१०८|८.३.१०८|८.३.१०८ सनोतेरनः
The स of the verb सन् , when it loses its न् is changed to ष , under the same circumstances.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.109|8.3.109 saheH pRtanartaabhyaaM cha|saheH pRtanartaabhyaaM cha|saheH pRtanartaabhyaaM cha 8.3.109|सहेः पृतनर्ताभ्यां च|सहेः पृतनर्ताभ्यां च ८.३.१०९|८.३.१०९|८.३.१०९ सहेः पृतनर्ताभ्यां च
ष् is substituted for the स् of सह after पृतना  and ऋत।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.110|8.3.110 na raparasRpisRjispRshispRhisavanaadiinaam|na raparasRpisRjispRshispRhisavanaadiinaam|na raparasRpisRjispRshispRhisavanaadiinaam 8.3.110|न रपरसृपिसृजिस्पृशिस्पृहिसवनादीनाम्|न रपरसृपिसृजिस्पृशिस्पृहिसवनादीनाम् ८.३.११०|८.३.११०|८.३.११० न रपरसृपिसृजिस्पृशिस्पृहिसवनादीनाम्
The ष् substitution does not take place if र् follows the स् as well as in 1. सृप 2. सृज 3. स्पृश 4. स्पृह  and 5. सवन etc.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.111|8.3.111 saatpadaadyoH|saatpadaadyoH|saatpadaadyoH 8.3.111|सात्पदाद्योः|सात्पदाद्योः ८.३.१११|८.३.१११|८.३.१११ सात्पदाद्योः
The ष् substitution does not take place in the affix सात् and for that स् which stands at the beginning of a word.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.112|8.3.112 sicho yaNGi|sicho yaNGi|sicho yaNGi 8.3.112|सिचो यङि|सिचो यङि ८.३.११२|८.३.११२|८.३.११२ सिचो यङि
The ष् substitution does not take place in the स् of सिच् of the Intensive.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.113|8.3.113 sedhatergatau|sedhatergatau|sedhatergatau 8.3.113|सेधतेर्गतौ|सेधतेर्गतौ ८.३.११३|८.३.११३|८.३.११३ सेधतेर्गतौ
The ष् substitution does not take place in the स् of the verb सेध when the meaning is that of moving.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.114|8.3.114 pratistabdhanistabdhau cha|pratistabdhanistabdhau cha|pratistabdhanistabdhau cha 8.3.114|प्रतिस्तब्धनिस्तब्धौ च|प्रतिस्तब्धनिस्तब्धौ च ८.३.११४|८.३.११४|८.३.११४ प्रतिस्तब्धनिस्तब्धौ च
The words प्रतिस्तब्ध and निस्तब्ध are anomalous.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.115|8.3.115 soDhaH|soDhaH|soDhaH 8.3.115|सोढः|सोढः ८.३.११५|८.३.११५|८.३.११५ सोढः
The ष् substitution does not take place in the स् of सोढ form of the root सह।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.116|8.3.116 stambhusivusahaaM chaNGi|stambhusivusahaaM chaNGi|stambhusivusahaaM chaNGi 8.3.116|स्तम्भुसिवुसहां चङि|स्तम्भुसिवुसहां चङि ८.३.११६|८.३.११६|८.३.११६ स्तम्भुसिवुसहां चङि
The ष् substitution does not take place in the reduplicated Aorist of the roots 1. स्तम्भ् 2. सिव्  and 3. सह।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.117|8.3.117 sunoteH syasanoH|sunoteH syasanoH|sunoteH syasanoH 8.3.117|सुनोतेः स्यसनोः|सुनोतेः स्यसनोः ८.३.११७|८.३.११७|८.३.११७ सुनोतेः स्यसनोः
The ष् substitution does not take place in the स् of सु (सुनोति) in the Future, Conditional and Desiderative.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.118|8.3.118 sadiShvanjoH parasya liTi|sadiShvanjoH parasya liTi|sadiShvanjoH parasya liTi 8.3.118|सदिष्वञ्जोः परस्य लिटि|सदिष्वञ्जोः परस्य लिटि ८.३.११८|८.३.११८|८.३.११८ सदिष्वञ्जोः परस्य लिटि
The ष् substitution does not take place in the स् of सद्  and ष्वञ्ज् after the reduplicate in the लिट् (Perfect Tense).<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.3.119|8.3.119 nivyabhibhyo.aDvyaavaye vaa Chandasi|nivyabhibhyo.aDvyaavaye vaa Chandasi|nivyabhibhyo.aDvyaavaye vaa Chandasi 8.3.119|निव्यभिभ्योऽड्व्यावये वा छन्दसि|निव्यभिभ्योऽड्व्यावये वा छन्दसि ८.३.११९|८.३.११९|८.३.११९ निव्यभिभ्योऽड्व्यावये वा छन्दसि
The ष् is optionally substituted in the छन्दस् (Vedas) after the उपसर्ग (Prepositions) नि , वि  and अभि when the augment अट् intervenes.<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

8.4.1|8.4.1 raShaabhyaaM no NaH samaanapade|raShaabhyaaM no NaH samaanapade|raShaabhyaaM no NaH samaanapade 8.4.1|रषाभ्यां नो णः समानपदे|रषाभ्यां नो णः समानपदे ८.४.१|८.४.१|८.४.१ रषाभ्यां नो णः समानपदे
After न् and ष् , the ण् is the substitute of न् , when they occur as component letters in the same word.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.2|8.4.2 aTkupvaaNGnumvyavaaye.api|aTkupvaaNGnumvyavaaye.api|aTkupvaaNGnumvyavaaye.api 8.4.2|अट्कुप्वाङ्नुम्व्यवायेऽपि|अट्कुप्वाङ्नुम्व्यवायेऽपि ८.४.२|८.४.२|८.४.२ अट्कुप्वाङ्नुम्व्यवायेऽपि
The substitute ण् takes the place of न् , even when a vowel or य् , व् , ह् or a guttural, or a labial, or the preposition आ , or the augment नुम् intervenes, causing separation.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.3|8.4.3 puurvapadaat‌ saMJNaayaamagaH|puurvapadaat‌ saMJNaayaamagaH|puurvapadaat‌ saMJNaayaamagaH 8.4.3|पूर्वपदात्‌ संज्ञायामगः|पूर्वपदात्‌ संज्ञायामगः ८.४.३|८.४.३|८.४.३ पूर्वपदात्‌ संज्ञायामगः
So also, न् is replaced by ण् , when the letter occasioning the substitution, occurs in the first member of a compound, and the whole compound is a Name, provided that the first member does not end with the letter ग।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.4|8.4.4 vanaM puragaamishrakaasidhrakaashaarikaakoTaraa.agrebhyaH|vanaM puragaamishrakaasidhrakaashaarikaakoTaraa.agrebhyaH|vanaM puragaamishrakaasidhrakaashaarikaakoTaraa.agrebhyaH 8.4.4|वनं पुरगामिश्रकासिध्रकाशारिकाकोटराऽग्रेभ्यः|वनं पुरगामिश्रकासिध्रकाशारिकाकोटराऽग्रेभ्यः ८.४.४|८.४.४|८.४.४ वनं पुरगामिश्रकासिध्रकाशारिकाकोटराऽग्रेभ्यः
The न of वन , is changed into ण , when preceded by the words पुरगा , मिश्रका , सिध्रका , शारिका , कोटरा and अग्रे , as first members of the compound, and the whole compound is a name.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास

8.4.5|8.4.5 pranirantaHsharexuplaxaamrakaarShyakhadirapiyuuxaabhyo.asaMJNaayaamapi|pranirantaHsharexuplaxaamrakaarShyakhadirapiyuuxaabhyo.asaMJNaayaamapi|pranirantaHsharexuplaxaamrakaarShyakhadirapiyuuxaabhyo.asaMJNaayaamapi 8.4.5|प्रनिरन्तःशरेक्षुप्लक्षाम्रकार्ष्यखदिरपियूक्षाभ्योऽसंज्ञायामपि|प्रनिरन्तःशरेक्षुप्लक्षाम्रकार्ष्यखदिरपियूक्षाभ्योऽसंज्ञायामपि ८.४.५|८.४.५|८.४.५ प्रनिरन्तःशरेक्षुप्लक्षाम्रकार्ष्यखदिरपियूक्षाभ्योऽसंज्ञायामपि
The न of वन , is replaced by ण , even when the compound is not a Name, when it is preceded by the words प्र , निर् , अन्तर , शर , इक्षु , प्लक्ष , आम्र , कार्ष्य , खदिर and पीयूक्षा।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास

8.4.6|8.4.6 vibhaaShauShadhivanaspatibhyaH|vibhaaShauShadhivanaspatibhyaH|vibhaaShauShadhivanaspatibhyaH 8.4.6|विभाषौषधिवनस्पतिभ्यः|विभाषौषधिवनस्पतिभ्यः ८.४.६|८.४.६|८.४.६ विभाषौषधिवनस्पतिभ्यः
The न of वन , is optionally replaced by ण , when the cause of change occurs in the first member of the compound and which denotes a perrenial herb or forest tree.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास

8.4.7|8.4.7 ahno.adantaat‌|ahno.adantaat‌|ahno.adantaat‌ 8.4.7|अह्नोऽदन्तात्‌|अह्नोऽदन्तात्‌ ८.४.७|८.४.७|८.४.७ अह्नोऽदन्तात्‌
The ण is the substitute of न of अहन् , when it is preceded by a word ending in अ , having in it a letter capable of producing a change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास

8.4.8|8.4.8 vaahanamaahitaat‌|vaahanamaahitaat‌|vaahanamaahitaat‌ 8.4.8|वाहनमाहितात्‌|वाहनमाहितात्‌ ८.४.८|८.४.८|८.४.८ वाहनमाहितात्‌
The न of वाहन is changed into ण , when the letter producing the change, occurs in the first member of a compound, denoting the thing carried.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word

8.4.9|8.4.9 paanaM deshe|paanaM deshe|paanaM deshe 8.4.9|पानं देशे|पानं देशे ८.४.९|८.४.९|८.४.९ पानं देशे
The न of पान is changed into ण , when occurs as the second member of a compound, the first member of which contains a letter causing change; and the whole compound denotes a country or people.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास-word

8.4.10|8.4.10 vaa bhaavakaraNayoH|vaa bhaavakaraNayoH|vaa bhaavakaraNayoH 8.4.10|वा भावकरणयोः|वा भावकरणयोः ८.४.१०|८.४.१०|८.४.१० वा भावकरणयोः
Optionally when the compound denotes a condition or an instrument, the न् of पान is changed to ण , when it is a second member, the cause of change occurring in the first member in a compound.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास-word

8.4.11|8.4.11 praatipadikaantanumvibhaktiShu cha|praatipadikaantanumvibhaktiShu cha|praatipadikaantanumvibhaktiShu cha 8.4.11|प्रातिपदिकान्तनुम्विभक्तिषु च|प्रातिपदिकान्तनुम्विभक्तिषु च ८.४.११|८.४.११|८.४.११ प्रातिपदिकान्तनुम्विभक्तिषु च
Optionally ण is substituted for न when it stands at the end of a Nominal-stem (प्रातिपदिक) or is the augment नुम् or is न of a case-affix, (when the cause of change occurs in the first member of the compound).<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास-word

8.4.12|8.4.12 ekaajuttarapade NaH|ekaajuttarapade NaH|ekaajuttarapade NaH 8.4.12|एकाजुत्तरपदे णः|एकाजुत्तरपदे णः ८.४.१२|८.४.१२|८.४.१२ एकाजुत्तरपदे णः
In a compound, the second member of which is a monosyllable, there is ण in the room of न of the second member, provided that the न is at the end of a प्रातिपदिक , or is the augment नुम् , or occurs in a विभक्ति; and when the first member contains a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-आगमन-विभक्ति

8.4.13|8.4.13 kumati cha|kumati cha|kumati cha 8.4.13|कुमति च|कुमति च ८.४.१३|८.४.१३|८.४.१३ कुमति च
In a compound, the second member of which contains a guttural, there is ण in the room of न , that follows anything which standing in the prior member is qualified to cause the change, provided the न be at the end of a प्रातिपदिक , or be the augment नुम् , or occur in a विभक्ति।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-आगमन-विभक्ति

8.4.14|8.4.14 upasargaadasamaase.api Nopadeshasya|upasargaadasamaase.api Nopadeshasya|upasargaadasamaase.api Nopadeshasya 8.4.14|उपसर्गादसमासेऽपि णोपदेशस्य|उपसर्गादसमासेऽपि णोपदेशस्य ८.४.१४|८.४.१४|८.४.१४ उपसर्गादसमासेऽपि णोपदेशस्य
Of a root which has ण in its original enunciation, when it comes after a cause of such change standing in an उपसर्ग , even though the word be not a समास , the न is changed to ण।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-आगमन-विभक्ति

8.4.15|8.4.15 hinumiinaa|hinumiinaa|hinumiinaa 8.4.15|हिनुमीना|हिनुमीना ८.४.१५|८.४.१५|८.४.१५ हिनुमीना
The न of हिनु and मीना is changed to ण , when coming after an उपसर्ग containing in it a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु-उपसर्ग

8.4.16|8.4.16 aani loT|aani loT|aani loT 8.4.16|आनि लोट्|आनि लोट् ८.४.१६|८.४.१६|८.४.१६ आनि लोट्
The न of आनि , the affix of the Imperative, First Person, is changed into ण when it follows a letter competent to cause such a change standing in an उपसर्ग।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word-उपसर्ग

8.4.17|8.4.17 nergadanadapatapadaghumaasyatihantiyaativaatidraatipsaativapativahatishaamyatichinotidegdhiShu cha|nergadanadapatapadaghumaasyatihantiyaativaatidraatipsaativapativahatishaamyatichinotidegdhiShu cha|nergadanadapatapadaghumaasyatihantiyaativaatidraatipsaativapativahatishaamyatichinotidegdhiShu cha 8.4.17|नेर्गदनदपतपदघुमास्यतिहन्तियातिवातिद्रातिप्सातिवपतिवहतिशाम्यतिचिनोतिदेग्धिषु च|नेर्गदनदपतपदघुमास्यतिहन्तियातिवातिद्रातिप्सातिवपतिवहतिशाम्यतिचिनोतिदेग्धिषु च ८.४.१७|८.४.१७|८.४.१७ नेर्गदनदपतपदघुमास्यतिहन्तियातिवातिद्रातिप्सातिवपतिवहतिशाम्यतिचिनोतिदेग्धिषु च
The ण is the substitute of न् of the prefix नि , following a cause for such change standing in an उपसर्ग when these words follow - गद 'to speak', नद 'to be happy', पत 'to fall', पद 'to go'; the घु verbs - मा 'to measure', शो 'to destroy', हन् 'to kill', या 'to go', वा 'to blow', द्रा 'to flee', प्शा 'to eat', वप् 'to weave', वह् 'to bear', शम् 'to be tranquil', चि 'to collect', and दिह् 'to anoint'.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-तिङ्-उपसर्ग

8.4.18|8.4.18 sheShe vibhaaShaa.akakhaadaavaShaanta upadeshe|sheShe vibhaaShaa.akakhaadaavaShaanta upadeshe|sheShe vibhaaShaa.akakhaadaavaShaanta upadeshe 8.4.18|शेषे विभाषाऽकखादावषान्त उपदेशे|शेषे विभाषाऽकखादावषान्त उपदेशे ८.४.१८|८.४.१८|८.४.१८ शेषे विभाषाऽकखादावषान्त उपदेशे
In the remaining verbs, optionally the न of नि is replaced by ण , when it is preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to cause the change; provided that, in the original enunciation, the verb has not an initial क or ख , nor ends with ष।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु-उपसर्ग

8.4.19|8.4.19 aniteH|aniteH|aniteH 8.4.19|अनितेः|अनितेः ८.४.१९|८.४.१९|८.४.१९ अनितेः
The न of the verb अन् 'to breathe', is changed to ण , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to produce the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.20|8.4.20 antaH|antaH|antaH 8.4.20|अन्तः|अन्तः ८.४.२०|८.४.२०|८.४.२० अन्तः
The न of the verb अन् 'to breathe', is changed to ण , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to produce the change, provided it occurs at the end of a पद।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.21|8.4.21 ubhau saabhyaasasya|ubhau saabhyaasasya|ubhau saabhyaasasya 8.4.21|उभौ साभ्यासस्य|उभौ साभ्यासस्य ८.४.२१|८.४.२१|८.४.२१ उभौ साभ्यासस्य
Both the न-s are changed into ण in the reduplicated forms of the verb अन् , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to cause the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.22|8.4.22 hanteratpuurvasya|hanteratpuurvasya|hanteratpuurvasya 8.4.22|हन्तेरत्पूर्वस्य|हन्तेरत्पूर्वस्य ८.४.२२|८.४.२२|८.४.२२ हन्तेरत्पूर्वस्य
The न , when preceded by अ , in the root हन् , is changed to ण , when the verb is preceded by a preposition competent to cause the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.23|8.4.23 vamorvaa|vamorvaa|vamorvaa 8.4.23|वमोर्वा|वमोर्वा ८.४.२३|८.४.२३|८.४.२३ वमोर्वा
Optionally when व or म follow, the न of हन् is changed to ण , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to cause the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.24|8.4.24 antaradeshe|antaradeshe|antaradeshe 8.4.24|अन्तरदेशे|अन्तरदेशे ८.४.२४|८.४.२४|८.४.२४ अन्तरदेशे
The न preceded by short अ of the root हन् is changed into ण , when the root follows the उपसर्ग - अन्तर and the word does not mean 'a country'.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.25|8.4.25 ayanaM cha|ayanaM cha|ayanaM cha 8.4.25|अयनं च|अयनं च ८.४.२५|८.४.२५|८.४.२५ अयनं च
The न of अयन is changed to ण , when preceded by the word अन्तर् and the word does not denote a country.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.26|8.4.26 ChandasyRdavagrahaat‌|ChandasyRdavagrahaat‌|ChandasyRdavagrahaat‌ 8.4.26|छन्दस्यृदवग्रहात्‌|छन्दस्यृदवग्रहात्‌ ८.४.२६|८.४.२६|८.४.२६ छन्दस्यृदवग्रहात्‌
In the छन्दस् , न of a second term is changed into ण , when prior term ends with a short ऋ even when there is an अवग्रह or hiatus between the two terms.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

8.4.27|8.4.27 nashcha dhaatusthoruShubhyaH|nashcha dhaatusthoruShubhyaH|nashcha dhaatusthoruShubhyaH 8.4.27|नश्च धातुस्थोरुषुभ्यः|नश्च धातुस्थोरुषुभ्यः ८.४.२७|८.४.२७|८.४.२७ नश्च धातुस्थोरुषुभ्यः
In the छन्दस् , the न of (the Pronoun) नस् is changed into ण , when it comes after a root having a र or ष or after the words उरु and षु (सु)।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-छन्दस्

8.4.28|8.4.28 upasargaad bahulam|upasargaad bahulam|upasargaad bahulam 8.4.28|उपसर्गाद् बहुलम्|उपसर्गाद् बहुलम् ८.४.२८|८.४.२८|८.४.२८ उपसर्गाद् बहुलम्
The न of नस् is changed diversely into ण , when it comes after an उपसर्ग having a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-छन्दस्

8.4.29|8.4.29 kRtyachaH|kRtyachaH|kRtyachaH 8.4.29|कृत्यचः|कृत्यचः ८.४.२९|८.४.२९|८.४.२९ कृत्यचः
The न of कृत् affix, preceded by a vowel, is changed into ण , when it follows an उपसर्ग having the cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word-उपसर्ग

8.4.30|8.4.30 NervibhaaShaa|NervibhaaShaa|NervibhaaShaa 8.4.30|णेर्विभाषा|णेर्विभाषा ८.४.३०|८.४.३०|८.४.३० णेर्विभाषा
The न of कृत् affix ordained after a causative verb (णयन्त), is optionally changed into ण , when it comes after an उपसर्ग having a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

8.4.31|8.4.31 halashcha ijupadhaat‌|halashcha ijupadhaat‌|halashcha ijupadhaat‌ 8.4.31|हलश्च इजुपधात्‌|हलश्च इजुपधात्‌ ८.४.३१|८.४.३१|८.४.३१ हलश्च इजुपधात्‌
The कृत् affix, coming after a verb, which begins with a consonant and has a penultimate इच् vowel, changes optionally its न् , which is preceded by a vowel, into ण् , when it comes after उपसर्ग having a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

8.4.32|8.4.32 ijaadeH sanumaH|ijaadeH sanumaH|ijaadeH sanumaH 8.4.32|इजादेः सनुमः|इजादेः सनुमः ८.४.३२|८.४.३२|८.४.३२ इजादेः सनुमः
A कृत् affix ordained after a verb beginning with an इच् vowel, having the augment नुम् in it, and ending with a consonant, changes it s न् into ण् , when preceded by an उपसर्ग having in it the cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

8.4.33|8.4.33 vaa niMsanixanindaam|vaa niMsanixanindaam|vaa niMsanixanindaam 8.4.33|वा निंसनिक्षनिन्दाम्|वा निंसनिक्षनिन्दाम् ८.४.३३|८.४.३३|८.४.३३ वा निंसनिक्षनिन्दाम्
The न् of निस् , निक्ष and निन्द is changed to a ण optionally, when preceded by an उपसर्ग having in it a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

8.4.34|8.4.34 na bhaabhuupuukamigamipyaayiivepaam|na bhaabhuupuukamigamipyaayiivepaam|na bhaabhuupuukamigamipyaayiivepaam 8.4.34|न भाभूपूकमिगमिप्यायीवेपाम्|न भाभूपूकमिगमिप्यायीवेपाम् ८.४.३४|८.४.३४|८.४.३४ न भाभूपूकमिगमिप्यायीवेपाम्
The न of a कृत् affix is not changed to ण , though preceded by an उपसर्ग having in it a cause of change, when the affix is added to the following verbs - भा 'to shine', भू 'to be', पू 'to purify', कमि 'to be brilliant', गमि 'to go', प्यायि 'to increase', वेप 'to shake'.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word-उपसर्ग

8.4.35|8.4.35 Shaat‌ padaantaat‌|Shaat‌ padaantaat‌|Shaat‌ padaantaat‌ 8.4.35|षात्‌ पदान्तात्‌|षात्‌ पदान्तात्‌ ८.४.३५|८.४.३५|८.४.३५ षात्‌ पदान्तात्‌
After a ष् final in a पद , the न् is not changed to ण।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु-उपसर्ग

8.4.36|8.4.36 nasheH Shaantasya|nasheH Shaantasya|nasheH Shaantasya 8.4.36|नशेः षान्तस्य|नशेः षान्तस्य ८.४.३६|८.४.३६|८.४.३६ नशेः षान्तस्य
ण् is not the substitute of the verb नश 'to destroy', when ending in ष्।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.37|8.4.37 padaantasya|padaantasya|padaantasya 8.4.37|पदान्तस्य|पदान्तस्य ८.४.३७|८.४.३७|८.४.३७ पदान्तस्य
Of a न् final in a पद , ण् is not the substitute.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.38|8.4.38 padavyavaaye.api|padavyavaaye.api|padavyavaaye.api 8.4.38|पदव्यवायेऽपि|पदव्यवायेऽपि ८.४.३८|८.४.३८|८.४.३८ पदव्यवायेऽपि
The न् is not changed to ण् when a पद intervenes between the cause of the change and the word containing the न्।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.39|8.4.39 xubhnaa.a.adiShu cha|xubhnaa.a.adiShu cha|xubhnaa.a.adiShu cha 8.4.39|क्षुभ्नाऽऽदिषु च|क्षुभ्नाऽऽदिषु च ८.४.३९|८.४.३९|८.४.३९ क्षुभ्नाऽऽदिषु च
The ण् is not the susbtitute of न् in the words क्षुभ्ना etc.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.40|8.4.40 stoH shchunaa shchuH|stoH shchunaa shchuH|stoH shchunaa shchuH 8.4.40|स्तोः श्चुना श्चुः|स्तोः श्चुना श्चुः ८.४.४०|८.४.४०|८.४.४० स्तोः श्चुना श्चुः
The letters स् and the dentals when coming in contact with श् and the palatals, are changed to श् and palatals respectively.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word

8.4.41|8.4.41 ShTunaa ShTuH|ShTunaa ShTuH|ShTunaa ShTuH 8.4.41|ष्टुना ष्टुः|ष्टुना ष्टुः ८.४.४१|८.४.४१|८.४.४१ ष्टुना ष्टुः
The letters स् and the dentals when coming in contact with ष् and the cerebrals, are changed to ष् and cerebrals respectively.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.42|8.4.42 na padaantaaTToranaam|na padaantaaTToranaam|na padaantaaTToranaam 8.4.42|न पदान्ताट्टोरनाम्|न पदान्ताट्टोरनाम् ८.४.४२|८.४.४२|८.४.४२ न पदान्ताट्टोरनाम्
After टु final in a पद , the change of a dental (स्तु) to a cerebral (ष्टु), does not take place, except in the case of the affix नाम्।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.43|8.4.43 toH Shi|toH Shi|toH Shi 8.4.43|तोः षि|तोः षि ८.४.४३|८.४.४३|८.४.४३ तोः षि
In the room of तु there is not a cerebral substitute, when ष् follows.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.44|8.4.44 shaat‌|shaat‌|shaat‌ 8.4.44|शात्‌|शात्‌ ८.४.४४|८.४.४४|८.४.४४ शात्‌
In the room of तु there is not a palatal substitute, when श् precedes.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.45|8.4.45 yaro.anunaasike.anunaasiko vaa|yaro.anunaasike.anunaasiko vaa|yaro.anunaasike.anunaasiko vaa 8.4.45|यरोऽनुनासिकेऽनुनासिको वा|यरोऽनुनासिकेऽनुनासिको वा ८.४.४५|८.४.४५|८.४.४५ यरोऽनुनासिकेऽनुनासिको वा
In the room of a यर् letter (every consonant except ह final) in a पद , when Nasal follows, there is optionally a Nasal substitute.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.46|8.4.46 acho rahaabhyaaM dve|acho rahaabhyaaM dve|acho rahaabhyaaM dve 8.4.46|अचो रहाभ्यां द्वे|अचो रहाभ्यां द्वे ८.४.४६|८.४.४६|८.४.४६ अचो रहाभ्यां द्वे
There is reduplication of यर् , i.e. all the consonants except ह after the letters र् and ह् following a vowel.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.47|8.4.47 anachi cha|anachi cha|anachi cha 8.4.47|अनचि च|अनचि च ८.४.४७|८.४.४७|८.४.४७ अनचि च
When a vowel does not follow, there is reduplication of यर् (all consonants except ह) after a vowel.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.48|8.4.48 naadinyaakroshe putrasya|naadinyaakroshe putrasya|naadinyaakroshe putrasya 8.4.48|नादिन्याक्रोशे पुत्रस्य|नादिन्याक्रोशे पुत्रस्य ८.४.४८|८.४.४८|८.४.४८ नादिन्याक्रोशे पुत्रस्य
There is not reduplication of the letters of पुत्र , when the word आदिनी follows, the sense being that of reviling or cursing.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

8.4.49|8.4.49 sharo.achi|sharo.achi|sharo.achi 8.4.49|शरोऽचि|शरोऽचि ८.४.४९|८.४.४९|८.४.४९ शरोऽचि
There are not two in the room of a sibilant (शर्), when a vowel follows.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.50|8.4.50 triprabhRtiShu shaakaTaayanasya|triprabhRtiShu shaakaTaayanasya|triprabhRtiShu shaakaTaayanasya 8.4.50|त्रिप्रभृतिषु शाकटायनस्य|त्रिप्रभृतिषु शाकटायनस्य ८.४.५०|८.४.५०|८.४.५० त्रिप्रभृतिषु शाकटायनस्य
According to the option of शाकटायन , the doubling does not take place when the conjunct consonants are three or more in number.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.51|8.4.51 sarvatra shaakalyasya|sarvatra shaakalyasya|sarvatra shaakalyasya 8.4.51|सर्वत्र शाकल्यस्य|सर्वत्र शाकल्यस्य ८.४.५१|८.४.५१|८.४.५१ सर्वत्र शाकल्यस्य
According to the opnion of शाकल्य , there is reduplication no where.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.52|8.4.52 diirghaadaachaaryaaNaam|diirghaadaachaaryaaNaam|diirghaadaachaaryaaNaam 8.4.52|दीर्घादाचार्याणाम्|दीर्घादाचार्याणाम् ८.४.५२|८.४.५२|८.४.५२ दीर्घादाचार्याणाम्
According to the opinion of all the Teachers, there is no doubling after a long vowel.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.53|8.4.53 jhalaaM jash jhashi|jhalaaM jash jhashi|jhalaaM jash jhashi 8.4.53|झलां जश् झशि|झलां जश् झशि ८.४.५३|८.४.५३|८.४.५३ झलां जश् झशि
In the room of झल् letters, there is substitution of जश् letters, when झश् letters follow.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.54|8.4.54 abhyaase charchcha|abhyaase charchcha|abhyaase charchcha 8.4.54|अभ्यासे चर्च्च|अभ्यासे चर्च्च ८.४.५४|८.४.५४|८.४.५४ अभ्यासे चर्च्च
The चर् is also substitute of झल् letters occuring in a reduplicate syllable, as well as जश्।<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.55|8.4.55 khari cha|khari cha|khari cha 8.4.55|खरि च|खरि च ८.४.५५|८.४.५५|८.४.५५ खरि च
In the room of झल् , there is the substitute चर् , when खर् follows.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.56|8.4.56 vaa.avasaane|vaa.avasaane|vaa.avasaane 8.4.56|वाऽवसाने|वाऽवसाने ८.४.५६|८.४.५६|८.४.५६ वाऽवसाने
The चर् is optionally the substitute of a झल् that occurs in a Pause.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.57|8.4.57 aNo.apragRhyasyaanunaasikaH|aNo.apragRhyasyaanunaasikaH|aNo.apragRhyasyaanunaasikaH 8.4.57|अणोऽप्रगृह्यस्यानुनासिकः|अणोऽप्रगृह्यस्यानुनासिकः ८.४.५७|८.४.५७|८.४.५७ अणोऽप्रगृह्यस्यानुनासिकः
The अनुनासिका is optionally the substitute of an अण् vowel which occurs in a Pause, and is not a परिगृह्य।<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.58|8.4.58 anusvaarasya yayi parasavarNaH|anusvaarasya yayi parasavarNaH|anusvaarasya yayi parasavarNaH 8.4.58|अनुस्वारस्य ययि परसवर्णः|अनुस्वारस्य ययि परसवर्णः ८.४.५८|८.४.५८|८.४.५८ अनुस्वारस्य ययि परसवर्णः
In the room of अनुस्वारा, when यय् follows, a letter homogenous with the latter is substituted.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.59|8.4.59 vaa padaantasya|vaa padaantasya|vaa padaantasya 8.4.59|वा पदान्तस्य|वा पदान्तस्य ८.४.५९|८.४.५९|८.४.५९ वा पदान्तस्य
In the room of अनुस्वारा, final in a पद, the substitution of a letter homogenous with the latter is optional.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.60|8.4.60 torli|torli|torli 8.4.60|तोर्लि|तोर्लि ८.४.६०|८.४.६०|८.४.६० तोर्लि
In the room of तु (a dental) when the letter ल follows, one homogenous with the latter is substituted.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.61|8.4.61 udaH sthaastambhoH puurvasya|udaH sthaastambhoH puurvasya|udaH sthaastambhoH puurvasya 8.4.61|उदः स्थास्तम्भोः पूर्वस्य|उदः स्थास्तम्भोः पूर्वस्य ८.४.६१|८.४.६१|८.४.६१ उदः स्थास्तम्भोः पूर्वस्य
After उद्, in the room of the स of स्था or स्थम्भ, the substitute is a letter belonging to the class of the prior (i.e. a dental is substituted for this स).<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.62|8.4.62 jhayo ho.anyatarasyaam|jhayo ho.anyatarasyaam|jhayo ho.anyatarasyaam 8.4.62|झयो होऽन्यतरस्याम्|झयो होऽन्यतरस्याम् ८.४.६२|८.४.६२|८.४.६२ झयो होऽन्यतरस्याम्
In the room of ह after (a sonant Mute) there is optionally a letter homogenous with the prior.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.63|8.4.63 shashCho.aTi|shashCho.aTi|shashCho.aTi 8.4.63|शश्छोऽटि|शश्छोऽटि ८.४.६३|८.४.६३|८.४.६३ शश्छोऽटि
in the room of श preceded by a surd Mute, there is optionally the letter छ् when a vowel or य, व or र follows such श।<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.64|8.4.64 halo yamaaM yami lopaH|halo yamaaM yami lopaH|halo yamaaM yami lopaH 8.4.64|हलो यमां यमि लोपः|हलो यमां यमि लोपः ८.४.६४|८.४.६४|८.४.६४ हलो यमां यमि लोपः
After a consonant, the following semi-vowel or a nasal is elided optionally, when the same letters follow it<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.65|8.4.65 jharo jhari savarNe|jharo jhari savarNe|jharo jhari savarNe 8.4.65|झरो झरि सवर्णे|झरो झरि सवर्णे ८.४.६५|८.४.६५|८.४.६५ झरो झरि सवर्णे
The mute of sibiliant (झर्) preceded by a consonant and followed by a homogenous mute of sibilant, is optionally elided<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.66|8.4.66 udaattaadanudaattasya svaritaH|udaattaadanudaattasya svaritaH|udaattaadanudaattasya svaritaH 8.4.66|उदात्तादनुदात्तस्य स्वरितः|उदात्तादनुदात्तस्य स्वरितः ८.४.६६|८.४.६६|८.४.६६ उदात्तादनुदात्तस्य स्वरितः
The स्वरित is the substitute of an अनुदात्त vowel which follows an उदात्त vowel.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.67|8.4.67 nodaattasvaritodayamagaargyakaashyapagaalavaanaam‌|nodaattasvaritodayamagaargyakaashyapagaalavaanaam‌|nodaattasvaritodayamagaargyakaashyapagaalavaanaam‌ 8.4.67|नोदात्तस्वरितोदयमगार्ग्यकाश्यपगालवानाम्‌|नोदात्तस्वरितोदयमगार्ग्यकाश्यपगालवानाम्‌ ८.४.६७|८.४.६७|८.४.६७ नोदात्तस्वरितोदयमगार्ग्यकाश्यपगालवानाम्‌
All prohibit the above substitution of स्वरित, except the आचार्याः - गार्ग्य, काश्यप and गाल्व; when an उदात्त or a स्वरित follows.<br><br>Terms: 

8.4.68|8.4.68 a a iti|a a iti|a a iti 8.4.68|अ अ इति|अ अ इति ८.४.६८|८.४.६८|८.४.६८ अ अ इति
The अ which was considered to be open (विवृत) in all the preceding operations of the Grammar, is now made contracted (संवृत)<br><br>Terms: 

